(271, 50, 'Page 5', 'One evening, she arrived at a vibrant village near the border. However, the village was suffering. A localized drought had dried their well, and the nearby river had been dammed by a rockslide miles away. The villagers were exhausted and desperate.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_50_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"evening,\", \"she\", \"arrived\", \"at\", \"a\", \"vibrant\", \"village\", \"near\", \"the\", \"border.\", \"However,\", \"the\", \"village\", \"was\", \"suffering.\", \"A\", \"localized\", \"drought\", \"had\", \"dried\", \"their\", \"well,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"nearby\", \"river\", \"had\", \"been\", \"dammed\", \"by\", \"a\", \"rockslide\", \"miles\", \"away.\", \"The\", \"villagers\", \"were\", \"exhausted\", \"and\", \"desperate.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.836, 1.033, 1.451, 1.556, 1.649, 2.09, 2.519, 2.717, 2.833, 3.866, 4.609, 4.76, 5.085, 5.248, 6.42, 6.594, 7.21, 7.581, 7.732, 8.046, 8.255, 8.638, 8.835, 8.94, 9.369, 9.671, 9.81, 10.019, 10.403, 10.577, 10.681, 11.273, 11.656, 12.678, 12.841, 13.34, 13.526, 14.199, 14.385], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.766, 0.975, 1.405, 1.521, 1.579, 2.043, 2.473, 2.682, 2.786, 3.355, 4.493, 4.714, 5.05, 5.201, 5.909, 6.502, 7.175, 7.523, 7.697, 8.011, 8.197, 8.615, 8.789, 8.905, 9.253, 9.601, 9.776, 9.961, 10.344, 10.519, 10.612, 11.238, 11.61, 12.167, 12.794, 13.293, 13.479, 14.129, 14.315, 15.139]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(272, 50, 'Page 6', 'Elowen didn\'t hesitate. She didn\'t announce who she was. Instead, she organized a group of strong workers, hiked to the rockslide, and spent four grueling days moving heavy stones to free the river’s flow. She negotiated a fair trade of grain with a neighboring merchant to sustain the town until the crops recovered. She listened to their worries and offered clear, calm solutions.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_50_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elowen\", \"didn\'t\", \"hesitate.\", \"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"announce\", \"who\", \"she\", \"was.\", \"Instead,\", \"she\", \"organized\", \"a\", \"group\", \"of\", \"strong\", \"workers,\", \"hiked\", \"to\", \"the\", \"rockslide,\", \"and\", \"spent\", \"four\", \"grueling\", \"days\", \"moving\", \"heavy\", \"stones\", \"to\", \"free\", \"the\", \"riveru2019s\", \"flow.\", \"She\", \"negotiated\", \"a\", \"fair\", \"trade\", \"of\", \"grain\", \"with\", \"a\", \"neighboring\", \"merchant\", \"to\", \"sustain\", \"the\", \"town\", \"until\", \"the\", \"crops\", \"recovered.\", \"She\", \"listened\", \"to\", \"their\", \"worries\", \"and\", \"offered\", \"clear,\", \"calm\", \"solutions.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.615, 0.906, 1.776, 1.962, 2.218, 2.601, 2.775, 2.949, 3.831, 4.563, 4.807, 5.317, 5.387, 5.619, 5.747, 6.142, 7.082, 7.43, 7.57, 7.697, 8.615, 8.824, 9.172, 9.555, 10.066, 10.472, 10.832, 11.122, 11.564, 11.726, 11.981, 12.098, 12.457, 13.456, 13.653, 14.269, 14.362, 14.628, 14.896, 15.023, 15.36, 15.534, 15.627, 16.08, 16.498, 16.625, 17.043, 17.159, 17.485, 17.74, 17.844, 18.193, 19.249, 19.458, 19.795, 19.888, 20.062, 20.526, 20.724, 21.072, 21.49, 21.885], \"end_times\": [0.557, 0.848, 1.533, 1.904, 2.183, 2.577, 2.717, 2.879, 3.506, 4.481, 4.725, 5.283, 5.341, 5.573, 5.677, 6.072, 6.803, 7.361, 7.512, 7.639, 8.44, 8.766, 9.079, 9.474, 9.996, 10.379, 10.751, 11.064, 11.505, 11.633, 11.947, 12.051, 12.388, 12.945, 13.584, 14.234, 14.303, 14.57, 14.872, 14.954, 15.302, 15.499, 15.569, 16.01, 16.463, 16.567, 16.997, 17.113, 17.426, 17.694, 17.81, 18.135, 18.808, 19.389, 19.772, 19.841, 20.027, 20.468, 20.654, 21.002, 21.432, 21.815, 22.895]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(273, 50, 'Page 7', 'By the end of the week, the village was thriving again.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_50_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"By\", \"the\", \"end\", \"of\", \"the\", \"week,\", \"the\", \"village\", \"was\", \"thriving\", \"again.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.43, 0.546, 0.627, 0.731, 1.022, 1.161, 1.486, 1.637, 2.067], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.383, 0.511, 0.592, 0.697, 0.998, 1.115, 1.451, 1.579, 2.02, 2.647]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(274, 50, 'Page 8', 'As the elder thanked her, calling her a natural leader, Elowen realized a profound truth. She had fled the palace to avoid ruling, but ruling was not about wearing a heavy gold ring or sitting in a high chair. It was about taking responsibility for the well-being of others.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_50_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"elder\", \"thanked\", \"her,\", \"calling\", \"her\", \"a\", \"natural\", \"leader,\", \"Elowen\", \"realized\", \"a\", \"profound\", \"truth.\", \"She\", \"had\", \"fled\", \"the\", \"palace\", \"to\", \"avoid\", \"ruling,\", \"but\", \"ruling\", \"was\", \"not\", \"about\", \"wearing\", \"a\", \"heavy\", \"gold\", \"ring\", \"or\", \"sitting\", \"in\", \"a\", \"high\", \"chair.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"about\", \"taking\", \"responsibility\", \"for\", \"the\", \"well-being\", \"of\", \"others.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.418, 0.685, 0.975, 1.312, 1.66, 1.8, 1.881, 2.287, 2.995, 3.413, 3.82, 3.889, 4.342, 5.213, 5.399, 5.55, 5.805, 5.921, 6.281, 6.409, 6.757, 7.454, 7.663, 8.011, 8.185, 8.359, 8.591, 8.916, 9.009, 9.265, 9.543, 9.903, 10.112, 10.391, 10.484, 10.553, 10.762, 11.482, 11.645, 11.796, 12.086, 12.457, 13.317, 13.479, 13.584, 14.083, 14.199], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.36, 0.639, 0.94, 1.196, 1.602, 1.741, 1.823, 2.229, 2.752, 3.355, 3.785, 3.843, 4.296, 4.83, 5.352, 5.503, 5.77, 5.875, 6.246, 6.327, 6.699, 7.303, 7.616, 7.964, 8.115, 8.324, 8.557, 8.87, 8.94, 9.207, 9.485, 9.787, 10.054, 10.356, 10.437, 10.507, 10.716, 11.157, 11.61, 11.749, 12.04, 12.388, 13.259, 13.433, 13.549, 14.036, 14.141, 14.861]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(275, 50, 'Page 9', 'She had rejected the symbol of the crown, only to embrace the true work it represented out in the wild.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_50_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"had\", \"rejected\", \"the\", \"symbol\", \"of\", \"the\", \"crown,\", \"only\", \"to\", \"embrace\", \"the\", \"true\", \"work\", \"it\", \"represented\", \"out\", \"in\", \"the\", \"wild.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.511, 0.975, 1.08, 1.382, 1.463, 1.567, 2.334, 2.647, 2.798, 3.146, 3.262, 3.518, 3.762, 3.878, 4.47, 4.632, 4.725, 4.83], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.464, 0.94, 1.045, 1.335, 1.428, 1.533, 2.009, 2.589, 2.717, 3.111, 3.216, 3.483, 3.715, 3.831, 4.423, 4.598, 4.679, 4.795, 5.48]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(276, 50, 'Page 10', 'She returned to the capital the next morning, ready to rule not from a throne, but from the ground up.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_50_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"the\", \"capital\", \"the\", \"next\", \"morning,\", \"ready\", \"to\", \"rule\", \"not\", \"from\", \"a\", \"throne,\", \"but\", \"from\", \"the\", \"ground\", \"up.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.697, 0.789, 0.894, 1.358, 1.463, 1.741, 2.299, 2.601, 2.775, 3.123, 3.355, 3.541, 3.622, 4.272, 4.458, 4.632, 4.737, 5.097], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.673, 0.743, 0.859, 1.289, 1.428, 1.672, 2.183, 2.543, 2.682, 3.065, 3.309, 3.483, 3.564, 4.156, 4.423, 4.598, 4.702, 5.016, 5.48]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(277, 51, 'Page 1', 'Long ago, in a land where winter lasted half the year, there stood a forest unlike any other. Its trees were made entirely of glass. Their trunks were smooth crystal, and their leaves were delicate shards that chimed like small bells in the wind.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Long\", \"ago,\", \"in\", \"a\", \"land\", \"where\", \"winter\", \"lasted\", \"half\", \"the\", \"year,\", \"there\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"forest\", \"unlike\", \"any\", \"other.\", \"Its\", \"trees\", \"were\", \"made\", \"entirely\", \"of\", \"glass.\", \"Their\", \"trunks\", \"were\", \"smooth\", \"crystal,\", \"and\", \"their\", \"leaves\", \"were\", \"delicate\", \"shards\", \"that\", \"chimed\", \"like\", \"small\", \"bells\", \"in\", \"the\", \"wind.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.952, 1.149, 1.231, 1.533, 1.765, 2.113, 2.508, 2.763, 2.902, 3.564, 3.762, 3.971, 4.052, 4.458, 4.818, 5.062, 5.979, 6.235, 6.641, 6.792, 7.001, 7.581, 7.709, 8.638, 8.893, 9.23, 9.427, 9.822, 10.472, 10.681, 10.879, 11.25, 11.424, 11.865, 12.307, 12.481, 12.875, 13.073, 13.444, 13.804, 13.909, 14.025], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.906, 1.091, 1.173, 1.486, 1.718, 2.043, 2.45, 2.705, 2.833, 3.32, 3.738, 3.947, 3.994, 4.4, 4.772, 4.992, 5.468, 6.177, 6.583, 6.769, 6.966, 7.535, 7.639, 8.313, 8.847, 9.183, 9.381, 9.752, 10.403, 10.635, 10.82, 11.204, 11.378, 11.831, 12.26, 12.434, 12.829, 13.026, 13.375, 13.758, 13.874, 13.978, 14.629]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(278, 51, 'Page 2', 'The forest was beautiful but dangerous. The edges of the clear leaves were sharper than swords.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"forest\", \"was\", \"beautiful\", \"but\", \"dangerous.\", \"The\", \"edges\", \"of\", \"the\", \"clear\", \"leaves\", \"were\", \"sharper\", \"than\", \"swords.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.662, 0.824, 1.277, 1.451, 2.334, 2.531, 2.844, 2.961, 3.088, 3.425, 3.75, 3.913, 4.284, 4.47], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.627, 0.766, 1.219, 1.393, 2.159, 2.45, 2.798, 2.914, 3.03, 3.344, 3.704, 3.878, 4.238, 4.412, 5.248]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(279, 51, 'Page 3', 'Prince Alaric, known for his bravery in battle and skill with a blade, decided he would conquer the Glass Forest to prove his worth. He strapped on his heavy iron armor, drew his thickest steel sword, and marched boldly into the crystal woods.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Prince\", \"Alaric,\", \"known\", \"for\", \"his\", \"bravery\", \"in\", \"battle\", \"and\", \"skill\", \"with\", \"a\", \"blade,\", \"decided\", \"he\", \"would\", \"conquer\", \"the\", \"Glass\", \"Forest\", \"to\", \"prove\", \"his\", \"worth.\", \"He\", \"strapped\", \"on\", \"his\", \"heavy\", \"iron\", \"armor,\", \"drew\", \"his\", \"thickest\", \"steel\", \"sword,\", \"and\", \"marched\", \"boldly\", \"into\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"woods.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395, 0.859, 1.126, 1.3, 1.463, 1.939, 2.09, 2.496, 2.67, 3.007, 3.17, 3.228, 4.063, 4.609, 4.702, 4.899, 5.283, 5.387, 5.735, 6.142, 6.269, 6.571, 6.734, 7.825, 7.999, 8.406, 8.545, 8.707, 9.009, 9.334, 9.938, 10.205, 10.379, 10.867, 11.238, 11.877, 12.098, 12.457, 12.968, 13.201, 13.305, 13.665], \"end_times\": [0.36, 0.836, 1.068, 1.242, 1.405, 1.881, 2.02, 2.45, 2.601, 2.961, 3.135, 3.193, 3.738, 4.551, 4.667, 4.853, 5.236, 5.352, 5.666, 6.095, 6.2, 6.536, 6.676, 7.221, 7.941, 8.359, 8.498, 8.649, 8.94, 9.276, 9.81, 10.159, 10.31, 10.786, 11.169, 11.703, 12.028, 12.388, 12.899, 13.142, 13.27, 13.618, 14.303]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(280, 51, 'Page 4', 'He slashed at the low-hanging branches, intending to carve a path straight through the center. But the moment his blade struck the glass, the vibration shattered the branch, sending a shower of razor-sharp shards raining down upon his armor. The harder he fought, the more dangerous the forest became. Within an hour, his shield was scarred, his armor battered, and he was exhausted, unable to move past the dense, ringing thicket.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"slashed\", \"at\", \"the\", \"low-hanging\", \"branches,\", \"intending\", \"to\", \"carve\", \"a\", \"path\", \"straight\", \"through\", \"the\", \"center.\", \"But\", \"the\", \"moment\", \"his\", \"blade\", \"struck\", \"the\", \"glass,\", \"the\", \"vibration\", \"shattered\", \"the\", \"branch,\", \"sending\", \"a\", \"shower\", \"of\", \"razor-sharp\", \"shards\", \"raining\", \"down\", \"upon\", \"his\", \"armor.\", \"The\", \"harder\", \"he\", \"fought,\", \"the\", \"more\", \"dangerous\", \"the\", \"forest\", \"became.\", \"Within\", \"an\", \"hour,\", \"his\", \"shield\", \"was\", \"scarred,\", \"his\", \"armor\", \"battered,\", \"and\", \"he\", \"was\", \"exhausted,\", \"unable\", \"to\", \"move\", \"past\", \"the\", \"dense,\", \"ringing\", \"thicket.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.871, 0.987, 1.115, 1.637, 2.287, 2.844, 2.972, 3.262, 3.344, 3.762, 4.11, 4.4, 4.516, 5.422, 5.596, 5.724, 6.06, 6.223, 6.594, 6.92, 7.024, 7.721, 7.883, 8.626, 9.102, 9.207, 10.043, 10.414, 10.495, 10.937, 11.099, 11.819, 12.307, 12.69, 12.956, 13.247, 13.386, 14.268, 14.443, 14.779, 14.919, 15.499, 15.662, 15.859, 16.381, 16.509, 16.857, 18.076, 18.425, 18.529, 19.203, 19.377, 19.725, 19.864, 20.619, 20.805, 21.107, 22.094, 22.303, 22.43, 22.604, 23.731, 24.102, 24.218, 24.45, 24.775, 24.903, 25.577, 25.971], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.836, 0.952, 1.057, 1.591, 2.241, 2.786, 2.902, 3.228, 3.286, 3.669, 4.075, 4.365, 4.47, 5.039, 5.573, 5.666, 6.002, 6.177, 6.56, 6.861, 6.989, 7.593, 7.825, 8.51, 9.067, 9.172, 9.764, 10.368, 10.437, 10.867, 11.006, 11.749, 12.214, 12.632, 12.898, 13.189, 13.34, 13.885, 14.385, 14.721, 14.837, 15.383, 15.604, 15.813, 16.335, 16.451, 16.811, 17.473, 18.378, 18.483, 19.029, 19.33, 19.667, 19.83, 20.468, 20.758, 21.049, 21.71, 22.233, 22.372, 22.546, 23.405, 24.067, 24.16, 24.404, 24.741, 24.845, 25.402, 25.902, 26.61]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(281, 51, 'Page 5', 'Defeated, he retreated.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Defeated,\", \"he\", \"retreated.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.604, 0.743], \"end_times\": [0.569, 0.673, 1.44]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(282, 51, 'Page 6', 'A week later, a quiet young woman named Elara, a weaver from the village, approached the forest edge. She wore no armor and carried no weapon. Instead, she brought a thick cloak of soft, spun wool.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"week\", \"later,\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"young\", \"woman\", \"named\", \"Elara,\", \"a\", \"weaver\", \"from\", \"the\", \"village,\", \"approached\", \"the\", \"forest\", \"edge.\", \"She\", \"wore\", \"no\", \"armor\", \"and\", \"carried\", \"no\", \"weapon.\", \"Instead,\", \"she\", \"brought\", \"a\", \"thick\", \"cloak\", \"of\", \"soft,\", \"spun\", \"wool.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.511, 1.022, 1.173, 1.591, 1.8, 2.125, 2.38, 3.019, 3.17, 3.541, 3.704, 3.808, 4.563, 5.027, 5.143, 5.573, 6.583, 6.757, 7.012, 7.233, 7.721, 7.941, 8.301, 8.452, 9.381, 10.147, 10.333, 10.565, 10.658, 10.925, 11.273, 11.424, 11.889, 12.26], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.441, 0.94, 1.08, 1.544, 1.753, 2.067, 2.322, 2.937, 3.088, 3.483, 3.669, 3.773, 4.354, 5.004, 5.097, 5.503, 6.072, 6.711, 6.943, 7.152, 7.605, 7.883, 8.255, 8.394, 8.94, 10.054, 10.286, 10.542, 10.588, 10.867, 11.204, 11.343, 11.842, 12.202, 12.771]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(283, 51, 'Page 7', 'She didn\'t try to chop down the trees. She stepped carefully, observing the natural gaps between the glass trunks. When a low branch blocked her path, she didn\'t strike it. She gently draped her heavy wool cloak over the sharp edges, softening the danger entirely, and slipped past unharmed. She moved with patience, respecting the fragile yet dangerous nature of the place rather than fighting it.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"try\", \"to\", \"chop\", \"down\", \"the\", \"trees.\", \"She\", \"stepped\", \"carefully,\", \"observing\", \"the\", \"natural\", \"gaps\", \"between\", \"the\", \"glass\", \"trunks.\", \"When\", \"a\", \"low\", \"branch\", \"blocked\", \"her\", \"path,\", \"she\", \"didn\'t\", \"strike\", \"it.\", \"She\", \"gently\", \"draped\", \"her\", \"heavy\", \"wool\", \"cloak\", \"over\", \"the\", \"sharp\", \"edges,\", \"softening\", \"the\", \"danger\", \"entirely,\", \"and\", \"slipped\", \"past\", \"unharmed.\", \"She\", \"moved\", \"with\", \"patience,\", \"respecting\", \"the\", \"fragile\", \"yet\", \"dangerous\", \"nature\", \"of\", \"the\", \"place\", \"rather\", \"than\", \"fighting\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.546, 0.743, 0.848, 1.149, 1.358, 1.474, 2.252, 2.438, 2.752, 3.68, 4.168, 4.284, 4.667, 5.016, 5.341, 5.433, 5.747, 6.966, 7.187, 7.268, 7.488, 7.848, 8.173, 8.301, 8.893, 9.067, 9.311, 9.625, 10.263, 10.472, 10.82, 11.157, 11.285, 11.529, 11.773, 12.121, 12.365, 12.469, 12.771, 13.63, 14.187, 14.303, 14.675, 15.545, 15.754, 16.103, 16.486, 17.867, 18.088, 18.378, 18.552, 19.319, 19.888, 20.004, 20.503, 20.735, 21.246, 21.606, 21.71, 21.815, 22.198, 22.488, 22.662, 23.022], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.522, 0.685, 0.789, 1.08, 1.324, 1.428, 2.078, 2.392, 2.705, 3.471, 4.122, 4.238, 4.609, 4.969, 5.306, 5.41, 5.7, 6.362, 7.152, 7.21, 7.419, 7.802, 8.139, 8.255, 8.777, 9.021, 9.276, 9.59, 9.938, 10.403, 10.762, 11.122, 11.227, 11.482, 11.703, 12.04, 12.318, 12.434, 12.701, 13.351, 14.129, 14.257, 14.617, 15.453, 15.696, 16.056, 16.416, 17.171, 18.007, 18.343, 18.506, 19.203, 19.841, 19.957, 20.457, 20.677, 21.188, 21.571, 21.664, 21.78, 22.152, 22.442, 22.604, 22.964, 23.405]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(284, 51, 'Page 8', 'She emerged peacefully on the other side by sunset.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"emerged\", \"peacefully\", \"on\", \"the\", \"other\", \"side\", \"by\", \"sunset.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.789, 1.265, 1.37, 1.486, 1.707, 1.997, 2.159], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.731, 1.219, 1.335, 1.44, 1.66, 1.962, 2.101, 2.926]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(285, 51, 'Page 9', 'Alaric watched her from his camp, realizing that conquering an obstacle doesn\'t always require a sword. Sometimes, the strongest armor is a soft touch.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_51_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Alaric\", \"watched\", \"her\", \"from\", \"his\", \"camp,\", \"realizing\", \"that\", \"conquering\", \"an\", \"obstacle\", \"doesn\'t\", \"always\", \"require\", \"a\", \"sword.\", \"Sometimes,\", \"the\", \"strongest\", \"armor\", \"is\", \"a\", \"soft\", \"touch.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.569, 0.871, 0.987, 1.149, 1.289, 1.823, 2.368, 2.554, 3.007, 3.123, 3.646, 3.982, 4.331, 4.772, 4.865, 5.956, 6.525, 6.641, 7.117, 7.477, 7.616, 7.697, 8.069], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.836, 0.94, 1.115, 1.231, 1.707, 2.322, 2.496, 2.972, 3.065, 3.599, 3.936, 4.272, 4.737, 4.807, 5.352, 6.502, 6.594, 7.059, 7.407, 7.57, 7.651, 8.011, 8.731]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(286, 52, 'Page 1', 'In a kingdom where dragons were feared more than storms lived a girl named Mira. For generations, dragons had nested in the mountains beyond the castle walls. Their silhouettes against the sky terrified villagers.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"kingdom\", \"where\", \"dragons\", \"were\", \"feared\", \"more\", \"than\", \"storms\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"girl\", \"named\", \"Mira.\", \"For\", \"generations,\", \"dragons\", \"had\", \"nested\", \"in\", \"the\", \"mountains\", \"beyond\", \"the\", \"castle\", \"walls.\", \"Their\", \"silhouettes\", \"against\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"terrified\", \"villagers.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.383, 0.789, 0.975, 1.416, 1.625, 2.02, 2.183, 2.38, 2.949, 3.216, 3.286, 3.587, 3.924, 5.097, 5.306, 6.409, 6.885, 7.059, 7.477, 7.57, 7.674, 8.15, 8.51, 8.626, 9.021, 9.973, 10.228, 10.809, 11.134, 11.25, 11.633, 12.272], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.313, 0.743, 0.94, 1.37, 1.567, 1.962, 2.148, 2.31, 2.868, 3.181, 3.239, 3.506, 3.843, 4.493, 5.248, 6.235, 6.838, 7.001, 7.43, 7.535, 7.639, 8.081, 8.464, 8.58, 8.986, 9.59, 10.182, 10.774, 11.088, 11.204, 11.552, 12.225, 13.142]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(287, 52, 'Page 2', 'Knights hunted them for glory, but the dragons always retreated higher into the freezing peaks, rarely striking back but always remaining a terrifying presence in stories.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Knights\", \"hunted\", \"them\", \"for\", \"glory,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"dragons\", \"always\", \"retreated\", \"higher\", \"into\", \"the\", \"freezing\", \"peaks,\", \"rarely\", \"striking\", \"back\", \"but\", \"always\", \"remaining\", \"a\", \"terrifying\", \"presence\", \"in\", \"stories.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.58, 0.917, 1.126, 1.289, 1.939, 2.136, 2.252, 2.81, 3.135, 3.622, 4.04, 4.261, 4.377, 4.807, 5.817, 6.235, 6.687, 7.303, 7.546, 7.941, 8.371, 8.464, 9.125, 9.601, 9.752], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.882, 1.057, 1.242, 1.846, 2.101, 2.206, 2.752, 3.077, 3.553, 3.959, 4.203, 4.331, 4.725, 5.433, 6.177, 6.618, 7.024, 7.488, 7.872, 8.324, 8.406, 9.067, 9.555, 9.683, 10.681]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(288, 52, 'Page 3', 'Mira found an injured young dragon in a deep valley one afternoon. It had torn its wing on jagged rocks and could not fly. Instead of running for the guards, Mira approached slowly, laying down the small walking stick she carried. She sat at a distance, humming a soft, rhythmic tune she usually sang to calm anxious horses.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"found\", \"an\", \"injured\", \"young\", \"dragon\", \"in\", \"a\", \"deep\", \"valley\", \"one\", \"afternoon.\", \"It\", \"had\", \"torn\", \"its\", \"wing\", \"on\", \"jagged\", \"rocks\", \"and\", \"could\", \"not\", \"fly.\", \"Instead\", \"of\", \"running\", \"for\", \"the\", \"guards,\", \"Mira\", \"approached\", \"slowly,\", \"laying\", \"down\", \"the\", \"small\", \"walking\", \"stick\", \"she\", \"carried.\", \"She\", \"sat\", \"at\", \"a\", \"distance,\", \"humming\", \"a\", \"soft,\", \"rhythmic\", \"tune\", \"she\", \"usually\", \"sang\", \"to\", \"calm\", \"anxious\", \"horses.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.72, 0.848, 1.254, 1.498, 2.032, 2.171, 2.264, 2.519, 2.902, 3.053, 4.203, 4.365, 4.493, 4.76, 4.923, 5.178, 5.329, 5.724, 6.177, 6.351, 6.548, 6.745, 8.022, 8.394, 8.499, 8.789, 8.916, 9.033, 9.729, 10.031, 10.565, 11.61, 11.947, 12.167, 12.283, 12.608, 12.98, 13.224, 13.363, 14.443, 14.64, 14.884, 14.977, 15.058, 15.767, 16.115, 16.196, 16.626, 17.02, 17.369, 17.554, 17.961, 18.344, 18.472, 18.855, 19.25], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.673, 0.789, 1.196, 1.44, 1.939, 2.125, 2.194, 2.45, 2.844, 3.019, 3.762, 4.331, 4.458, 4.714, 4.876, 5.108, 5.259, 5.666, 6.142, 6.293, 6.502, 6.687, 7.326, 8.359, 8.44, 8.742, 8.882, 8.986, 9.613, 9.996, 10.495, 11.285, 11.889, 12.132, 12.237, 12.55, 12.934, 13.189, 13.305, 13.932, 14.582, 14.838, 14.942, 15, 15.708, 16.068, 16.138, 16.591, 16.974, 17.322, 17.485, 17.903, 18.274, 18.402, 18.774, 19.203, 19.969]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(289, 52, 'Page 4', 'For three days, she brought the creature fish from the river. She didn\'t try to touch it or tame it. She simply shared space with it.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"For\", \"three\", \"days,\", \"she\", \"brought\", \"the\", \"creature\", \"fish\", \"from\", \"the\", \"river.\", \"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"try\", \"to\", \"touch\", \"it\", \"or\", \"tame\", \"it.\", \"She\", \"simply\", \"shared\", \"space\", \"with\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.58, 1.103, 1.289, 1.533, 1.637, 1.997, 2.287, 2.485, 2.601, 3.251, 3.425, 3.657, 3.843, 3.959, 4.238, 4.365, 4.493, 4.783, 5.236, 5.433, 5.759, 6.037, 6.397, 6.594], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.534, 0.987, 1.242, 1.498, 1.602, 1.95, 2.229, 2.438, 2.554, 3.007, 3.379, 3.634, 3.785, 3.901, 4.191, 4.307, 4.447, 4.748, 5.027, 5.364, 5.712, 5.991, 6.362, 6.536, 6.966]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(290, 52, 'Page 5', 'Eventually, the young dragon allowed her close enough to inspect the wing. She carefully removed the sharp rock splinter embedded in the leathery skin and applied a poultice of river moss.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Eventually,\", \"the\", \"young\", \"dragon\", \"allowed\", \"her\", \"close\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"inspect\", \"the\", \"wing.\", \"She\", \"carefully\", \"removed\", \"the\", \"sharp\", \"rock\", \"splinter\", \"embedded\", \"in\", \"the\", \"leathery\", \"skin\", \"and\", \"applied\", \"a\", \"poultice\", \"of\", \"river\", \"moss.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 1.149, 1.312, 1.544, 1.881, 2.218, 2.368, 2.682, 2.949, 3.088, 3.541, 3.657, 4.528, 4.714, 5.178, 5.538, 5.654, 6.002, 6.281, 6.745, 7.21, 7.303, 7.43, 7.837, 8.51, 8.742, 9.102, 9.183, 9.625, 9.764, 10.031], \"end_times\": [0.975, 1.254, 1.486, 1.846, 2.171, 2.299, 2.647, 2.902, 3.007, 3.495, 3.611, 4.087, 4.656, 5.12, 5.515, 5.608, 5.909, 6.223, 6.676, 7.163, 7.268, 7.372, 7.767, 8.185, 8.696, 9.079, 9.137, 9.59, 9.683, 9.985, 10.728]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(291, 52, 'Page 6', 'When the wing healed enough for flight, a massive, older dragon—the mother—landed with a thundering crash near the clearing. Mira froze, expecting fire.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"When\", \"the\", \"wing\", \"healed\", \"enough\", \"for\", \"flight,\", \"a\", \"massive,\", \"older\", \"dragonu2014the\", \"motheru2014landed\", \"with\", \"a\", \"thundering\", \"crash\", \"near\", \"the\", \"clearing.\", \"Mira\", \"froze,\", \"expecting\", \"fire.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.453, 0.708, 1.01, 1.265, 1.44, 2.02, 2.206, 2.775, 3.204, 4.156, 5.306, 5.468, 5.573, 6.049, 6.467, 6.653, 6.757, 7.709, 8.081, 8.58, 9.114], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.418, 0.639, 0.975, 1.231, 1.37, 1.869, 2.09, 2.74, 3.146, 4.098, 5.271, 5.433, 5.503, 5.991, 6.409, 6.618, 6.722, 7.268, 7.999, 8.545, 9.044, 9.892]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(292, 52, 'Page 7', 'Instead, the mother nudged the youngster gently, then lowered her massive, scaled head directly in front of Mira. She didn\'t breathe flame; she huffed a warm gust of smoke that smelled like pine, a gesture of profound respect in the dragon realm.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Instead,\", \"the\", \"mother\", \"nudged\", \"the\", \"youngster\", \"gently,\", \"then\", \"lowered\", \"her\", \"massive,\", \"scaled\", \"head\", \"directly\", \"in\", \"front\", \"of\", \"Mira.\", \"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"breathe\", \"flame;\", \"she\", \"huffed\", \"a\", \"warm\", \"gust\", \"of\", \"smoke\", \"that\", \"smelled\", \"like\", \"pine,\", \"a\", \"gesture\", \"of\", \"profound\", \"respect\", \"in\", \"the\", \"dragon\", \"realm.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.743, 0.871, 1.161, 1.509, 1.637, 2.078, 2.868, 3.111, 3.483, 3.657, 4.203, 4.702, 5.039, 5.584, 5.712, 5.956, 6.072, 7.245, 7.419, 7.674, 7.999, 8.893, 9.079, 9.369, 9.451, 9.799, 10.089, 10.228, 10.6, 10.786, 11.122, 11.32, 11.947, 12.098, 12.516, 12.655, 13.201, 13.723, 13.827, 13.944, 14.373], \"end_times\": [0.72, 0.813, 1.103, 1.463, 1.579, 2.009, 2.659, 3.042, 3.425, 3.576, 4.18, 4.644, 4.957, 5.538, 5.654, 5.909, 6.002, 6.548, 7.372, 7.639, 7.941, 8.568, 9.021, 9.346, 9.392, 9.741, 10.043, 10.159, 10.565, 10.739, 11.088, 11.273, 11.831, 12.016, 12.481, 12.574, 13.131, 13.677, 13.793, 13.897, 14.303, 14.907]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(293, 52, 'Page 8', 'Mira returned to the village not with a trophy or a slain beast, but with a simple understanding: monsters are often just creatures guarding their own fears, waiting for someone brave enough to offer peace instead of a sword.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_52_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"the\", \"village\", \"not\", \"with\", \"a\", \"trophy\", \"or\", \"a\", \"slain\", \"beast,\", \"but\", \"with\", \"a\", \"simple\", \"understanding:\", \"monsters\", \"are\", \"often\", \"just\", \"creatures\", \"guarding\", \"their\", \"own\", \"fears,\", \"waiting\", \"for\", \"someone\", \"brave\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"offer\", \"peace\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"a\", \"sword.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.511, 0.917, 1.022, 1.126, 1.533, 1.73, 1.892, 1.974, 2.543, 2.763, 2.844, 3.204, 3.878, 4.052, 4.214, 4.307, 4.679, 6.165, 6.745, 6.908, 7.233, 7.465, 7.953, 8.359, 8.58, 8.812, 9.799, 10.205, 10.379, 10.751, 11.018, 11.308, 11.459, 11.784, 12.167, 12.539, 12.643, 12.713], \"end_times\": [0.453, 0.894, 0.964, 1.091, 1.486, 1.695, 1.858, 1.927, 2.426, 2.705, 2.798, 3.135, 3.727, 4.017, 4.18, 4.238, 4.632, 5.561, 6.687, 6.873, 7.175, 7.419, 7.883, 8.301, 8.533, 8.742, 9.416, 10.147, 10.321, 10.716, 10.983, 11.262, 11.378, 11.703, 12.121, 12.504, 12.597, 12.666, 13.328]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(294, 53, 'Page 1', 'In a kingdom surrounded by high stone walls lived a young queen named Seraphine. She had inherited the throne unexpectedly after her father’s sudden passing. Though wise beyond her years, she felt unprepared for the quiet loneliness that came with ruling.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"kingdom\", \"surrounded\", \"by\", \"high\", \"stone\", \"walls\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"young\", \"queen\", \"named\", \"Seraphine.\", \"She\", \"had\", \"inherited\", \"the\", \"throne\", \"unexpectedly\", \"after\", \"her\", \"fatheru2019s\", \"sudden\", \"passing.\", \"Though\", \"wise\", \"beyond\", \"her\", \"years,\", \"she\", \"felt\", \"unprepared\", \"for\", \"the\", \"quiet\", \"loneliness\", \"that\", \"came\", \"with\", \"ruling.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.348, 0.731, 1.149, 1.335, 1.567, 1.881, 2.612, 2.844, 2.926, 3.146, 3.46, 3.715, 5.143, 5.329, 5.492, 5.991, 6.107, 6.455, 7.361, 7.674, 7.802, 8.162, 8.464, 9.822, 10.066, 10.368, 10.693, 10.844, 11.564, 11.749, 11.993, 12.666, 12.806, 12.934, 13.282, 13.827, 14.013, 14.269, 14.443], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.302, 0.662, 1.103, 1.254, 1.521, 1.846, 2.287, 2.821, 2.868, 3.088, 3.402, 3.669, 4.447, 5.271, 5.433, 5.956, 6.06, 6.397, 7.291, 7.616, 7.755, 8.139, 8.406, 9.125, 10.031, 10.321, 10.635, 10.786, 11.389, 11.691, 11.935, 12.597, 12.771, 12.875, 13.235, 13.793, 13.967, 14.245, 14.396, 15.093]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(295, 53, 'Page 2', 'The castle was grand, filled with echoing halls and advisors who spoke in riddles. To escape the heavy atmosphere, Seraphine spent hours in an old, forgotten garden tucked behind the library wing. It was overgrown with thorny vines and choked with weeds.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"castle\", \"was\", \"grand,\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"echoing\", \"halls\", \"and\", \"advisors\", \"who\", \"spoke\", \"in\", \"riddles.\", \"To\", \"escape\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"atmosphere,\", \"Seraphine\", \"spent\", \"hours\", \"in\", \"an\", \"old,\", \"forgotten\", \"garden\", \"tucked\", \"behind\", \"the\", \"library\", \"wing.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"overgrown\", \"with\", \"thorny\", \"vines\", \"and\", \"choked\", \"with\", \"weeds.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.627, 0.801, 1.498, 1.823, 2.02, 2.438, 2.856, 2.972, 3.587, 3.738, 4.029, 4.156, 5.445, 5.631, 6.014, 6.13, 6.385, 7.349, 7.918, 8.231, 8.615, 8.719, 8.858, 9.195, 9.694, 10.159, 10.472, 10.762, 10.879, 11.343, 12.632, 12.783, 12.934, 13.526, 13.711, 14.071, 14.605, 14.803, 15.151, 15.325], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.592, 0.731, 1.382, 1.8, 1.939, 2.368, 2.81, 2.937, 3.553, 3.68, 3.994, 4.087, 4.748, 5.561, 5.979, 6.084, 6.327, 7.14, 7.883, 8.173, 8.568, 8.673, 8.777, 9.16, 9.636, 10.077, 10.437, 10.728, 10.832, 11.285, 11.819, 12.748, 12.875, 13.468, 13.665, 14.002, 14.559, 14.745, 15.116, 15.279, 16.022]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(296, 53, 'Page 3', 'Instead of ordering the royal gardeners to fix it, she began clearing the plot herself. Her hands blistered, her dresses grew stained with dirt, but she found peace in the simple, honest labor.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Instead\", \"of\", \"ordering\", \"the\", \"royal\", \"gardeners\", \"to\", \"fix\", \"it,\", \"she\", \"began\", \"clearing\", \"the\", \"plot\", \"herself.\", \"Her\", \"hands\", \"blistered,\", \"her\", \"dresses\", \"grew\", \"stained\", \"with\", \"dirt,\", \"but\", \"she\", \"found\", \"peace\", \"in\", \"the\", \"simple,\", \"honest\", \"labor.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.511, 0.627, 1.022, 1.138, 1.428, 1.892, 2.032, 2.357, 2.879, 3.088, 3.402, 3.738, 3.843, 4.122, 5.074, 5.294, 5.642, 6.548, 6.711, 7.129, 7.361, 7.755, 7.964, 8.684, 8.87, 9.044, 9.323, 9.718, 9.845, 9.985, 10.577, 11.076], \"end_times\": [0.476, 0.569, 0.975, 1.091, 1.37, 1.846, 1.95, 2.276, 2.67, 3.019, 3.344, 3.704, 3.808, 4.063, 4.748, 5.224, 5.584, 6.374, 6.653, 7.07, 7.303, 7.721, 7.895, 8.44, 8.835, 8.963, 9.253, 9.671, 9.799, 9.915, 10.461, 10.995, 11.703]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(297, 53, 'Page 4', 'One afternoon, while pulling up a stubborn root, her trowel struck something hard. Buried beneath centuries of soil was a small, intricately carved wooden box. Inside were dozens of small, ancient seeds, perfectly preserved.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"afternoon,\", \"while\", \"pulling\", \"up\", \"a\", \"stubborn\", \"root,\", \"her\", \"trowel\", \"struck\", \"something\", \"hard.\", \"Buried\", \"beneath\", \"centuries\", \"of\", \"soil\", \"was\", \"a\", \"small,\", \"intricately\", \"carved\", \"wooden\", \"box.\", \"Inside\", \"were\", \"dozens\", \"of\", \"small,\", \"ancient\", \"seeds,\", \"perfectly\", \"preserved.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.929, 1.138, 1.463, 1.591, 1.672, 2.078, 2.392, 2.543, 2.926, 3.251, 3.611, 4.586, 4.981, 5.306, 5.817, 5.933, 6.281, 6.444, 6.525, 6.978, 7.581, 7.976, 8.278, 9.218, 9.729, 9.927, 10.368, 10.484, 10.937, 11.355, 11.726, 12.237], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.906, 1.103, 1.416, 1.544, 1.614, 2.032, 2.345, 2.496, 2.856, 3.193, 3.541, 4.075, 4.946, 5.248, 5.77, 5.875, 6.223, 6.397, 6.467, 6.943, 7.523, 7.93, 8.22, 8.777, 9.694, 9.868, 10.321, 10.426, 10.902, 11.297, 11.691, 12.179, 12.957]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(298, 53, 'Page 5', 'Intrigued, she planted them in the freshly cleared earth. She watered them diligently.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Intrigued,\", \"she\", \"planted\", \"them\", \"in\", \"the\", \"freshly\", \"cleared\", \"earth.\", \"She\", \"watered\", \"them\", \"diligently.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.673, 0.836, 1.173, 1.324, 1.416, 1.521, 1.892, 2.159, 2.74, 2.926, 3.262, 3.437], \"end_times\": [0.65, 0.778, 1.149, 1.289, 1.382, 1.486, 1.846, 2.136, 2.566, 2.868, 3.239, 3.379, 4.272]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(299, 53, 'Page 6', 'Weeks later, the seeds sprouted, revealing plants unlike anything seen in the kingdom. The flowers glowed softly down silver stems, their petals a vibrant, luminescent blue. They smelled faintly of sea salt and old parchment.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Weeks\", \"later,\", \"the\", \"seeds\", \"sprouted,\", \"revealing\", \"plants\", \"unlike\", \"anything\", \"seen\", \"in\", \"the\", \"kingdom.\", \"The\", \"flowers\", \"glowed\", \"softly\", \"down\", \"silver\", \"stems,\", \"their\", \"petals\", \"a\", \"vibrant,\", \"luminescent\", \"blue.\", \"They\", \"smelled\", \"faintly\", \"of\", \"sea\", \"salt\", \"and\", \"old\", \"parchment.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.499, 1.126, 1.289, 1.625, 2.647, 3.077, 3.506, 3.843, 4.284, 4.516, 4.609, 4.714, 5.747, 5.909, 6.385, 6.699, 7.187, 7.454, 7.802, 8.603, 8.824, 9.253, 9.381, 9.903, 10.542, 11.436, 11.645, 11.993, 12.399, 12.516, 12.725, 13.084, 13.282, 13.491], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.975, 1.231, 1.579, 2.322, 3.019, 3.448, 3.796, 4.214, 4.47, 4.574, 4.679, 5.236, 5.863, 6.327, 6.664, 7.14, 7.384, 7.744, 8.429, 8.777, 9.195, 9.288, 9.857, 10.495, 10.995, 11.598, 11.935, 12.341, 12.457, 12.678, 13.038, 13.212, 13.433, 14.303]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(300, 53, 'Page 7', 'The entire kingdom marveled at the new growth.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"entire\", \"kingdom\", \"marveled\", \"at\", \"the\", \"new\", \"growth.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.673, 1.068, 1.509, 1.602, 1.718, 1.881], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.639, 0.998, 1.474, 1.567, 1.672, 1.834, 2.554]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(301, 53, 'Page 8', 'Seraphine realized that the kingdom, like the garden, had been choked by old thorns and rigid traditions. By breaking ground herself, she had created space for something beautifully new to grow. She began applying the patience and direct effort of a gardener to her rule, tending the needs of her people directly rather than shouting orders from a balcony.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_53_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Seraphine\", \"realized\", \"that\", \"the\", \"kingdom,\", \"like\", \"the\", \"garden,\", \"had\", \"been\", \"choked\", \"by\", \"old\", \"thorns\", \"and\", \"rigid\", \"traditions.\", \"By\", \"breaking\", \"ground\", \"herself,\", \"she\", \"had\", \"created\", \"space\", \"for\", \"something\", \"beautifully\", \"new\", \"to\", \"grow.\", \"She\", \"began\", \"applying\", \"the\", \"patience\", \"and\", \"direct\", \"effort\", \"of\", \"a\", \"gardener\", \"to\", \"her\", \"rule,\", \"tending\", \"the\", \"needs\", \"of\", \"her\", \"people\", \"directly\", \"rather\", \"than\", \"shouting\", \"orders\", \"from\", \"a\", \"balcony.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.662, 1.265, 1.474, 1.602, 2.368, 2.601, 2.74, 3.622, 3.785, 3.982, 4.354, 4.528, 4.76, 5.283, 5.503, 5.817, 7.314, 7.512, 7.895, 8.197, 8.847, 9.056, 9.218, 9.648, 10.066, 10.228, 10.635, 11.18, 11.401, 11.529, 12.562, 12.748, 13.038, 13.433, 13.549, 14.072, 14.211, 14.571, 14.884, 14.989, 15.07, 15.488, 15.639, 15.813, 16.637, 17.079, 17.206, 17.531, 17.648, 17.787, 18.112, 18.797, 19.087, 19.273, 19.679, 20.074, 20.26, 20.341], \"end_times\": [0.627, 1.196, 1.44, 1.544, 2.252, 2.566, 2.67, 3.297, 3.75, 3.936, 4.307, 4.458, 4.714, 5.236, 5.422, 5.782, 6.618, 7.454, 7.848, 8.139, 8.754, 8.998, 9.16, 9.601, 10.019, 10.182, 10.553, 11.111, 11.343, 11.471, 12.051, 12.69, 13.003, 13.398, 13.502, 14.037, 14.153, 14.513, 14.85, 14.942, 15.012, 15.43, 15.558, 15.743, 16.254, 17.021, 17.148, 17.485, 17.589, 17.729, 18.077, 18.646, 19.041, 19.215, 19.61, 20.028, 20.213, 20.283, 21.038]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(302, 54, 'Page 1', 'In a small town famous for its towering clock tower lived a master clockmaker named Aldric. His workshop was filled with gears, springs, and delicate hands that ticked in perfect rhythm.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"small\", \"town\", \"famous\", \"for\", \"its\", \"towering\", \"clock\", \"tower\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"master\", \"clockmaker\", \"named\", \"Aldric.\", \"His\", \"workshop\", \"was\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"gears,\", \"springs,\", \"and\", \"delicate\", \"hands\", \"that\", \"ticked\", \"in\", \"perfect\", \"rhythm.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.372, 0.697, 1.022, 1.382, 1.533, 1.695, 2.159, 2.473, 2.868, 3.1, 3.181, 3.553, 4.133, 4.389, 5.283, 5.492, 5.968, 6.13, 6.42, 6.606, 7.279, 7.79, 7.953, 8.359, 8.742, 8.928, 9.253, 9.392, 9.81], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.325, 0.639, 0.952, 1.335, 1.486, 1.649, 2.113, 2.415, 2.786, 3.065, 3.123, 3.495, 4.075, 4.331, 4.899, 5.445, 5.909, 6.072, 6.385, 6.536, 7.163, 7.767, 7.895, 8.324, 8.696, 8.882, 9.207, 9.311, 9.764, 10.403]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(303, 54, 'Page 2', 'Aldric possessed a secret tool: a small silver key that, when turned in the back of his final masterpiece clock, could rewind time in the town by exactly one hour. He used it only for the gravest mistakes—preventing accidents or fixing broken hearts.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Aldric\", \"possessed\", \"a\", \"secret\", \"tool:\", \"a\", \"small\", \"silver\", \"key\", \"that,\", \"when\", \"turned\", \"in\", \"the\", \"back\", \"of\", \"his\", \"final\", \"masterpiece\", \"clock,\", \"could\", \"rewind\", \"time\", \"in\", \"the\", \"town\", \"by\", \"exactly\", \"one\", \"hour.\", \"He\", \"used\", \"it\", \"only\", \"for\", \"the\", \"gravest\", \"mistakesu2014preventing\", \"accidents\", \"or\", \"fixing\", \"broken\", \"hearts.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.511, 0.94, 1.033, 1.463, 2.357, 2.508, 2.879, 3.262, 3.553, 3.855, 4.087, 4.377, 4.458, 4.563, 4.818, 4.934, 5.097, 5.433, 6.014, 6.722, 6.966, 7.512, 7.906, 8.022, 8.139, 8.731, 8.963, 9.567, 9.799, 11.006, 11.227, 11.552, 11.691, 11.993, 12.144, 12.272, 12.783, 14.153, 14.733, 14.884, 15.29, 15.697], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.906, 0.964, 1.416, 2.032, 2.415, 2.821, 3.193, 3.483, 3.808, 4.04, 4.342, 4.423, 4.528, 4.772, 4.876, 5.039, 5.387, 5.979, 6.444, 6.908, 7.43, 7.872, 7.976, 8.092, 8.557, 8.882, 9.485, 9.752, 10.31, 11.134, 11.494, 11.633, 11.935, 12.098, 12.214, 12.713, 14.095, 14.687, 14.826, 15.221, 15.627, 16.393]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(304, 54, 'Page 3', 'His daughter, Elin, knew the secret. She often felt overwhelmed by life\'s daily blunders. If she dropped a plate, she wished she could turn the key. If she spoke sharply to a friend, she thought of the clock.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"His\", \"daughter,\", \"Elin,\", \"knew\", \"the\", \"secret.\", \"She\", \"often\", \"felt\", \"overwhelmed\", \"by\", \"life\'s\", \"daily\", \"blunders.\", \"If\", \"she\", \"dropped\", \"a\", \"plate,\", \"she\", \"wished\", \"she\", \"could\", \"turn\", \"the\", \"key.\", \"If\", \"she\", \"spoke\", \"sharply\", \"to\", \"a\", \"friend,\", \"she\", \"thought\", \"of\", \"the\", \"clock.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.662, 1.219, 1.451, 1.567, 2.566, 2.775, 3.065, 3.32, 4.04, 4.261, 4.598, 4.923, 6.281, 6.455, 6.594, 6.873, 6.954, 7.593, 7.802, 8.127, 8.266, 8.429, 8.661, 8.777, 9.601, 9.776, 9.927, 10.228, 10.6, 10.739, 10.832, 11.296, 11.482, 11.714, 11.807, 11.912], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.615, 1.173, 1.405, 1.521, 2.183, 2.705, 3.019, 3.262, 3.971, 4.168, 4.54, 4.865, 5.677, 6.409, 6.536, 6.85, 6.908, 7.477, 7.732, 8.057, 8.22, 8.406, 8.626, 8.731, 9.218, 9.729, 9.857, 10.194, 10.553, 10.67, 10.774, 11.238, 11.424, 11.68, 11.761, 11.877, 12.539]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(305, 54, 'Page 4', 'One busy market day, Elin accidentally bumped a merchant\'s table, sending dozens of valuable glass ornaments shattering to the cobblestones. The merchant was furious, shouting at her carelessness.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"busy\", \"market\", \"day,\", \"Elin\", \"accidentally\", \"bumped\", \"a\", \"merchant\'s\", \"table,\", \"sending\", \"dozens\", \"of\", \"valuable\", \"glass\", \"ornaments\", \"shattering\", \"to\", \"the\", \"cobblestones.\", \"The\", \"merchant\", \"was\", \"furious,\", \"shouting\", \"at\", \"her\", \"carelessness.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.848, 1.196, 1.695, 2.067, 2.717, 2.995, 3.077, 3.529, 4.272, 4.656, 5.085, 5.178, 5.584, 5.909, 6.327, 6.815, 6.92, 7.024, 8.824, 8.998, 9.346, 9.532, 10.333, 10.774, 10.89, 11.029], \"end_times\": [0.499, 0.778, 1.149, 1.579, 1.997, 2.659, 2.961, 3.019, 3.483, 4.029, 4.586, 5.039, 5.132, 5.561, 5.851, 6.293, 6.757, 6.873, 6.989, 7.872, 8.94, 9.311, 9.451, 10.217, 10.728, 10.844, 10.971, 12.028]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(306, 54, 'Page 5', 'Humiliated and panicked, Elin ran straight for her father\'s workshop. She found the silver key on his desk. She reached for it, desperate to erase the terrible moment.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Humiliated\", \"and\", \"panicked,\", \"Elin\", \"ran\", \"straight\", \"for\", \"her\", \"father\'s\", \"workshop.\", \"She\", \"found\", \"the\", \"silver\", \"key\", \"on\", \"his\", \"desk.\", \"She\", \"reached\", \"for\", \"it,\", \"desperate\", \"to\", \"erase\", \"the\", \"terrible\", \"moment.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.894, 1.033, 1.614, 1.95, 2.171, 2.473, 2.612, 2.728, 3.065, 3.994, 4.18, 4.4, 4.516, 4.853, 5.074, 5.213, 5.375, 6.072, 6.293, 6.594, 6.792, 6.966, 7.43, 7.57, 7.953, 8.069, 8.452], \"end_times\": [0.848, 0.975, 1.533, 1.892, 2.101, 2.438, 2.566, 2.682, 3.03, 3.669, 4.122, 4.365, 4.47, 4.783, 5.016, 5.155, 5.317, 5.828, 6.211, 6.548, 6.722, 6.92, 7.396, 7.488, 7.906, 8.022, 8.417, 9.056]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(307, 54, 'Page 6', 'But Aldric’s hand gently stopped hers.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"Aldricu2019s\", \"hand\", \"gently\", \"stopped\", \"hers.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.639, 0.871, 1.173, 1.486], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.615, 0.813, 1.138, 1.451, 2.043]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(308, 54, 'Page 7', '\"If you turn the key for every broken glass,\" he said softly, \"you will never learn to hold things carefully.\"', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"\"If\", \"you\", \"turn\", \"the\", \"key\", \"for\", \"every\", \"broken\", \"glass,\"\", \"he\", \"said\", \"softly,\", \"\"you\", \"will\", \"never\", \"learn\", \"to\", \"hold\", \"things\", \"carefully.\"\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.43, 0.685, 0.801, 1.045, 1.231, 1.486, 1.834, 2.508, 2.635, 2.891, 3.866, 4.122, 4.307, 4.551, 4.795, 4.911, 5.166, 5.468], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.36, 0.639, 0.755, 0.975, 1.161, 1.44, 1.788, 2.392, 2.577, 2.833, 3.541, 4.087, 4.261, 4.493, 4.748, 4.841, 5.108, 5.41, 6.873]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(309, 54, 'Page 8', 'Elin paused. She understood. Erasing the mistake meant erasing the lesson.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elin\", \"paused.\", \"She\", \"understood.\", \"Erasing\", \"the\", \"mistake\", \"meant\", \"erasing\", \"the\", \"lesson.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.499, 1.312, 1.498, 2.31, 2.798, 2.902, 3.332, 3.564, 3.994, 4.11], \"end_times\": [0.441, 1.068, 1.44, 2.101, 2.763, 2.868, 3.297, 3.506, 3.947, 4.063, 4.69]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(310, 54, 'Page 9', 'She left the key on the desk, returned to the market square, pulled out a small broom, and spent the entire afternoon sweeping up glass, apologizing sincerely, and offering her own saved coins to repair the damage.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"left\", \"the\", \"key\", \"on\", \"the\", \"desk,\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"the\", \"market\", \"square,\", \"pulled\", \"out\", \"a\", \"small\", \"broom,\", \"and\", \"spent\", \"the\", \"entire\", \"afternoon\", \"sweeping\", \"up\", \"glass,\", \"apologizing\", \"sincerely,\", \"and\", \"offering\", \"her\", \"own\", \"saved\", \"coins\", \"to\", \"repair\", \"the\", \"damage.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.534, 0.639, 0.836, 0.94, 1.057, 1.741, 2.136, 2.229, 2.334, 2.67, 3.367, 3.692, 3.878, 3.959, 4.284, 4.667, 4.841, 5.097, 5.224, 5.689, 6.235, 6.641, 6.792, 7.57, 8.371, 9.334, 9.567, 9.961, 10.124, 10.391, 10.728, 11.134, 11.262, 11.598, 11.703], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.499, 0.604, 0.789, 0.906, 1.01, 1.567, 2.113, 2.183, 2.299, 2.624, 3.158, 3.646, 3.831, 3.901, 4.226, 4.632, 4.795, 5.062, 5.166, 5.642, 6.165, 6.594, 6.734, 7.326, 8.313, 9.125, 9.497, 9.903, 10.054, 10.321, 10.67, 11.076, 11.192, 11.552, 11.668, 12.446]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(311, 54, 'Page 10', 'She didn\'t fix the past, but the respect she earned from the merchant that afternoon shaped her future far better than turning back the clock ever could.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_54_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"fix\", \"the\", \"past,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"respect\", \"she\", \"earned\", \"from\", \"the\", \"merchant\", \"that\", \"afternoon\", \"shaped\", \"her\", \"future\", \"far\", \"better\", \"than\", \"turning\", \"back\", \"the\", \"clock\", \"ever\", \"could.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.592, 0.859, 0.975, 1.8, 1.985, 2.125, 2.635, 2.844, 3.146, 3.332, 3.448, 3.901, 4.133, 5.132, 5.515, 5.666, 6.153, 6.467, 6.896, 7.117, 7.442, 7.663, 7.767, 8.092, 8.324], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.534, 0.801, 0.929, 1.591, 1.962, 2.055, 2.577, 2.763, 3.111, 3.286, 3.402, 3.855, 4.075, 4.748, 5.48, 5.608, 6.072, 6.397, 6.78, 7.082, 7.396, 7.616, 7.732, 8.022, 8.266, 8.87]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(312, 55, 'Page 1', 'In a village surrounded by dark forests lived a boy named Theo who feared the night. The forest seemed endless after sunset, and the sky above felt too vast.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"village\", \"surrounded\", \"by\", \"dark\", \"forests\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"boy\", \"named\", \"Theo\", \"who\", \"feared\", \"the\", \"night.\", \"The\", \"forest\", \"seemed\", \"endless\", \"after\", \"sunset,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"above\", \"felt\", \"too\", \"vast.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.348, 0.673, 1.115, 1.265, 1.556, 2.159, 2.368, 2.438, 2.682, 2.949, 3.355, 3.541, 3.808, 3.924, 4.934, 5.097, 5.422, 5.735, 6.165, 6.432, 7.059, 7.233, 7.338, 7.674, 8.057, 8.324, 8.545], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.302, 0.65, 1.08, 1.207, 1.474, 2.101, 2.345, 2.392, 2.612, 2.891, 3.297, 3.471, 3.785, 3.878, 4.331, 5.05, 5.387, 5.666, 6.118, 6.374, 7.024, 7.187, 7.303, 7.605, 8.011, 8.278, 8.487, 9.334]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(313, 55, 'Page 2', 'To comfort himself, the town elder gave Theo a small leather pouch filled with what looked like ordinary white pebbles.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"To\", \"comfort\", \"himself,\", \"the\", \"town\", \"elder\", \"gave\", \"Theo\", \"a\", \"small\", \"leather\", \"pouch\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"what\", \"looked\", \"like\", \"ordinary\", \"white\", \"pebbles.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.58, 1.289, 1.44, 1.707, 1.985, 2.206, 2.485, 2.577, 2.926, 3.216, 3.843, 4.18, 4.342, 4.528, 4.783, 5.039, 5.55, 5.793], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.557, 1.138, 1.393, 1.649, 1.927, 2.171, 2.415, 2.508, 2.856, 3.17, 3.564, 4.145, 4.307, 4.481, 4.748, 4.981, 5.503, 5.759, 6.502]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(314, 55, 'Page 3', '\"These are star seeds,\" the elder whispered. \"Plant them where the dark scares you most, and they will grow.\"', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"\"These\", \"are\", \"star\", \"seeds,\"\", \"the\", \"elder\", \"whispered.\", \"\"Plant\", \"them\", \"where\", \"the\", \"dark\", \"scares\", \"you\", \"most,\", \"and\", \"they\", \"will\", \"grow.\"\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.372, 0.511, 0.813, 1.405, 1.579, 1.869, 2.566, 3.007, 3.181, 3.379, 3.495, 3.785, 4.238, 4.4, 4.853, 5.039, 5.19, 5.41], \"end_times\": [0.348, 0.488, 0.755, 1.335, 1.521, 1.811, 2.392, 2.972, 3.146, 3.344, 3.448, 3.727, 4.18, 4.331, 4.83, 4.992, 5.155, 5.352, 6.687]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(315, 55, 'Page 4', 'Theo thought it was a foolish tale, but the next evening, when the shadows grew long and terrifying at the forest edge, he pressed one pebble firmly into the soft dirt.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Theo\", \"thought\", \"it\", \"was\", \"a\", \"foolish\", \"tale,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"next\", \"evening,\", \"when\", \"the\", \"shadows\", \"grew\", \"long\", \"and\", \"terrifying\", \"at\", \"the\", \"forest\", \"edge,\", \"he\", \"pressed\", \"one\", \"pebble\", \"firmly\", \"into\", \"the\", \"soft\", \"dirt.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.673, 0.755, 0.894, 0.975, 1.37, 1.939, 2.136, 2.252, 2.531, 3.402, 3.622, 3.738, 4.191, 4.458, 4.783, 4.934, 5.608, 5.724, 5.851, 6.293, 7.198, 7.349, 7.721, 7.953, 8.348, 8.789, 9.021, 9.137, 9.497], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.639, 0.72, 0.848, 0.917, 1.324, 1.823, 2.101, 2.206, 2.461, 3.077, 3.587, 3.692, 4.133, 4.389, 4.725, 4.876, 5.55, 5.689, 5.793, 6.211, 6.757, 7.279, 7.651, 7.906, 8.278, 8.731, 8.951, 9.091, 9.439, 10.077]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(316, 55, 'Page 5', 'Nothing happened immediately.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Nothing\", \"happened\", \"immediately.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.522, 0.848], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.824, 1.625]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(317, 55, 'Page 6', 'But as the darkness fully settled, a faint, bioluminescent glow began to seep upward through the soil. Small, delicate mushrooms, glowing with a soft, steady white light resembling distant stars, sprouted from the pebble perfectly.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"as\", \"the\", \"darkness\", \"fully\", \"settled,\", \"a\", \"faint,\", \"bioluminescent\", \"glow\", \"began\", \"to\", \"seep\", \"upward\", \"through\", \"the\", \"soil.\", \"Small,\", \"delicate\", \"mushrooms,\", \"glowing\", \"with\", \"a\", \"soft,\", \"steady\", \"white\", \"light\", \"resembling\", \"distant\", \"stars,\", \"sprouted\", \"from\", \"the\", \"pebble\", \"perfectly.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.476, 0.58, 0.998, 1.324, 2.148, 2.334, 2.81, 3.785, 4.133, 4.458, 4.586, 4.888, 5.259, 5.515, 5.631, 6.757, 7.303, 7.767, 8.475, 8.916, 9.091, 9.183, 9.683, 10.089, 10.368, 10.693, 11.285, 11.726, 12.632, 13.119, 13.305, 13.421, 13.793], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.406, 0.546, 0.964, 1.254, 1.904, 2.218, 2.74, 3.727, 4.063, 4.412, 4.516, 4.818, 5.224, 5.48, 5.584, 6.153, 7.256, 7.732, 8.417, 8.87, 9.044, 9.114, 9.625, 10.031, 10.321, 10.623, 11.215, 11.668, 12.353, 13.073, 13.259, 13.375, 13.735, 14.675]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(318, 55, 'Page 7', 'Over the summer, Theo walked the perimeter of his village, planting a pebble wherever the path felt too dark or the woods felt too deep. By autumn, the village was surrounded by a gentle, glowing perimeter of earthen stars.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Over\", \"the\", \"summer,\", \"Theo\", \"walked\", \"the\", \"perimeter\", \"of\", \"his\", \"village,\", \"planting\", \"a\", \"pebble\", \"wherever\", \"the\", \"path\", \"felt\", \"too\", \"dark\", \"or\", \"the\", \"woods\", \"felt\", \"too\", \"deep.\", \"By\", \"autumn,\", \"the\", \"village\", \"was\", \"surrounded\", \"by\", \"a\", \"gentle,\", \"glowing\", \"perimeter\", \"of\", \"earthen\", \"stars.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.546, 0.975, 1.277, 1.521, 1.649, 2.159, 2.276, 2.426, 3.158, 3.564, 3.646, 4.307, 4.748, 4.876, 5.19, 5.457, 5.666, 6.037, 6.211, 6.327, 6.664, 6.908, 7.105, 8.081, 8.29, 8.916, 9.067, 9.381, 9.52, 9.996, 10.17, 10.263, 10.762, 11.18, 11.738, 11.889, 12.237], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.499, 0.917, 1.219, 1.498, 1.591, 2.101, 2.218, 2.38, 2.914, 3.518, 3.587, 4.133, 4.702, 4.818, 5.143, 5.399, 5.608, 5.956, 6.153, 6.281, 6.606, 6.873, 7.059, 7.477, 8.231, 8.766, 9.021, 9.346, 9.485, 9.95, 10.101, 10.194, 10.681, 11.111, 11.645, 11.819, 12.179, 13.003]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(319, 55, 'Page 8', 'The terrifying darkness had been changed not by pushing it away, but by introducing small points of light within it.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"terrifying\", \"darkness\", \"had\", \"been\", \"changed\", \"not\", \"by\", \"pushing\", \"it\", \"away,\", \"but\", \"by\", \"introducing\", \"small\", \"points\", \"of\", \"light\", \"within\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.824, 1.254, 1.382, 1.556, 2.02, 2.252, 2.403, 2.74, 2.833, 3.541, 3.715, 3.878, 4.458, 4.772, 5.05, 5.178, 5.387, 5.666], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.766, 1.219, 1.347, 1.509, 1.95, 2.206, 2.345, 2.694, 2.798, 3.216, 3.68, 3.808, 4.389, 4.714, 5.016, 5.108, 5.352, 5.619, 6.037]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(320, 55, 'Page 9', 'Theo learned that courage wasn\'t about destroying the dark, but trusting your ability to create a little light exactly where you needed it most.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_55_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Theo\", \"learned\", \"that\", \"courage\", \"wasn\'t\", \"about\", \"destroying\", \"the\", \"dark,\", \"but\", \"trusting\", \"your\", \"ability\", \"to\", \"create\", \"a\", \"little\", \"light\", \"exactly\", \"where\", \"you\", \"needed\", \"it\", \"most.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.871, 1.045, 1.498, 1.811, 2.067, 2.496, 2.601, 3.228, 3.437, 3.913, 4.063, 4.528, 4.667, 4.969, 5.039, 5.283, 5.584, 6.153, 6.327, 6.455, 6.745, 6.861], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.824, 0.998, 1.451, 1.776, 2.02, 2.461, 2.566, 2.984, 3.402, 3.866, 4.029, 4.458, 4.598, 4.946, 5.004, 5.259, 5.526, 6.118, 6.293, 6.397, 6.699, 6.803, 7.477]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(321, 56, 'Page 1', 'In a kingdom of grand halls and golden tapestries stood a mirror unlike any other. It was tall as a door and framed in silver vines. Legend said it revealed a person’s true name — not the name given at birth, but the name that described who they truly were.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"kingdom\", \"of\", \"grand\", \"halls\", \"and\", \"golden\", \"tapestries\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"mirror\", \"unlike\", \"any\", \"other.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"tall\", \"as\", \"a\", \"door\", \"and\", \"framed\", \"in\", \"silver\", \"vines.\", \"Legend\", \"said\", \"it\", \"revealed\", \"a\", \"personu2019s\", \"true\", \"name\", \"u2014\", \"not\", \"the\", \"name\", \"given\", \"at\", \"birth,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"name\", \"that\", \"described\", \"who\", \"they\", \"truly\", \"were.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.36, 0.72, 0.824, 1.173, 1.509, 1.637, 1.985, 2.937, 3.228, 3.309, 3.762, 4.226, 4.493, 5.492, 5.642, 5.805, 6.153, 6.269, 6.351, 6.653, 6.815, 7.245, 7.396, 7.755, 9.253, 9.718, 10.054, 10.17, 10.623, 10.716, 11.18, 11.471, 11.923, 12.376, 12.597, 12.713, 12.922, 13.154, 13.27, 13.967, 14.164, 14.292, 14.512, 14.663, 15.174, 15.36, 15.523, 15.906], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.302, 0.673, 0.766, 1.103, 1.474, 1.579, 1.939, 2.694, 3.193, 3.251, 3.646, 4.18, 4.435, 4.981, 5.608, 5.747, 6.095, 6.223, 6.304, 6.583, 6.745, 7.198, 7.314, 7.709, 8.44, 9.648, 9.985, 10.124, 10.577, 10.658, 11.122, 11.424, 11.807, 11.993, 12.562, 12.666, 12.887, 13.119, 13.224, 13.793, 14.129, 14.234, 14.489, 14.617, 15.139, 15.302, 15.476, 15.848, 16.486]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(322, 56, 'Page 2', 'The vain King Roderick stood before it daily, expecting to see words like \"The Magnificent\" or \"The Conqueror\" appear in the reflection. Every day, the mirror remained an empty, polished surface showing only his face. Frustrated, he eventually locked the room and forbade anyone from entering.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"vain\", \"King\", \"Roderick\", \"stood\", \"before\", \"it\", \"daily,\", \"expecting\", \"to\", \"see\", \"words\", \"like\", \"\"The\", \"Magnificent\"\", \"or\", \"\"The\", \"Conqueror\"\", \"appear\", \"in\", \"the\", \"reflection.\", \"Every\", \"day,\", \"the\", \"mirror\", \"remained\", \"an\", \"empty,\", \"polished\", \"surface\", \"showing\", \"only\", \"his\", \"face.\", \"Frustrated,\", \"he\", \"eventually\", \"locked\", \"the\", \"room\", \"and\", \"forbade\", \"anyone\", \"from\", \"entering.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.604, 0.859, 1.289, 1.544, 1.881, 2.009, 2.554, 3.123, 3.228, 3.425, 3.715, 4.122, 4.377, 5.375, 5.573, 5.724, 6.444, 6.815, 6.896, 7.012, 8.58, 8.94, 9.346, 9.52, 9.81, 10.182, 10.333, 10.82, 11.366, 11.9, 12.307, 12.632, 12.806, 14.338, 15.348, 15.488, 15.975, 16.254, 16.382, 16.637, 16.765, 17.194, 17.566, 17.775], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.522, 0.789, 1.242, 1.498, 1.846, 1.962, 2.496, 3.077, 3.17, 3.379, 3.669, 4.087, 4.319, 5.306, 5.538, 5.666, 6.397, 6.769, 6.873, 6.966, 7.767, 8.882, 9.288, 9.451, 9.764, 10.147, 10.252, 10.751, 11.308, 11.854, 12.225, 12.574, 12.748, 13.386, 15.174, 15.418, 15.917, 16.219, 16.324, 16.591, 16.707, 17.16, 17.531, 17.705, 18.437]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(323, 56, 'Page 3', 'A young scullery maid named Anya, tasked with cleaning the dusty halls near the locked room, accidentally pushed the heavy door open while wiping the floorboards.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"young\", \"scullery\", \"maid\", \"named\", \"Anya,\", \"tasked\", \"with\", \"cleaning\", \"the\", \"dusty\", \"halls\", \"near\", \"the\", \"locked\", \"room,\", \"accidentally\", \"pushed\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"door\", \"open\", \"while\", \"wiping\", \"the\", \"floorboards.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.522, 0.975, 1.219, 1.509, 2.206, 2.659, 2.844, 3.193, 3.309, 3.669, 3.994, 4.156, 4.272, 4.586, 5.236, 5.944, 6.223, 6.351, 6.583, 6.815, 7.14, 7.338, 7.651, 7.744], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.453, 0.929, 1.161, 1.44, 2.032, 2.624, 2.798, 3.158, 3.262, 3.599, 3.947, 4.122, 4.226, 4.528, 4.957, 5.886, 6.2, 6.293, 6.536, 6.745, 7.094, 7.314, 7.616, 7.721, 8.591]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(324, 56, 'Page 4', 'Curious, she walked straight up to the massive glass. She didn\'t puff out her chest or strike a royal pose. She simply looked at her hands, tired from washing dishes, and sighed.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Curious,\", \"she\", \"walked\", \"straight\", \"up\", \"to\", \"the\", \"massive\", \"glass.\", \"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"puff\", \"out\", \"her\", \"chest\", \"or\", \"strike\", \"a\", \"royal\", \"pose.\", \"She\", \"simply\", \"looked\", \"at\", \"her\", \"hands,\", \"tired\", \"from\", \"washing\", \"dishes,\", \"and\", \"sighed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.685, 0.848, 1.115, 1.405, 1.544, 1.649, 1.765, 2.159, 3.053, 3.239, 3.495, 3.762, 3.924, 4.063, 4.481, 4.632, 4.934, 5.016, 5.306, 6.2, 6.385, 6.711, 6.931, 7.024, 7.163, 7.546, 7.953, 8.139, 8.51, 9.207, 9.427], \"end_times\": [0.662, 0.789, 1.08, 1.37, 1.498, 1.591, 1.718, 2.125, 2.775, 3.193, 3.46, 3.704, 3.866, 4.005, 4.423, 4.574, 4.899, 4.957, 5.248, 5.817, 6.327, 6.664, 6.908, 6.978, 7.105, 7.512, 7.918, 8.081, 8.452, 9.091, 9.358, 10.077]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(325, 56, 'Page 5', 'The mirror shivered like water.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"mirror\", \"shivered\", \"like\", \"water.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.627, 0.975, 1.173], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.569, 0.94, 1.126, 1.811]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(326, 56, 'Page 6', 'Slowly, glowing letters formed across the silver surface: \"The Gentle Observer.\"', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Slowly,\", \"glowing\", \"letters\", \"formed\", \"across\", \"the\", \"silver\", \"surface:\", \"\"The\", \"Gentle\", \"Observer.\"\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.848, 1.265, 1.625, 1.904, 2.218, 2.322, 2.647, 3.274, 3.541, 3.924], \"end_times\": [0.766, 1.207, 1.567, 1.881, 2.183, 2.287, 2.601, 3.216, 3.483, 3.889, 4.644]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(327, 56, 'Page 7', 'Anya smiled. She rarely spoke, but she watched the court closely, often bringing a warm cup of cider to a shivering guard or quietly sweeping away a hazard before someone tripped.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Anya\", \"smiled.\", \"She\", \"rarely\", \"spoke,\", \"but\", \"she\", \"watched\", \"the\", \"court\", \"closely,\", \"often\", \"bringing\", \"a\", \"warm\", \"cup\", \"of\", \"cider\", \"to\", \"a\", \"shivering\", \"guard\", \"or\", \"quietly\", \"sweeping\", \"away\", \"a\", \"hazard\", \"before\", \"someone\", \"tripped.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 1.44, 1.649, 2.009, 2.612, 2.81, 2.984, 3.297, 3.402, 3.657, 4.493, 4.83, 5.178, 5.248, 5.538, 5.724, 5.84, 6.211, 6.362, 6.455, 6.908, 7.221, 7.349, 7.814, 8.22, 8.452, 8.545, 9.242, 9.613, 9.95], \"end_times\": [0.418, 1.115, 1.579, 1.95, 2.496, 2.775, 2.914, 3.262, 3.367, 3.611, 4.284, 4.795, 5.12, 5.201, 5.48, 5.677, 5.782, 6.153, 6.281, 6.385, 6.85, 7.175, 7.291, 7.755, 8.185, 8.406, 8.475, 9.033, 9.567, 9.927, 10.542]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(328, 56, 'Page 8', 'King Roderick, having heard the door squeak, burst into the room just in time to see the fading letters. Surprised, he asked how a mere servant commanded magic that a king could not.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"King\", \"Roderick,\", \"having\", \"heard\", \"the\", \"door\", \"squeak,\", \"burst\", \"into\", \"the\", \"room\", \"just\", \"in\", \"time\", \"to\", \"see\", \"the\", \"fading\", \"letters.\", \"Surprised,\", \"he\", \"asked\", \"how\", \"a\", \"mere\", \"servant\", \"commanded\", \"magic\", \"that\", \"a\", \"king\", \"could\", \"not.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.383, 0.859, 1.161, 1.358, 1.463, 1.718, 2.508, 2.868, 3.065, 3.17, 3.39, 3.646, 3.773, 4.04, 4.145, 4.319, 4.435, 4.76, 5.77, 6.385, 6.502, 6.792, 6.954, 7.024, 7.279, 7.686, 8.173, 8.568, 8.731, 8.812, 9.044, 9.253], \"end_times\": [0.325, 0.836, 1.091, 1.324, 1.428, 1.649, 2.229, 2.821, 3.007, 3.135, 3.332, 3.599, 3.727, 4.005, 4.087, 4.284, 4.389, 4.714, 5.329, 6.362, 6.444, 6.757, 6.896, 6.978, 7.21, 7.628, 8.104, 8.522, 8.696, 8.754, 8.998, 9.207, 9.845]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(329, 56, 'Page 9', 'Anya looked at the man draped in gold and heavy jewels. \"A mirror cannot reflect what is hidden behind armor, Your Majesty. It only shows what you are brave enough to present quietly.\"', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Anya\", \"looked\", \"at\", \"the\", \"man\", \"draped\", \"in\", \"gold\", \"and\", \"heavy\", \"jewels.\", \"\"A\", \"mirror\", \"cannot\", \"reflect\", \"what\", \"is\", \"hidden\", \"behind\", \"armor,\", \"Your\", \"Majesty.\", \"It\", \"only\", \"shows\", \"what\", \"you\", \"are\", \"brave\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"present\", \"quietly.\"\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.72, 0.824, 0.952, 1.254, 1.591, 1.741, 2.067, 2.206, 2.485, 3.471, 3.738, 4.098, 4.481, 4.934, 5.108, 5.236, 5.561, 5.944, 6.293, 6.444, 7.477, 7.674, 7.941, 8.301, 8.464, 8.58, 8.719, 9.009, 9.288, 9.404, 9.776], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.697, 0.789, 0.894, 1.184, 1.556, 1.66, 2.02, 2.136, 2.415, 3.088, 3.646, 4.04, 4.423, 4.888, 5.062, 5.178, 5.503, 5.875, 6.258, 6.397, 7.152, 7.616, 7.883, 8.255, 8.429, 8.533, 8.696, 8.975, 9.242, 9.346, 9.729, 10.774]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(330, 56, 'Page 10', 'The King finally understood. He spent the next year working not to build monuments to his glory, but to actually govern fairly. When he finally stood before the mirror without his crown or royal robes, simply asking to see his truth, the glass rippled and offered one quiet word: \"Student.\"', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"King\", \"finally\", \"understood.\", \"He\", \"spent\", \"the\", \"next\", \"year\", \"working\", \"not\", \"to\", \"build\", \"monuments\", \"to\", \"his\", \"glory,\", \"but\", \"to\", \"actually\", \"govern\", \"fairly.\", \"When\", \"he\", \"finally\", \"stood\", \"before\", \"the\", \"mirror\", \"without\", \"his\", \"crown\", \"or\", \"royal\", \"robes,\", \"simply\", \"asking\", \"to\", \"see\", \"his\", \"truth,\", \"the\", \"glass\", \"rippled\", \"and\", \"offered\", \"one\", \"quiet\", \"word:\", \"\"Student.\"\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.557, 0.929, 2.125, 2.276, 2.508, 2.624, 2.879, 3.123, 3.518, 3.785, 3.901, 4.18, 4.667, 4.795, 4.957, 5.747, 5.921, 6.037, 6.513, 6.931, 8.359, 8.568, 8.684, 9.067, 9.334, 9.636, 9.752, 10.066, 10.414, 10.577, 10.995, 11.18, 11.517, 12.156, 12.539, 12.934, 13.05, 13.259, 13.444, 14.141, 14.292, 14.687, 15.163, 15.383, 15.732, 15.952, 16.312, 17.31], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.488, 0.882, 1.614, 2.229, 2.485, 2.577, 2.844, 3.053, 3.448, 3.738, 3.843, 4.098, 4.632, 4.725, 4.899, 5.573, 5.886, 5.968, 6.444, 6.85, 7.546, 8.533, 8.626, 9.021, 9.3, 9.601, 9.706, 10.019, 10.356, 10.519, 10.925, 11.099, 11.447, 12.04, 12.481, 12.875, 12.992, 13.212, 13.375, 13.967, 14.245, 14.617, 15.093, 15.314, 15.673, 15.906, 16.266, 16.8, 18.715]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(331, 56, 'Page 11', 'It was the greatest title he possessed.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_56_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"was\", \"the\", \"greatest\", \"title\", \"he\", \"possessed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.406, 0.534, 0.906, 1.231, 1.347], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.36, 0.476, 0.871, 1.196, 1.289, 2.043]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(332, 8, 'Page 1', 'In the middle of a quiet valley, wrapped in soft morning mist, stood an ancient clock tower. It had been there for centuries. Its stones were covered with moss, and its tall windows caught the sunlight at dawn. At the very top rested a great golden clock. This clock did more than show the time. It kept the valley in balance.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"the\", \"middle\", \"of\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"valley,\", \"wrapped\", \"in\", \"soft\", \"morning\", \"mist,\", \"stood\", \"an\", \"ancient\", \"clock\", \"tower.\", \"It\", \"had\", \"been\", \"there\", \"for\", \"centuries.\", \"Its\", \"stones\", \"were\", \"covered\", \"with\", \"moss,\", \"and\", \"its\", \"tall\", \"windows\", \"caught\", \"the\", \"sunlight\", \"at\", \"dawn.\", \"At\", \"the\", \"very\", \"top\", \"rested\", \"a\", \"great\", \"golden\", \"clock.\", \"This\", \"clock\", \"did\", \"more\", \"than\", \"show\", \"the\", \"time.\", \"It\", \"kept\", \"the\", \"valley\", \"in\", \"balance.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.383, 0.65, 0.743, 0.813, 1.173, 1.741, 2.125, 2.276, 2.67, 3.019, 3.646, 3.959, 4.11, 4.54, 4.888, 5.886, 6.049, 6.188, 6.374, 6.571, 6.745, 7.755, 7.976, 8.394, 8.557, 8.858, 9.056, 9.764, 9.95, 10.124, 10.426, 10.855, 11.111, 11.227, 11.645, 11.773, 12.783, 12.98, 13.108, 13.398, 13.816, 14.199, 14.28, 14.606, 14.989, 16.01, 16.266, 16.591, 16.788, 16.997, 17.183, 17.392, 17.508, 18.263, 18.448, 18.704, 18.832, 19.157, 19.273], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.337, 0.615, 0.697, 0.766, 1.115, 1.625, 2.09, 2.194, 2.601, 2.961, 3.471, 3.924, 4.029, 4.481, 4.818, 5.445, 6.014, 6.142, 6.339, 6.536, 6.687, 7.512, 7.941, 8.359, 8.522, 8.835, 8.986, 9.613, 9.892, 10.077, 10.368, 10.786, 11.088, 11.18, 11.598, 11.714, 12.272, 12.945, 13.05, 13.34, 13.7, 14.153, 14.222, 14.524, 14.931, 15.569, 16.208, 16.533, 16.73, 16.962, 17.125, 17.334, 17.462, 18.019, 18.39, 18.669, 18.774, 19.122, 19.215, 20.062]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(333, 8, 'Page 2', 'Every morning, when the sun rose, the clock shimmered gently. In the evenings, it glowed with warm golden light. Flowers bloomed exactly when they should. Leaves fell at the perfect moment. Birds migrated without confusion. Life in the valley moved in harmony.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Every\", \"morning,\", \"when\", \"the\", \"sun\", \"rose,\", \"the\", \"clock\", \"shimmered\", \"gently.\", \"In\", \"the\", \"evenings,\", \"it\", \"glowed\", \"with\", \"warm\", \"golden\", \"light.\", \"Flowers\", \"bloomed\", \"exactly\", \"when\", \"they\", \"should.\", \"Leaves\", \"fell\", \"at\", \"the\", \"perfect\", \"moment.\", \"Birds\", \"migrated\", \"without\", \"confusion.\", \"Life\", \"in\", \"the\", \"valley\", \"moved\", \"in\", \"harmony.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.488, 0.836, 1.01, 1.126, 1.405, 1.997, 2.159, 2.508, 2.902, 4.04, 4.214, 4.354, 5.05, 5.236, 5.619, 5.817, 6.2, 6.583, 7.697, 8.197, 8.533, 9.044, 9.195, 9.346, 10.205, 10.635, 10.913, 11.029, 11.146, 11.552, 12.481, 12.875, 13.34, 13.665, 14.919, 15.221, 15.325, 15.453, 15.824, 16.115, 16.254], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.813, 0.975, 1.08, 1.335, 1.846, 2.101, 2.426, 2.856, 3.437, 4.168, 4.284, 4.934, 5.178, 5.584, 5.747, 6.13, 6.525, 7.001, 8.15, 8.487, 9.009, 9.16, 9.3, 9.764, 10.565, 10.855, 10.995, 11.099, 11.494, 12.04, 12.817, 13.293, 13.618, 14.408, 15.186, 15.279, 15.395, 15.755, 16.08, 16.184, 16.951]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(334, 8, 'Page 3', 'Until one morning, everything changed.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Until\", \"one\", \"morning,\", \"everything\", \"changed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.639, 0.975, 1.44], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.604, 0.952, 1.382, 2.183]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(335, 8, 'Page 4', 'The clock had stopped.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"clock\", \"had\", \"stopped.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.522, 0.662], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.476, 0.615, 1.3]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(336, 8, 'Page 5', 'The large hands no longer moved. They did not tick forward. They did not fall back. They simply remained still.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"large\", \"hands\", \"no\", \"longer\", \"moved.\", \"They\", \"did\", \"not\", \"tick\", \"forward.\", \"They\", \"did\", \"not\", \"fall\", \"back.\", \"They\", \"simply\", \"remained\", \"still.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.604, 0.964, 1.103, 1.393, 1.997, 2.194, 2.357, 2.531, 2.775, 3.448, 3.646, 3.808, 3.982, 4.191, 4.83, 5.062, 5.422, 5.817], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.557, 0.906, 1.045, 1.335, 1.846, 2.159, 2.31, 2.496, 2.705, 3.274, 3.611, 3.762, 3.936, 4.133, 4.586, 5.004, 5.352, 5.77, 6.409]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(337, 8, 'Page 6', 'At first, no one worried. But within days, strange things began to happen. Flowers opened halfway and stayed frozen in that moment. The wind seemed unsure whether to blow or stay quiet. Birds sat on branches as if they had forgotten where they were going.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"first,\", \"no\", \"one\", \"worried.\", \"But\", \"within\", \"days,\", \"strange\", \"things\", \"began\", \"to\", \"happen.\", \"Flowers\", \"opened\", \"halfway\", \"and\", \"stayed\", \"frozen\", \"in\", \"that\", \"moment.\", \"The\", \"wind\", \"seemed\", \"unsure\", \"whether\", \"to\", \"blow\", \"or\", \"stay\", \"quiet.\", \"Birds\", \"sat\", \"on\", \"branches\", \"as\", \"if\", \"they\", \"had\", \"forgotten\", \"where\", \"they\", \"were\", \"going.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.836, 1.033, 1.184, 2.194, 2.368, 2.694, 3.379, 3.796, 4.087, 4.377, 4.505, 5.55, 6.049, 6.385, 7.082, 7.291, 7.605, 8.069, 8.197, 8.417, 9.392, 9.567, 9.845, 10.217, 10.704, 10.995, 11.111, 11.517, 11.691, 11.97, 12.91, 13.305, 13.549, 13.688, 14.315, 14.547, 14.675, 14.826, 14.977, 15.395, 15.569, 15.708, 15.871], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.72, 0.964, 1.149, 1.753, 2.345, 2.624, 3.204, 3.762, 4.04, 4.331, 4.435, 5.039, 5.991, 6.327, 6.931, 7.233, 7.546, 7.999, 8.15, 8.348, 8.951, 9.52, 9.776, 10.136, 10.67, 10.948, 11.053, 11.401, 11.633, 11.912, 12.527, 13.27, 13.491, 13.63, 14.222, 14.489, 14.64, 14.791, 14.93, 15.372, 15.534, 15.673, 15.836, 16.44]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(338, 8, 'Page 7', 'Time continued to exist, but the valley felt paused.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Time\", \"continued\", \"to\", \"exist,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"valley\", \"felt\", \"paused.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.917, 1.057, 1.486, 1.637, 1.765, 2.09, 2.345], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.894, 0.975, 1.463, 1.602, 1.707, 2.043, 2.287, 3.065]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:11'),
(339, 8, 'Page 8', 'A young girl named Elara passed the tower every day. When she noticed the still clock, a quiet uneasiness filled her heart. To her, the tower was not just stone and metal. It was the heart of the valley.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"young\", \"girl\", \"named\", \"Elara\", \"passed\", \"the\", \"tower\", \"every\", \"day.\", \"When\", \"she\", \"noticed\", \"the\", \"still\", \"clock,\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"uneasiness\", \"filled\", \"her\", \"heart.\", \"To\", \"her,\", \"the\", \"tower\", \"was\", \"not\", \"just\", \"stone\", \"and\", \"metal.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"the\", \"heart\", \"of\", \"the\", \"valley.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.522, 0.813, 1.068, 1.498, 1.858, 1.962, 2.345, 2.624, 3.576, 3.785, 3.947, 4.319, 4.447, 4.772, 5.561, 5.712, 6.2, 6.838, 7.152, 7.314, 9.067, 9.288, 9.834, 9.996, 10.298, 10.472, 10.693, 11.018, 11.459, 11.645, 12.492, 12.655, 12.794, 12.945, 13.235, 13.351, 13.468], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.464, 0.743, 1.022, 1.428, 1.823, 1.927, 2.264, 2.577, 3.065, 3.75, 3.878, 4.284, 4.389, 4.702, 5.352, 5.631, 6.118, 6.78, 7.105, 7.245, 7.767, 9.195, 9.683, 9.938, 10.24, 10.403, 10.635, 10.925, 11.413, 11.575, 12.109, 12.608, 12.748, 12.864, 13.177, 13.293, 13.421, 14.164]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(340, 8, 'Page 9', 'One morning, she gathered her courage and stepped inside.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"morning,\", \"she\", \"gathered\", \"her\", \"courage\", \"and\", \"stepped\", \"inside.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.65, 0.813, 1.184, 1.312, 1.66, 1.788, 2.101], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.627, 0.755, 1.149, 1.265, 1.625, 1.73, 2.067, 2.879]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(341, 8, 'Page 10', 'The air was cool and heavy. A spiral staircase wound upward through shadows and light. With each step, her footsteps echoed softly against the stone walls. The higher she climbed, the quieter the world seemed.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"air\", \"was\", \"cool\", \"and\", \"heavy.\", \"A\", \"spiral\", \"staircase\", \"wound\", \"upward\", \"through\", \"shadows\", \"and\", \"light.\", \"With\", \"each\", \"step,\", \"her\", \"footsteps\", \"echoed\", \"softly\", \"against\", \"the\", \"stone\", \"walls.\", \"The\", \"higher\", \"she\", \"climbed,\", \"the\", \"quieter\", \"the\", \"world\", \"seemed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.534, 0.731, 1.091, 1.231, 2.206, 2.345, 2.775, 3.297, 3.576, 3.936, 4.18, 4.656, 4.807, 5.526, 5.747, 5.956, 6.571, 6.734, 7.326, 7.709, 8.185, 8.533, 8.649, 8.975, 10.286, 10.449, 10.751, 10.913, 11.587, 11.749, 12.283, 12.399, 12.701], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.476, 0.65, 1.022, 1.173, 1.765, 2.276, 2.717, 3.262, 3.506, 3.901, 4.133, 4.609, 4.737, 5.248, 5.7, 5.909, 6.455, 6.676, 7.256, 7.651, 8.139, 8.487, 8.603, 8.94, 9.59, 10.403, 10.693, 10.844, 11.436, 11.691, 12.225, 12.353, 12.643, 13.375]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(342, 8, 'Page 11', 'At the top, she reached the great mechanism behind the clock face. Large gears and delicate wheels were connected in perfect order. Nothing appeared broken. Nothing was missing. But at the center of it all, a crystal sat dull and lifeless.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"the\", \"top,\", \"she\", \"reached\", \"the\", \"great\", \"mechanism\", \"behind\", \"the\", \"clock\", \"face.\", \"Large\", \"gears\", \"and\", \"delicate\", \"wheels\", \"were\", \"connected\", \"in\", \"perfect\", \"order.\", \"Nothing\", \"appeared\", \"broken.\", \"Nothing\", \"was\", \"missing.\", \"But\", \"at\", \"the\", \"center\", \"of\", \"it\", \"all,\", \"a\", \"crystal\", \"sat\", \"dull\", \"and\", \"lifeless.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.418, 0.882, 1.103, 1.393, 1.509, 1.765, 2.252, 2.577, 2.682, 2.984, 4.331, 4.702, 5.108, 5.271, 5.677, 6.037, 6.211, 6.687, 6.827, 7.279, 8.208, 8.545, 8.905, 9.659, 9.996, 10.17, 11.146, 11.32, 11.413, 11.529, 11.854, 11.958, 12.063, 12.388, 12.539, 13.038, 13.34, 13.711, 13.897], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.372, 0.813, 1.022, 1.37, 1.463, 1.695, 2.194, 2.531, 2.647, 2.926, 3.518, 4.644, 5.062, 5.201, 5.654, 5.991, 6.177, 6.641, 6.745, 7.221, 7.697, 8.51, 8.87, 9.509, 9.95, 10.101, 10.704, 11.297, 11.378, 11.482, 11.784, 11.912, 12.028, 12.353, 12.469, 12.957, 13.27, 13.618, 13.827, 14.768]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(343, 8, 'Page 12', 'It was clear that this crystal once shone brightly. Now it looked like an ordinary stone.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"was\", \"clear\", \"that\", \"this\", \"crystal\", \"once\", \"shone\", \"brightly.\", \"Now\", \"it\", \"looked\", \"like\", \"an\", \"ordinary\", \"stone.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.464, 0.72, 0.871, 1.068, 1.509, 1.765, 2.02, 3.181, 3.413, 3.518, 3.727, 3.913, 4.017, 4.493], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.395, 0.673, 0.836, 0.998, 1.428, 1.73, 1.985, 2.577, 3.355, 3.483, 3.704, 3.878, 3.971, 4.423, 5.155]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(344, 8, 'Page 13', 'Elara stepped closer. She studied the gears carefully. The system was intact. The balance was there. But the light was gone.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elara\", \"stepped\", \"closer.\", \"She\", \"studied\", \"the\", \"gears\", \"carefully.\", \"The\", \"system\", \"was\", \"intact.\", \"The\", \"balance\", \"was\", \"there.\", \"But\", \"the\", \"light\", \"was\", \"gone.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.836, 1.753, 1.95, 2.31, 2.415, 2.717, 3.541, 3.704, 4.04, 4.203, 4.934, 5.108, 5.48, 5.642, 6.455, 6.653, 6.792, 7.047, 7.233], \"end_times\": [0.488, 0.789, 1.37, 1.892, 2.287, 2.38, 2.659, 3.367, 3.657, 3.994, 4.145, 4.818, 5.05, 5.445, 5.584, 6.072, 6.618, 6.722, 7.001, 7.163, 7.848]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(345, 8, 'Page 14', 'She thought about the valley. For days, everyone had been worried. No one sang in the mornings. No one laughed in the fields. Everyone waited for the clock to move again.', 14, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_14.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"thought\", \"about\", \"the\", \"valley.\", \"For\", \"days,\", \"everyone\", \"had\", \"been\", \"worried.\", \"No\", \"one\", \"sang\", \"in\", \"the\", \"mornings.\", \"No\", \"one\", \"laughed\", \"in\", \"the\", \"fields.\", \"Everyone\", \"waited\", \"for\", \"the\", \"clock\", \"to\", \"move\", \"again.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.58, 0.789, 0.917, 1.741, 1.95, 2.368, 2.74, 2.868, 3.03, 3.855, 4.075, 4.272, 4.574, 4.667, 4.772, 5.619, 5.817, 5.991, 6.327, 6.42, 6.536, 7.338, 7.779, 8.069, 8.197, 8.301, 8.615, 8.742, 8.951], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.557, 0.755, 0.859, 1.463, 1.892, 2.334, 2.717, 2.833, 2.995, 3.529, 3.994, 4.214, 4.528, 4.632, 4.737, 5.375, 5.747, 5.944, 6.293, 6.385, 6.49, 7.094, 7.744, 8.034, 8.162, 8.266, 8.557, 8.673, 8.916, 9.52]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(346, 8, 'Page 15', 'Perhaps the clock was waiting too.', 15, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_15.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Perhaps\", \"the\", \"clock\", \"was\", \"waiting\", \"too.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.557, 0.662, 0.929, 1.091, 1.428], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.627, 0.882, 1.033, 1.37, 1.997]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(347, 8, 'Page 16', 'Elara gently placed her hand on the crystal. She closed her eyes. She thought about her fear, her hope, and her belief that things could change.', 16, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_16.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elara\", \"gently\", \"placed\", \"her\", \"hand\", \"on\", \"the\", \"crystal.\", \"She\", \"closed\", \"her\", \"eyes.\", \"She\", \"thought\", \"about\", \"her\", \"fear,\", \"her\", \"hope,\", \"and\", \"her\", \"belief\", \"that\", \"things\", \"could\", \"change.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.569, 0.894, 1.184, 1.324, 1.567, 1.672, 1.776, 2.821, 3.007, 3.332, 3.495, 4.609, 4.795, 5.027, 5.236, 5.375, 6.014, 6.223, 6.85, 7.059, 7.187, 7.523, 7.686, 7.964, 8.173], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.836, 1.149, 1.265, 1.509, 1.637, 1.741, 2.38, 2.949, 3.286, 3.425, 4.005, 4.737, 5.004, 5.201, 5.317, 5.863, 6.153, 6.676, 7.001, 7.129, 7.477, 7.651, 7.906, 8.127, 8.916]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(348, 8, 'Page 17', 'A faint vibration traveled through her hand.', 17, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_17.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"faint\", \"vibration\", \"traveled\", \"through\", \"her\", \"hand.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.488, 1.033, 1.416, 1.66, 1.811], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.441, 0.987, 1.393, 1.625, 1.753, 2.368]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(349, 8, 'Page 18', 'A small click echoed in the tower.', 18, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_18.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"small\", \"click\", \"echoed\", \"in\", \"the\", \"tower.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.557, 0.836, 1.149, 1.231, 1.335], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.499, 0.766, 1.115, 1.196, 1.3, 1.904]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(350, 8, 'Page 19', 'Then another.', 19, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_19.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Then\", \"another.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.975]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(351, 8, 'Page 20', 'The crystal slowly shifted from dull gray to a soft golden glow. The gears began to turn, first slowly, then smoothly. The hands of the clock moved again.', 20, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_20.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"crystal\", \"slowly\", \"shifted\", \"from\", \"dull\", \"gray\", \"to\", \"a\", \"soft\", \"golden\", \"glow.\", \"The\", \"gears\", \"began\", \"to\", \"turn,\", \"first\", \"slowly,\", \"then\", \"smoothly.\", \"The\", \"hands\", \"of\", \"the\", \"clock\", \"moved\", \"again.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.697, 1.126, 1.567, 1.788, 2.067, 2.426, 2.589, 2.67, 3.042, 3.413, 4.493, 4.667, 4.992, 5.294, 5.41, 5.898, 6.2, 6.711, 6.943, 7.976, 8.162, 8.406, 8.499, 8.615, 8.94, 9.195], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.639, 1.068, 1.521, 1.707, 2.009, 2.357, 2.519, 2.612, 2.984, 3.367, 3.889, 4.621, 4.934, 5.248, 5.352, 5.817, 6.153, 6.687, 6.885, 7.593, 8.104, 8.382, 8.464, 8.568, 8.87, 9.16, 9.752]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(352, 8, 'Page 21', 'Light poured from the tower windows and spread across the valley. Flowers opened fully. The wind found its rhythm. Birds lifted into the sky and traced graceful paths through the air.', 21, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_21.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Light\", \"poured\", \"from\", \"the\", \"tower\", \"windows\", \"and\", \"spread\", \"across\", \"the\", \"valley.\", \"Flowers\", \"opened\", \"fully.\", \"The\", \"wind\", \"found\", \"its\", \"rhythm.\", \"Birds\", \"lifted\", \"into\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"and\", \"traced\", \"graceful\", \"paths\", \"through\", \"the\", \"air.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.801, 0.987, 1.091, 1.463, 1.881, 2.032, 2.322, 2.659, 2.775, 3.715, 4.238, 4.586, 5.166, 5.329, 5.608, 5.863, 6.014, 6.664, 7.047, 7.396, 7.628, 7.744, 8.115, 8.243, 8.591, 9.044, 9.404, 9.636, 9.776], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.766, 0.94, 1.057, 1.405, 1.834, 1.974, 2.287, 2.624, 2.728, 3.274, 4.18, 4.54, 5.05, 5.283, 5.538, 5.805, 5.968, 6.455, 6.989, 7.349, 7.558, 7.697, 8.046, 8.197, 8.545, 8.975, 9.369, 9.601, 9.706, 10.263]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(353, 8, 'Page 22', 'Time had never truly disappeared. It had simply been waiting.', 22, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_22.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Time\", \"had\", \"never\", \"truly\", \"disappeared.\", \"It\", \"had\", \"simply\", \"been\", \"waiting.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.58, 0.824, 1.161, 1.811, 1.974, 2.101, 2.426, 2.601], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.522, 0.778, 1.115, 1.765, 1.939, 2.067, 2.38, 2.566, 3.204]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(354, 8, 'Page 23', 'Elara walked out of the tower into the warm sunlight. The steady ticking echoed behind her, calm and strong.', 23, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_23.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elara\", \"walked\", \"out\", \"of\", \"the\", \"tower\", \"into\", \"the\", \"warm\", \"sunlight.\", \"The\", \"steady\", \"ticking\", \"echoed\", \"behind\", \"her,\", \"calm\", \"and\", \"strong.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.534, 0.801, 0.94, 1.033, 1.149, 1.544, 1.741, 1.858, 2.136, 2.879, 3.065, 3.425, 3.855, 4.214, 4.609, 5.062, 5.445, 5.596], \"end_times\": [0.476, 0.766, 0.906, 0.987, 1.103, 1.474, 1.695, 1.811, 2.078, 2.67, 3.019, 3.355, 3.773, 4.18, 4.54, 4.888, 5.399, 5.538, 6.223]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(355, 8, 'Page 24', 'She understood something new that day.', 24, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_24.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"understood\", \"something\", \"new\", \"that\", \"day.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.755, 1.091, 1.254, 1.428], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.72, 1.033, 1.207, 1.382, 1.904]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(356, 8, 'Page 25', 'The magic had never been inside the gears.', 25, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_25.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"magic\", \"had\", \"never\", \"been\", \"inside\", \"the\", \"gears.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.627, 0.755, 0.975, 1.161, 1.498, 1.602], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.58, 0.72, 0.929, 1.126, 1.474, 1.567, 2.276]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(357, 8, 'Page 26', 'It had always been inside the courage to step forward.', 26, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_26.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"had\", \"always\", \"been\", \"inside\", \"the\", \"courage\", \"to\", \"step\", \"forward.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.43, 0.72, 0.906, 1.254, 1.37, 1.788, 1.916, 2.218], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.383, 0.685, 0.871, 1.231, 1.324, 1.753, 1.858, 2.148, 2.926]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(358, 8, 'Page 27', 'And sometimes, all it takes to start time again is one brave heart.', 27, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_8_page_27.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"sometimes,\", \"all\", \"it\", \"takes\", \"to\", \"start\", \"time\", \"again\", \"is\", \"one\", \"brave\", \"heart.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.882, 1.08, 1.173, 1.44, 1.567, 1.823, 2.067, 2.461, 2.659, 2.844, 3.135], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.859, 1.022, 1.149, 1.405, 1.509, 1.788, 2.032, 2.38, 2.589, 2.821, 3.088, 3.669]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(359, 9, 'Page 1', 'At the edge of a quiet kingdom stood a forest unlike any other. Its trees shimmered in shades of emerald and gold. The rivers reflected pink sunsets even at noon, and butterflies carried patterns like stained glass. The forest did not simply grow; it glowed.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"the\", \"edge\", \"of\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"kingdom\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"forest\", \"unlike\", \"any\", \"other.\", \"Its\", \"trees\", \"shimmered\", \"in\", \"shades\", \"of\", \"emerald\", \"and\", \"gold.\", \"The\", \"rivers\", \"reflected\", \"pink\", \"sunsets\", \"even\", \"at\", \"noon,\", \"and\", \"butterflies\", \"carried\", \"patterns\", \"like\", \"stained\", \"glass.\", \"The\", \"forest\", \"did\", \"not\", \"simply\", \"grow;\", \"it\", \"glowed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.418, 0.592, 0.697, 0.778, 1.161, 1.591, 1.823, 1.927, 2.496, 2.902, 3.158, 4.145, 4.4, 4.818, 5.259, 5.41, 5.77, 5.909, 6.327, 6.478, 7.477, 7.674, 8.022, 8.499, 8.789, 9.485, 9.752, 9.903, 10.646, 10.855, 11.447, 11.807, 12.237, 12.423, 12.794, 14.187, 14.362, 14.721, 14.884, 15.07, 15.43, 16.196, 16.393], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.348, 0.569, 0.65, 0.72, 1.103, 1.533, 1.8, 1.846, 2.403, 2.856, 3.088, 3.541, 4.342, 4.748, 5.224, 5.329, 5.735, 5.828, 6.281, 6.42, 6.966, 7.605, 7.953, 8.44, 8.719, 9.358, 9.718, 9.834, 10.368, 10.797, 11.389, 11.761, 12.19, 12.388, 12.748, 13.375, 14.303, 14.675, 14.838, 15.023, 15.372, 15.952, 16.335, 17.461]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(360, 9, 'Page 2', 'For many years, the colors never faded.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"For\", \"many\", \"years,\", \"the\", \"colors\", \"never\", \"faded.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.522, 0.848, 0.975, 1.324, 1.579], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.476, 0.824, 0.929, 1.277, 1.521, 2.183]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(361, 9, 'Page 3', 'Then one morning, the green leaves turned pale. The flowers lost their brightness. The river reflected nothing but a dull gray sky. It was as if someone had gently erased the world’s paint.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Then\", \"one\", \"morning,\", \"the\", \"green\", \"leaves\", \"turned\", \"pale.\", \"The\", \"flowers\", \"lost\", \"their\", \"brightness.\", \"The\", \"river\", \"reflected\", \"nothing\", \"but\", \"a\", \"dull\", \"gray\", \"sky.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"as\", \"if\", \"someone\", \"had\", \"gently\", \"erased\", \"the\", \"worldu2019s\", \"paint.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.511, 1.277, 1.44, 1.73, 2.043, 2.334, 3.332, 3.495, 3.971, 4.238, 4.412, 5.642, 5.817, 6.084, 6.653, 7.024, 7.175, 7.256, 7.546, 7.814, 9.091, 9.253, 9.416, 9.555, 9.706, 10.054, 10.228, 10.658, 11.122, 11.238, 11.598], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.476, 1.068, 1.382, 1.66, 1.997, 2.287, 2.821, 3.448, 3.913, 4.203, 4.377, 5.132, 5.759, 6.026, 6.583, 6.954, 7.14, 7.198, 7.488, 7.755, 8.487, 9.207, 9.358, 9.497, 9.648, 10.019, 10.17, 10.6, 11.088, 11.192, 11.552, 12.214]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(362, 9, 'Page 4', 'A young boy named Rowan, who often wandered beneath the tall branches, noticed the change immediately. He had grown up watching the forest breathe with color. Seeing it silent and washed of life felt wrong.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"young\", \"boy\", \"named\", \"Rowan,\", \"who\", \"often\", \"wandered\", \"beneath\", \"the\", \"tall\", \"branches,\", \"noticed\", \"the\", \"change\", \"immediately.\", \"He\", \"had\", \"grown\", \"up\", \"watching\", \"the\", \"forest\", \"breathe\", \"with\", \"color.\", \"Seeing\", \"it\", \"silent\", \"and\", \"washed\", \"of\", \"life\", \"felt\", \"wrong.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.511, 0.778, 1.045, 1.823, 2.043, 2.345, 2.752, 3.053, 3.17, 3.425, 4.54, 4.946, 5.074, 5.433, 6.827, 6.978, 7.105, 7.384, 7.558, 7.976, 8.092, 8.475, 8.777, 8.951, 10.263, 10.635, 10.774, 11.262, 11.424, 11.796, 11.947, 12.225, 12.492], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.453, 0.708, 0.987, 1.579, 1.974, 2.299, 2.717, 3.019, 3.123, 3.367, 4.214, 4.911, 5.016, 5.41, 6.223, 6.931, 7.059, 7.349, 7.488, 7.918, 8.046, 8.417, 8.742, 8.905, 9.451, 10.577, 10.716, 11.204, 11.355, 11.761, 11.865, 12.19, 12.446, 13.142]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(363, 9, 'Page 5', 'He walked deeper than he ever had before. The air felt heavier, quieter. At the heart of the forest stood an ancient stone basin filled with clear water. This basin was said to hold the forest’s first drop of color.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"walked\", \"deeper\", \"than\", \"he\", \"ever\", \"had\", \"before.\", \"The\", \"air\", \"felt\", \"heavier,\", \"quieter.\", \"At\", \"the\", \"heart\", \"of\", \"the\", \"forest\", \"stood\", \"an\", \"ancient\", \"stone\", \"basin\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"clear\", \"water.\", \"This\", \"basin\", \"was\", \"said\", \"to\", \"hold\", \"the\", \"forestu2019s\", \"first\", \"drop\", \"of\", \"color.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.72, 1.126, 1.324, 1.463, 1.73, 1.939, 3.297, 3.506, 3.762, 4.04, 4.876, 6.316, 6.513, 6.641, 6.85, 6.943, 7.07, 7.488, 7.767, 7.895, 8.336, 8.673, 9.242, 9.567, 9.764, 10.112, 11.192, 11.459, 11.865, 12.016, 12.225, 12.341, 12.562, 12.678, 13.201, 13.595, 13.932, 14.06], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.639, 1.057, 1.265, 1.382, 1.672, 1.881, 2.601, 3.437, 3.692, 3.982, 4.632, 5.712, 6.478, 6.583, 6.815, 6.896, 7.012, 7.43, 7.732, 7.837, 8.278, 8.626, 9.125, 9.543, 9.694, 10.043, 10.681, 11.389, 11.807, 11.97, 12.19, 12.272, 12.516, 12.632, 13.131, 13.514, 13.874, 13.99, 14.675]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(364, 9, 'Page 6', 'Now the water was colorless.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Now\", \"the\", \"water\", \"was\", \"colorless.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.464, 0.731, 0.871], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.43, 0.685, 0.824, 1.718]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(365, 9, 'Page 7', 'Rowan knelt beside it and looked at his reflection. He saw fear in his eyes, but also determination. He dipped his fingers into the basin and closed his eyes. He remembered the sound of laughter beneath the trees, the warmth of sunlight through leaves, the joy of running barefoot through soft grass.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Rowan\", \"knelt\", \"beside\", \"it\", \"and\", \"looked\", \"at\", \"his\", \"reflection.\", \"He\", \"saw\", \"fear\", \"in\", \"his\", \"eyes,\", \"but\", \"also\", \"determination.\", \"He\", \"dipped\", \"his\", \"fingers\", \"into\", \"the\", \"basin\", \"and\", \"closed\", \"his\", \"eyes.\", \"He\", \"remembered\", \"the\", \"sound\", \"of\", \"laughter\", \"beneath\", \"the\", \"trees,\", \"the\", \"warmth\", \"of\", \"sunlight\", \"through\", \"leaves,\", \"the\", \"joy\", \"of\", \"running\", \"barefoot\", \"through\", \"soft\", \"grass.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.72, 1.103, 1.219, 1.358, 1.602, 1.707, 1.858, 3.274, 3.437, 3.68, 3.994, 4.11, 4.272, 4.946, 5.143, 5.445, 7.012, 7.175, 7.396, 7.535, 7.906, 8.104, 8.208, 8.638, 8.777, 9.102, 9.265, 10.739, 10.902, 11.308, 11.424, 11.726, 11.854, 12.307, 12.608, 12.713, 13.688, 13.839, 14.153, 14.281, 14.699, 14.942, 15.825, 15.999, 16.254, 16.359, 16.661, 17.125, 17.369, 17.694], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.673, 1.068, 1.173, 1.3, 1.579, 1.66, 1.8, 2.577, 3.39, 3.587, 3.924, 4.052, 4.214, 4.83, 5.108, 5.375, 6.316, 7.117, 7.372, 7.488, 7.86, 8.046, 8.173, 8.591, 8.719, 9.067, 9.195, 9.787, 10.844, 11.285, 11.378, 11.68, 11.784, 12.237, 12.574, 12.678, 13.305, 13.793, 14.118, 14.211, 14.675, 14.908, 15.442, 15.929, 16.208, 16.312, 16.603, 17.09, 17.334, 17.648, 18.344]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(366, 9, 'Page 8', 'A single ripple spread across the surface.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"single\", \"ripple\", \"spread\", \"across\", \"the\", \"surface.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.592, 0.894, 1.161, 1.463, 1.567], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.557, 0.859, 1.126, 1.428, 1.533, 2.322]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(367, 9, 'Page 9', 'Faint streaks of blue and gold began to swirl in the water. The ripple widened, carrying color outward like a quiet wave. Slowly, gently, green returned to the leaves. The river shimmered again. Petals unfolded in bright shades.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Faint\", \"streaks\", \"of\", \"blue\", \"and\", \"gold\", \"began\", \"to\", \"swirl\", \"in\", \"the\", \"water.\", \"The\", \"ripple\", \"widened,\", \"carrying\", \"color\", \"outward\", \"like\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"wave.\", \"Slowly,\", \"gently,\", \"green\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"the\", \"leaves.\", \"The\", \"river\", \"shimmered\", \"again.\", \"Petals\", \"unfolded\", \"in\", \"bright\", \"shades.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.906, 1.057, 1.428, 1.625, 1.962, 2.252, 2.368, 2.74, 2.821, 2.926, 4.075, 4.261, 4.574, 5.341, 5.817, 6.142, 6.525, 6.687, 6.78, 7.163, 8.51, 9.485, 10.472, 10.855, 11.273, 11.366, 11.482, 12.771, 12.957, 13.293, 13.665, 14.698, 15.163, 15.801, 15.929, 16.242], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.859, 0.975, 1.382, 1.544, 1.904, 2.206, 2.31, 2.694, 2.786, 2.891, 3.471, 4.203, 4.54, 5.19, 5.747, 6.084, 6.478, 6.664, 6.722, 7.117, 7.697, 9.276, 10.194, 10.774, 11.25, 11.32, 11.436, 12.074, 12.899, 13.212, 13.63, 14.187, 15.105, 15.755, 15.871, 16.184, 17.043]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(368, 9, 'Page 10', 'The forest had not lost its magic. It had simply been waiting for someone to remember it.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"forest\", \"had\", \"not\", \"lost\", \"its\", \"magic.\", \"It\", \"had\", \"simply\", \"been\", \"waiting\", \"for\", \"someone\", \"to\", \"remember\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.639, 0.778, 0.94, 1.207, 1.37, 2.136, 2.31, 2.45, 2.775, 2.949, 3.274, 3.425, 3.75, 3.866, 4.296], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.604, 0.731, 0.894, 1.161, 1.324, 1.927, 2.276, 2.403, 2.728, 2.914, 3.216, 3.379, 3.715, 3.796, 4.226, 4.737]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(369, 9, 'Page 11', 'And sometimes, remembering is the strongest spell of all.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_9_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"sometimes,\", \"remembering\", \"is\", \"the\", \"strongest\", \"spell\", \"of\", \"all.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.882, 1.37, 1.486, 1.591, 2.009, 2.276, 2.38], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.836, 1.324, 1.44, 1.556, 1.985, 2.229, 2.322, 2.833]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(370, 10, 'Page 1', 'In the oldest part of town stood a library filled with towering shelves and dusty books. Most visitors came for stories, but one girl named Mira came for something else. She came for the feeling that something hidden waited between the pages.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"the\", \"oldest\", \"part\", \"of\", \"town\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"library\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"towering\", \"shelves\", \"and\", \"dusty\", \"books.\", \"Most\", \"visitors\", \"came\", \"for\", \"stories,\", \"but\", \"one\", \"girl\", \"named\", \"Mira\", \"came\", \"for\", \"something\", \"else.\", \"She\", \"came\", \"for\", \"the\", \"feeling\", \"that\", \"something\", \"hidden\", \"waited\", \"between\", \"the\", \"pages.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.406, 0.743, 0.952, 1.068, 1.428, 1.672, 1.753, 2.276, 2.601, 2.775, 3.286, 3.692, 3.831, 4.214, 5.399, 5.712, 6.165, 6.385, 6.548, 7.523, 7.744, 7.93, 8.15, 8.382, 8.789, 9.021, 9.183, 9.543, 10.6, 10.786, 11.006, 11.134, 11.262, 11.622, 11.807, 12.202, 12.562, 12.899, 13.212, 13.317], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.348, 0.697, 0.929, 1.01, 1.37, 1.637, 1.695, 2.194, 2.566, 2.728, 3.216, 3.657, 3.773, 4.156, 4.795, 5.654, 6.107, 6.351, 6.49, 7.245, 7.686, 7.895, 8.092, 8.348, 8.719, 8.986, 9.125, 9.485, 9.996, 10.728, 10.971, 11.099, 11.204, 11.575, 11.749, 12.132, 12.492, 12.852, 13.189, 13.282, 14.118]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(371, 10, 'Page 2', 'One afternoon, while tracing her fingers along the spines of forgotten books, she noticed a draft of cool air behind a tall shelf. Curious, she pushed gently.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"afternoon,\", \"while\", \"tracing\", \"her\", \"fingers\", \"along\", \"the\", \"spines\", \"of\", \"forgotten\", \"books,\", \"she\", \"noticed\", \"a\", \"draft\", \"of\", \"cool\", \"air\", \"behind\", \"a\", \"tall\", \"shelf.\", \"Curious,\", \"she\", \"pushed\", \"gently.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.824, 1.01, 1.405, 1.533, 1.916, 2.183, 2.299, 2.728, 2.844, 3.286, 4.017, 4.214, 4.54, 4.609, 4.923, 5.05, 5.364, 5.608, 5.909, 5.979, 6.258, 7.465, 8.115, 8.301, 8.615], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.801, 0.987, 1.347, 1.474, 1.869, 2.136, 2.252, 2.694, 2.786, 3.228, 3.808, 4.145, 4.505, 4.563, 4.888, 4.981, 5.294, 5.55, 5.851, 5.933, 6.188, 6.769, 8.081, 8.243, 8.568, 9.288]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(372, 10, 'Page 3', 'The shelf moved.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"shelf\", \"moved.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.615], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.534, 1.254]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(373, 10, 'Page 4', 'Behind it was a narrow wooden door carved with symbols of moons, keys, and feathers. It opened without a sound.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Behind\", \"it\", \"was\", \"a\", \"narrow\", \"wooden\", \"door\", \"carved\", \"with\", \"symbols\", \"of\", \"moons,\", \"keys,\", \"and\", \"feathers.\", \"It\", \"opened\", \"without\", \"a\", \"sound.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.557, 0.72, 0.906, 0.998, 1.312, 1.591, 1.892, 2.241, 2.392, 2.798, 2.961, 3.599, 4.098, 4.331, 5.445, 5.631, 6.002, 6.316, 6.397], \"end_times\": [0.488, 0.65, 0.848, 0.929, 1.277, 1.556, 1.8, 2.206, 2.357, 2.752, 2.868, 3.483, 4.063, 4.249, 4.934, 5.584, 5.944, 6.281, 6.339, 7.059]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(374, 10, 'Page 5', 'Beyond the door lay a vast room of floating lights. Books hovered in midair, their pages turning slowly as if moved by invisible hands. The air shimmered like morning mist.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Beyond\", \"the\", \"door\", \"lay\", \"a\", \"vast\", \"room\", \"of\", \"floating\", \"lights.\", \"Books\", \"hovered\", \"in\", \"midair,\", \"their\", \"pages\", \"turning\", \"slowly\", \"as\", \"if\", \"moved\", \"by\", \"invisible\", \"hands.\", \"The\", \"air\", \"shimmered\", \"like\", \"morning\", \"mist.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.569, 0.813, 0.998, 1.08, 1.486, 1.776, 1.892, 2.287, 3.146, 3.495, 3.866, 3.982, 4.714, 4.911, 5.306, 5.642, 6.072, 6.2, 6.374, 6.687, 6.85, 7.361, 8.231, 8.429, 8.673, 9.079, 9.3, 9.636], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.534, 0.755, 0.94, 1.022, 1.405, 1.718, 1.834, 2.229, 2.821, 3.437, 3.831, 3.924, 4.563, 4.876, 5.259, 5.584, 6.014, 6.153, 6.293, 6.641, 6.792, 7.314, 7.953, 8.359, 8.603, 9.033, 9.253, 9.578, 10.263]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(375, 10, 'Page 6', 'Each book in this hidden room held unfinished stories. Tales that had been abandoned. Dreams that had been forgotten.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Each\", \"book\", \"in\", \"this\", \"hidden\", \"room\", \"held\", \"unfinished\", \"stories.\", \"Tales\", \"that\", \"had\", \"been\", \"abandoned.\", \"Dreams\", \"that\", \"had\", \"been\", \"forgotten.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.685, 0.801, 0.975, 1.277, 1.614, 1.904, 2.403, 3.39, 3.785, 3.924, 4.029, 4.191, 5.004, 5.538, 5.689, 5.793, 5.968], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.639, 0.755, 0.929, 1.207, 1.533, 1.823, 2.38, 3.065, 3.75, 3.889, 4.005, 4.156, 4.795, 5.48, 5.654, 5.77, 5.921, 6.687]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(376, 10, 'Page 7', 'Mira stepped forward, and one book drifted toward her. As she touched it, words began to appear on the blank pages. They formed sentences about courage, about kindness, about hope.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"stepped\", \"forward,\", \"and\", \"one\", \"book\", \"drifted\", \"toward\", \"her.\", \"As\", \"she\", \"touched\", \"it,\", \"words\", \"began\", \"to\", \"appear\", \"on\", \"the\", \"blank\", \"pages.\", \"They\", \"formed\", \"sentences\", \"about\", \"courage,\", \"about\", \"kindness,\", \"about\", \"hope.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.766, 1.207, 1.416, 1.625, 1.858, 2.218, 2.531, 3.379, 3.587, 3.75, 4.098, 4.481, 4.865, 5.178, 5.329, 5.666, 5.77, 5.875, 6.177, 7.117, 7.338, 7.651, 8.231, 8.522, 9.265, 9.567, 10.437, 10.797], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.731, 1.184, 1.335, 1.591, 1.811, 2.183, 2.473, 2.868, 3.541, 3.68, 4.052, 4.331, 4.807, 5.12, 5.248, 5.608, 5.735, 5.84, 6.107, 6.792, 7.279, 7.605, 8.173, 8.464, 9.091, 9.52, 10.321, 10.728, 11.378]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(377, 10, 'Page 8', 'The more she believed in the story, the clearer the words became.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"more\", \"she\", \"believed\", \"in\", \"the\", \"story,\", \"the\", \"clearer\", \"the\", \"words\", \"became.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.464, 0.615, 0.929, 1.01, 1.115, 1.451, 1.579, 1.962, 2.078, 2.38], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.43, 0.557, 0.894, 0.975, 1.08, 1.428, 1.521, 1.904, 2.032, 2.322, 3.065]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(378, 10, 'Page 9', 'The room was not powered by magic alone. It responded to imagination.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"room\", \"was\", \"not\", \"powered\", \"by\", \"magic\", \"alone.\", \"It\", \"responded\", \"to\", \"imagination.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.441, 0.58, 0.766, 1.115, 1.277, 1.625, 2.299, 2.461, 2.891, 3.03], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.406, 0.534, 0.72, 1.08, 1.196, 1.579, 2.125, 2.415, 2.856, 2.949, 4.04]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(379, 10, 'Page 10', 'When she finally stepped back through the door, the shelf returned to its place. The library looked the same as always.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"When\", \"she\", \"finally\", \"stepped\", \"back\", \"through\", \"the\", \"door,\", \"the\", \"shelf\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"its\", \"place.\", \"The\", \"library\", \"looked\", \"the\", \"same\", \"as\", \"always.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.499, 0.859, 1.149, 1.37, 1.579, 1.672, 2.067, 2.218, 2.519, 2.868, 2.972, 3.146, 3.924, 4.098, 4.551, 4.783, 4.899, 5.155, 5.294], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.43, 0.813, 1.115, 1.324, 1.556, 1.649, 2.02, 2.171, 2.461, 2.844, 2.914, 3.088, 3.646, 4.04, 4.505, 4.76, 4.853, 5.12, 5.236, 5.991]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(380, 10, 'Page 11', 'But Mira understood something new.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"Mira\", \"understood\", \"something\", \"new.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.627, 1.08, 1.44], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.569, 1.045, 1.37, 1.95]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(381, 10, 'Page 12', 'Magic does not always hide in secret rooms.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Magic\", \"does\", \"not\", \"always\", \"hide\", \"in\", \"secret\", \"rooms.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.557, 0.731, 0.906, 1.207, 1.451, 1.579, 1.927], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.697, 0.859, 1.173, 1.416, 1.521, 1.881, 2.601]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(382, 10, 'Page 13', 'Sometimes it waits for someone brave enough to begin the next page.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_10_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Sometimes\", \"it\", \"waits\", \"for\", \"someone\", \"brave\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"begin\", \"the\", \"next\", \"page.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.65, 0.755, 1.033, 1.184, 1.509, 1.811, 2.136, 2.276, 2.543, 2.647, 2.937], \"end_times\": [0.604, 0.72, 0.987, 1.138, 1.474, 1.776, 2.078, 2.218, 2.496, 2.612, 2.868, 3.669]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(383, 11, 'Page 1', 'In a village surrounded by mountains, wind never stopped moving. It whispered through rooftops, carried leaves across the ground, and hummed softly at night.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"village\", \"surrounded\", \"by\", \"mountains,\", \"wind\", \"never\", \"stopped\", \"moving.\", \"It\", \"whispered\", \"through\", \"rooftops,\", \"carried\", \"leaves\", \"across\", \"the\", \"ground,\", \"and\", \"hummed\", \"softly\", \"at\", \"night.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.372, 0.755, 1.184, 1.358, 2.02, 2.415, 2.682, 3.053, 3.982, 4.156, 4.586, 4.853, 5.735, 6.13, 6.444, 6.78, 6.885, 7.546, 7.767, 8.127, 8.591, 8.707], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.313, 0.72, 1.149, 1.289, 1.904, 2.322, 2.624, 2.995, 3.541, 4.11, 4.551, 4.807, 5.608, 6.072, 6.409, 6.745, 6.85, 7.372, 7.709, 8.069, 8.533, 8.661, 9.195]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(384, 11, 'Page 2', 'Most people ignored it.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Most\", \"people\", \"ignored\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395, 0.662, 1.01], \"end_times\": [0.36, 0.627, 0.964, 1.347]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(385, 11, 'Page 3', 'But a quiet girl named Elin could hear something more within the wind. Beneath the sound of rustling trees, she sensed patterns—soft rhythms that felt almost like words.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"girl\", \"named\", \"Elin\", \"could\", \"hear\", \"something\", \"more\", \"within\", \"the\", \"wind.\", \"Beneath\", \"the\", \"sound\", \"of\", \"rustling\", \"trees,\", \"she\", \"sensed\", \"patternsu2014soft\", \"rhythms\", \"that\", \"felt\", \"almost\", \"like\", \"words.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.43, 0.859, 1.126, 1.405, 1.776, 1.985, 2.218, 2.624, 2.868, 3.17, 3.286, 4.586, 4.934, 5.05, 5.352, 5.48, 5.909, 6.432, 6.641, 7.001, 8.475, 8.882, 9.067, 9.358, 9.752, 9.95], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.372, 0.801, 1.068, 1.335, 1.718, 1.939, 2.159, 2.554, 2.833, 3.123, 3.239, 3.773, 4.899, 5.004, 5.306, 5.41, 5.851, 6.385, 6.571, 6.943, 8.429, 8.835, 9.021, 9.3, 9.706, 9.915, 11.006]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(386, 11, 'Page 4', 'One evening, as the sky turned deep violet, the wind changed. It grew restless and uneven. Leaves spun in strange directions. The mountains echoed with unfamiliar tones.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"evening,\", \"as\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"turned\", \"deep\", \"violet,\", \"the\", \"wind\", \"changed.\", \"It\", \"grew\", \"restless\", \"and\", \"uneven.\", \"Leaves\", \"spun\", \"in\", \"strange\", \"directions.\", \"The\", \"mountains\", \"echoed\", \"with\", \"unfamiliar\", \"tones.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.813, 1.033, 1.149, 1.521, 1.904, 2.171, 2.926, 3.1, 3.413, 4.505, 4.679, 4.899, 5.41, 5.584, 6.49, 6.815, 7.221, 7.372, 7.814, 8.928, 9.091, 9.509, 9.892, 10.101, 10.751], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.778, 0.975, 1.103, 1.451, 1.834, 2.101, 2.752, 3.042, 3.332, 4.063, 4.632, 4.841, 5.364, 5.503, 6.165, 6.78, 7.152, 7.303, 7.767, 8.649, 9.044, 9.439, 9.857, 10.031, 10.693, 11.517]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(387, 11, 'Page 5', 'Elin climbed to the highest hill and stood still. Instead of fighting the wind, she listened.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elin\", \"climbed\", \"to\", \"the\", \"highest\", \"hill\", \"and\", \"stood\", \"still.\", \"Instead\", \"of\", \"fighting\", \"the\", \"wind,\", \"she\", \"listened.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.72, 0.813, 0.94, 1.277, 1.486, 1.614, 1.881, 2.949, 3.344, 3.448, 3.762, 3.878, 4.203, 4.377], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.697, 0.766, 0.882, 1.231, 1.44, 1.556, 1.823, 2.345, 3.32, 3.402, 3.715, 3.831, 4.18, 4.307, 5.062]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(388, 11, 'Page 6', 'She realized the wind was tangled, caught between currents pulling in opposite directions. It was not angry. It was confused.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"realized\", \"the\", \"wind\", \"was\", \"tangled,\", \"caught\", \"between\", \"currents\", \"pulling\", \"in\", \"opposite\", \"directions.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"not\", \"angry.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"confused.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.778, 0.894, 1.138, 1.3, 1.939, 2.218, 2.566, 3.007, 3.355, 3.471, 3.878, 4.981, 5.132, 5.283, 5.503, 6.223, 6.374, 6.513], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.743, 0.848, 1.08, 1.242, 1.823, 2.183, 2.508, 2.949, 3.309, 3.413, 3.855, 4.656, 5.097, 5.224, 5.445, 6.072, 6.339, 6.455, 7.384]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(389, 11, 'Page 7', 'Elin closed her eyes and began to breathe slowly. In and out. Steady and calm.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elin\", \"closed\", \"her\", \"eyes\", \"and\", \"began\", \"to\", \"breathe\", \"slowly.\", \"In\", \"and\", \"out.\", \"Steady\", \"and\", \"calm.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.766, 0.917, 1.138, 1.265, 1.579, 1.707, 1.997, 2.635, 2.868, 3.03, 3.483, 3.901, 4.063], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.731, 0.848, 1.103, 1.219, 1.521, 1.637, 1.962, 2.485, 2.821, 2.961, 3.332, 3.843, 3.994, 4.598]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(390, 11, 'Page 8', 'Gradually, the wind followed her rhythm. The gusts softened. The currents aligned. The mountains fell quiet once more.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Gradually,\", \"the\", \"wind\", \"followed\", \"her\", \"rhythm.\", \"The\", \"gusts\", \"softened.\", \"The\", \"currents\", \"aligned.\", \"The\", \"mountains\", \"fell\", \"quiet\", \"once\", \"more.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.604, 0.72, 0.975, 1.347, 1.474, 2.02, 2.194, 2.554, 3.239, 3.413, 3.855, 4.795, 4.957, 5.41, 5.631, 6.014, 6.258], \"end_times\": [0.58, 0.673, 0.906, 1.3, 1.428, 1.846, 2.136, 2.508, 3.111, 3.367, 3.796, 4.412, 4.911, 5.352, 5.561, 5.956, 6.211, 6.734]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(391, 11, 'Page 9', 'From that day forward, Elin knew that magic was not about controlling the world.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"From\", \"that\", \"day\", \"forward,\", \"Elin\", \"knew\", \"that\", \"magic\", \"was\", \"not\", \"about\", \"controlling\", \"the\", \"world.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.534, 0.755, 1.265, 1.66, 1.916, 2.101, 2.519, 2.694, 2.891, 3.135, 3.669, 3.785], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.476, 0.685, 1.207, 1.591, 1.858, 2.043, 2.461, 2.635, 2.856, 3.088, 3.622, 3.738, 4.412]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(392, 11, 'Page 10', 'It was about understanding it.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"was\", \"about\", \"understanding\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.418, 0.65, 1.347], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.383, 0.604, 1.277, 1.765]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(393, 11, 'Page 11', 'And sometimes the strongest magic is simply learning to listen.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_11_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"sometimes\", \"the\", \"strongest\", \"magic\", \"is\", \"simply\", \"learning\", \"to\", \"listen.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.836, 0.952, 1.405, 1.811, 1.939, 2.276, 2.589, 2.705], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.789, 0.906, 1.358, 1.741, 1.904, 2.218, 2.543, 2.647, 3.39]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(394, 12, 'Page 1', 'Far in the north, where winter ruled nearly every season, stood a quiet village wrapped in endless snow. The houses were small and wooden, their rooftops heavy with frost. Smoke curled gently from chimneys, rising into pale skies that seemed almost silver in the cold light.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Far\", \"in\", \"the\", \"north,\", \"where\", \"winter\", \"ruled\", \"nearly\", \"every\", \"season,\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"village\", \"wrapped\", \"in\", \"endless\", \"snow.\", \"The\", \"houses\", \"were\", \"small\", \"and\", \"wooden,\", \"their\", \"rooftops\", \"heavy\", \"with\", \"frost.\", \"Smoke\", \"curled\", \"gently\", \"from\", \"chimneys,\", \"rising\", \"into\", \"pale\", \"skies\", \"that\", \"seemed\", \"almost\", \"silver\", \"in\", \"the\", \"cold\", \"light.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.453, 0.58, 1.219, 1.463, 1.823, 2.125, 2.473, 2.763, 3.692, 3.947, 4.029, 4.4, 4.795, 5.155, 5.317, 5.759, 7.291, 7.465, 7.848, 8.022, 8.359, 8.475, 9.358, 9.578, 10.124, 10.368, 10.553, 12.121, 12.55, 12.922, 13.293, 13.502, 14.652, 15.047, 15.267, 15.592, 16.057, 16.231, 16.544, 16.916, 17.31, 17.403, 17.519, 17.833], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.418, 0.522, 1.103, 1.428, 1.753, 2.09, 2.415, 2.705, 3.367, 3.924, 3.971, 4.342, 4.76, 5.12, 5.236, 5.712, 6.339, 7.407, 7.802, 7.976, 8.313, 8.429, 8.975, 9.543, 10.066, 10.333, 10.507, 11.169, 12.492, 12.875, 13.235, 13.433, 14.211, 15, 15.197, 15.557, 16.01, 16.184, 16.486, 16.858, 17.264, 17.369, 17.473, 17.775, 18.437]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(395, 12, 'Page 2', 'At the center of the village stood something extraordinary — a tall crystal carved entirely from ancient ice. It rose like a frozen flame, clear and sharp, yet glowing softly from within. At night it cast a gentle silver light across the snow, turning the village into something that looked almost like a dream.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"the\", \"center\", \"of\", \"the\", \"village\", \"stood\", \"something\", \"extraordinary\", \"u2014\", \"a\", \"tall\", \"crystal\", \"carved\", \"entirely\", \"from\", \"ancient\", \"ice.\", \"It\", \"rose\", \"like\", \"a\", \"frozen\", \"flame,\", \"clear\", \"and\", \"sharp,\", \"yet\", \"glowing\", \"softly\", \"from\", \"within.\", \"At\", \"night\", \"it\", \"cast\", \"a\", \"gentle\", \"silver\", \"light\", \"across\", \"the\", \"snow,\", \"turning\", \"the\", \"village\", \"into\", \"something\", \"that\", \"looked\", \"almost\", \"like\", \"a\", \"dream.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.395, 0.72, 0.801, 0.917, 1.335, 1.637, 2.032, 2.972, 3.506, 3.646, 3.982, 4.528, 4.888, 5.503, 5.712, 6.118, 7.303, 7.523, 7.918, 8.092, 8.173, 8.615, 9.485, 9.95, 10.147, 10.983, 11.227, 11.668, 12.179, 12.365, 14.234, 14.466, 14.803, 14.942, 15.302, 15.383, 15.766, 16.149, 16.416, 16.799, 16.915, 17.926, 18.309, 18.413, 18.808, 19.04, 19.377, 19.516, 19.772, 20.131, 20.306, 20.387], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.348, 0.673, 0.766, 0.871, 1.289, 1.591, 1.962, 2.798, 3.065, 3.564, 3.901, 4.435, 4.841, 5.445, 5.642, 6.06, 6.606, 7.442, 7.883, 8.069, 8.115, 8.545, 9.16, 9.868, 10.077, 10.704, 11.169, 11.587, 12.121, 12.318, 12.934, 14.396, 14.745, 14.884, 15.256, 15.325, 15.72, 16.091, 16.37, 16.753, 16.869, 17.484, 18.274, 18.378, 18.773, 18.97, 19.342, 19.481, 19.725, 20.085, 20.282, 20.329, 21.083]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(396, 12, 'Page 3', 'The villagers believed the crystal protected them. When blizzards approached, its glow grew brighter. When winds howled through the valley, the crystal shimmered steadily, as if pushing the storm away.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"villagers\", \"believed\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"protected\", \"them.\", \"When\", \"blizzards\", \"approached,\", \"its\", \"glow\", \"grew\", \"brighter.\", \"When\", \"winds\", \"howled\", \"through\", \"the\", \"valley,\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"shimmered\", \"steadily,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"pushing\", \"the\", \"storm\", \"away.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.697, 1.057, 1.173, 1.544, 2.02, 2.612, 2.833, 3.228, 3.738, 3.913, 4.226, 4.423, 5.213, 5.445, 5.747, 6.06, 6.269, 6.385, 6.722, 6.838, 7.198, 7.558, 8.081, 8.266, 8.406, 8.742, 8.858, 9.149], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.65, 1.01, 1.126, 1.498, 1.985, 2.334, 2.786, 3.193, 3.704, 3.866, 4.168, 4.389, 4.934, 5.399, 5.7, 6.037, 6.246, 6.339, 6.699, 6.792, 7.14, 7.523, 8.057, 8.208, 8.348, 8.707, 8.812, 9.102, 9.752]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(397, 12, 'Page 4', 'For generations, it had never failed.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"For\", \"generations,\", \"it\", \"had\", \"never\", \"failed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.964, 1.068, 1.207, 1.474], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.94, 1.033, 1.161, 1.405, 2.09]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(398, 12, 'Page 5', 'Until one winter, the glow began to fade.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Until\", \"one\", \"winter,\", \"the\", \"glow\", \"began\", \"to\", \"fade.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.499, 0.673, 1.01, 1.115, 1.347, 1.649, 1.776], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.639, 0.975, 1.08, 1.289, 1.602, 1.707, 2.368]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(399, 12, 'Page 6', 'At first, it was barely noticeable. The light was simply dimmer than usual. But as days passed, the crystal grew dull. Its silver radiance weakened until it stood cold and dark against the snow.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"first,\", \"it\", \"was\", \"barely\", \"noticeable.\", \"The\", \"light\", \"was\", \"simply\", \"dimmer\", \"than\", \"usual.\", \"But\", \"as\", \"days\", \"passed,\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"grew\", \"dull.\", \"Its\", \"silver\", \"radiance\", \"weakened\", \"until\", \"it\", \"stood\", \"cold\", \"and\", \"dark\", \"against\", \"the\", \"snow.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.604, 0.708, 0.848, 1.219, 2.032, 2.206, 2.426, 2.566, 2.949, 3.262, 3.471, 4.423, 4.644, 4.818, 5.166, 5.817, 5.968, 6.385, 6.641, 7.558, 7.767, 8.162, 8.707, 9.218, 9.52, 9.636, 9.938, 10.344, 10.495, 10.797, 11.157, 11.285], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.58, 0.673, 0.789, 1.149, 1.881, 2.148, 2.392, 2.519, 2.879, 3.216, 3.39, 4.04, 4.598, 4.737, 5.097, 5.7, 5.921, 6.327, 6.571, 7.117, 7.732, 8.092, 8.649, 9.16, 9.462, 9.59, 9.868, 10.298, 10.426, 10.751, 11.111, 11.227, 11.889]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(400, 12, 'Page 7', 'Soon after, the storms grew harsher.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Soon\", \"after,\", \"the\", \"storms\", \"grew\", \"harsher.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.72, 0.836, 1.173, 1.37], \"end_times\": [0.348, 0.685, 0.789, 1.138, 1.324, 1.997]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(401, 12, 'Page 8', 'The wind cut through the village like a blade. Snow piled against doors and windows, trapping families indoors. The sky remained gray for weeks, and the air felt heavier than ever before.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"wind\", \"cut\", \"through\", \"the\", \"village\", \"like\", \"a\", \"blade.\", \"Snow\", \"piled\", \"against\", \"doors\", \"and\", \"windows,\", \"trapping\", \"families\", \"indoors.\", \"The\", \"sky\", \"remained\", \"gray\", \"for\", \"weeks,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"air\", \"felt\", \"heavier\", \"than\", \"ever\", \"before.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.592, 0.789, 0.998, 1.091, 1.451, 1.625, 1.695, 2.496, 2.868, 3.262, 3.576, 3.889, 4.005, 4.69, 5.132, 5.573, 6.711, 6.885, 7.21, 7.558, 7.814, 7.988, 8.615, 8.8, 8.928, 9.172, 9.474, 9.868, 10.031, 10.252], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.522, 0.755, 0.975, 1.068, 1.416, 1.602, 1.649, 2.171, 2.798, 3.228, 3.529, 3.843, 3.959, 4.598, 5.062, 5.526, 6.269, 6.838, 7.129, 7.512, 7.755, 7.93, 8.464, 8.754, 8.87, 9.102, 9.404, 9.81, 9.985, 10.194, 10.913]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(402, 12, 'Page 9', 'Among the villagers lived a young child named Soren. He had grown up hearing stories about the crystal from his grandmother — stories that said it was not ordinary ice, but something older, something alive.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Among\", \"the\", \"villagers\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"young\", \"child\", \"named\", \"Soren.\", \"He\", \"had\", \"grown\", \"up\", \"hearing\", \"stories\", \"about\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"from\", \"his\", \"grandmother\", \"u2014\", \"stories\", \"that\", \"said\", \"it\", \"was\", \"not\", \"ordinary\", \"ice,\", \"but\", \"something\", \"older,\", \"something\", \"alive.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.557, 1.045, 1.265, 1.358, 1.602, 2.032, 2.345, 3.437, 3.576, 3.692, 3.924, 4.052, 4.365, 4.76, 4.969, 5.074, 5.457, 5.631, 5.77, 6.455, 6.711, 7.094, 7.268, 7.488, 7.581, 7.744, 7.988, 8.545, 8.893, 9.091, 9.497, 10.356, 10.728], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.522, 0.987, 1.242, 1.289, 1.533, 1.974, 2.276, 2.926, 3.541, 3.657, 3.889, 4.005, 4.296, 4.725, 4.934, 5.039, 5.41, 5.584, 5.724, 6.246, 6.536, 7.059, 7.221, 7.454, 7.546, 7.674, 7.93, 8.475, 8.858, 9.044, 9.416, 10.112, 10.67, 11.796]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(403, 12, 'Page 10', 'One afternoon, while the wind roared through narrow streets, Soren wrapped himself in layers of wool and stepped outside. Snow pressed against his boots with each step. The cold bit at his cheeks and made his eyes water, but he kept walking toward the silent crystal.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"afternoon,\", \"while\", \"the\", \"wind\", \"roared\", \"through\", \"narrow\", \"streets,\", \"Soren\", \"wrapped\", \"himself\", \"in\", \"layers\", \"of\", \"wool\", \"and\", \"stepped\", \"outside.\", \"Snow\", \"pressed\", \"against\", \"his\", \"boots\", \"with\", \"each\", \"step.\", \"The\", \"cold\", \"bit\", \"at\", \"his\", \"cheeks\", \"and\", \"made\", \"his\", \"eyes\", \"water,\", \"but\", \"he\", \"kept\", \"walking\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"silent\", \"crystal.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 1.196, 1.474, 1.602, 1.997, 2.368, 2.659, 2.972, 3.855, 4.214, 4.505, 4.911, 5.05, 5.399, 5.55, 6.002, 6.246, 6.594, 8.661, 9.021, 9.358, 9.694, 9.857, 10.194, 10.379, 10.588, 11.68, 11.865, 12.167, 12.365, 12.481, 12.643, 13.108, 13.305, 13.502, 13.677, 13.978, 14.977, 15.163, 15.267, 15.546, 15.975, 16.242, 16.358, 16.753], \"end_times\": [0.372, 1.103, 1.44, 1.544, 1.881, 2.334, 2.612, 2.914, 3.611, 4.18, 4.481, 4.853, 4.981, 5.352, 5.468, 5.828, 6.177, 6.56, 7.361, 8.951, 9.334, 9.636, 9.799, 10.147, 10.333, 10.542, 11.076, 11.807, 12.121, 12.318, 12.434, 12.585, 13.061, 13.247, 13.468, 13.607, 13.92, 14.536, 15.128, 15.209, 15.488, 15.917, 16.208, 16.312, 16.707, 17.508]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(404, 12, 'Page 11', 'It stood tall, unmoving.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"stood\", \"tall,\", \"unmoving.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.569, 0.929], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.534, 0.882, 1.672]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(405, 12, 'Page 12', 'He reached out and placed his small hands against its frozen surface. Instead of warmth or light, he felt emptiness. The crystal did not hum. It did not glow. It felt hollow.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"reached\", \"out\", \"and\", \"placed\", \"his\", \"small\", \"hands\", \"against\", \"its\", \"frozen\", \"surface.\", \"Instead\", \"of\", \"warmth\", \"or\", \"light,\", \"he\", \"felt\", \"emptiness.\", \"The\", \"crystal\", \"did\", \"not\", \"hum.\", \"It\", \"did\", \"not\", \"glow.\", \"It\", \"felt\", \"hollow.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.604, 0.766, 0.871, 1.173, 1.289, 1.614, 1.927, 2.287, 2.45, 2.868, 4.272, 4.656, 4.783, 5.19, 5.364, 6.014, 6.165, 6.42, 7.616, 7.779, 8.162, 8.324, 8.51, 9.253, 9.427, 9.59, 9.764, 10.461, 10.635, 10.879], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.569, 0.731, 0.836, 1.138, 1.254, 1.556, 1.881, 2.229, 2.403, 2.81, 3.576, 4.621, 4.714, 5.12, 5.294, 5.805, 6.095, 6.374, 7.175, 7.732, 8.104, 8.278, 8.464, 8.928, 9.381, 9.543, 9.718, 10.286, 10.588, 10.82, 11.564]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(406, 12, 'Page 13', 'Soren remembered something his grandmother once told him. She had said that true warmth was not always fire. Sometimes it was kindness passed from one heart to another.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Soren\", \"remembered\", \"something\", \"his\", \"grandmother\", \"once\", \"told\", \"him.\", \"She\", \"had\", \"said\", \"that\", \"true\", \"warmth\", \"was\", \"not\", \"always\", \"fire.\", \"Sometimes\", \"it\", \"was\", \"kindness\", \"passed\", \"from\", \"one\", \"heart\", \"to\", \"another.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.522, 0.94, 1.312, 1.451, 1.962, 2.206, 2.496, 2.949, 3.135, 3.297, 3.529, 3.692, 3.982, 4.365, 4.563, 4.772, 5.074, 6.316, 6.792, 6.885, 7.036, 7.523, 7.837, 8.081, 8.301, 8.568, 8.742], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.906, 1.242, 1.405, 1.892, 2.159, 2.438, 2.775, 3.077, 3.239, 3.495, 3.657, 3.936, 4.307, 4.493, 4.725, 5.016, 5.619, 6.757, 6.85, 6.978, 7.477, 7.802, 7.988, 8.243, 8.522, 8.649, 9.381]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(407, 12, 'Page 14', 'The crystal, she had whispered, listens.', 14, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_14.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"crystal,\", \"she\", \"had\", \"whispered,\", \"listens.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.848, 1.045, 1.173, 1.579], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.789, 0.987, 1.138, 1.556, 2.276]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(408, 12, 'Page 15', 'Soren did not know exactly what that meant, but he decided to act.', 15, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_15.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Soren\", \"did\", \"not\", \"know\", \"exactly\", \"what\", \"that\", \"meant,\", \"but\", \"he\", \"decided\", \"to\", \"act.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.639, 0.801, 0.987, 1.486, 1.649, 1.846, 2.322, 2.519, 2.635, 3.053, 3.181], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.592, 0.755, 0.917, 1.44, 1.614, 1.788, 2.206, 2.473, 2.566, 3.019, 3.111, 3.715]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(409, 12, 'Page 16', 'The next morning, before the sun rose, he began helping quietly. He shoveled heavy snow away from neighbors’ doors so they could step outside. He carried bundles of firewood to those who had run out. He left warm bread on doorsteps without waiting for thanks.', 16, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_16.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"next\", \"morning,\", \"before\", \"the\", \"sun\", \"rose,\", \"he\", \"began\", \"helping\", \"quietly.\", \"He\", \"shoveled\", \"heavy\", \"snow\", \"away\", \"from\", \"neighborsu2019\", \"doors\", \"so\", \"they\", \"could\", \"step\", \"outside.\", \"He\", \"carried\", \"bundles\", \"of\", \"firewood\", \"to\", \"those\", \"who\", \"had\", \"run\", \"out.\", \"He\", \"left\", \"warm\", \"bread\", \"on\", \"doorsteps\", \"without\", \"waiting\", \"for\", \"thanks.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.58, 1.103, 1.44, 1.556, 1.8, 2.589, 2.717, 3.03, 3.413, 4.818, 5.004, 5.41, 5.677, 6.026, 6.304, 6.49, 6.838, 7.384, 7.57, 7.709, 7.883, 8.139, 9.427, 9.59, 9.927, 10.298, 10.391, 10.89, 11.018, 11.25, 11.389, 11.54, 11.749, 12.783, 12.957, 13.224, 13.479, 13.758, 13.886, 14.489, 14.838, 15.151, 15.302], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.511, 1.057, 1.405, 1.509, 1.73, 2.345, 2.659, 2.961, 3.344, 4.122, 4.934, 5.364, 5.619, 5.956, 6.246, 6.432, 6.815, 7.268, 7.512, 7.686, 7.848, 8.081, 8.824, 9.532, 9.88, 10.252, 10.344, 10.855, 10.948, 11.227, 11.343, 11.494, 11.691, 12.179, 12.899, 13.154, 13.433, 13.7, 13.827, 14.431, 14.791, 15.093, 15.255, 16.022]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(410, 12, 'Page 17', 'Other villagers began to notice.', 17, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_17.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Other\", \"villagers\", \"began\", \"to\", \"notice.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.882, 1.184, 1.312], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.824, 1.138, 1.242, 2.043]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(411, 12, 'Page 18', 'They started helping too. Blankets were shared. Soup was delivered to the elderly. Children cleared paths together, laughing despite the wind.', 18, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_18.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"They\", \"started\", \"helping\", \"too.\", \"Blankets\", \"were\", \"shared.\", \"Soup\", \"was\", \"delivered\", \"to\", \"the\", \"elderly.\", \"Children\", \"cleared\", \"paths\", \"together,\", \"laughing\", \"despite\", \"the\", \"wind.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.615, 0.952, 1.579, 2.02, 2.183, 3.019, 3.332, 3.495, 3.878, 3.971, 4.11, 4.946, 5.41, 5.735, 6.118, 6.711, 7.175, 7.57, 7.674], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.58, 0.894, 1.37, 1.985, 2.148, 2.694, 3.286, 3.437, 3.855, 3.924, 4.04, 4.702, 5.352, 5.689, 6.072, 6.594, 7.105, 7.546, 7.639, 8.266]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(412, 12, 'Page 19', 'Days passed.', 19, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_19.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Days\", \"passed.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453], \"end_times\": [0.395, 1.161]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(413, 12, 'Page 20', 'One night, as the storm clouds gathered once more, a faint shimmer flickered at the heart of the crystal.', 20, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_20.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"night,\", \"as\", \"the\", \"storm\", \"clouds\", \"gathered\", \"once\", \"more,\", \"a\", \"faint\", \"shimmer\", \"flickered\", \"at\", \"the\", \"heart\", \"of\", \"the\", \"crystal.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.766, 0.929, 1.057, 1.393, 1.753, 2.194, 2.461, 3.135, 3.286, 3.599, 3.994, 4.412, 4.516, 4.656, 4.934, 5.039, 5.143], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.731, 0.871, 0.998, 1.347, 1.707, 2.136, 2.415, 2.856, 3.193, 3.529, 3.913, 4.377, 4.481, 4.586, 4.888, 4.992, 5.108, 5.851]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(414, 12, 'Page 21', 'It was small. Almost invisible.', 21, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_21.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"was\", \"small.\", \"Almost\", \"invisible.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.43, 0.906, 1.254], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.383, 0.859, 1.207, 1.997]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(415, 12, 'Page 22', 'But it was there.', 22, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_22.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"it\", \"was\", \"there.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.395, 0.569], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.36, 0.499, 1.207]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(416, 12, 'Page 23', 'As kindness spread through the village, the crystal’s glow slowly strengthened. The silver light returned, brighter each evening. The wind softened. Snow fell gently instead of violently. The storms no longer roared with the same fury.', 23, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_23.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"kindness\", \"spread\", \"through\", \"the\", \"village,\", \"the\", \"crystalu2019s\", \"glow\", \"slowly\", \"strengthened.\", \"The\", \"silver\", \"light\", \"returned,\", \"brighter\", \"each\", \"evening.\", \"The\", \"wind\", \"softened.\", \"Snow\", \"fell\", \"gently\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"violently.\", \"The\", \"storms\", \"no\", \"longer\", \"roared\", \"with\", \"the\", \"same\", \"fury.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.859, 1.173, 1.382, 1.486, 2.113, 2.264, 2.705, 3.053, 3.46, 4.841, 5.016, 5.352, 5.596, 6.165, 6.594, 6.827, 7.639, 7.825, 8.15, 9.125, 9.485, 9.752, 10.263, 10.646, 10.751, 11.97, 12.144, 12.585, 12.771, 13.131, 13.468, 13.63, 13.746, 14.083], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.836, 1.138, 1.358, 1.451, 1.997, 2.218, 2.659, 2.972, 3.402, 4.145, 4.957, 5.294, 5.538, 6.13, 6.536, 6.769, 7.314, 7.767, 8.057, 8.8, 9.404, 9.671, 10.182, 10.612, 10.693, 11.459, 12.086, 12.516, 12.69, 13.061, 13.444, 13.584, 13.7, 14.025, 14.768]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(417, 12, 'Page 24', 'The villagers gathered in the square one night and saw the crystal shining as it once had — perhaps even brighter.', 24, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_24.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"villagers\", \"gathered\", \"in\", \"the\", \"square\", \"one\", \"night\", \"and\", \"saw\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"shining\", \"as\", \"it\", \"once\", \"had\", \"u2014\", \"perhaps\", \"even\", \"brighter.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.72, 1.091, 1.173, 1.277, 1.602, 1.765, 2.055, 2.241, 2.473, 2.589, 3.019, 3.46, 3.599, 3.738, 4.005, 4.389, 4.748, 5.155, 5.375], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.662, 1.057, 1.138, 1.242, 1.544, 1.741, 1.997, 2.171, 2.415, 2.543, 2.937, 3.402, 3.541, 3.68, 3.959, 4.238, 4.47, 5.097, 5.329, 5.991]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(418, 12, 'Page 25', 'Soren stood quietly in the crowd, watching the light ripple through the snow.', 25, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_25.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Soren\", \"stood\", \"quietly\", \"in\", \"the\", \"crowd,\", \"watching\", \"the\", \"light\", \"ripple\", \"through\", \"the\", \"snow.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.789, 1.265, 1.37, 1.474, 2.043, 2.45, 2.554, 2.856, 3.135, 3.379, 3.483], \"end_times\": [0.488, 0.743, 1.219, 1.335, 1.44, 1.927, 2.403, 2.519, 2.786, 3.111, 3.344, 3.448, 4.04]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(419, 12, 'Page 26', 'The crystal had never drawn power from the cold.', 26, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_26.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"crystal\", \"had\", \"never\", \"drawn\", \"power\", \"from\", \"the\", \"cold.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.615, 0.755, 0.975, 1.242, 1.591, 1.753, 1.869], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.569, 0.708, 0.929, 1.184, 1.544, 1.718, 1.823, 2.508]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(420, 12, 'Page 27', 'It had drawn power from warmth.', 27, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_27.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"had\", \"drawn\", \"power\", \"from\", \"warmth.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.372, 0.673, 1.022, 1.231], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.348, 0.615, 0.975, 1.161, 1.904]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(421, 12, 'Page 28', 'And warmth had never been about temperature.', 28, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_28.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"warmth\", \"had\", \"never\", \"been\", \"about\", \"temperature.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.662, 0.789, 0.998, 1.138, 1.347], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.627, 0.755, 0.952, 1.115, 1.312, 2.136]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(422, 12, 'Page 29', 'It had always been about people.', 29, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_12_page_29.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"had\", \"always\", \"been\", \"about\", \"people.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.43, 0.72, 0.882, 1.126], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.383, 0.685, 0.859, 1.08, 1.718]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(423, 13, 'Page 1', 'Along the edge of a restless sea stood a small coastal town painted in shades of white and blue. Fishing boats rocked gently in the harbor, and seagulls filled the sky with wide, graceful circles.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Along\", \"the\", \"edge\", \"of\", \"a\", \"restless\", \"sea\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"small\", \"coastal\", \"town\", \"painted\", \"in\", \"shades\", \"of\", \"white\", \"and\", \"blue.\", \"Fishing\", \"boats\", \"rocked\", \"gently\", \"in\", \"the\", \"harbor,\", \"and\", \"seagulls\", \"filled\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"with\", \"wide,\", \"graceful\", \"circles.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.488, 0.639, 0.882, 0.998, 1.103, 1.591, 2.043, 2.334, 2.403, 2.763, 3.216, 3.762, 4.203, 4.331, 4.679, 4.807, 5.097, 5.236, 6.769, 7.163, 7.465, 7.837, 8.231, 8.336, 8.452, 9.091, 9.311, 9.799, 10.077, 10.194, 10.542, 10.751, 11.111, 11.587], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.557, 0.848, 0.952, 1.033, 1.544, 1.927, 2.299, 2.357, 2.694, 3.158, 3.553, 4.156, 4.272, 4.644, 4.737, 5.062, 5.19, 5.654, 7.117, 7.396, 7.767, 8.185, 8.301, 8.406, 8.916, 9.242, 9.741, 10.054, 10.147, 10.484, 10.681, 11.088, 11.517, 12.353]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(424, 13, 'Page 2', 'In this town lived a boy named Aris who loved color more than anything else. His hands were often stained with paint. He painted the sea at sunrise, the rooftops at sunset, and the quiet corners of the harbor when no one else was watching.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"this\", \"town\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"boy\", \"named\", \"Aris\", \"who\", \"loved\", \"color\", \"more\", \"than\", \"anything\", \"else.\", \"His\", \"hands\", \"were\", \"often\", \"stained\", \"with\", \"paint.\", \"He\", \"painted\", \"the\", \"sea\", \"at\", \"sunrise,\", \"the\", \"rooftops\", \"at\", \"sunset,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"quiet\", \"corners\", \"of\", \"the\", \"harbor\", \"when\", \"no\", \"one\", \"else\", \"was\", \"watching.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.488, 0.743, 0.94, 1.01, 1.219, 1.498, 2.043, 2.252, 2.519, 2.868, 3.065, 3.239, 3.622, 4.563, 4.772, 5.062, 5.236, 5.538, 5.886, 6.06, 7.14, 7.314, 7.663, 7.779, 7.976, 8.115, 8.94, 9.091, 9.625, 9.752, 10.612, 10.786, 10.89, 11.227, 11.575, 11.668, 11.796, 12.214, 12.411, 12.562, 12.701, 12.91, 13.084], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.43, 0.697, 0.917, 0.964, 1.161, 1.428, 1.962, 2.183, 2.461, 2.798, 3.03, 3.193, 3.564, 4.052, 4.725, 5.027, 5.19, 5.48, 5.863, 6.014, 6.536, 7.256, 7.628, 7.732, 7.941, 8.057, 8.824, 9.044, 9.578, 9.706, 10.437, 10.751, 10.855, 11.18, 11.54, 11.633, 11.738, 12.144, 12.365, 12.504, 12.678, 12.875, 13.026, 13.746]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(425, 13, 'Page 3', 'But one morning, something strange happened.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"one\", \"morning,\", \"something\", \"strange\", \"happened.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.511, 0.882, 1.231, 1.602], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.476, 0.848, 1.173, 1.567, 2.229]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(426, 13, 'Page 4', 'The birds stopped flying.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"birds\", \"stopped\", \"flying.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.534, 0.848], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.499, 0.813, 1.533]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(427, 13, 'Page 5', 'They stood along the shoreline in long silent rows. Their wings drooped at their sides. Even when the wind lifted off the water, they remained still.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"They\", \"stood\", \"along\", \"the\", \"shoreline\", \"in\", \"long\", \"silent\", \"rows.\", \"Their\", \"wings\", \"drooped\", \"at\", \"their\", \"sides.\", \"Even\", \"when\", \"the\", \"wind\", \"lifted\", \"off\", \"the\", \"water,\", \"they\", \"remained\", \"still.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.58, 0.824, 0.94, 1.463, 1.591, 1.927, 2.392, 3.228, 3.471, 3.796, 4.168, 4.261, 4.458, 5.387, 5.677, 5.828, 5.933, 6.177, 6.525, 6.711, 6.827, 7.43, 7.639, 8.022], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.546, 0.789, 0.894, 1.428, 1.521, 1.846, 2.334, 2.902, 3.425, 3.727, 4.133, 4.226, 4.412, 5.004, 5.642, 5.805, 5.898, 6.107, 6.478, 6.664, 6.78, 7.279, 7.581, 7.976, 8.638]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(428, 13, 'Page 6', 'The sky felt empty.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"sky\", \"felt\", \"empty.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.569, 0.813], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.499, 0.755, 1.44]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(429, 13, 'Page 7', 'Aris walked closer and noticed something unsettling. The birds’ wings looked faded. Not broken, not injured — just dull. As if the shine had drained away from them.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Aris\", \"walked\", \"closer\", \"and\", \"noticed\", \"something\", \"unsettling.\", \"The\", \"birdsu2019\", \"wings\", \"looked\", \"faded.\", \"Not\", \"broken,\", \"not\", \"injured\", \"u2014\", \"just\", \"dull.\", \"As\", \"if\", \"the\", \"shine\", \"had\", \"drained\", \"away\", \"from\", \"them.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.499, 0.789, 1.277, 1.451, 1.823, 2.206, 3.379, 3.553, 3.866, 4.191, 4.435, 5.329, 5.584, 6.223, 6.467, 7.024, 7.279, 7.605, 8.812, 9.021, 9.16, 9.276, 9.636, 9.776, 10.054, 10.275, 10.461], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.731, 1.196, 1.393, 1.765, 2.136, 2.937, 3.506, 3.831, 4.145, 4.389, 5.004, 5.526, 6.107, 6.409, 6.873, 7.105, 7.512, 8.115, 8.963, 9.102, 9.23, 9.601, 9.741, 10.031, 10.228, 10.414, 10.867]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(430, 13, 'Page 8', 'He returned home, troubled.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"returned\", \"home,\", \"troubled.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.685, 0.894], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.65, 0.871, 1.533]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(431, 13, 'Page 9', 'In his small room overlooking the sea, he began mixing paints unlike any he had created before. He blended silver with soft blues. He added hints of sunrise gold and pale lavender. These were not colors he could see clearly — they were colors he felt.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"his\", \"small\", \"room\", \"overlooking\", \"the\", \"sea,\", \"he\", \"began\", \"mixing\", \"paints\", \"unlike\", \"any\", \"he\", \"had\", \"created\", \"before.\", \"He\", \"blended\", \"silver\", \"with\", \"soft\", \"blues.\", \"He\", \"added\", \"hints\", \"of\", \"sunrise\", \"gold\", \"and\", \"pale\", \"lavender.\", \"These\", \"were\", \"not\", \"colors\", \"he\", \"could\", \"see\", \"clearly\", \"u2014\", \"they\", \"were\", \"colors\", \"he\", \"felt.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.453, 0.789, 1.068, 1.591, 1.718, 2.508, 2.635, 2.972, 3.355, 3.704, 4.063, 4.354, 4.458, 4.598, 5.027, 5.991, 6.188, 6.629, 7.036, 7.221, 7.581, 8.51, 8.684, 8.986, 9.3, 9.439, 9.95, 10.403, 10.623, 10.902, 12.051, 12.307, 12.469, 12.655, 13.038, 13.131, 13.305, 13.491, 14.129, 14.431, 14.594, 14.745, 15.139, 15.279], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.406, 0.731, 0.998, 1.544, 1.66, 2.183, 2.577, 2.902, 3.286, 3.646, 4.005, 4.284, 4.412, 4.551, 4.981, 5.55, 6.118, 6.548, 6.978, 7.163, 7.512, 8.185, 8.626, 8.928, 9.242, 9.369, 9.903, 10.321, 10.565, 10.867, 11.54, 12.283, 12.434, 12.597, 12.98, 13.084, 13.27, 13.444, 13.92, 14.187, 14.559, 14.71, 15.07, 15.209, 15.836]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(432, 13, 'Page 10', 'That afternoon, he returned to the shore.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"That\", \"afternoon,\", \"he\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"the\", \"shore.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.836, 0.975, 1.335, 1.416, 1.533], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.801, 0.894, 1.312, 1.382, 1.486, 2.136]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(433, 13, 'Page 11', 'Instead of touching the birds, he painted in the air around them. Gentle strokes traced invisible lines along their wings. He imagined restoring not feathers, but courage. Not flight, but memory.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Instead\", \"of\", \"touching\", \"the\", \"birds,\", \"he\", \"painted\", \"in\", \"the\", \"air\", \"around\", \"them.\", \"Gentle\", \"strokes\", \"traced\", \"invisible\", \"lines\", \"along\", \"their\", \"wings.\", \"He\", \"imagined\", \"restoring\", \"not\", \"feathers,\", \"but\", \"courage.\", \"Not\", \"flight,\", \"but\", \"memory.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.557, 0.871, 0.987, 1.753, 1.916, 2.38, 2.519, 2.67, 2.984, 3.32, 4.423, 4.853, 5.329, 5.77, 6.293, 6.699, 6.989, 7.175, 8.266, 8.44, 8.951, 9.509, 9.752, 10.565, 10.786, 11.691, 11.958, 12.701, 12.934], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.511, 0.824, 0.94, 1.579, 1.834, 2.322, 2.461, 2.589, 2.914, 3.274, 3.727, 4.807, 5.271, 5.712, 6.246, 6.653, 6.943, 7.129, 7.755, 8.382, 8.893, 9.439, 9.694, 10.414, 10.728, 11.447, 11.889, 12.527, 12.875, 13.607]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(434, 13, 'Page 12', 'The townspeople saw only a boy moving a brush through empty space.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"townspeople\", \"saw\", \"only\", \"a\", \"boy\", \"moving\", \"a\", \"brush\", \"through\", \"empty\", \"space.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.848, 1.068, 1.335, 1.405, 1.672, 1.974, 2.043, 2.334, 2.589, 2.902], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.813, 0.998, 1.277, 1.358, 1.602, 1.927, 1.997, 2.299, 2.543, 2.844, 3.622]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(435, 13, 'Page 13', 'But something shifted.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"something\", \"shifted.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.627], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.569, 1.3]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(436, 13, 'Page 14', 'One bird lifted its wings slightly. Another stretched, uncertain but curious. A breeze passed through the line of still figures, and this time one bird leaped into the air.', 14, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_14.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"bird\", \"lifted\", \"its\", \"wings\", \"slightly.\", \"Another\", \"stretched,\", \"uncertain\", \"but\", \"curious.\", \"A\", \"breeze\", \"passed\", \"through\", \"the\", \"line\", \"of\", \"still\", \"figures,\", \"and\", \"this\", \"time\", \"one\", \"bird\", \"leaped\", \"into\", \"the\", \"air.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.708, 1.057, 1.196, 1.44, 2.148, 2.624, 3.274, 3.808, 3.982, 4.981, 5.143, 5.526, 5.828, 6.06, 6.177, 6.455, 6.56, 6.861, 7.535, 7.744, 7.941, 8.371, 8.661, 8.986, 9.288, 9.509, 9.648], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.65, 1.01, 1.161, 1.416, 1.974, 2.554, 3.181, 3.75, 3.936, 4.598, 5.074, 5.48, 5.805, 6.037, 6.13, 6.432, 6.513, 6.792, 7.419, 7.686, 7.883, 8.301, 8.615, 8.916, 9.253, 9.439, 9.578, 10.124]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(437, 13, 'Page 15', 'Then another.', 15, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_15.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Then\", \"another.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36], \"end_times\": [0.302, 1.022]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(438, 13, 'Page 16', 'Soon the sky filled with motion again. Wings cut through wind. The harbor echoed with familiar sounds.', 16, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_16.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Soon\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"motion\", \"again.\", \"Wings\", \"cut\", \"through\", \"wind.\", \"The\", \"harbor\", \"echoed\", \"with\", \"familiar\", \"sounds.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.511, 0.824, 1.126, 1.289, 1.614, 2.322, 2.74, 2.972, 3.239, 3.936, 4.11, 4.458, 4.783, 4.957, 5.41], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.476, 0.731, 1.091, 1.242, 1.567, 1.997, 2.67, 2.937, 3.193, 3.611, 4.052, 4.389, 4.76, 4.911, 5.352, 6.177]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(439, 13, 'Page 17', 'Aris watched quietly as the birds rose higher, circling above the sea with renewed strength.', 17, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_17.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Aris\", \"watched\", \"quietly\", \"as\", \"the\", \"birds\", \"rose\", \"higher,\", \"circling\", \"above\", \"the\", \"sea\", \"with\", \"renewed\", \"strength.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.778, 1.231, 1.37, 1.474, 1.776, 2.02, 2.635, 3.088, 3.344, 3.471, 3.704, 3.889, 4.272], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.731, 1.184, 1.312, 1.44, 1.718, 1.974, 2.461, 3.042, 3.309, 3.413, 3.646, 3.831, 4.226, 4.969]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(440, 13, 'Page 18', 'He understood something then.', 18, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_18.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"understood\", \"something\", \"then.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.743, 1.091], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.708, 1.045, 1.579]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(441, 13, 'Page 19', 'Art does not always change the world in visible ways.', 19, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_19.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Art\", \"does\", \"not\", \"always\", \"change\", \"the\", \"world\", \"in\", \"visible\", \"ways.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.522, 0.72, 1.01, 1.358, 1.474, 1.776, 1.904, 2.322], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.476, 0.673, 0.952, 1.324, 1.428, 1.718, 1.846, 2.276, 3.019]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(442, 13, 'Page 20', 'Sometimes it restores what cannot be seen.', 20, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_20.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Sometimes\", \"it\", \"restores\", \"what\", \"cannot\", \"be\", \"seen.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.592, 0.685, 1.126, 1.289, 1.637, 1.788], \"end_times\": [0.557, 0.65, 1.091, 1.242, 1.591, 1.741, 2.415]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(443, 13, 'Page 21', 'And sometimes what is invisible is what matters most.', 21, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_13_page_21.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"sometimes\", \"what\", \"is\", \"invisible\", \"is\", \"what\", \"matters\", \"most.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.743, 0.917, 1.057, 1.707, 1.858, 2.043, 2.392], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.708, 0.871, 0.998, 1.649, 1.811, 1.997, 2.334, 3.019]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(444, 14, 'Page 1', 'Behind an old stone wall at the edge of town lay a forgotten garden. During the day it looked abandoned. The soil appeared dry, the vines brittle, the paths empty and silent.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Behind\", \"an\", \"old\", \"stone\", \"wall\", \"at\", \"the\", \"edge\", \"of\", \"town\", \"lay\", \"a\", \"forgotten\", \"garden.\", \"During\", \"the\", \"day\", \"it\", \"looked\", \"abandoned.\", \"The\", \"soil\", \"appeared\", \"dry,\", \"the\", \"vines\", \"brittle,\", \"the\", \"paths\", \"empty\", \"and\", \"silent.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.662, 0.882, 1.231, 1.521, 1.614, 1.741, 1.916, 2.032, 2.368, 2.554, 2.635, 3.088, 4.307, 4.632, 4.748, 5.12, 5.271, 5.526, 6.525, 6.699, 7.012, 7.338, 7.941, 8.104, 8.499, 9.23, 9.381, 9.799, 10.194, 10.344], \"end_times\": [0.488, 0.604, 0.824, 1.196, 1.474, 1.579, 1.683, 1.892, 1.974, 2.299, 2.508, 2.577, 3.03, 3.704, 4.586, 4.702, 5.039, 5.224, 5.492, 6.2, 6.641, 6.954, 7.314, 7.825, 8.046, 8.429, 9.021, 9.323, 9.729, 10.136, 10.275, 11.099]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(445, 14, 'Page 2', 'Children passed by without noticing it.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Children\", \"passed\", \"by\", \"without\", \"noticing\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.488, 0.766, 0.929, 1.231, 1.66], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.731, 0.871, 1.184, 1.602, 2.043]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(446, 14, 'Page 3', 'But at midnight, when the world grew quiet and the moon climbed high, something extraordinary happened.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"at\", \"midnight,\", \"when\", \"the\", \"world\", \"grew\", \"quiet\", \"and\", \"the\", \"moon\", \"climbed\", \"high,\", \"something\", \"extraordinary\", \"happened.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.395, 1.068, 1.277, 1.382, 1.625, 1.811, 2.31, 2.485, 2.589, 2.833, 3.181, 3.913, 4.307, 5.05], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.337, 0.952, 1.242, 1.347, 1.579, 1.776, 2.241, 2.438, 2.554, 2.775, 3.135, 3.587, 4.249, 5.004, 5.759]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(447, 14, 'Page 4', 'Silver vines began to stir. They crept slowly along trellises, weaving delicate patterns. Buds formed where nothing had been before. One by one, luminous flowers unfolded, glowing softly under the moonlight. The air filled with a faint, sweet fragrance that drifted beyond the walls.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Silver\", \"vines\", \"began\", \"to\", \"stir.\", \"They\", \"crept\", \"slowly\", \"along\", \"trellises,\", \"weaving\", \"delicate\", \"patterns.\", \"Buds\", \"formed\", \"where\", \"nothing\", \"had\", \"been\", \"before.\", \"One\", \"by\", \"one,\", \"luminous\", \"flowers\", \"unfolded,\", \"glowing\", \"softly\", \"under\", \"the\", \"moonlight.\", \"The\", \"air\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"a\", \"faint,\", \"sweet\", \"fragrance\", \"that\", \"drifted\", \"beyond\", \"the\", \"walls.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.522, 0.906, 1.231, 1.347, 2.752, 2.961, 3.274, 3.715, 4.017, 4.992, 5.422, 5.863, 7.094, 7.5, 7.848, 8.046, 8.348, 8.499, 8.707, 9.892, 10.159, 10.368, 10.983, 11.482, 11.935, 12.957, 13.41, 13.897, 14.106, 14.222, 15.406, 15.615, 15.836, 16.149, 16.312, 16.416, 16.765, 17.09, 17.647, 17.845, 18.262, 18.588, 18.692], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.836, 1.173, 1.289, 1.939, 2.914, 3.216, 3.657, 3.959, 4.865, 5.341, 5.828, 6.583, 7.43, 7.814, 7.999, 8.301, 8.452, 8.649, 9.288, 10.112, 10.286, 10.809, 11.424, 11.877, 12.713, 13.328, 13.839, 14.06, 14.176, 14.896, 15.546, 15.778, 16.115, 16.277, 16.347, 16.73, 17.032, 17.601, 17.798, 18.216, 18.541, 18.657, 19.412]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(448, 14, 'Page 5', 'The garden lived only in darkness.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"garden\", \"lived\", \"only\", \"in\", \"darkness.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.546, 0.789, 1.057, 1.173], \"end_times\": [0.209, 0.499, 0.743, 0.998, 1.126, 1.95]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(449, 14, 'Page 6', 'A curious girl named Liora discovered it by accident one sleepless night. She had followed a flicker of pale light and found the gate slightly open.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"curious\", \"girl\", \"named\", \"Liora\", \"discovered\", \"it\", \"by\", \"accident\", \"one\", \"sleepless\", \"night.\", \"She\", \"had\", \"followed\", \"a\", \"flicker\", \"of\", \"pale\", \"light\", \"and\", \"found\", \"the\", \"gate\", \"slightly\", \"open.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.743, 1.022, 1.289, 1.753, 2.218, 2.322, 2.496, 3.053, 3.262, 3.762, 4.667, 4.853, 4.981, 5.317, 5.41, 5.782, 5.921, 6.258, 6.618, 6.827, 7.059, 7.163, 7.396, 7.814], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.685, 0.952, 1.231, 1.683, 2.183, 2.276, 2.426, 2.984, 3.228, 3.715, 4.156, 4.807, 4.934, 5.294, 5.341, 5.724, 5.851, 6.211, 6.548, 6.757, 7.024, 7.129, 7.372, 7.755, 8.406]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(450, 14, 'Page 7', 'She stepped inside and waited.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"stepped\", \"inside\", \"and\", \"waited.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.604, 1.033, 1.149], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.569, 0.998, 1.103, 1.718]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(451, 14, 'Page 8', 'When the first flower bloomed before her eyes, it did not burst open dramatically. It unfolded carefully, petal by petal, as if unsure whether it was safe to grow.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"When\", \"the\", \"first\", \"flower\", \"bloomed\", \"before\", \"her\", \"eyes,\", \"it\", \"did\", \"not\", \"burst\", \"open\", \"dramatically.\", \"It\", \"unfolded\", \"carefully,\", \"petal\", \"by\", \"petal,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"unsure\", \"whether\", \"it\", \"was\", \"safe\", \"to\", \"grow.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.453, 0.755, 1.149, 1.556, 1.892, 2.043, 2.624, 2.775, 2.914, 3.077, 3.39, 3.646, 4.888, 5.074, 5.55, 6.42, 6.769, 6.931, 7.581, 7.79, 7.953, 8.371, 8.661, 8.754, 8.893, 9.172, 9.288], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.406, 0.697, 1.091, 1.509, 1.846, 1.974, 2.508, 2.74, 2.879, 3.03, 3.332, 3.611, 4.377, 5.016, 5.503, 6.177, 6.711, 6.873, 7.43, 7.732, 7.872, 8.336, 8.603, 8.719, 8.847, 9.137, 9.23, 9.799]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(452, 14, 'Page 9', 'Liora returned the next night. And the next.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Liora\", \"returned\", \"the\", \"next\", \"night.\", \"And\", \"the\", \"next.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.615, 0.975, 1.08, 1.335, 1.776, 1.974, 2.078], \"end_times\": [0.546, 0.94, 1.045, 1.277, 1.649, 1.916, 2.043, 2.786]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(453, 14, 'Page 10', 'She did not rush the blooms. She did not demand brighter light. She simply cared for the soil during the day when nothing appeared to grow. She watered the ground that looked lifeless. She trimmed vines that seemed dry.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"did\", \"not\", \"rush\", \"the\", \"blooms.\", \"She\", \"did\", \"not\", \"demand\", \"brighter\", \"light.\", \"She\", \"simply\", \"cared\", \"for\", \"the\", \"soil\", \"during\", \"the\", \"day\", \"when\", \"nothing\", \"appeared\", \"to\", \"grow.\", \"She\", \"watered\", \"the\", \"ground\", \"that\", \"looked\", \"lifeless.\", \"She\", \"trimmed\", \"vines\", \"that\", \"seemed\", \"dry.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.476, 0.697, 0.975, 1.091, 2.148, 2.322, 2.485, 2.705, 3.239, 3.599, 4.493, 4.714, 5.097, 5.433, 5.573, 5.7, 6.084, 6.362, 6.478, 6.769, 6.978, 7.291, 7.674, 7.802, 8.882, 9.091, 9.462, 9.578, 9.973, 10.124, 10.391, 11.505, 11.714, 12.098, 12.562, 12.748, 13.084], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.418, 0.639, 0.917, 1.045, 1.707, 2.276, 2.438, 2.647, 3.158, 3.541, 4.052, 4.644, 5.039, 5.399, 5.526, 5.642, 6.014, 6.327, 6.432, 6.711, 6.92, 7.245, 7.639, 7.732, 8.371, 9.021, 9.439, 9.532, 9.927, 10.089, 10.321, 11.122, 11.645, 12.04, 12.504, 12.701, 13.015, 13.839]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(454, 14, 'Page 11', 'For weeks, nothing changed in daylight.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"For\", \"weeks,\", \"nothing\", \"changed\", \"in\", \"daylight.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.662, 0.975, 1.393, 1.509], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.627, 0.917, 1.335, 1.451, 2.229]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(455, 14, 'Page 12', 'But at midnight, the blooms grew stronger. The glow spread wider. The garden began to pulse with gentle light like a quiet heartbeat.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"at\", \"midnight,\", \"the\", \"blooms\", \"grew\", \"stronger.\", \"The\", \"glow\", \"spread\", \"wider.\", \"The\", \"garden\", \"began\", \"to\", \"pulse\", \"with\", \"gentle\", \"light\", \"like\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"heartbeat.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.406, 1.103, 1.254, 1.66, 1.881, 2.984, 3.158, 3.611, 4.005, 5.016, 5.19, 5.526, 5.793, 5.909, 6.304, 6.513, 6.908, 7.245, 7.43, 7.512, 7.895], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.348, 0.987, 1.207, 1.602, 1.834, 2.543, 3.111, 3.483, 3.947, 4.574, 5.132, 5.468, 5.747, 5.84, 6.258, 6.444, 6.861, 7.175, 7.407, 7.454, 7.848, 8.731]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(456, 14, 'Page 13', 'Liora realized that the garden did not bloom because it was commanded to. It bloomed because it was tended with patience.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Liora\", \"realized\", \"that\", \"the\", \"garden\", \"did\", \"not\", \"bloom\", \"because\", \"it\", \"was\", \"commanded\", \"to.\", \"It\", \"bloomed\", \"because\", \"it\", \"was\", \"tended\", \"with\", \"patience.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.604, 1.045, 1.184, 1.3, 1.66, 1.823, 2.009, 2.334, 2.635, 2.728, 2.891, 3.379, 4.156, 4.365, 4.807, 5.12, 5.213, 5.375, 5.747, 5.921], \"end_times\": [0.546, 1.022, 1.149, 1.254, 1.602, 1.776, 1.962, 2.276, 2.612, 2.694, 2.833, 3.332, 3.773, 4.307, 4.748, 5.085, 5.178, 5.317, 5.7, 5.875, 6.827]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(457, 14, 'Page 14', 'Some growth does not seek attention.', 14, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_14.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Some\", \"growth\", \"does\", \"not\", \"seek\", \"attention.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.697, 0.894, 1.068, 1.289], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.65, 0.848, 1.022, 1.242, 2.043]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(458, 14, 'Page 15', 'Some beauty reveals itself only when the world is still.', 15, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_15.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Some\", \"beauty\", \"reveals\", \"itself\", \"only\", \"when\", \"the\", \"world\", \"is\", \"still.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395, 0.685, 1.057, 1.451, 1.707, 1.846, 1.95, 2.206, 2.334], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.627, 1.01, 1.382, 1.672, 1.823, 1.916, 2.159, 2.287, 2.926]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(459, 14, 'Page 16', 'And sometimes the greatest magic happens in silence, far from applause.', 16, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_14_page_16.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"sometimes\", \"the\", \"greatest\", \"magic\", \"happens\", \"in\", \"silence,\", \"far\", \"from\", \"applause.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.778, 0.894, 1.254, 1.579, 1.974, 2.125, 2.972, 3.251, 3.448], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.731, 0.848, 1.196, 1.533, 1.927, 2.055, 2.728, 3.181, 3.402, 4.226]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(460, 36, 'Page 1', 'In a quiet city filled with tall buildings and crowded streets lived a boy named Elias. To everyone else, he seemed ordinary. He went to school, carried a backpack too heavy for his shoulders, and walked past the same bakery every morning.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"city\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"tall\", \"buildings\", \"and\", \"crowded\", \"streets\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"boy\", \"named\", \"Elias.\", \"To\", \"everyone\", \"else,\", \"he\", \"seemed\", \"ordinary.\", \"He\", \"went\", \"to\", \"school,\", \"carried\", \"a\", \"backpack\", \"too\", \"heavy\", \"for\", \"his\", \"shoulders,\", \"and\", \"walked\", \"past\", \"the\", \"same\", \"bakery\", \"every\", \"morning.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.372, 0.731, 1.045, 1.312, 1.474, 1.718, 2.136, 2.276, 2.647, 3.053, 3.309, 3.379, 3.657, 3.901, 4.957, 5.132, 5.526, 5.793, 5.909, 6.2, 7.082, 7.233, 7.43, 7.535, 8.301, 8.626, 8.696, 9.172, 9.381, 9.648, 9.81, 9.938, 10.658, 10.855, 11.169, 11.471, 11.587, 11.842, 12.237, 12.469], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.313, 0.673, 0.975, 1.289, 1.428, 1.672, 2.101, 2.218, 2.589, 2.984, 3.274, 3.332, 3.587, 3.855, 4.574, 5.062, 5.492, 5.77, 5.851, 6.142, 6.838, 7.187, 7.396, 7.488, 8.057, 8.603, 8.649, 9.114, 9.311, 9.59, 9.752, 9.903, 10.507, 10.797, 11.111, 11.424, 11.54, 11.807, 12.179, 12.423, 13.003]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(461, 36, 'Page 2', 'But Elias had a secret. He could pause time.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"Elias\", \"had\", \"a\", \"secret.\", \"He\", \"could\", \"pause\", \"time.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.72, 0.871, 0.952, 1.602, 1.753, 1.927, 2.31], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.673, 0.836, 0.906, 1.451, 1.707, 1.892, 2.264, 2.926]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(462, 36, 'Page 3', 'Not for long—only for a few seconds. When he clicked his tongue twice, the world stopped. A dropped coin would freeze in mid-air. A spilled cup of water would hover. People would stand perfectly still.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Not\", \"for\", \"longu2014only\", \"for\", \"a\", \"few\", \"seconds.\", \"When\", \"he\", \"clicked\", \"his\", \"tongue\", \"twice,\", \"the\", \"world\", \"stopped.\", \"A\", \"dropped\", \"coin\", \"would\", \"freeze\", \"in\", \"mid-air.\", \"A\", \"spilled\", \"cup\", \"of\", \"water\", \"would\", \"hover.\", \"People\", \"would\", \"stand\", \"perfectly\", \"still.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.383, 0.557, 1.428, 1.579, 1.66, 1.846, 3.181, 3.402, 3.518, 3.82, 3.959, 4.226, 4.876, 5.027, 5.329, 6.246, 6.397, 6.78, 7.094, 7.303, 7.628, 7.755, 8.568, 8.719, 9.056, 9.276, 9.404, 9.671, 9.845, 10.739, 11.053, 11.238, 11.552, 12.063], \"end_times\": [0.337, 0.499, 1.37, 1.533, 1.602, 1.8, 2.485, 3.355, 3.46, 3.785, 3.913, 4.203, 4.76, 4.981, 5.271, 5.921, 6.327, 6.722, 7.036, 7.245, 7.593, 7.697, 8.29, 8.638, 9.021, 9.218, 9.323, 9.636, 9.81, 10.298, 11.018, 11.204, 11.482, 12.005, 12.957]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(463, 36, 'Page 4', 'Elias mostly used it for small things. He caught falling apples before they hit the ground. He tied his shoelaces without holding up the line behind him. He liked the quiet feeling of those paused seconds.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elias\", \"mostly\", \"used\", \"it\", \"for\", \"small\", \"things.\", \"He\", \"caught\", \"falling\", \"apples\", \"before\", \"they\", \"hit\", \"the\", \"ground.\", \"He\", \"tied\", \"his\", \"shoelaces\", \"without\", \"holding\", \"up\", \"the\", \"line\", \"behind\", \"him.\", \"He\", \"liked\", \"the\", \"quiet\", \"feeling\", \"of\", \"those\", \"paused\", \"seconds.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.639, 1.033, 1.254, 1.358, 1.509, 1.834, 2.949, 3.111, 3.367, 3.738, 4.063, 4.342, 4.493, 4.667, 4.772, 5.863, 6.026, 6.327, 6.444, 7.036, 7.349, 7.651, 7.767, 7.895, 8.162, 8.533, 9.416, 9.613, 9.915, 10.031, 10.461, 10.832, 10.925, 11.18, 11.68], \"end_times\": [0.557, 0.964, 1.219, 1.312, 1.451, 1.776, 2.438, 3.053, 3.32, 3.68, 4.017, 4.307, 4.447, 4.632, 4.737, 5.259, 5.968, 6.293, 6.42, 6.989, 7.291, 7.616, 7.732, 7.837, 8.127, 8.475, 8.812, 9.532, 9.857, 9.985, 10.403, 10.786, 10.879, 11.122, 11.598, 12.446]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(464, 36, 'Page 5', 'One afternoon, during a busy festival in the city square, a strong wind suddenly tossed a large striped tent into the air. The heavy metal poles swung dangerously over a crowd of surprised people.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"afternoon,\", \"during\", \"a\", \"busy\", \"festival\", \"in\", \"the\", \"city\", \"square,\", \"a\", \"strong\", \"wind\", \"suddenly\", \"tossed\", \"a\", \"large\", \"striped\", \"tent\", \"into\", \"the\", \"air.\", \"The\", \"heavy\", \"metal\", \"poles\", \"swung\", \"dangerously\", \"over\", \"a\", \"crowd\", \"of\", \"surprised\", \"people.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395, 0.929, 1.196, 1.265, 1.533, 2.02, 2.125, 2.229, 2.508, 3.286, 3.413, 3.773, 4.087, 4.493, 4.853, 4.946, 5.306, 5.712, 6.06, 6.293, 6.432, 7.326, 7.5, 7.732, 7.999, 8.406, 8.742, 9.381, 9.625, 9.706, 10.054, 10.159, 10.704], \"end_times\": [0.36, 0.894, 1.149, 1.219, 1.474, 1.962, 2.078, 2.194, 2.45, 3.007, 3.344, 3.715, 4.005, 4.435, 4.818, 4.888, 5.271, 5.654, 6.002, 6.235, 6.362, 6.815, 7.442, 7.686, 7.953, 8.336, 8.673, 9.311, 9.578, 9.648, 10.008, 10.101, 10.646, 11.331]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(465, 36, 'Page 6', 'Elias was standing on the edge of the square. He saw the shadow of the falling pole before anyone else reacted.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elias\", \"was\", \"standing\", \"on\", \"the\", \"edge\", \"of\", \"the\", \"square.\", \"He\", \"saw\", \"the\", \"shadow\", \"of\", \"the\", \"falling\", \"pole\", \"before\", \"anyone\", \"else\", \"reacted.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.627, 0.743, 1.115, 1.207, 1.335, 1.498, 1.579, 1.683, 2.392, 2.566, 2.775, 2.879, 3.228, 3.332, 3.437, 3.785, 4.11, 4.435, 4.76, 4.981], \"end_times\": [0.58, 0.72, 1.068, 1.173, 1.277, 1.474, 1.544, 1.649, 2.148, 2.508, 2.728, 2.844, 3.17, 3.286, 3.402, 3.727, 4.063, 4.4, 4.725, 4.934, 5.759]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(466, 36, 'Page 7', 'Click, click.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Click,\", \"click.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395], \"end_times\": [0.372, 1.022]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(467, 36, 'Page 8', 'The world stopped. The festival music fell silent. The heavy canvas hung motionless in the air. The expressions of the people below were frozen in shock.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"world\", \"stopped.\", \"The\", \"festival\", \"music\", \"fell\", \"silent.\", \"The\", \"heavy\", \"canvas\", \"hung\", \"motionless\", \"in\", \"the\", \"air.\", \"The\", \"expressions\", \"of\", \"the\", \"people\", \"below\", \"were\", \"frozen\", \"in\", \"shock.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.267, 0.546, 1.498, 1.672, 2.148, 2.45, 2.659, 3.471, 3.669, 3.936, 4.412, 4.69, 5.259, 5.352, 5.492, 6.316, 6.49, 7.036, 7.14, 7.245, 7.57, 7.883, 8.069, 8.475, 8.603], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.499, 1.115, 1.614, 2.09, 2.403, 2.601, 3.262, 3.599, 3.878, 4.354, 4.598, 5.224, 5.317, 5.422, 5.933, 6.432, 7.001, 7.094, 7.21, 7.535, 7.825, 8.022, 8.429, 8.533, 9.242]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(468, 36, 'Page 9', 'Elias ran. The pause wouldn’t last long; he could already feel the familiar pressure building in his chest.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elias\", \"ran.\", \"The\", \"pause\", \"wouldnu2019t\", \"last\", \"long;\", \"he\", \"could\", \"already\", \"feel\", \"the\", \"familiar\", \"pressure\", \"building\", \"in\", \"his\", \"chest.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.604, 1.416, 1.579, 1.858, 2.136, 2.438, 2.972, 3.077, 3.251, 3.529, 3.762, 3.878, 4.365, 4.772, 5.108, 5.201, 5.341], \"end_times\": [0.522, 1.033, 1.533, 1.834, 2.101, 2.368, 2.844, 3.042, 3.216, 3.483, 3.715, 3.831, 4.296, 4.725, 5.074, 5.166, 5.294, 6.037]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(469, 36, 'Page 10', 'He pushed past the frozen crowd, planting his feet firmly under the largest metal pole. He grabbed it with both hands just as the sound of the square rushed back in. Time resumed. The heavy iron dropped, its full weight slamming into Elias’s hands.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"pushed\", \"past\", \"the\", \"frozen\", \"crowd,\", \"planting\", \"his\", \"feet\", \"firmly\", \"under\", \"the\", \"largest\", \"metal\", \"pole.\", \"He\", \"grabbed\", \"it\", \"with\", \"both\", \"hands\", \"just\", \"as\", \"the\", \"sound\", \"of\", \"the\", \"square\", \"rushed\", \"back\", \"in.\", \"Time\", \"resumed.\", \"The\", \"heavy\", \"iron\", \"dropped,\", \"its\", \"full\", \"weight\", \"slamming\", \"into\", \"Eliasu2019s\", \"hands.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.662, 0.964, 1.068, 1.428, 2.032, 2.45, 2.601, 2.891, 3.344, 3.541, 3.657, 4.075, 4.342, 5.526, 5.7, 6.037, 6.118, 6.281, 6.548, 6.931, 7.175, 7.326, 7.454, 7.744, 7.837, 7.941, 8.324, 8.638, 8.905, 9.567, 9.985, 10.913, 11.088, 11.366, 11.703, 12.457, 12.678, 12.957, 13.259, 13.723, 13.92, 14.443], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.592, 0.929, 1.033, 1.382, 1.858, 2.403, 2.543, 2.81, 3.286, 3.506, 3.611, 4.017, 4.296, 4.83, 5.642, 6.014, 6.095, 6.235, 6.478, 6.873, 7.129, 7.256, 7.396, 7.709, 7.802, 7.906, 8.278, 8.58, 8.824, 9.242, 9.95, 10.588, 11.029, 11.296, 11.645, 12.249, 12.62, 12.899, 13.189, 13.688, 13.851, 14.385, 15.139]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(470, 36, 'Page 11', 'He groaned under the burden, but he held it long enough for the people underneath to scramble away. Taking a deep breath, he let the pole clang safely against the empty pavement.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"groaned\", \"under\", \"the\", \"burden,\", \"but\", \"he\", \"held\", \"it\", \"long\", \"enough\", \"for\", \"the\", \"people\", \"underneath\", \"to\", \"scramble\", \"away.\", \"Taking\", \"a\", \"deep\", \"breath,\", \"he\", \"let\", \"the\", \"pole\", \"clang\", \"safely\", \"against\", \"the\", \"empty\", \"pavement.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.708, 0.917, 1.022, 1.556, 1.741, 1.869, 2.113, 2.229, 2.473, 2.728, 2.856, 2.961, 3.297, 3.82, 3.971, 4.423, 5.619, 6.026, 6.107, 6.351, 6.757, 6.896, 7.082, 7.187, 7.465, 7.802, 8.231, 8.591, 8.707, 8.998], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.662, 0.871, 0.987, 1.463, 1.707, 1.8, 2.067, 2.183, 2.426, 2.694, 2.821, 2.926, 3.251, 3.75, 3.901, 4.389, 4.923, 5.979, 6.049, 6.293, 6.711, 6.827, 7.047, 7.152, 7.43, 7.721, 8.173, 8.545, 8.661, 8.94, 9.799]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(471, 36, 'Page 12', 'No one knew he had paused time. They only saw a brave boy who had caught a falling tent pole.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"No\", \"one\", \"knew\", \"he\", \"had\", \"paused\", \"time.\", \"They\", \"only\", \"saw\", \"a\", \"brave\", \"boy\", \"who\", \"had\", \"caught\", \"a\", \"falling\", \"tent\", \"pole.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.383, 0.534, 0.743, 0.848, 0.987, 1.312, 2.09, 2.299, 2.519, 2.74, 2.81, 3.135, 3.39, 3.518, 3.634, 3.866, 3.936, 4.272, 4.516], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.499, 0.685, 0.801, 0.952, 1.265, 1.765, 2.252, 2.473, 2.694, 2.763, 3.088, 3.344, 3.483, 3.599, 3.843, 3.889, 4.226, 4.481, 5.016]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(472, 36, 'Page 13', 'Elias dusted off his hands. He realized his power wasn’t meant for hiding. It was meant for protecting the moments others couldn\'t see coming.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_36_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elias\", \"dusted\", \"off\", \"his\", \"hands.\", \"He\", \"realized\", \"his\", \"power\", \"wasnu2019t\", \"meant\", \"for\", \"hiding.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"meant\", \"for\", \"protecting\", \"the\", \"moments\", \"others\", \"couldn\'t\", \"see\", \"coming.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.639, 0.998, 1.161, 1.3, 2.032, 2.194, 2.601, 2.74, 3.042, 3.309, 3.518, 3.669, 4.644, 4.795, 4.969, 5.201, 5.352, 5.875, 5.991, 6.385, 6.722, 7.036, 7.233], \"end_times\": [0.58, 0.964, 1.115, 1.242, 1.788, 2.136, 2.554, 2.682, 2.995, 3.274, 3.471, 3.622, 4.203, 4.76, 4.899, 5.155, 5.306, 5.828, 5.944, 6.316, 6.664, 7.001, 7.187, 7.802]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(473, 37, 'Page 1', 'Mira always felt different. When she focused hard enough, objects around her felt lighter. Not floating wildly — just slightly lifted, as if the world had grown less heavy.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"always\", \"felt\", \"different.\", \"When\", \"she\", \"focused\", \"hard\", \"enough,\", \"objects\", \"around\", \"her\", \"felt\", \"lighter.\", \"Not\", \"floating\", \"wildly\", \"u2014\", \"just\", \"slightly\", \"lifted,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"the\", \"world\", \"had\", \"grown\", \"less\", \"heavy.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.755, 0.975, 1.962, 2.159, 2.299, 2.659, 2.879, 3.17, 3.564, 3.855, 3.994, 4.238, 5.155, 5.41, 5.793, 6.293, 6.409, 6.641, 7.094, 7.512, 7.663, 7.79, 7.906, 8.162, 8.301, 8.591, 8.835], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.72, 0.929, 1.521, 2.125, 2.241, 2.624, 2.833, 3.135, 3.529, 3.808, 3.936, 4.168, 4.714, 5.352, 5.735, 6.258, 6.339, 6.594, 7.024, 7.488, 7.605, 7.744, 7.86, 8.115, 8.255, 8.533, 8.777, 9.381]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(474, 37, 'Page 2', 'By concentrating, she could lift a heavy stack of books as if they were made of feathers. She kept this secret carefully hidden. She didn\'t want to be stared at or tested by scientists.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"By\", \"concentrating,\", \"she\", \"could\", \"lift\", \"a\", \"heavy\", \"stack\", \"of\", \"books\", \"as\", \"if\", \"they\", \"were\", \"made\", \"of\", \"feathers.\", \"She\", \"kept\", \"this\", \"secret\", \"carefully\", \"hidden.\", \"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"want\", \"to\", \"be\", \"stared\", \"at\", \"or\", \"tested\", \"by\", \"scientists.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 1.103, 1.254, 1.428, 1.66, 1.753, 1.997, 2.31, 2.438, 2.856, 3.042, 3.158, 3.309, 3.46, 3.646, 3.75, 4.876, 5.062, 5.294, 5.445, 5.84, 6.374, 7.256, 7.442, 7.674, 7.825, 7.93, 8.057, 8.475, 8.638, 8.777, 9.218, 9.392], \"end_times\": [0.255, 1.08, 1.207, 1.393, 1.614, 1.695, 1.939, 2.264, 2.368, 2.798, 2.984, 3.123, 3.274, 3.425, 3.622, 3.704, 4.365, 5.004, 5.271, 5.41, 5.782, 6.316, 6.815, 7.396, 7.639, 7.802, 7.872, 8.011, 8.429, 8.58, 8.719, 9.172, 9.334, 10.449]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(475, 37, 'Page 3', 'One day, the old stone bridge stretching across the river began to crack. A heavy delivery truck was stuck in the middle, and the ancient supports groaned dangerously under its weight.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"day,\", \"the\", \"old\", \"stone\", \"bridge\", \"stretching\", \"across\", \"the\", \"river\", \"began\", \"to\", \"crack.\", \"A\", \"heavy\", \"delivery\", \"truck\", \"was\", \"stuck\", \"in\", \"the\", \"middle,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"ancient\", \"supports\", \"groaned\", \"dangerously\", \"under\", \"its\", \"weight.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.383, 0.592, 0.743, 0.975, 1.3, 1.672, 2.113, 2.45, 2.577, 2.856, 3.193, 3.32, 4.331, 4.493, 4.76, 5.224, 5.503, 5.642, 5.898, 5.979, 6.084, 6.594, 6.78, 6.908, 7.291, 7.814, 8.266, 8.87, 9.091, 9.265], \"end_times\": [0.348, 0.557, 0.673, 0.917, 1.265, 1.625, 2.055, 2.415, 2.519, 2.786, 3.135, 3.251, 3.82, 4.412, 4.702, 5.166, 5.445, 5.608, 5.851, 5.956, 6.049, 6.478, 6.734, 6.85, 7.245, 7.732, 8.185, 8.824, 9.044, 9.207, 9.799]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(476, 37, 'Page 4', 'People gathered on the riverbanks, pointing and shouting, but the truck driver was too afraid to move. The bridge shuddered, dust falling into the water below.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"People\", \"gathered\", \"on\", \"the\", \"riverbanks,\", \"pointing\", \"and\", \"shouting,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"truck\", \"driver\", \"was\", \"too\", \"afraid\", \"to\", \"move.\", \"The\", \"bridge\", \"shuddered,\", \"dust\", \"falling\", \"into\", \"the\", \"water\", \"below.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.859, 0.964, 1.068, 1.741, 2.229, 2.345, 2.914, 3.077, 3.181, 3.425, 3.785, 3.947, 4.133, 4.458, 4.586, 5.631, 5.805, 6.165, 6.711, 7.047, 7.407, 7.616, 7.721, 8.011], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.813, 0.929, 1.033, 1.683, 2.183, 2.299, 2.833, 3.053, 3.146, 3.379, 3.727, 3.889, 4.087, 4.423, 4.516, 5.027, 5.759, 6.118, 6.641, 6.989, 7.361, 7.546, 7.686, 7.953, 8.684]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(477, 37, 'Page 5', 'Mira pushed her way to the front of the crowd. She focused intensely on the heavy metal mass of the truck. She felt the pulling sensation in her hands deepen. She closed her eyes and pushed against the invisible weight of gravity.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"pushed\", \"her\", \"way\", \"to\", \"the\", \"front\", \"of\", \"the\", \"crowd.\", \"She\", \"focused\", \"intensely\", \"on\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"metal\", \"mass\", \"of\", \"the\", \"truck.\", \"She\", \"felt\", \"the\", \"pulling\", \"sensation\", \"in\", \"her\", \"hands\", \"deepen.\", \"She\", \"closed\", \"her\", \"eyes\", \"and\", \"pushed\", \"against\", \"the\", \"invisible\", \"weight\", \"of\", \"gravity.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.708, 0.824, 0.987, 1.091, 1.196, 1.393, 1.474, 1.579, 2.206, 2.426, 2.856, 3.46, 3.564, 3.692, 3.971, 4.261, 4.551, 4.656, 4.772, 5.782, 5.991, 6.211, 6.327, 6.687, 7.279, 7.419, 7.57, 7.93, 8.8, 8.998, 9.392, 9.543, 9.845, 9.985, 10.31, 10.646, 10.774, 11.273, 11.494, 11.598], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.673, 0.778, 0.94, 1.045, 1.161, 1.37, 1.44, 1.544, 1.997, 2.345, 2.81, 3.402, 3.529, 3.634, 3.901, 4.203, 4.516, 4.609, 4.725, 5.271, 5.921, 6.177, 6.281, 6.629, 7.233, 7.349, 7.5, 7.872, 8.417, 8.928, 9.346, 9.474, 9.799, 9.927, 10.275, 10.6, 10.716, 11.238, 11.471, 11.54, 12.307]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(478, 37, 'Page 6', 'The bridge stopped groaning. The truck slowly began to reverse, its tires gripping the stone differently, almost as if it were sliding back on ice instead of crushing the weakened arch.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"bridge\", \"stopped\", \"groaning.\", \"The\", \"truck\", \"slowly\", \"began\", \"to\", \"reverse,\", \"its\", \"tires\", \"gripping\", \"the\", \"stone\", \"differently,\", \"almost\", \"as\", \"if\", \"it\", \"were\", \"sliding\", \"back\", \"on\", \"ice\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"crushing\", \"the\", \"weakened\", \"arch.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.627, 1.045, 1.672, 1.834, 2.148, 2.566, 2.856, 2.984, 3.704, 3.947, 4.4, 4.748, 4.853, 5.132, 5.909, 6.327, 6.467, 6.594, 6.687, 6.838, 7.245, 7.477, 7.651, 7.988, 8.348, 8.452, 8.812, 8.916, 9.265], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.569, 0.987, 1.521, 1.788, 2.067, 2.508, 2.81, 2.914, 3.576, 3.889, 4.331, 4.702, 4.818, 5.097, 5.735, 6.281, 6.409, 6.536, 6.653, 6.815, 7.198, 7.419, 7.57, 7.941, 8.313, 8.406, 8.766, 8.882, 9.23, 9.845]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(479, 37, 'Page 7', 'As the heavy wheels rolled onto solid ground, a massive section of the old stone finally gave way, collapsing into the river. But the truck and its driver were safe.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"wheels\", \"rolled\", \"onto\", \"solid\", \"ground,\", \"a\", \"massive\", \"section\", \"of\", \"the\", \"old\", \"stone\", \"finally\", \"gave\", \"way,\", \"collapsing\", \"into\", \"the\", \"river.\", \"But\", \"the\", \"truck\", \"and\", \"its\", \"driver\", \"were\", \"safe.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.476, 0.72, 1.08, 1.416, 1.683, 2.02, 2.717, 2.879, 3.297, 3.68, 3.785, 3.924, 4.168, 4.609, 5.12, 5.387, 5.933, 6.502, 6.711, 6.838, 7.558, 7.767, 7.883, 8.197, 8.336, 8.498, 8.916, 9.114], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.418, 0.673, 0.998, 1.358, 1.614, 1.985, 2.473, 2.786, 3.262, 3.634, 3.738, 3.855, 4.11, 4.54, 5.062, 5.341, 5.759, 6.455, 6.653, 6.78, 7.233, 7.732, 7.837, 8.139, 8.278, 8.452, 8.847, 9.067, 9.706]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(480, 37, 'Page 8', 'Mira slipped away unnoticed as the crowd cheered the driver\'s narrow escape. She smiled quietly, knowing her lightness had made a heavy difference.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_37_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"slipped\", \"away\", \"unnoticed\", \"as\", \"the\", \"crowd\", \"cheered\", \"the\", \"driver\'s\", \"narrow\", \"escape.\", \"She\", \"smiled\", \"quietly,\", \"knowing\", \"her\", \"lightness\", \"had\", \"made\", \"a\", \"heavy\", \"difference.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.813, 1.103, 1.695, 1.823, 1.939, 2.276, 2.624, 2.728, 3.204, 3.541, 4.69, 4.888, 5.317, 6.142, 6.525, 6.676, 7.117, 7.268, 7.442, 7.523, 7.779], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.778, 1.022, 1.649, 1.776, 1.892, 2.218, 2.589, 2.694, 3.146, 3.471, 4.087, 4.83, 5.271, 6.026, 6.455, 6.606, 7.082, 7.221, 7.419, 7.465, 7.721, 8.499]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(481, 38, 'Page 1', 'In a city where lights never fully dimmed, there lived a boy named Theo who could move through shadows. Not just hide in them, but slip through them like stepping through doorways. If two shadows touched, he could travel the distance between them instantly.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"city\", \"where\", \"lights\", \"never\", \"fully\", \"dimmed,\", \"there\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"boy\", \"named\", \"Theo\", \"who\", \"could\", \"move\", \"through\", \"shadows.\", \"Not\", \"just\", \"hide\", \"in\", \"them,\", \"but\", \"slip\", \"through\", \"them\", \"like\", \"stepping\", \"through\", \"doorways.\", \"If\", \"two\", \"shadows\", \"touched,\", \"he\", \"could\", \"travel\", \"the\", \"distance\", \"between\", \"them\", \"instantly.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.383, 0.639, 0.836, 1.149, 1.405, 1.695, 2.218, 2.438, 2.647, 2.728, 3.007, 3.251, 3.738, 3.913, 4.098, 4.307, 4.54, 5.851, 6.072, 6.304, 6.594, 6.711, 7.152, 7.361, 7.628, 7.872, 8.081, 8.278, 8.649, 8.87, 10.24, 10.426, 10.6, 11.018, 11.424, 11.517, 11.703, 12.074, 12.19, 12.655, 13.003, 13.189], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.325, 0.604, 0.789, 1.091, 1.347, 1.637, 2.125, 2.403, 2.624, 2.682, 2.937, 3.216, 3.622, 3.878, 4.052, 4.272, 4.505, 5.248, 6.026, 6.246, 6.56, 6.664, 7.07, 7.314, 7.581, 7.837, 8.022, 8.243, 8.615, 8.847, 9.543, 10.379, 10.542, 10.96, 11.389, 11.482, 11.68, 12.016, 12.144, 12.608, 12.968, 13.119, 14.071]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10');
