(482, 38, 'Page 2', 'He used this mostly to avoid bullies or to reach his secret reading spot on the library roof without climbing the stairs.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"used\", \"this\", \"mostly\", \"to\", \"avoid\", \"bullies\", \"or\", \"to\", \"reach\", \"his\", \"secret\", \"reading\", \"spot\", \"on\", \"the\", \"library\", \"roof\", \"without\", \"climbing\", \"the\", \"stairs.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.58, 0.813, 1.173, 1.3, 1.637, 2.171, 2.357, 2.485, 2.717, 2.844, 3.204, 3.518, 3.808, 3.913, 4.029, 4.528, 4.911, 5.248, 5.608, 5.712], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.557, 0.731, 1.126, 1.231, 1.591, 2.055, 2.299, 2.415, 2.67, 2.798, 3.158, 3.46, 3.762, 3.866, 3.982, 4.458, 4.795, 5.213, 5.573, 5.677, 6.455]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(483, 38, 'Page 3', 'Late one autumn evening, a fire erupted in an old apartment building downtown. The flames spread fast, blocking the main stairwell. The fire trucks wailed in the distance, but a family was trapped on the fourth floor, standing fearfully on a narrow balcony.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Late\", \"one\", \"autumn\", \"evening,\", \"a\", \"fire\", \"erupted\", \"in\", \"an\", \"old\", \"apartment\", \"building\", \"downtown.\", \"The\", \"flames\", \"spread\", \"fast,\", \"blocking\", \"the\", \"main\", \"stairwell.\", \"The\", \"fire\", \"trucks\", \"wailed\", \"in\", \"the\", \"distance,\", \"but\", \"a\", \"family\", \"was\", \"trapped\", \"on\", \"the\", \"fourth\", \"floor,\", \"standing\", \"fearfully\", \"on\", \"a\", \"narrow\", \"balcony.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.488, 0.731, 1.068, 1.66, 1.846, 2.299, 2.844, 2.972, 3.1, 3.344, 3.831, 4.203, 5.619, 5.793, 6.188, 6.571, 7.291, 7.79, 7.906, 8.15, 9.137, 9.311, 9.636, 10.043, 10.426, 10.507, 10.623, 11.459, 11.645, 11.726, 12.098, 12.26, 12.62, 12.725, 12.841, 13.131, 13.804, 14.303, 14.803, 14.919, 15, 15.302], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.697, 1.01, 1.544, 1.73, 2.252, 2.786, 2.914, 3.03, 3.297, 3.796, 4.145, 5.016, 5.735, 6.142, 6.49, 7.198, 7.744, 7.86, 8.081, 8.812, 9.253, 9.601, 9.961, 10.391, 10.484, 10.577, 11.308, 11.61, 11.668, 12.051, 12.214, 12.585, 12.69, 12.794, 13.084, 13.63, 14.234, 14.745, 14.872, 14.942, 15.244, 16.022]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(484, 38, 'Page 4', 'Theo watched from the street below. He looked at the shadows cast by the surrounding tall buildings. The fire created dancing light, but there were deep, cool shadows stretching up the side of the burning building, reaching the balcony itself.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Theo\", \"watched\", \"from\", \"the\", \"street\", \"below.\", \"He\", \"looked\", \"at\", \"the\", \"shadows\", \"cast\", \"by\", \"the\", \"surrounding\", \"tall\", \"buildings.\", \"The\", \"fire\", \"created\", \"dancing\", \"light,\", \"but\", \"there\", \"were\", \"deep,\", \"cool\", \"shadows\", \"stretching\", \"up\", \"the\", \"side\", \"of\", \"the\", \"burning\", \"building,\", \"reaching\", \"the\", \"balcony\", \"itself.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.499, 0.848, 1.022, 1.126, 1.416, 2.264, 2.438, 2.682, 2.786, 2.902, 3.379, 3.796, 3.959, 4.075, 4.574, 4.818, 5.805, 5.979, 6.316, 6.711, 7.117, 7.709, 7.883, 8.057, 8.231, 8.626, 8.951, 9.392, 9.81, 9.95, 10.066, 10.298, 10.391, 10.495, 10.809, 11.424, 11.796, 11.9, 12.33], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.813, 0.975, 1.091, 1.37, 1.881, 2.38, 2.659, 2.752, 2.856, 3.32, 3.727, 3.901, 4.029, 4.528, 4.772, 5.422, 5.921, 6.269, 6.676, 7.059, 7.535, 7.86, 8.022, 8.173, 8.557, 8.893, 9.358, 9.764, 9.903, 10.019, 10.275, 10.344, 10.461, 10.762, 11.273, 11.749, 11.865, 12.272, 13.003]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(485, 38, 'Page 5', 'He closed his eyes, stepped into the shadow of a parked car, and visualized the balcony.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"closed\", \"his\", \"eyes,\", \"stepped\", \"into\", \"the\", \"shadow\", \"of\", \"a\", \"parked\", \"car,\", \"and\", \"visualized\", \"the\", \"balcony.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.592, 0.743, 1.115, 1.44, 1.614, 1.707, 2.02, 2.113, 2.194, 2.485, 2.81, 2.961, 3.46, 3.564], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.557, 0.685, 1.045, 1.416, 1.567, 1.683, 1.974, 2.067, 2.148, 2.438, 2.786, 2.902, 3.437, 3.529, 4.272]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(486, 38, 'Page 6', 'He vanished.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"vanished.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337], \"end_times\": [0.267, 1.068]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(487, 38, 'Page 7', 'An instant later, he stepped out of the shadow cast by a potted plant on the fourth-floor balcony. The family gasped, startled by the sudden appearance of the teenager.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"An\", \"instant\", \"later,\", \"he\", \"stepped\", \"out\", \"of\", \"the\", \"shadow\", \"cast\", \"by\", \"a\", \"potted\", \"plant\", \"on\", \"the\", \"fourth-floor\", \"balcony.\", \"The\", \"family\", \"gasped,\", \"startled\", \"by\", \"the\", \"sudden\", \"appearance\", \"of\", \"the\", \"teenager.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.697, 1.022, 1.161, 1.486, 1.625, 1.707, 1.823, 2.241, 2.601, 2.763, 2.833, 3.193, 3.599, 3.715, 3.831, 4.389, 5.503, 5.666, 6.014, 6.769, 7.268, 7.419, 7.546, 7.837, 8.301, 8.406, 8.51], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.65, 0.987, 1.091, 1.463, 1.591, 1.672, 1.776, 2.159, 2.543, 2.705, 2.786, 3.146, 3.541, 3.68, 3.785, 4.331, 5.062, 5.608, 5.956, 6.653, 7.221, 7.361, 7.488, 7.802, 8.266, 8.359, 8.475, 9.288]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(488, 38, 'Page 8', '\"Follow me,\" he said calmly, taking the hand of the youngest child. He pulled them toward the thickest shadow against the brick wall. They hesitated, but the heat of the fire pushed them forward.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"\"Follow\", \"me,\"\", \"he\", \"said\", \"calmly,\", \"taking\", \"the\", \"hand\", \"of\", \"the\", \"youngest\", \"child.\", \"He\", \"pulled\", \"them\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"thickest\", \"shadow\", \"against\", \"the\", \"brick\", \"wall.\", \"They\", \"hesitated,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"heat\", \"of\", \"the\", \"fire\", \"pushed\", \"them\", \"forward.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.499, 0.917, 1.022, 1.231, 2.078, 2.426, 2.543, 2.798, 2.879, 3.007, 3.367, 4.516, 4.69, 4.957, 5.132, 5.422, 5.561, 6.037, 6.432, 6.745, 6.85, 7.105, 8.382, 8.591, 9.416, 9.601, 9.729, 9.961, 10.066, 10.182, 10.553, 10.855, 11.029], \"end_times\": [0.441, 0.836, 0.975, 1.184, 1.869, 2.38, 2.496, 2.74, 2.844, 2.949, 3.32, 3.913, 4.632, 4.934, 5.085, 5.387, 5.492, 5.956, 6.374, 6.711, 6.815, 7.047, 7.57, 8.545, 9.3, 9.567, 9.671, 9.915, 10.019, 10.136, 10.507, 10.809, 10.971, 12.307]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(489, 38, 'Page 9', 'One by one, he guided them into the dark shape. Within seconds, they stepped out onto the cool pavement of an alleyway two blocks away, safe from the heat and smoke.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"by\", \"one,\", \"he\", \"guided\", \"them\", \"into\", \"the\", \"dark\", \"shape.\", \"Within\", \"seconds,\", \"they\", \"stepped\", \"out\", \"onto\", \"the\", \"cool\", \"pavement\", \"of\", \"an\", \"alleyway\", \"two\", \"blocks\", \"away,\", \"safe\", \"from\", \"the\", \"heat\", \"and\", \"smoke.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.662, 1.219, 1.37, 1.718, 1.904, 2.125, 2.229, 2.508, 3.576, 3.947, 4.783, 4.992, 5.329, 5.526, 5.759, 5.875, 6.142, 6.56, 6.653, 6.769, 7.221, 7.396, 7.697, 8.29, 8.591, 8.777, 8.905, 9.183, 9.358], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.58, 1.045, 1.3, 1.683, 1.846, 2.055, 2.194, 2.45, 2.972, 3.866, 4.574, 4.934, 5.294, 5.468, 5.7, 5.828, 6.072, 6.525, 6.618, 6.711, 7.163, 7.349, 7.663, 8.081, 8.568, 8.731, 8.847, 9.114, 9.288, 9.938]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(490, 38, 'Page 10', 'Theo didn\'t wait for thanks. He just slipped back into the nearest shadow, a silent guardian of the city night.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_38_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Theo\", \"didn\'t\", \"wait\", \"for\", \"thanks.\", \"He\", \"just\", \"slipped\", \"back\", \"into\", \"the\", \"nearest\", \"shadow,\", \"a\", \"silent\", \"guardian\", \"of\", \"the\", \"city\", \"night.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.372, 0.615, 0.801, 0.952, 1.649, 1.846, 2.02, 2.334, 2.589, 2.81, 2.926, 3.251, 3.971, 4.122, 4.551, 5.004, 5.108, 5.224, 5.515], \"end_times\": [0.325, 0.592, 0.755, 0.894, 1.474, 1.765, 1.997, 2.287, 2.531, 2.74, 2.879, 3.216, 3.796, 4.04, 4.505, 4.946, 5.062, 5.178, 5.457, 6.13]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(491, 39, 'Page 1', 'In a city filled with noise, traffic, and endless motion lived a quiet girl named Lina. She had an unusual ability — she could hear when things were about to break.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"city\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"noise,\", \"traffic,\", \"and\", \"endless\", \"motion\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"girl\", \"named\", \"Lina.\", \"She\", \"had\", \"an\", \"unusual\", \"ability\", \"u2014\", \"she\", \"could\", \"hear\", \"when\", \"things\", \"were\", \"about\", \"to\", \"break.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.372, 0.639, 0.871, 1.068, 1.544, 2.032, 2.183, 2.554, 3.309, 3.587, 3.657, 4.029, 4.272, 4.54, 5.515, 5.712, 5.886, 5.991, 6.49, 7.082, 7.268, 7.43, 7.616, 7.825, 7.988, 8.243, 8.394, 8.638, 8.731], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.313, 0.592, 0.848, 0.987, 1.498, 2.009, 2.113, 2.496, 2.984, 3.553, 3.611, 3.971, 4.214, 4.47, 5.004, 5.654, 5.84, 5.944, 6.432, 6.931, 7.152, 7.384, 7.57, 7.779, 7.953, 8.208, 8.359, 8.603, 8.684, 9.334]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(492, 39, 'Page 2', 'It wasn’t a loud noise, but a high-pitched hum only she could catch. A glass about to shatter hummed softly. A frayed rope holding a heavy sign sung a frantic, trembling note.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"wasnu2019t\", \"a\", \"loud\", \"noise,\", \"but\", \"a\", \"high-pitched\", \"hum\", \"only\", \"she\", \"could\", \"catch.\", \"A\", \"glass\", \"about\", \"to\", \"shatter\", \"hummed\", \"softly.\", \"A\", \"frayed\", \"rope\", \"holding\", \"a\", \"heavy\", \"sign\", \"sung\", \"a\", \"frantic,\", \"trembling\", \"note.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.58, 0.685, 0.998, 1.567, 1.753, 1.846, 2.473, 2.879, 3.193, 3.379, 3.564, 4.423, 4.574, 4.911, 5.155, 5.259, 5.666, 6.037, 6.896, 7.047, 7.396, 7.674, 7.999, 8.092, 8.348, 8.754, 8.975, 9.067, 9.532, 10.054], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.534, 0.615, 0.94, 1.451, 1.718, 1.776, 2.426, 2.763, 3.135, 3.32, 3.529, 4.04, 4.505, 4.876, 5.12, 5.213, 5.596, 5.979, 6.653, 6.966, 7.338, 7.628, 7.953, 8.022, 8.29, 8.673, 8.928, 8.998, 9.509, 9.985, 10.542]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(493, 39, 'Page 3', 'Most days, she simply moved things out of the way or tightened loose screws.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Most\", \"days,\", \"she\", \"simply\", \"moved\", \"things\", \"out\", \"of\", \"the\", \"way\", \"or\", \"tightened\", \"loose\", \"screws.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.801, 0.964, 1.3, 1.544, 1.8, 1.939, 2.02, 2.125, 2.415, 2.566, 2.972, 3.228], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.778, 0.906, 1.231, 1.521, 1.765, 1.916, 1.985, 2.09, 2.345, 2.508, 2.914, 3.204, 3.994]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(494, 39, 'Page 4', 'During the annual city parade, thousands lined the streets to watch the massive, colorful floats roll by. The center attraction was a giant mechanical dragon, its head sweeping left and right over the crowd.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"During\", \"the\", \"annual\", \"city\", \"parade,\", \"thousands\", \"lined\", \"the\", \"streets\", \"to\", \"watch\", \"the\", \"massive,\", \"colorful\", \"floats\", \"roll\", \"by.\", \"The\", \"center\", \"attraction\", \"was\", \"a\", \"giant\", \"mechanical\", \"dragon,\", \"its\", \"head\", \"sweeping\", \"left\", \"and\", \"right\", \"over\", \"the\", \"crowd.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.522, 0.894, 1.161, 1.707, 2.415, 2.879, 2.995, 3.413, 3.553, 3.82, 3.959, 4.516, 5.039, 5.48, 5.735, 6.664, 6.85, 7.187, 7.755, 7.93, 8.034, 8.44, 9.009, 9.683, 9.903, 10.194, 10.67, 10.971, 11.122, 11.436, 11.656, 11.761], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.476, 0.836, 1.103, 1.637, 2.334, 2.81, 2.949, 3.355, 3.483, 3.773, 3.889, 4.47, 4.969, 5.399, 5.677, 6.223, 6.792, 7.14, 7.697, 7.883, 7.964, 8.382, 8.951, 9.567, 9.845, 10.112, 10.6, 10.913, 11.053, 11.378, 11.61, 11.726, 12.353]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(495, 39, 'Page 5', 'As the dragon approached, Lina heard it. A sharp, terrifying screech vibrating above the marching band music. It was coming from the massive steel axle supporting the dragon’s head.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"dragon\", \"approached,\", \"Lina\", \"heard\", \"it.\", \"A\", \"sharp,\", \"terrifying\", \"screech\", \"vibrating\", \"above\", \"the\", \"marching\", \"band\", \"music.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"coming\", \"from\", \"the\", \"massive\", \"steel\", \"axle\", \"supporting\", \"the\", \"dragonu2019s\", \"head.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.453, 0.801, 1.312, 1.602, 1.823, 2.392, 2.554, 2.926, 3.599, 4.04, 4.54, 4.772, 4.888, 5.259, 5.526, 6.548, 6.699, 6.873, 7.187, 7.361, 7.477, 7.86, 8.197, 8.673, 9.125, 9.23, 9.683], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.406, 0.766, 1.265, 1.544, 1.776, 2.148, 2.473, 2.902, 3.529, 3.982, 4.493, 4.748, 4.841, 5.201, 5.468, 6.107, 6.664, 6.803, 7.129, 7.326, 7.43, 7.825, 8.127, 8.638, 9.091, 9.195, 9.636, 10.17]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(496, 39, 'Page 6', 'She looked up. A heavy bolt had snapped, though it wasn\'t visible yet. The massive head was swaying too far, drifting toward the grandstands where children sat waving.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"looked\", \"up.\", \"A\", \"heavy\", \"bolt\", \"had\", \"snapped,\", \"though\", \"it\", \"wasn\'t\", \"visible\", \"yet.\", \"The\", \"massive\", \"head\", \"was\", \"swaying\", \"too\", \"far,\", \"drifting\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"grandstands\", \"where\", \"children\", \"sat\", \"waving.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.604, 1.3, 1.463, 1.741, 2.009, 2.159, 2.74, 2.972, 3.065, 3.332, 3.715, 4.772, 4.946, 5.306, 5.48, 5.619, 6.002, 6.235, 6.711, 7.117, 7.326, 7.43, 8.081, 8.266, 8.684, 8.94], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.557, 0.917, 1.382, 1.672, 1.962, 2.113, 2.624, 2.949, 3.03, 3.297, 3.68, 4.075, 4.888, 5.271, 5.433, 5.584, 5.944, 6.165, 6.618, 7.07, 7.303, 7.396, 8.046, 8.231, 8.626, 8.882, 9.567]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(497, 39, 'Page 7', 'She didn\'t hesitate. Lina pushed past the security barriers and ran directly toward the front wheels of the moving float.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"didn\'t\", \"hesitate.\", \"Lina\", \"pushed\", \"past\", \"the\", \"security\", \"barriers\", \"and\", \"ran\", \"directly\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"front\", \"wheels\", \"of\", \"the\", \"moving\", \"float.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.58, 1.904, 2.218, 2.508, 2.81, 2.926, 3.402, 3.843, 3.982, 4.203, 4.644, 4.899, 5.004, 5.236, 5.596, 5.7, 5.817, 6.153], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.534, 1.207, 2.159, 2.473, 2.763, 2.879, 3.344, 3.808, 3.924, 4.145, 4.598, 4.865, 4.969, 5.201, 5.55, 5.654, 5.77, 6.095, 6.734]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(498, 39, 'Page 8', '\"Stop!\" she screamed, waving her arms frantically at the driver.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"\"Stop!\"\", \"she\", \"screamed,\", \"waving\", \"her\", \"arms\", \"frantically\", \"at\", \"the\", \"driver.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.766, 0.952, 1.416, 1.753, 1.881, 2.148, 2.635, 2.728, 2.821], \"end_times\": [0.685, 0.894, 1.393, 1.695, 1.823, 2.09, 2.601, 2.694, 2.798, 3.483]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(499, 39, 'Page 9', 'The driver hit the brakes hard. The sudden jolt was enough. With a groan of tearing metal, the dragon\'s head collapsed, crashing heavily into the street just feet away from the barriers, instead of swinging into the crowd.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"driver\", \"hit\", \"the\", \"brakes\", \"hard.\", \"The\", \"sudden\", \"jolt\", \"was\", \"enough.\", \"With\", \"a\", \"groan\", \"of\", \"tearing\", \"metal,\", \"the\", \"dragon\'s\", \"head\", \"collapsed,\", \"crashing\", \"heavily\", \"into\", \"the\", \"street\", \"just\", \"feet\", \"away\", \"from\", \"the\", \"barriers,\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"swinging\", \"into\", \"the\", \"crowd.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.685, 0.859, 0.964, 1.312, 1.974, 2.148, 2.473, 2.752, 2.926, 3.75, 3.971, 4.04, 4.365, 4.481, 4.934, 5.399, 5.55, 6.037, 6.293, 7.094, 7.628, 7.999, 8.197, 8.301, 8.649, 8.916, 9.172, 9.392, 9.543, 9.648, 10.414, 10.809, 10.913, 11.331, 11.505, 11.61], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.627, 0.824, 0.929, 1.242, 1.8, 2.09, 2.415, 2.705, 2.868, 3.367, 3.924, 3.994, 4.319, 4.423, 4.853, 5.317, 5.503, 5.979, 6.223, 6.978, 7.558, 7.953, 8.15, 8.266, 8.591, 8.847, 9.137, 9.346, 9.509, 9.613, 10.24, 10.774, 10.855, 11.285, 11.459, 11.575, 12.214]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(500, 39, 'Page 10', 'People gasped in shock, realizing how close a disaster had been. Lina stood trembling but relieved. The silence of the unbroken was the sweetest sound to her ears.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_39_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"People\", \"gasped\", \"in\", \"shock,\", \"realizing\", \"how\", \"close\", \"a\", \"disaster\", \"had\", \"been.\", \"Lina\", \"stood\", \"trembling\", \"but\", \"relieved.\", \"The\", \"silence\", \"of\", \"the\", \"unbroken\", \"was\", \"the\", \"sweetest\", \"sound\", \"to\", \"her\", \"ears.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.882, 0.998, 1.556, 2.101, 2.276, 2.612, 2.694, 3.216, 3.355, 4.47, 4.772, 5.027, 5.48, 5.631, 6.49, 6.653, 7.059, 7.152, 7.291, 7.802, 7.988, 8.115, 8.615, 8.951, 9.102, 9.253], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.848, 0.94, 1.44, 2.043, 2.206, 2.577, 2.635, 3.158, 3.309, 3.773, 4.725, 4.992, 5.422, 5.584, 6.165, 6.606, 7.036, 7.105, 7.221, 7.744, 7.93, 8.057, 8.545, 8.905, 9.021, 9.195, 9.892]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(501, 40, 'Page 1', 'Mateo always felt connected to people in a strange way. When someone nearby felt strong emotion — fear, sadness, joy — he sensed a thin, glowing thread linking them. He couldn’t hear their thoughts, but he could feel the direction of their panic or relief.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mateo\", \"always\", \"felt\", \"connected\", \"to\", \"people\", \"in\", \"a\", \"strange\", \"way.\", \"When\", \"someone\", \"nearby\", \"felt\", \"strong\", \"emotion\", \"u2014\", \"fear,\", \"sadness,\", \"joy\", \"u2014\", \"he\", \"sensed\", \"a\", \"thin,\", \"glowing\", \"thread\", \"linking\", \"them.\", \"He\", \"couldnu2019t\", \"hear\", \"their\", \"thoughts,\", \"but\", \"he\", \"could\", \"feel\", \"the\", \"direction\", \"of\", \"their\", \"panic\", \"or\", \"relief.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.662, 0.952, 1.161, 1.556, 1.672, 1.985, 2.113, 2.183, 2.566, 3.75, 3.982, 4.296, 4.748, 5.027, 5.352, 6.026, 6.235, 6.861, 7.639, 8.173, 8.394, 8.545, 8.94, 9.102, 9.543, 10.008, 10.356, 10.739, 11.923, 12.074, 12.388, 12.562, 12.748, 13.584, 13.746, 13.827, 14.002, 14.222, 14.327, 14.791, 14.884, 15.07, 15.499, 15.65], \"end_times\": [0.58, 0.917, 1.115, 1.521, 1.614, 1.939, 2.067, 2.136, 2.519, 3.053, 3.924, 4.272, 4.656, 4.957, 5.294, 5.817, 6.084, 6.711, 7.523, 7.964, 8.278, 8.475, 8.882, 8.986, 9.462, 9.938, 10.286, 10.681, 11.111, 12.04, 12.341, 12.516, 12.713, 13.41, 13.723, 13.793, 13.967, 14.176, 14.292, 14.745, 14.838, 15.023, 15.43, 15.592, 16.347]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(502, 40, 'Page 2', 'He usually ignored the threads, navigating the busy subway stations by avoiding the bright, jagged lines of modern anxiety.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"usually\", \"ignored\", \"the\", \"threads,\", \"navigating\", \"the\", \"busy\", \"subway\", \"stations\", \"by\", \"avoiding\", \"the\", \"bright,\", \"jagged\", \"lines\", \"of\", \"modern\", \"anxiety.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.743, 1.08, 1.184, 1.881, 2.438, 2.543, 2.821, 3.17, 3.669, 3.831, 4.238, 4.354, 4.702, 5.108, 5.433, 5.561, 5.886], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.697, 1.057, 1.149, 1.707, 2.392, 2.508, 2.763, 3.123, 3.611, 3.773, 4.191, 4.307, 4.656, 5.05, 5.387, 5.492, 5.851, 6.734]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(503, 40, 'Page 3', 'But one chaotic rush hour, he felt a thread of pure terror. It wasn\'t the usual stress of being late; it was the cold, sharp pull of someone lost and terrified.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"one\", \"chaotic\", \"rush\", \"hour,\", \"he\", \"felt\", \"a\", \"thread\", \"of\", \"pure\", \"terror.\", \"It\", \"wasn\'t\", \"the\", \"usual\", \"stress\", \"of\", \"being\", \"late;\", \"it\", \"was\", \"the\", \"cold,\", \"sharp\", \"pull\", \"of\", \"someone\", \"lost\", \"and\", \"terrified.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.604, 1.115, 1.382, 1.765, 1.916, 2.171, 2.276, 2.612, 2.763, 3.1, 3.982, 4.156, 4.458, 4.598, 4.981, 5.294, 5.41, 5.724, 6.374, 6.513, 6.664, 6.792, 7.21, 7.581, 7.918, 8.046, 8.406, 8.766, 8.893], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.557, 1.057, 1.335, 1.718, 1.846, 2.125, 2.206, 2.566, 2.67, 3.053, 3.599, 4.11, 4.423, 4.528, 4.923, 5.259, 5.352, 5.642, 6.095, 6.478, 6.618, 6.734, 7.163, 7.5, 7.86, 7.976, 8.359, 8.719, 8.847, 9.706]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(504, 40, 'Page 4', 'He followed the invisible line through the crowded terminal. He pushed past businessmen and hurried commuters until he reached the darkest, most confusing intersection of the underground tunnels.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"followed\", \"the\", \"invisible\", \"line\", \"through\", \"the\", \"crowded\", \"terminal.\", \"He\", \"pushed\", \"past\", \"businessmen\", \"and\", \"hurried\", \"commuters\", \"until\", \"he\", \"reached\", \"the\", \"darkest,\", \"most\", \"confusing\", \"intersection\", \"of\", \"the\", \"underground\", \"tunnels.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.627, 0.743, 1.219, 1.509, 1.718, 1.811, 2.171, 2.868, 3.03, 3.309, 3.587, 4.133, 4.249, 4.563, 5.085, 5.352, 5.468, 5.759, 5.863, 6.374, 6.606, 7.187, 7.802, 7.906, 8.022, 8.464], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.604, 0.697, 1.184, 1.486, 1.695, 1.788, 2.136, 2.694, 2.984, 3.262, 3.541, 4.098, 4.203, 4.516, 5.039, 5.306, 5.399, 5.724, 5.828, 6.327, 6.56, 7.129, 7.755, 7.86, 7.976, 8.429, 9.149]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(505, 40, 'Page 5', 'There, sitting huddled against a tiled wall and crying silently, was a small girl who had let go of her mother’s hand in the rush.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"There,\", \"sitting\", \"huddled\", \"against\", \"a\", \"tiled\", \"wall\", \"and\", \"crying\", \"silently,\", \"was\", \"a\", \"small\", \"girl\", \"who\", \"had\", \"let\", \"go\", \"of\", \"her\", \"motheru2019s\", \"hand\", \"in\", \"the\", \"rush.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 1.01, 1.358, 1.66, 1.997, 2.09, 2.496, 2.856, 3.042, 3.448, 4.389, 4.598, 4.679, 5.016, 5.341, 5.503, 5.654, 5.84, 6.026, 6.13, 6.246, 6.571, 6.85, 6.943, 7.059], \"end_times\": [0.731, 1.312, 1.637, 1.95, 2.032, 2.45, 2.775, 2.972, 3.379, 4.11, 4.551, 4.621, 4.957, 5.271, 5.468, 5.596, 5.793, 5.956, 6.084, 6.2, 6.525, 6.792, 6.908, 7.012, 7.663]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(506, 40, 'Page 6', 'Mateo knelt gently beside her. He didn\'t ask her name at first. He just followed another, thicker thread glowing nearby—the frantic, desperate line of a searching mother.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mateo\", \"knelt\", \"gently\", \"beside\", \"her.\", \"He\", \"didn\'t\", \"ask\", \"her\", \"name\", \"at\", \"first.\", \"He\", \"just\", \"followed\", \"another,\", \"thicker\", \"thread\", \"glowing\", \"nearbyu2014the\", \"frantic,\", \"desperate\", \"line\", \"of\", \"a\", \"searching\", \"mother.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.615, 0.917, 1.3, 1.741, 2.485, 2.647, 2.937, 3.17, 3.309, 3.518, 3.646, 4.505, 4.69, 4.923, 5.306, 6.002, 6.409, 6.792, 7.21, 8.324, 9.021, 9.555, 9.845, 9.938, 10.019, 10.414], \"end_times\": [0.557, 0.836, 1.242, 1.695, 2.043, 2.589, 2.891, 3.123, 3.251, 3.483, 3.587, 4.18, 4.621, 4.876, 5.271, 5.793, 6.339, 6.734, 7.152, 8.266, 8.905, 9.509, 9.81, 9.892, 9.961, 10.356, 11.006]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(507, 40, 'Page 7', 'He took the girl\'s hand and led her purposefully back through the crowd, following the glowing trail only he could see, until they burst into the main ticketing hall where a woman stood frantically talking to a security guard.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"took\", \"the\", \"girl\'s\", \"hand\", \"and\", \"led\", \"her\", \"purposefully\", \"back\", \"through\", \"the\", \"crowd,\", \"following\", \"the\", \"glowing\", \"trail\", \"only\", \"he\", \"could\", \"see,\", \"until\", \"they\", \"burst\", \"into\", \"the\", \"main\", \"ticketing\", \"hall\", \"where\", \"a\", \"woman\", \"stood\", \"frantically\", \"talking\", \"to\", \"a\", \"security\", \"guard.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.476, 0.58, 0.848, 1.091, 1.207, 1.382, 1.521, 2.113, 2.322, 2.531, 2.635, 3.541, 3.994, 4.11, 4.493, 4.853, 5.178, 5.306, 5.503, 6.246, 6.513, 6.676, 6.989, 7.198, 7.314, 7.546, 7.964, 8.185, 8.394, 8.475, 8.8, 9.16, 9.741, 10.124, 10.263, 10.333, 10.762], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.43, 0.546, 0.801, 1.045, 1.161, 1.335, 1.463, 2.055, 2.287, 2.508, 2.601, 3.158, 3.947, 4.063, 4.435, 4.772, 5.108, 5.248, 5.457, 5.921, 6.478, 6.618, 6.943, 7.14, 7.268, 7.488, 7.906, 8.139, 8.359, 8.417, 8.731, 9.079, 9.694, 10.066, 10.182, 10.286, 10.716, 11.285]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(508, 40, 'Page 8', 'The reunion was tearful and loud. Mateo simply walked away, the bright thread of relief warming the air behind him.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_40_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"reunion\", \"was\", \"tearful\", \"and\", \"loud.\", \"Mateo\", \"simply\", \"walked\", \"away,\", \"the\", \"bright\", \"thread\", \"of\", \"relief\", \"warming\", \"the\", \"air\", \"behind\", \"him.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.697, 0.882, 1.37, 1.521, 2.276, 2.682, 3.007, 3.332, 3.959, 4.098, 4.389, 4.644, 4.737, 5.097, 5.457, 5.584, 5.793, 6.177], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.65, 0.813, 1.312, 1.451, 1.997, 2.624, 2.949, 3.297, 3.785, 4.063, 4.342, 4.609, 4.69, 5.027, 5.422, 5.526, 5.735, 6.107, 6.641]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(509, 41, 'Page 1', 'Ava loved storms. While others hid indoors, she stood at windows watching lightning split the sky. She felt energized when thunder rolled across rooftops.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Ava\", \"loved\", \"storms.\", \"While\", \"others\", \"hid\", \"indoors,\", \"she\", \"stood\", \"at\", \"windows\", \"watching\", \"lightning\", \"split\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"She\", \"felt\", \"energized\", \"when\", \"thunder\", \"rolled\", \"across\", \"rooftops.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.511, 0.824, 1.602, 1.881, 2.229, 2.45, 3.019, 3.204, 3.471, 3.576, 4.052, 4.447, 4.888, 5.213, 5.329, 6.153, 6.339, 6.583, 7.279, 7.5, 7.895, 8.15, 8.51], \"end_times\": [0.43, 0.766, 1.428, 1.834, 2.171, 2.415, 2.961, 3.146, 3.437, 3.529, 3.982, 4.377, 4.795, 5.166, 5.283, 5.828, 6.281, 6.513, 7.233, 7.43, 7.825, 8.127, 8.452, 9.427]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(510, 41, 'Page 2', 'She discovered her secret during a summer blackout. When a massive thunderstorm knocked out the city\'s power grid, plunging everything into darkness, Ava realized her skin was faintly glowing. She could absorb the ambient static electricity in the air and release it as a soft, continuous light from her hands.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"discovered\", \"her\", \"secret\", \"during\", \"a\", \"summer\", \"blackout.\", \"When\", \"a\", \"massive\", \"thunderstorm\", \"knocked\", \"out\", \"the\", \"city\'s\", \"power\", \"grid,\", \"plunging\", \"everything\", \"into\", \"darkness,\", \"Ava\", \"realized\", \"her\", \"skin\", \"was\", \"faintly\", \"glowing.\", \"She\", \"could\", \"absorb\", \"the\", \"ambient\", \"static\", \"electricity\", \"in\", \"the\", \"air\", \"and\", \"release\", \"it\", \"as\", \"a\", \"soft,\", \"continuous\", \"light\", \"from\", \"her\", \"hands.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.813, 0.952, 1.324, 1.591, 1.66, 1.95, 3.297, 3.518, 3.622, 4.133, 4.876, 5.201, 5.364, 5.48, 5.828, 6.2, 6.827, 7.361, 7.918, 8.139, 9.207, 9.532, 9.985, 10.124, 10.414, 10.623, 11.064, 11.993, 12.156, 12.33, 12.713, 12.864, 13.351, 13.746, 14.327, 14.42, 14.559, 15.14, 15.441, 15.871, 16.01, 16.138, 16.231, 16.672, 17.346, 17.589, 17.787, 17.926], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.778, 0.894, 1.277, 1.544, 1.614, 1.904, 2.601, 3.483, 3.553, 4.087, 4.818, 5.166, 5.317, 5.433, 5.782, 6.142, 6.618, 7.268, 7.86, 8.081, 8.882, 9.474, 9.938, 10.066, 10.356, 10.53, 11.006, 11.61, 12.121, 12.295, 12.655, 12.783, 13.293, 13.7, 14.28, 14.385, 14.489, 14.815, 15.372, 15.825, 15.952, 16.092, 16.173, 16.637, 17.287, 17.555, 17.729, 17.868, 18.623]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(511, 41, 'Page 3', 'As the city sat in dark confusion, the hospital on the hill faced a crisis. The backup generators had failed during a critical moment. Doctors and nurses scrambled with weak flashlights.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"city\", \"sat\", \"in\", \"dark\", \"confusion,\", \"the\", \"hospital\", \"on\", \"the\", \"hill\", \"faced\", \"a\", \"crisis.\", \"The\", \"backup\", \"generators\", \"had\", \"failed\", \"during\", \"a\", \"critical\", \"moment.\", \"Doctors\", \"and\", \"nurses\", \"scrambled\", \"with\", \"weak\", \"flashlights.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.43, 0.72, 0.975, 1.103, 1.347, 2.229, 2.392, 2.891, 2.995, 3.111, 3.379, 3.68, 3.75, 4.725, 4.899, 5.271, 5.782, 5.956, 6.281, 6.536, 6.618, 7.001, 7.872, 8.324, 8.44, 8.858, 9.358, 9.532, 9.752], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.395, 0.662, 0.929, 1.045, 1.3, 2.055, 2.334, 2.833, 2.961, 3.065, 3.297, 3.646, 3.704, 4.4, 4.841, 5.213, 5.735, 5.886, 6.258, 6.49, 6.56, 6.931, 7.488, 8.29, 8.394, 8.8, 9.334, 9.474, 9.706, 10.681]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(512, 41, 'Page 4', 'Ava felt the heavy static in the air outside. She ran through the pouring rain, the energy filling her until she shone like a blue star in the dark streets.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Ava\", \"felt\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"static\", \"in\", \"the\", \"air\", \"outside.\", \"She\", \"ran\", \"through\", \"the\", \"pouring\", \"rain,\", \"the\", \"energy\", \"filling\", \"her\", \"until\", \"she\", \"shone\", \"like\", \"a\", \"blue\", \"star\", \"in\", \"the\", \"dark\", \"streets.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.662, 0.789, 1.045, 1.498, 1.602, 1.741, 1.95, 3.03, 3.262, 3.553, 3.773, 3.878, 4.284, 4.818, 5.004, 5.422, 5.782, 5.909, 6.177, 6.351, 6.664, 6.85, 6.943, 7.233, 7.605, 7.697, 7.802, 8.081], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.627, 0.731, 0.998, 1.44, 1.556, 1.672, 1.892, 2.589, 3.181, 3.495, 3.75, 3.843, 4.214, 4.702, 4.923, 5.352, 5.724, 5.863, 6.118, 6.269, 6.629, 6.815, 6.873, 7.187, 7.558, 7.663, 7.767, 8.022, 8.87]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(513, 41, 'Page 5', 'She reached the hospital emergency room. It was pitch black and filled with worried voices.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"reached\", \"the\", \"hospital\", \"emergency\", \"room.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"pitch\", \"black\", \"and\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"worried\", \"voices.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.592, 0.697, 1.103, 1.625, 2.078, 2.229, 2.392, 2.67, 3.065, 3.262, 3.564, 3.715, 4.052], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.569, 0.662, 1.057, 1.556, 1.962, 2.194, 2.322, 2.624, 2.995, 3.181, 3.529, 3.68, 4.017, 4.83]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(514, 41, 'Page 6', 'Ava closed her eyes, placed her hands against the main electrical panel in the hallway, and let the stormlight flow.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Ava\", \"closed\", \"her\", \"eyes,\", \"placed\", \"her\", \"hands\", \"against\", \"the\", \"main\", \"electrical\", \"panel\", \"in\", \"the\", \"hallway,\", \"and\", \"let\", \"the\", \"stormlight\", \"flow.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.778, 0.94, 1.521, 1.846, 1.962, 2.229, 2.543, 2.647, 2.868, 3.355, 3.669, 3.773, 3.889, 4.551, 4.748, 4.934, 5.05, 5.677], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.731, 0.871, 1.393, 1.811, 1.916, 2.194, 2.496, 2.612, 2.81, 3.297, 3.634, 3.727, 3.843, 4.435, 4.69, 4.899, 5.004, 5.608, 6.269]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(515, 41, 'Page 7', 'A brilliant blue-white glow flooded the corridor, steady and bright as daylight. It wasn\'t enough to power the machines, but it provided enough intense, shadowless light for the doctors to see clearly while they worked on the most urgent cases.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"brilliant\", \"blue-white\", \"glow\", \"flooded\", \"the\", \"corridor,\", \"steady\", \"and\", \"bright\", \"as\", \"daylight.\", \"It\", \"wasn\'t\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"power\", \"the\", \"machines,\", \"but\", \"it\", \"provided\", \"enough\", \"intense,\", \"shadowless\", \"light\", \"for\", \"the\", \"doctors\", \"to\", \"see\", \"clearly\", \"while\", \"they\", \"worked\", \"on\", \"the\", \"most\", \"urgent\", \"cases.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.72, 1.277, 1.707, 2.043, 2.159, 2.891, 3.367, 3.529, 3.866, 4.04, 5.329, 5.492, 5.782, 6.049, 6.153, 6.444, 6.548, 7.303, 7.488, 7.593, 8.057, 8.348, 8.951, 9.555, 9.787, 9.915, 10.019, 10.437, 10.565, 10.774, 11.25, 11.447, 11.61, 11.9, 12.005, 12.121, 12.399, 12.771], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.65, 1.231, 1.591, 2.02, 2.113, 2.74, 3.297, 3.471, 3.808, 3.959, 4.632, 5.445, 5.735, 6.014, 6.095, 6.397, 6.513, 7.187, 7.454, 7.558, 8.011, 8.29, 8.882, 9.509, 9.741, 9.88, 9.985, 10.391, 10.507, 10.728, 11.192, 11.424, 11.552, 11.865, 11.97, 12.074, 12.318, 12.725, 13.56]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(516, 41, 'Page 8', 'She stood there for an hour, a living beacon, humming with the energy of the storm outside, guiding the helpers through the dark.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_41_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"stood\", \"there\", \"for\", \"an\", \"hour,\", \"a\", \"living\", \"beacon,\", \"humming\", \"with\", \"the\", \"energy\", \"of\", \"the\", \"storm\", \"outside,\", \"guiding\", \"the\", \"helpers\", \"through\", \"the\", \"dark.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.604, 0.813, 0.975, 1.08, 1.649, 1.8, 2.159, 2.856, 3.251, 3.413, 3.553, 3.936, 4.04, 4.156, 4.505, 5.271, 5.666, 5.793, 6.211, 6.467, 6.571], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.569, 0.778, 0.929, 1.033, 1.533, 1.718, 2.078, 2.682, 3.204, 3.379, 3.483, 3.889, 3.994, 4.11, 4.447, 5.097, 5.619, 5.735, 6.165, 6.432, 6.536, 7.152]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(517, 42, 'Page 1', 'In a neighborhood filled with tall buildings lived a boy named Omar who had a subtle power — he could improve tiny probabilities.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"neighborhood\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"tall\", \"buildings\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"boy\", \"named\", \"Omar\", \"who\", \"had\", \"a\", \"subtle\", \"power\", \"u2014\", \"he\", \"could\", \"improve\", \"tiny\", \"probabilities.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.383, 0.906, 1.196, 1.358, 1.637, 2.508, 2.763, 2.833, 3.077, 3.355, 4.087, 4.331, 4.516, 4.609, 4.946, 5.526, 5.747, 5.863, 6.049, 6.571, 6.954], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.325, 0.836, 1.173, 1.324, 1.579, 2.125, 2.74, 2.786, 3.019, 3.286, 3.762, 4.261, 4.47, 4.54, 4.911, 5.317, 5.573, 5.817, 6.014, 6.513, 6.908, 8.081]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(518, 42, 'Page 2', 'If a coin was flipped, he could make it land on heads. If someone dropped a fragile vase, he could ensure it hit the softest patch of carpet instead of tile. It wasn\'t grand magic, just nudging luck firmly in the right direction.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"If\", \"a\", \"coin\", \"was\", \"flipped,\", \"he\", \"could\", \"make\", \"it\", \"land\", \"on\", \"heads.\", \"If\", \"someone\", \"dropped\", \"a\", \"fragile\", \"vase,\", \"he\", \"could\", \"ensure\", \"it\", \"hit\", \"the\", \"softest\", \"patch\", \"of\", \"carpet\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"tile.\", \"It\", \"wasn\'t\", \"grand\", \"magic,\", \"just\", \"nudging\", \"luck\", \"firmly\", \"in\", \"the\", \"right\", \"direction.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.372, 0.604, 0.778, 1.498, 1.614, 1.8, 1.985, 2.101, 2.368, 2.519, 3.634, 3.831, 4.168, 4.458, 4.516, 4.899, 5.596, 5.712, 5.886, 6.211, 6.304, 6.455, 6.583, 7.024, 7.268, 7.384, 7.767, 8.104, 8.22, 9.404, 9.59, 9.903, 10.194, 10.89, 11.192, 11.575, 11.842, 12.26, 12.353, 12.457, 12.655], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.325, 0.557, 0.708, 1.289, 1.567, 1.753, 1.95, 2.055, 2.31, 2.45, 3.03, 3.773, 4.133, 4.435, 4.481, 4.865, 5.445, 5.666, 5.851, 6.177, 6.269, 6.42, 6.525, 6.978, 7.233, 7.314, 7.721, 8.069, 8.162, 8.8, 9.532, 9.857, 10.136, 10.716, 11.111, 11.517, 11.761, 12.214, 12.318, 12.423, 12.62, 13.421]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(519, 42, 'Page 3', 'One windy afternoon, an old man was walking his small dog near a busy intersection. The dog spotted a squirrel and suddenly bolted, ripping the leash from the man\'s frail hands. The dog dashed straight toward the oncoming traffic.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"windy\", \"afternoon,\", \"an\", \"old\", \"man\", \"was\", \"walking\", \"his\", \"small\", \"dog\", \"near\", \"a\", \"busy\", \"intersection.\", \"The\", \"dog\", \"spotted\", \"a\", \"squirrel\", \"and\", \"suddenly\", \"bolted,\", \"ripping\", \"the\", \"leash\", \"from\", \"the\", \"man\'s\", \"frail\", \"hands.\", \"The\", \"dog\", \"dashed\", \"straight\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"oncoming\", \"traffic.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.418, 0.755, 1.358, 1.533, 1.753, 1.985, 2.159, 2.543, 2.682, 3.007, 3.344, 3.529, 3.611, 3.889, 4.923, 5.085, 5.352, 5.712, 5.782, 6.2, 6.362, 6.769, 7.488, 7.814, 7.93, 8.197, 8.348, 8.452, 8.742, 9.079, 9.961, 10.124, 10.403, 10.693, 11.006, 11.238, 11.366, 11.807], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.685, 1.324, 1.463, 1.695, 1.927, 2.09, 2.485, 2.635, 2.949, 3.274, 3.495, 3.553, 3.831, 4.644, 5.039, 5.306, 5.677, 5.735, 6.13, 6.304, 6.699, 7.314, 7.767, 7.883, 8.15, 8.313, 8.417, 8.707, 9.009, 9.578, 10.077, 10.344, 10.67, 10.971, 11.215, 11.308, 11.761, 12.492]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(520, 42, 'Page 4', 'Cars barely had time to react. The sounds of screeching tires echoed loudly.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Cars\", \"barely\", \"had\", \"time\", \"to\", \"react.\", \"The\", \"sounds\", \"of\", \"screeching\", \"tires\", \"echoed\", \"loudly.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.743, 0.894, 1.138, 1.265, 1.858, 2.02, 2.31, 2.403, 2.844, 3.286, 3.622], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.697, 0.848, 1.103, 1.196, 1.741, 1.974, 2.276, 2.357, 2.786, 3.216, 3.576, 4.272]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(521, 42, 'Page 5', 'Omar, standing on the corner, focused his eyes entirely on the chaotic path of the small dog.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Omar,\", \"standing\", \"on\", \"the\", \"corner,\", \"focused\", \"his\", \"eyes\", \"entirely\", \"on\", \"the\", \"chaotic\", \"path\", \"of\", \"the\", \"small\", \"dog.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.534, 0.94, 1.045, 1.161, 1.788, 2.218, 2.368, 2.601, 3.204, 3.344, 3.448, 3.936, 4.284, 4.412, 4.528, 4.865], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.894, 1.01, 1.115, 1.637, 2.183, 2.31, 2.543, 3.135, 3.309, 3.413, 3.878, 4.238, 4.354, 4.481, 4.807, 5.48]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(522, 42, 'Page 6', 'He nudged the probabilities.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"nudged\", \"the\", \"probabilities.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.546, 0.65], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.522, 0.615, 1.625]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(523, 42, 'Page 7', 'A delivery truck slammed on its brakes, stopping an inch short. A swerving sports car precisely grazed the bumper of a parked van instead of hitting the animal. A discarded newspaper blew perfectly across the road, startling the dog just enough to make it freeze in the only safe triangle of asphalt between the sliding vehicles.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"delivery\", \"truck\", \"slammed\", \"on\", \"its\", \"brakes,\", \"stopping\", \"an\", \"inch\", \"short.\", \"A\", \"swerving\", \"sports\", \"car\", \"precisely\", \"grazed\", \"the\", \"bumper\", \"of\", \"a\", \"parked\", \"van\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"hitting\", \"the\", \"animal.\", \"A\", \"discarded\", \"newspaper\", \"blew\", \"perfectly\", \"across\", \"the\", \"road,\", \"startling\", \"the\", \"dog\", \"just\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"make\", \"it\", \"freeze\", \"in\", \"the\", \"only\", \"safe\", \"triangle\", \"of\", \"asphalt\", \"between\", \"the\", \"sliding\", \"vehicles.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.72, 1.045, 1.521, 1.637, 1.811, 2.519, 3.007, 3.17, 3.564, 4.528, 4.702, 5.236, 5.642, 5.968, 6.641, 7.094, 7.21, 7.57, 7.674, 7.755, 8.081, 8.429, 8.789, 8.882, 9.149, 9.288, 10.275, 10.414, 11.029, 11.587, 11.865, 12.434, 12.829, 12.957, 13.549, 14.048, 14.153, 14.478, 14.733, 15.012, 15.128, 15.314, 15.453, 15.918, 16.034, 16.185, 16.544, 16.87, 17.427, 17.555, 18.065, 18.402, 18.507, 18.913], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.673, 0.975, 1.474, 1.591, 1.753, 2.368, 2.961, 3.077, 3.448, 4.087, 4.609, 5.166, 5.584, 5.886, 6.571, 7.047, 7.163, 7.512, 7.628, 7.697, 8.034, 8.359, 8.754, 8.835, 9.102, 9.218, 9.764, 10.344, 10.96, 11.529, 11.796, 12.388, 12.783, 12.899, 13.375, 14.002, 14.118, 14.42, 14.675, 14.977, 15.07, 15.279, 15.383, 15.883, 15.987, 16.103, 16.475, 16.835, 17.392, 17.485, 18.019, 18.367, 18.472, 18.866, 19.737]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(524, 42, 'Page 8', 'The dog sat, confused but completely unharmed. The old man rushed forward and scooped it up, his heart pounding.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"dog\", \"sat,\", \"confused\", \"but\", \"completely\", \"unharmed.\", \"The\", \"old\", \"man\", \"rushed\", \"forward\", \"and\", \"scooped\", \"it\", \"up,\", \"his\", \"heart\", \"pounding.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.58, 0.975, 1.509, 1.66, 2.194, 3.088, 3.262, 3.437, 3.669, 3.936, 4.331, 4.47, 4.783, 4.888, 5.097, 5.294, 5.573], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.511, 0.94, 1.474, 1.625, 2.136, 2.763, 3.204, 3.39, 3.611, 3.889, 4.296, 4.412, 4.76, 4.83, 5.062, 5.224, 5.503, 6.269]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(525, 42, 'Page 9', 'No massive powers were displayed. No lightning or super strength. Just a precisely arranged sequence of very lucky moments. Omar adjusted his backpack and walked home, knowing the smallest miracles save the most lives.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_42_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"No\", \"massive\", \"powers\", \"were\", \"displayed.\", \"No\", \"lightning\", \"or\", \"super\", \"strength.\", \"Just\", \"a\", \"precisely\", \"arranged\", \"sequence\", \"of\", \"very\", \"lucky\", \"moments.\", \"Omar\", \"adjusted\", \"his\", \"backpack\", \"and\", \"walked\", \"home,\", \"knowing\", \"the\", \"smallest\", \"miracles\", \"save\", \"the\", \"most\", \"lives.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.987, 1.416, 1.579, 2.601, 2.856, 3.39, 3.599, 3.982, 4.853, 5.085, 5.166, 5.805, 6.339, 6.931, 7.105, 7.419, 7.744, 9.079, 9.439, 9.868, 10.019, 10.519, 10.646, 10.96, 11.564, 11.889, 12.016, 12.527, 13.061, 13.351, 13.456, 13.758], \"end_times\": [0.348, 0.929, 1.382, 1.544, 2.276, 2.763, 3.309, 3.506, 3.924, 4.528, 5.05, 5.108, 5.747, 6.246, 6.873, 7.024, 7.361, 7.674, 8.382, 9.404, 9.834, 9.961, 10.461, 10.588, 10.913, 11.389, 11.842, 11.958, 12.457, 13.003, 13.317, 13.421, 13.677, 14.489]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(526, 43, 'Page 1', 'Far below the surface of the ocean, where sunlight softened into turquoise beams, there stood a hidden underwater city built among towering coral reefs. The spires of the city were woven directly into the living rock, shimmering with the brilliant colors of anemones and sea fans. This was Lumina, home to intelligent sea creatures who lived in harmony with the reef.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_43_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Far\", \"below\", \"the\", \"surface\", \"of\", \"the\", \"ocean,\", \"where\", \"sunlight\", \"softened\", \"into\", \"turquoise\", \"beams,\", \"there\", \"stood\", \"a\", \"hidden\", \"underwater\", \"city\", \"built\", \"among\", \"towering\", \"coral\", \"reefs.\", \"The\", \"spires\", \"of\", \"the\", \"city\", \"were\", \"woven\", \"directly\", \"into\", \"the\", \"living\", \"rock,\", \"shimmering\", \"with\", \"the\", \"brilliant\", \"colors\", \"of\", \"anemones\", \"and\", \"sea\", \"fans.\", \"This\", \"was\", \"Lumina,\", \"home\", \"to\", \"intelligent\", \"sea\", \"creatures\", \"who\", \"lived\", \"in\", \"harmony\", \"with\", \"the\", \"reef.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395, 0.673, 0.778, 1.161, 1.254, 1.405, 2.078, 2.322, 2.752, 3.239, 3.46, 4.04, 4.911, 5.143, 5.468, 5.584, 6.002, 6.629, 7.268, 7.593, 7.883, 8.44, 8.858, 10.112, 10.275, 10.751, 10.844, 10.971, 11.262, 11.447, 11.807, 12.388, 12.608, 12.725, 13.038, 13.688, 14.187, 14.327, 14.431, 14.872, 15.337, 15.453, 16.033, 16.196, 16.428, 17.45, 17.74, 17.949, 18.878, 19.168, 19.319, 19.969, 20.19, 20.689, 20.863, 21.095, 21.235, 21.652, 21.827, 21.966], \"end_times\": [0.337, 0.615, 0.743, 1.126, 1.207, 1.324, 1.962, 2.287, 2.705, 3.193, 3.39, 3.982, 4.667, 5.108, 5.41, 5.503, 5.886, 6.56, 6.989, 7.546, 7.814, 8.371, 8.777, 9.416, 10.228, 10.716, 10.797, 10.913, 11.204, 11.413, 11.761, 12.33, 12.55, 12.678, 12.968, 13.479, 14.152, 14.292, 14.396, 14.814, 15.267, 15.395, 15.987, 16.126, 16.37, 17.067, 17.67, 17.868, 18.599, 19.133, 19.238, 19.911, 20.132, 20.642, 20.805, 21.06, 21.153, 21.606, 21.792, 21.896, 22.523]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(527, 43, 'Page 2', 'Unlike human cities, Lumina had no roads. Its inhabitants traveled along gentle, invisible currents, guided by the glowing patterns woven into the coral walls.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_43_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Unlike\", \"human\", \"cities,\", \"Lumina\", \"had\", \"no\", \"roads.\", \"Its\", \"inhabitants\", \"traveled\", \"along\", \"gentle,\", \"invisible\", \"currents,\", \"guided\", \"by\", \"the\", \"glowing\", \"patterns\", \"woven\", \"into\", \"the\", \"coral\", \"walls.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.58, 0.894, 1.625, 2.032, 2.229, 2.426, 3.297, 3.518, 4.133, 4.563, 4.934, 5.41, 5.956, 6.722, 7.117, 7.268, 7.372, 7.744, 8.208, 8.545, 8.731, 8.835, 9.172], \"end_times\": [0.546, 0.836, 1.474, 1.974, 2.171, 2.345, 2.972, 3.471, 4.087, 4.528, 4.841, 5.364, 5.921, 6.571, 7.059, 7.21, 7.338, 7.686, 8.15, 8.498, 8.684, 8.8, 9.114, 9.845]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(528, 43, 'Page 3', 'At the heart of Lumina stood the Coral Crown, a massive, ancient structure that filtered the entire reef’s water, keeping the ocean clean and vibrant. It rested silently, maintained by the careful sweeping of specialized crab colonies and the gentle pruning of small, diligent fish.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_43_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"the\", \"heart\", \"of\", \"Lumina\", \"stood\", \"the\", \"Coral\", \"Crown,\", \"a\", \"massive,\", \"ancient\", \"structure\", \"that\", \"filtered\", \"the\", \"entire\", \"reefu2019s\", \"water,\", \"keeping\", \"the\", \"ocean\", \"clean\", \"and\", \"vibrant.\", \"It\", \"rested\", \"silently,\", \"maintained\", \"by\", \"the\", \"careful\", \"sweeping\", \"of\", \"specialized\", \"crab\", \"colonies\", \"and\", \"the\", \"gentle\", \"pruning\", \"of\", \"small,\", \"diligent\", \"fish.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.43, 0.673, 0.789, 1.265, 1.544, 1.672, 2.09, 2.833, 2.995, 3.518, 3.971, 4.702, 4.946, 5.41, 5.538, 6.014, 6.339, 7.082, 7.454, 7.593, 7.964, 8.394, 8.533, 9.776, 9.973, 10.403, 11.227, 11.784, 11.923, 12.04, 12.469, 12.899, 13.003, 13.688, 14.048, 14.838, 15.058, 15.186, 15.546, 15.987, 16.115, 16.556, 17.101], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.36, 0.639, 0.731, 1.173, 1.509, 1.614, 2.009, 2.682, 2.902, 3.495, 3.924, 4.586, 4.876, 5.375, 5.48, 5.956, 6.281, 6.838, 7.407, 7.523, 7.883, 8.324, 8.475, 9.172, 9.915, 10.333, 11.111, 11.738, 11.877, 11.993, 12.399, 12.852, 12.945, 13.63, 13.978, 14.594, 15.012, 15.128, 15.499, 15.929, 16.045, 16.521, 17.032, 17.786]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(529, 43, 'Page 4', 'One day, the Crown began to hum a low, unsettling vibration. The colors around it began to pale. A young octopus named Kael noticed the change immediately; the usually steady currents around his home felt sluggish and murky.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_43_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"day,\", \"the\", \"Crown\", \"began\", \"to\", \"hum\", \"a\", \"low,\", \"unsettling\", \"vibration.\", \"The\", \"colors\", \"around\", \"it\", \"began\", \"to\", \"pale.\", \"A\", \"young\", \"octopus\", \"named\", \"Kael\", \"noticed\", \"the\", \"change\", \"immediately;\", \"the\", \"usually\", \"steady\", \"currents\", \"around\", \"his\", \"home\", \"felt\", \"sluggish\", \"and\", \"murky.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.673, 0.801, 1.103, 1.44, 1.567, 1.788, 1.904, 2.31, 3.065, 4.307, 4.47, 4.83, 5.143, 5.248, 5.55, 5.666, 6.943, 7.105, 7.338, 7.883, 8.173, 8.568, 8.94, 9.056, 9.427, 10.53, 10.716, 11.157, 11.505, 11.889, 12.19, 12.353, 12.701, 13.003, 13.537, 13.688], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.65, 0.743, 1.057, 1.382, 1.498, 1.73, 1.823, 2.276, 3.007, 3.866, 4.423, 4.795, 5.097, 5.201, 5.503, 5.596, 6.246, 7.024, 7.279, 7.825, 8.104, 8.475, 8.905, 9.009, 9.392, 10.205, 10.635, 11.099, 11.447, 11.854, 12.132, 12.295, 12.643, 12.934, 13.479, 13.618, 14.35]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(530, 43, 'Page 5', 'Investigating the Crown, Kael realized that heavy, unrecognizable silt from the surface had settled deep within the complex coral filters, clogging the natural flow. It was too dense for the usual sweepers to reach.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_43_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Investigating\", \"the\", \"Crown,\", \"Kael\", \"realized\", \"that\", \"heavy,\", \"unrecognizable\", \"silt\", \"from\", \"the\", \"surface\", \"had\", \"settled\", \"deep\", \"within\", \"the\", \"complex\", \"coral\", \"filters,\", \"clogging\", \"the\", \"natural\", \"flow.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"too\", \"dense\", \"for\", \"the\", \"usual\", \"sweepers\", \"to\", \"reach.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.882, 0.998, 1.776, 2.078, 2.554, 2.74, 3.135, 4.075, 4.4, 4.586, 4.702, 5.468, 5.677, 6.049, 6.327, 6.618, 6.734, 7.326, 7.697, 8.522, 9.021, 9.137, 9.578, 11.088, 11.25, 11.413, 11.633, 12.016, 12.156, 12.295, 12.643, 13.096, 13.235], \"end_times\": [0.836, 0.952, 1.567, 2.009, 2.519, 2.67, 3.065, 4.017, 4.354, 4.54, 4.656, 5.387, 5.619, 6.002, 6.281, 6.571, 6.687, 7.256, 7.639, 8.348, 8.963, 9.091, 9.509, 10.136, 11.215, 11.355, 11.564, 11.958, 12.121, 12.225, 12.585, 13.05, 13.154, 13.839]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(531, 43, 'Page 6', 'Using his flexible tentacles, Kael reached deeply into the narrowest crevices of the Coral Crown. He didn\'t use force. Instead, he carefully rearranged the inner stones, creating new channels that forced a sharp, localized current to burst through the blockage. The silt washed away, and the vibrant hum returned to Lumina.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_43_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Using\", \"his\", \"flexible\", \"tentacles,\", \"Kael\", \"reached\", \"deeply\", \"into\", \"the\", \"narrowest\", \"crevices\", \"of\", \"the\", \"Coral\", \"Crown.\", \"He\", \"didn\'t\", \"use\", \"force.\", \"Instead,\", \"he\", \"carefully\", \"rearranged\", \"the\", \"inner\", \"stones,\", \"creating\", \"new\", \"channels\", \"that\", \"forced\", \"a\", \"sharp,\", \"localized\", \"current\", \"to\", \"burst\", \"through\", \"the\", \"blockage.\", \"The\", \"silt\", \"washed\", \"away,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"vibrant\", \"hum\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"Lumina.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.522, 0.685, 1.161, 2.09, 2.543, 2.961, 3.483, 3.704, 3.831, 4.342, 4.923, 5.027, 5.143, 5.48, 6.362, 6.513, 6.803, 7.059, 8.034, 8.905, 9.044, 9.567, 10.205, 10.333, 10.612, 11.471, 11.947, 12.121, 12.597, 12.794, 13.189, 13.293, 13.967, 14.594, 14.977, 15.128, 15.488, 15.778, 15.871, 16.661, 16.835, 17.102, 17.415, 18.007, 18.205, 18.332, 18.785, 19.052, 19.447, 19.575], \"end_times\": [0.476, 0.627, 1.126, 1.939, 2.461, 2.844, 3.425, 3.646, 3.773, 4.284, 4.865, 4.981, 5.097, 5.422, 6.037, 6.467, 6.745, 7.001, 7.709, 8.754, 8.975, 9.474, 10.159, 10.275, 10.542, 11.297, 11.877, 12.063, 12.55, 12.736, 13.131, 13.224, 13.793, 14.536, 14.931, 15.047, 15.43, 15.743, 15.848, 16.51, 16.777, 17.055, 17.38, 17.891, 18.158, 18.274, 18.739, 18.971, 19.424, 19.505, 20.248]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(532, 44, 'Page 1', 'In the deepest parts of the ocean, where darkness hummed like a quiet echo, lived a young humpback whale named Nakoa. Every year, whales crossed vast oceans guided by ancient songs passed from generation to generation. These songs told them where to find cold feeding grounds and warm waters for resting.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_44_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"the\", \"deepest\", \"parts\", \"of\", \"the\", \"ocean,\", \"where\", \"darkness\", \"hummed\", \"like\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"echo,\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"young\", \"humpback\", \"whale\", \"named\", \"Nakoa.\", \"Every\", \"year,\", \"whales\", \"crossed\", \"vast\", \"oceans\", \"guided\", \"by\", \"ancient\", \"songs\", \"passed\", \"from\", \"generation\", \"to\", \"generation.\", \"These\", \"songs\", \"told\", \"them\", \"where\", \"to\", \"find\", \"cold\", \"feeding\", \"grounds\", \"and\", \"warm\", \"waters\", \"for\", \"resting.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.406, 0.813, 1.091, 1.196, 1.335, 1.916, 2.183, 2.694, 3.1, 3.286, 3.367, 3.785, 4.447, 4.69, 4.795, 5.085, 5.596, 5.921, 6.13, 7.523, 7.895, 8.603, 8.986, 9.404, 9.81, 10.344, 10.658, 10.844, 11.25, 11.726, 12.086, 12.283, 12.864, 12.98, 14.594, 14.884, 15.302, 15.558, 15.709, 15.871, 15.964, 16.243, 16.568, 16.893, 17.264, 17.404, 17.647, 18.019, 18.193], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.36, 0.755, 1.057, 1.149, 1.265, 1.834, 2.125, 2.635, 3.053, 3.251, 3.309, 3.727, 4.272, 4.667, 4.714, 5.016, 5.526, 5.875, 6.107, 6.827, 7.837, 8.394, 8.928, 9.346, 9.741, 10.275, 10.623, 10.762, 11.192, 11.656, 12.051, 12.225, 12.806, 12.922, 13.781, 14.838, 15.244, 15.523, 15.674, 15.848, 15.918, 16.173, 16.51, 16.858, 17.218, 17.346, 17.601, 17.961, 18.135, 18.901]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(533, 44, 'Page 2', 'But Nakoa had lost his way. During an unusually strong subsurface storm, he had been separated from his pod. When the waters calmed, he was alone in a vast, unfamiliar expanse of blue.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_44_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"Nakoa\", \"had\", \"lost\", \"his\", \"way.\", \"During\", \"an\", \"unusually\", \"strong\", \"subsurface\", \"storm,\", \"he\", \"had\", \"been\", \"separated\", \"from\", \"his\", \"pod.\", \"When\", \"the\", \"waters\", \"calmed,\", \"he\", \"was\", \"alone\", \"in\", \"a\", \"vast,\", \"unfamiliar\", \"expanse\", \"of\", \"blue.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.731, 0.882, 1.184, 1.358, 2.009, 2.31, 2.438, 3.053, 3.425, 4.017, 4.632, 4.748, 4.865, 5.062, 5.584, 5.77, 5.921, 6.896, 7.094, 7.198, 7.546, 8.092, 8.231, 8.394, 8.8, 8.916, 9.009, 9.52, 10.24, 10.704, 10.82], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.673, 0.836, 1.138, 1.3, 1.765, 2.276, 2.368, 2.995, 3.355, 3.994, 4.481, 4.714, 4.83, 5.004, 5.538, 5.724, 5.863, 6.385, 7.07, 7.163, 7.488, 8.046, 8.173, 8.336, 8.754, 8.87, 8.94, 9.462, 10.182, 10.67, 10.762, 11.378]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(534, 44, 'Page 3', 'He tried to sing the traveling song, calling out to find an echo of his family. But his voice sounded thin in the immense empty space, and the only reply was the low, steady rumble of shifting tectonic plates far below.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_44_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"tried\", \"to\", \"sing\", \"the\", \"traveling\", \"song,\", \"calling\", \"out\", \"to\", \"find\", \"an\", \"echo\", \"of\", \"his\", \"family.\", \"But\", \"his\", \"voice\", \"sounded\", \"thin\", \"in\", \"the\", \"immense\", \"empty\", \"space,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"only\", \"reply\", \"was\", \"the\", \"low,\", \"steady\", \"rumble\", \"of\", \"shifting\", \"tectonic\", \"plates\", \"far\", \"below.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.592, 0.708, 0.975, 1.091, 1.591, 2.229, 2.624, 2.798, 2.902, 3.158, 3.286, 3.576, 3.704, 3.855, 4.795, 4.992, 5.143, 5.422, 5.793, 6.095, 6.211, 6.339, 6.734, 7.036, 7.744, 7.93, 8.069, 8.371, 8.812, 8.986, 9.149, 9.474, 9.903, 10.298, 10.449, 10.902, 11.494, 11.9, 12.225], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.557, 0.639, 0.917, 1.045, 1.521, 2.055, 2.566, 2.763, 2.844, 3.111, 3.228, 3.506, 3.646, 3.796, 4.47, 4.957, 5.085, 5.399, 5.735, 6.026, 6.165, 6.281, 6.687, 6.989, 7.593, 7.883, 7.999, 8.29, 8.731, 8.928, 9.067, 9.427, 9.822, 10.252, 10.368, 10.832, 11.424, 11.819, 12.156, 12.864]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(535, 44, 'Page 4', 'Frightened, Nakoa began swimming faster, but directionless movement only exhausted him.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_44_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Frightened,\", \"Nakoa\", \"began\", \"swimming\", \"faster,\", \"but\", \"directionless\", \"movement\", \"only\", \"exhausted\", \"him.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.801, 1.207, 1.509, 1.881, 2.659, 2.856, 3.495, 3.913, 4.191, 4.725], \"end_times\": [0.685, 1.149, 1.451, 1.823, 2.45, 2.821, 3.437, 3.843, 4.133, 4.679, 5.155]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(536, 44, 'Page 5', 'He eventually stopped, letting himself drift slowly in the silence. As he calmed, he began to hear something entirely different. It wasn\'t the loud, echoing call of whales. It was the faint, rhythmic clicking of a massive school of tiny shrimp moving in a coordinated pattern, chasing a specific nutrient-rich current.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_44_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"eventually\", \"stopped,\", \"letting\", \"himself\", \"drift\", \"slowly\", \"in\", \"the\", \"silence.\", \"As\", \"he\", \"calmed,\", \"he\", \"began\", \"to\", \"hear\", \"something\", \"entirely\", \"different.\", \"It\", \"wasn\'t\", \"the\", \"loud,\", \"echoing\", \"call\", \"of\", \"whales.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"the\", \"faint,\", \"rhythmic\", \"clicking\", \"of\", \"a\", \"massive\", \"school\", \"of\", \"tiny\", \"shrimp\", \"moving\", \"in\", \"a\", \"coordinated\", \"pattern,\", \"chasing\", \"a\", \"specific\", \"nutrient-rich\", \"current.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.859, 1.451, 1.73, 2.101, 2.426, 2.833, 2.926, 3.042, 4.505, 4.725, 4.853, 5.782, 5.933, 6.316, 6.467, 6.745, 7.129, 7.674, 8.812, 8.975, 9.253, 9.404, 10.101, 10.577, 10.937, 11.053, 12.283, 12.434, 12.597, 12.736, 13.154, 13.618, 14.036, 14.153, 14.245, 14.663, 15.046, 15.162, 15.545, 16.068, 16.428, 16.521, 16.602, 17.194, 17.705, 18.123, 18.204, 18.785, 19.528], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.813, 1.358, 1.695, 2.043, 2.368, 2.798, 2.891, 2.995, 3.692, 4.667, 4.783, 5.457, 5.863, 6.258, 6.385, 6.676, 7.07, 7.628, 8.208, 8.928, 9.218, 9.323, 9.927, 10.495, 10.879, 10.983, 11.68, 12.399, 12.55, 12.666, 13.073, 13.549, 13.978, 14.095, 14.176, 14.629, 14.988, 15.093, 15.476, 15.859, 16.381, 16.486, 16.544, 17.148, 17.624, 18.076, 18.146, 18.703, 19.481, 20.154]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(537, 44, 'Page 6', 'Nakoa realized he didn\'t need to sing the song perfectly to find his way; he could read the ocean itself. He aligned himself with the current the shrimp were following, a path that naturally circled back toward the major migratory routes. He followed the ocean\'s silent map instead of a loud voice, eventually reuniting with the distant calls of his pod.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_44_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Nakoa\", \"realized\", \"he\", \"didn\'t\", \"need\", \"to\", \"sing\", \"the\", \"song\", \"perfectly\", \"to\", \"find\", \"his\", \"way;\", \"he\", \"could\", \"read\", \"the\", \"ocean\", \"itself.\", \"He\", \"aligned\", \"himself\", \"with\", \"the\", \"current\", \"the\", \"shrimp\", \"were\", \"following,\", \"a\", \"path\", \"that\", \"naturally\", \"circled\", \"back\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"major\", \"migratory\", \"routes.\", \"He\", \"followed\", \"the\", \"ocean\'s\", \"silent\", \"map\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"a\", \"loud\", \"voice,\", \"eventually\", \"reuniting\", \"with\", \"the\", \"distant\", \"calls\", \"of\", \"his\", \"pod.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.58, 1.045, 1.138, 1.37, 1.544, 1.637, 1.846, 1.962, 2.241, 2.717, 2.821, 3.088, 3.262, 3.727, 3.843, 4.029, 4.226, 4.377, 4.714, 6.142, 6.316, 6.676, 7.07, 7.221, 7.338, 7.779, 7.93, 8.243, 8.417, 9.242, 9.381, 9.671, 9.857, 10.344, 10.716, 10.983, 11.238, 11.355, 11.726, 12.388, 13.781, 13.967, 14.385, 14.535, 14.977, 15.476, 15.894, 16.289, 16.393, 16.498, 16.869, 17.751, 18.518, 19.261, 19.435, 19.551, 19.969, 20.329, 20.445, 20.608], \"end_times\": [0.522, 1.01, 1.091, 1.335, 1.521, 1.591, 1.8, 1.916, 2.171, 2.67, 2.763, 3.03, 3.193, 3.611, 3.796, 3.982, 4.18, 4.296, 4.656, 5.329, 6.258, 6.641, 7.024, 7.187, 7.291, 7.721, 7.872, 8.197, 8.371, 9.067, 9.3, 9.636, 9.799, 10.286, 10.681, 10.925, 11.204, 11.308, 11.668, 12.318, 12.968, 13.897, 14.35, 14.466, 14.93, 15.406, 15.778, 16.254, 16.347, 16.416, 16.799, 17.426, 18.402, 19.191, 19.4, 19.505, 19.911, 20.282, 20.387, 20.538, 21.269]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(538, 45, 'Page 1', 'Near a wide stretch of sandy seabed lived an octopus named Arin. Unlike reef creatures surrounded by color and structure, Arin’s world was open and exposed. Over generations, his kind had mastered the art of camouflage, able to change their skin to perfectly match the pale, rippling sand, the shadows of passing clouds, or the texture of scattered shells.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_45_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Near\", \"a\", \"wide\", \"stretch\", \"of\", \"sandy\", \"seabed\", \"lived\", \"an\", \"octopus\", \"named\", \"Arin.\", \"Unlike\", \"reef\", \"creatures\", \"surrounded\", \"by\", \"color\", \"and\", \"structure,\", \"Arinu2019s\", \"world\", \"was\", \"open\", \"and\", \"exposed.\", \"Over\", \"generations,\", \"his\", \"kind\", \"had\", \"mastered\", \"the\", \"art\", \"of\", \"camouflage,\", \"able\", \"to\", \"change\", \"their\", \"skin\", \"to\", \"perfectly\", \"match\", \"the\", \"pale,\", \"rippling\", \"sand,\", \"the\", \"shadows\", \"of\", \"passing\", \"clouds,\", \"or\", \"the\", \"texture\", \"of\", \"scattered\", \"shells.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.522, 0.848, 1.196, 1.324, 1.753, 2.38, 2.647, 2.763, 3.32, 3.587, 4.865, 5.375, 5.654, 6.095, 6.571, 6.78, 7.21, 7.419, 8.499, 8.893, 9.195, 9.404, 9.915, 10.159, 11.552, 11.854, 12.655, 12.899, 13.293, 13.479, 13.967, 14.106, 14.338, 14.466, 15.662, 16.01, 16.138, 16.486, 16.683, 17.043, 17.194, 17.682, 17.995, 18.123, 18.46, 18.878, 19.748, 19.899, 20.306, 20.433, 20.828, 21.234, 21.374, 21.49, 21.989, 22.082, 22.488], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.464, 0.813, 1.149, 1.254, 1.672, 2.229, 2.612, 2.705, 3.251, 3.529, 4.052, 5.306, 5.584, 6.06, 6.536, 6.699, 7.14, 7.349, 8.057, 8.858, 9.149, 9.311, 9.799, 10.101, 10.948, 11.796, 12.608, 12.817, 13.235, 13.41, 13.932, 14.036, 14.292, 14.396, 15.337, 15.975, 16.068, 16.451, 16.637, 16.962, 17.113, 17.612, 17.937, 18.065, 18.436, 18.808, 19.365, 19.853, 20.271, 20.364, 20.77, 21.211, 21.316, 21.443, 21.954, 22.036, 22.453, 23.173]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(539, 45, 'Page 2', 'Arin was proud of his ability. He could become entirely invisible, hiding from sharks or rays passing overhead.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_45_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Arin\", \"was\", \"proud\", \"of\", \"his\", \"ability.\", \"He\", \"could\", \"become\", \"entirely\", \"invisible,\", \"hiding\", \"from\", \"sharks\", \"or\", \"rays\", \"passing\", \"overhead.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.511, 0.685, 0.964, 1.057, 1.184, 2.043, 2.183, 2.345, 2.647, 3.251, 4.11, 4.458, 4.656, 5.097, 5.294, 5.584, 5.933], \"end_times\": [0.453, 0.615, 0.929, 1.01, 1.149, 1.718, 2.148, 2.322, 2.612, 3.204, 3.866, 4.412, 4.586, 5.027, 5.224, 5.526, 5.886, 6.548]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(540, 45, 'Page 3', 'One evening, a violent undersea landslide occurred miles away, sending a massive, thick cloud of turbid mud rushing across the usually clear sandy plains. The water turned dark and chaotic.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_45_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"evening,\", \"a\", \"violent\", \"undersea\", \"landslide\", \"occurred\", \"miles\", \"away,\", \"sending\", \"a\", \"massive,\", \"thick\", \"cloud\", \"of\", \"turbid\", \"mud\", \"rushing\", \"across\", \"the\", \"usually\", \"clear\", \"sandy\", \"plains.\", \"The\", \"water\", \"turned\", \"dark\", \"and\", \"chaotic.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.929, 1.091, 1.579, 2.067, 2.705, 3.135, 3.541, 4.145, 4.516, 4.632, 5.236, 5.573, 6.06, 6.177, 6.629, 7.001, 7.442, 7.872, 8.034, 8.557, 9.033, 9.462, 10.542, 10.739, 11.088, 11.436, 11.865, 12.063], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.871, 0.998, 1.509, 2.009, 2.682, 3.053, 3.495, 3.994, 4.47, 4.551, 5.19, 5.492, 6.014, 6.118, 6.56, 6.885, 7.384, 7.825, 7.953, 8.475, 8.916, 9.404, 10.101, 10.681, 11.029, 11.366, 11.784, 12.005, 12.957]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(541, 45, 'Page 4', 'Camouflage became useless. Trying to blend into a swirling storm of mud meant Arin was blind and disoriented, tumbling helplessly in the heavy flow.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_45_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Camouflage\", \"became\", \"useless.\", \"Trying\", \"to\", \"blend\", \"into\", \"a\", \"swirling\", \"storm\", \"of\", \"mud\", \"meant\", \"Arin\", \"was\", \"blind\", \"and\", \"disoriented,\", \"tumbling\", \"helplessly\", \"in\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"flow.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.778, 1.149, 2.392, 2.786, 2.902, 3.309, 3.553, 3.634, 4.087, 4.412, 4.539, 4.818, 5.074, 5.399, 5.573, 5.991, 6.107, 7.314, 7.848, 8.452, 8.568, 8.696, 8.986], \"end_times\": [0.743, 1.091, 1.788, 2.728, 2.844, 3.239, 3.483, 3.576, 4.029, 4.365, 4.47, 4.76, 5.004, 5.352, 5.515, 5.933, 6.06, 6.931, 7.779, 8.406, 8.522, 8.638, 8.916, 9.567]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(542, 45, 'Page 5', 'He quickly realized hiding was the wrong strategy. He needed stability, not invisibility. He grabbed a heavy, discarded conch shell he had often ignored. He tucked himself tightly inside its smooth curves, allowing the dense weight of the shell to anchor him firmly to the firmest part of the seabed while the chaotic mudstorm blasted harmlessly over the hard exterior.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_45_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"quickly\", \"realized\", \"hiding\", \"was\", \"the\", \"wrong\", \"strategy.\", \"He\", \"needed\", \"stability,\", \"not\", \"invisibility.\", \"He\", \"grabbed\", \"a\", \"heavy,\", \"discarded\", \"conch\", \"shell\", \"he\", \"had\", \"often\", \"ignored.\", \"He\", \"tucked\", \"himself\", \"tightly\", \"inside\", \"its\", \"smooth\", \"curves,\", \"allowing\", \"the\", \"dense\", \"weight\", \"of\", \"the\", \"shell\", \"to\", \"anchor\", \"him\", \"firmly\", \"to\", \"the\", \"firmest\", \"part\", \"of\", \"the\", \"seabed\", \"while\", \"the\", \"chaotic\", \"mudstorm\", \"blasted\", \"harmlessly\", \"over\", \"the\", \"hard\", \"exterior.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.662, 1.184, 1.533, 1.683, 1.8, 2.078, 3.019, 3.181, 3.471, 4.331, 4.54, 5.863, 6.037, 6.351, 6.444, 6.792, 7.326, 7.686, 8.046, 8.139, 8.278, 8.58, 9.555, 9.718, 9.985, 10.391, 10.786, 11.204, 11.355, 11.738, 12.388, 12.864, 12.992, 13.34, 13.63, 13.735, 13.851, 14.164, 14.304, 14.64, 14.849, 15.325, 15.465, 15.592, 16.01, 16.219, 16.301, 16.417, 17.16, 17.404, 17.508, 18.03, 18.669, 19.191, 19.784, 19.981, 20.109, 20.364], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.604, 1.126, 1.498, 1.637, 1.753, 2.009, 2.81, 3.123, 3.425, 4.18, 4.493, 5.422, 5.979, 6.327, 6.385, 6.745, 7.268, 7.628, 7.964, 8.104, 8.231, 8.545, 9.172, 9.671, 9.961, 10.333, 10.739, 11.169, 11.32, 11.668, 12.318, 12.817, 12.934, 13.282, 13.584, 13.688, 13.804, 14.106, 14.222, 14.582, 14.756, 15.256, 15.407, 15.534, 15.952, 16.184, 16.266, 16.37, 16.835, 17.38, 17.473, 17.961, 18.588, 19.133, 19.714, 19.935, 20.051, 20.318, 21.223]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(543, 45, 'Page 6', 'He survived the chaos not by relying on his greatest talent, but by adapting to the situation that rendered it useless.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_45_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"survived\", \"the\", \"chaos\", \"not\", \"by\", \"relying\", \"on\", \"his\", \"greatest\", \"talent,\", \"but\", \"by\", \"adapting\", \"to\", \"the\", \"situation\", \"that\", \"rendered\", \"it\", \"useless.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.755, 0.859, 1.289, 1.463, 1.625, 2.055, 2.159, 2.299, 2.659, 3.286, 3.471, 3.634, 4.098, 4.203, 4.307, 4.853, 5.004, 5.329, 5.457], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.72, 0.824, 1.231, 1.428, 1.556, 2.009, 2.125, 2.252, 2.624, 3.17, 3.437, 3.576, 4.052, 4.145, 4.272, 4.818, 4.957, 5.294, 5.387, 6.177]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(544, 46, 'Page 1', 'In a warm, shallow sea filled with dancing light lived a coral reef that never slept. Parrotfish scraped gently at coral walls, tiny shrimp snapped in hidden crevices, and bright angelfish darted through tunnels of color. It was a chaotic, beautiful symphony of survival.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"warm,\", \"shallow\", \"sea\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"dancing\", \"light\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"coral\", \"reef\", \"that\", \"never\", \"slept.\", \"Parrotfish\", \"scraped\", \"gently\", \"at\", \"coral\", \"walls,\", \"tiny\", \"shrimp\", \"snapped\", \"in\", \"hidden\", \"crevices,\", \"and\", \"bright\", \"angelfish\", \"darted\", \"through\", \"tunnels\", \"of\", \"color.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"a\", \"chaotic,\", \"beautiful\", \"symphony\", \"of\", \"survival.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.372, 0.894, 1.405, 1.788, 2.183, 2.368, 2.844, 3.529, 3.82, 3.901, 4.319, 4.644, 4.853, 5.132, 6.2, 6.85, 7.279, 7.674, 7.802, 8.139, 9.056, 9.404, 9.787, 10.194, 10.31, 10.565, 11.494, 11.691, 11.97, 12.608, 12.922, 13.142, 13.491, 13.607, 14.698, 14.849, 14.988, 15.058, 15.79, 16.277, 16.73, 16.834], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.313, 0.836, 1.312, 1.695, 2.136, 2.322, 2.775, 3.146, 3.785, 3.843, 4.238, 4.586, 4.795, 5.074, 5.689, 6.792, 7.198, 7.628, 7.744, 8.081, 8.731, 9.358, 9.706, 10.159, 10.252, 10.519, 11.285, 11.633, 11.912, 12.539, 12.899, 13.108, 13.444, 13.537, 14.094, 14.814, 14.942, 15.023, 15.708, 16.208, 16.672, 16.776, 17.647]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(545, 46, 'Page 2', 'A small, silver damselfish named Elara knew the rhythm of the reef perfectly. She knew when the predatory moray eels hunted and when the larger groupers swept through.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"small,\", \"silver\", \"damselfish\", \"named\", \"Elara\", \"knew\", \"the\", \"rhythm\", \"of\", \"the\", \"reef\", \"perfectly.\", \"She\", \"knew\", \"when\", \"the\", \"predatory\", \"moray\", \"eels\", \"hunted\", \"and\", \"when\", \"the\", \"larger\", \"groupers\", \"swept\", \"through.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.673, 1.033, 1.695, 1.939, 2.647, 2.879, 3.007, 3.297, 3.379, 3.506, 3.738, 4.69, 4.899, 5.097, 5.259, 5.387, 5.979, 6.42, 6.78, 7.407, 7.663, 7.825, 7.953, 8.324, 8.754, 9.079], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.639, 0.987, 1.625, 1.892, 2.438, 2.833, 2.949, 3.239, 3.344, 3.448, 3.68, 4.412, 4.841, 5.062, 5.224, 5.329, 5.909, 6.351, 6.722, 7.198, 7.628, 7.779, 7.895, 8.278, 8.719, 9.033, 9.706]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(546, 46, 'Page 3', 'One morning, she woke to absolute silence.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"morning,\", \"she\", \"woke\", \"to\", \"absolute\", \"silence.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.65, 0.813, 1.057, 1.207, 1.718], \"end_times\": [0.313, 0.627, 0.755, 1.022, 1.126, 1.683, 2.461]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(547, 46, 'Page 4', 'The reef was still vibrant with color, but the movement had stopped. The parrotfish hovered nervously in caves. The shrimp were still. The crabs didn\'t click. A heavy, invisible tension weighed on the water.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"reef\", \"was\", \"still\", \"vibrant\", \"with\", \"color,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"movement\", \"had\", \"stopped.\", \"The\", \"parrotfish\", \"hovered\", \"nervously\", \"in\", \"caves.\", \"The\", \"shrimp\", \"were\", \"still.\", \"The\", \"crabs\", \"didn\'t\", \"click.\", \"A\", \"heavy,\", \"invisible\", \"tension\", \"weighed\", \"on\", \"the\", \"water.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.499, 0.627, 0.871, 1.254, 1.405, 1.858, 2.032, 2.148, 2.508, 2.659, 3.46, 3.622, 4.18, 4.505, 4.957, 5.074, 5.805, 5.979, 6.258, 6.42, 7.105, 7.268, 7.616, 7.883, 8.615, 8.812, 9.183, 9.741, 10.194, 10.495, 10.6, 10.716], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.441, 0.592, 0.813, 1.231, 1.358, 1.788, 1.997, 2.101, 2.473, 2.612, 3.216, 3.564, 4.133, 4.47, 4.911, 5.016, 5.631, 5.921, 6.211, 6.385, 6.931, 7.221, 7.57, 7.848, 8.371, 8.696, 9.16, 9.706, 10.112, 10.461, 10.565, 10.67, 11.331]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(548, 46, 'Page 5', 'Elara swam cautiously to the reef\'s edge and looked out into the deeper blue. There, circling slowly, was an enormous shadow—a massive tiger shark, silently patrolling the boundary of their home. Its presence had terrified the entire ecosystem into stillness.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elara\", \"swam\", \"cautiously\", \"to\", \"the\", \"reef\'s\", \"edge\", \"and\", \"looked\", \"out\", \"into\", \"the\", \"deeper\", \"blue.\", \"There,\", \"circling\", \"slowly,\", \"was\", \"an\", \"enormous\", \"shadowu2014a\", \"massive\", \"tiger\", \"shark,\", \"silently\", \"patrolling\", \"the\", \"boundary\", \"of\", \"their\", \"home.\", \"Its\", \"presence\", \"had\", \"terrified\", \"the\", \"entire\", \"ecosystem\", \"into\", \"stillness.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.627, 0.975, 1.544, 1.66, 1.788, 2.148, 2.612, 2.868, 3.146, 3.379, 3.611, 3.727, 4.075, 5.108, 5.724, 6.269, 6.978, 7.198, 7.326, 7.837, 8.847, 9.369, 9.764, 10.53, 11.18, 11.726, 11.842, 12.307, 12.423, 12.632, 13.886, 14.129, 14.605, 14.768, 15.395, 15.534, 16.033, 16.742, 16.997], \"end_times\": [0.569, 0.894, 1.486, 1.602, 1.73, 2.067, 2.531, 2.81, 3.1, 3.309, 3.541, 3.68, 4.017, 4.505, 5.608, 6.2, 6.861, 7.152, 7.268, 7.79, 8.731, 9.323, 9.706, 10.252, 11.122, 11.668, 11.796, 12.249, 12.365, 12.585, 13.073, 14.071, 14.571, 14.721, 15.348, 15.464, 15.975, 16.684, 16.927, 17.833]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(549, 46, 'Page 6', 'Waiting meant starvation for the smaller creatures.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Waiting\", \"meant\", \"starvation\", \"for\", \"the\", \"smaller\", \"creatures.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.569, 0.778, 1.405, 1.556, 1.672, 2.043], \"end_times\": [0.522, 0.731, 1.347, 1.509, 1.625, 1.985, 2.879]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(550, 46, 'Page 7', 'Elara didn\'t panic. She realized the shark hunted by seeking isolated movement. She quickly swam between the hiding places, communicating with subtle fin flicks to the vast schools of tiny silversides and neon tetras. Instead of hiding, they gathered into an enormous, shifting sphere thousands of fish strong. They moved as one massive, shimmering entity, flashing confusing light in every direction.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Elara\", \"didn\'t\", \"panic.\", \"She\", \"realized\", \"the\", \"shark\", \"hunted\", \"by\", \"seeking\", \"isolated\", \"movement.\", \"She\", \"quickly\", \"swam\", \"between\", \"the\", \"hiding\", \"places,\", \"communicating\", \"with\", \"subtle\", \"fin\", \"flicks\", \"to\", \"the\", \"vast\", \"schools\", \"of\", \"tiny\", \"silversides\", \"and\", \"neon\", \"tetras.\", \"Instead\", \"of\", \"hiding,\", \"they\", \"gathered\", \"into\", \"an\", \"enormous,\", \"shifting\", \"sphere\", \"thousands\", \"of\", \"fish\", \"strong.\", \"They\", \"moved\", \"as\", \"one\", \"massive,\", \"shimmering\", \"entity,\", \"flashing\", \"confusing\", \"light\", \"in\", \"every\", \"direction.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.569, 0.824, 1.672, 1.881, 2.368, 2.485, 2.798, 3.216, 3.413, 3.855, 4.412, 5.387, 5.596, 5.968, 6.327, 6.653, 6.757, 7.082, 7.86, 8.591, 8.766, 9.102, 9.346, 9.741, 9.88, 9.996, 10.426, 10.89, 11.006, 11.401, 12.109, 12.283, 12.632, 13.769, 14.153, 14.269, 14.989, 15.175, 15.662, 15.929, 16.034, 16.661, 17.16, 17.613, 18.112, 18.228, 18.518, 19.412, 19.633, 19.981, 20.167, 20.446, 20.945, 21.444, 22.28, 22.733, 23.302, 23.557, 23.708, 23.975], \"end_times\": [0.522, 0.789, 1.393, 1.811, 2.334, 2.438, 2.728, 3.146, 3.332, 3.762, 4.354, 5.004, 5.526, 5.909, 6.269, 6.629, 6.722, 7.036, 7.686, 8.545, 8.707, 9.056, 9.276, 9.683, 9.822, 9.95, 10.344, 10.832, 10.948, 11.331, 12.063, 12.202, 12.574, 13.328, 14.118, 14.211, 14.838, 15.14, 15.593, 15.848, 15.987, 16.603, 17.09, 17.555, 18.077, 18.17, 18.46, 19.087, 19.575, 19.935, 20.086, 20.388, 20.922, 21.374, 22.036, 22.686, 23.244, 23.511, 23.627, 23.929, 24.799]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(551, 46, 'Page 8', 'The massive shark, unable to target a single meal in the dazzling display, eventually lost interest and drifted away into the deeper ocean. The rhythm of the reef quickly returned.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_46_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"massive\", \"shark,\", \"unable\", \"to\", \"target\", \"a\", \"single\", \"meal\", \"in\", \"the\", \"dazzling\", \"display,\", \"eventually\", \"lost\", \"interest\", \"and\", \"drifted\", \"away\", \"into\", \"the\", \"deeper\", \"ocean.\", \"The\", \"rhythm\", \"of\", \"the\", \"reef\", \"quickly\", \"returned.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.685, 1.207, 1.649, 1.788, 2.218, 2.334, 2.763, 3.042, 3.146, 3.274, 3.75, 4.679, 5.248, 5.608, 6.06, 6.2, 6.594, 6.838, 7.047, 7.163, 7.523, 8.812, 8.998, 9.323, 9.451, 9.59, 9.903, 10.333], \"end_times\": [0.221, 0.65, 1.115, 1.614, 1.718, 2.159, 2.252, 2.717, 2.995, 3.1, 3.216, 3.692, 4.435, 5.19, 5.538, 6.002, 6.153, 6.56, 6.803, 6.978, 7.117, 7.454, 8.115, 8.94, 9.265, 9.392, 9.52, 9.834, 10.263, 11.099]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(552, 47, 'Page 1', 'Far below where sunlight could reach, where the ocean turned dark blue and nearly black, a small exploration submarine named Aurora descended carefully into the abyss. Inside, scientists tracked pressure levels and mapped the unseen floor.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Far\", \"below\", \"where\", \"sunlight\", \"could\", \"reach,\", \"where\", \"the\", \"ocean\", \"turned\", \"dark\", \"blue\", \"and\", \"nearly\", \"black,\", \"a\", \"small\", \"exploration\", \"submarine\", \"named\", \"Aurora\", \"descended\", \"carefully\", \"into\", \"the\", \"abyss.\", \"Inside,\", \"scientists\", \"tracked\", \"pressure\", \"levels\", \"and\", \"mapped\", \"the\", \"unseen\", \"floor.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.383, 0.697, 0.906, 1.312, 1.521, 2.113, 2.334, 2.485, 2.879, 3.251, 3.599, 3.971, 4.145, 4.516, 5.341, 5.503, 5.863, 6.583, 7.117, 7.396, 8.115, 8.638, 9.149, 9.369, 9.497, 10.855, 11.784, 12.388, 12.736, 13.096, 13.502, 13.688, 13.967, 14.106, 14.547], \"end_times\": [0.325, 0.65, 0.859, 1.277, 1.463, 1.939, 2.299, 2.403, 2.821, 3.17, 3.529, 3.913, 4.075, 4.458, 5.097, 5.41, 5.793, 6.513, 7.07, 7.349, 7.872, 8.58, 9.102, 9.3, 9.439, 10.043, 11.575, 12.353, 12.678, 13.061, 13.444, 13.63, 13.932, 14.036, 14.478, 15.093]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(553, 47, 'Page 2', 'Their mission was to find a legendary hydrothermal vent system, untouched and unmapped.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Their\", \"mission\", \"was\", \"to\", \"find\", \"a\", \"legendary\", \"hydrothermal\", \"vent\", \"system,\", \"untouched\", \"and\", \"unmapped.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.627, 0.778, 0.882, 1.138, 1.219, 1.776, 2.403, 2.612, 3.367, 3.971, 4.214], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.58, 0.731, 0.836, 1.08, 1.161, 1.718, 2.357, 2.566, 3.088, 3.924, 4.133, 4.969]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(554, 47, 'Page 3', 'As they dropped deeper, their primary sonar system failed. A sudden pressure spike damaged the sensitive array. Without sonar, moving through the total darkness of the deep trench was dangerous; they could easily collide with an unseen rock pillar.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"they\", \"dropped\", \"deeper,\", \"their\", \"primary\", \"sonar\", \"system\", \"failed.\", \"A\", \"sudden\", \"pressure\", \"spike\", \"damaged\", \"the\", \"sensitive\", \"array.\", \"Without\", \"sonar,\", \"moving\", \"through\", \"the\", \"total\", \"darkness\", \"of\", \"the\", \"deep\", \"trench\", \"was\", \"dangerous;\", \"they\", \"could\", \"easily\", \"collide\", \"with\", \"an\", \"unseen\", \"rock\", \"pillar.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.464, 0.755, 1.231, 1.44, 1.881, 2.241, 2.647, 3.483, 3.634, 3.959, 4.331, 4.702, 5.19, 5.317, 5.77, 6.49, 6.908, 7.663, 7.988, 8.255, 8.359, 8.673, 9.125, 9.242, 9.358, 9.625, 9.973, 10.147, 11.215, 11.389, 11.575, 11.981, 12.411, 12.574, 12.69, 13.131, 13.363], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.418, 0.731, 1.173, 1.393, 1.823, 2.183, 2.554, 3.158, 3.553, 3.901, 4.296, 4.644, 5.143, 5.259, 5.747, 6.246, 6.827, 7.512, 7.941, 8.22, 8.324, 8.626, 9.079, 9.195, 9.311, 9.567, 9.927, 10.089, 10.832, 11.355, 11.517, 11.923, 12.388, 12.539, 12.632, 13.061, 13.317, 13.886]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(555, 47, 'Page 4', 'The captain considered aborting the mission.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"captain\", \"considered\", \"aborting\", \"the\", \"mission.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.662, 1.103, 1.486, 1.591], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.604, 1.08, 1.44, 1.556, 2.229]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(556, 47, 'Page 5', 'However, a marine biologist on board diverted power from the external floodlights to the highly sensitive passive acoustic microphones.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"However,\", \"a\", \"marine\", \"biologist\", \"on\", \"board\", \"diverted\", \"power\", \"from\", \"the\", \"external\", \"floodlights\", \"to\", \"the\", \"highly\", \"sensitive\", \"passive\", \"acoustic\", \"microphones.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.755, 0.882, 1.126, 1.672, 1.788, 2.241, 2.694, 3.03, 3.204, 3.332, 3.75, 4.481, 4.667, 4.807, 5.178, 5.759, 6.258, 6.722], \"end_times\": [0.685, 0.813, 1.103, 1.625, 1.741, 2.09, 2.647, 2.972, 3.17, 3.274, 3.704, 4.307, 4.598, 4.737, 5.12, 5.7, 6.235, 6.676, 7.57]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(557, 47, 'Page 6', 'They turned off the loud engine thrusts and simply listened. In the absolute darkness, they began to hear a low, bubbling hiss. The sound of superheated water blasting forced through narrow rock vents.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"They\", \"turned\", \"off\", \"the\", \"loud\", \"engine\", \"thrusts\", \"and\", \"simply\", \"listened.\", \"In\", \"the\", \"absolute\", \"darkness,\", \"they\", \"began\", \"to\", \"hear\", \"a\", \"low,\", \"bubbling\", \"hiss.\", \"The\", \"sound\", \"of\", \"superheated\", \"water\", \"blasting\", \"forced\", \"through\", \"narrow\", \"rock\", \"vents.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.604, 0.766, 0.894, 1.138, 1.428, 1.823, 1.985, 2.368, 3.587, 3.762, 3.913, 4.528, 5.143, 5.341, 5.724, 5.863, 6.084, 6.188, 6.525, 7.024, 7.837, 8.034, 8.394, 8.522, 9.16, 9.485, 10.066, 10.403, 10.646, 10.948, 11.204], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.569, 0.72, 0.836, 1.08, 1.393, 1.776, 1.916, 2.299, 2.984, 3.727, 3.831, 4.493, 5.097, 5.294, 5.654, 5.793, 6.026, 6.107, 6.478, 6.943, 7.558, 7.976, 8.348, 8.452, 9.114, 9.427, 9.95, 10.379, 10.612, 10.89, 11.134, 11.842]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(558, 47, 'Page 7', 'They carefully engaged low-power thrusters, navigating not by sight or reflection, but entirely by sound, homing in on the acoustic signature of the heat. The Aurora softly touched down near the massive, towering chimneys of the vent, discovering a thriving alien ecosystem simply by learning how to listen in the dark.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_47_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"They\", \"carefully\", \"engaged\", \"low-power\", \"thrusters,\", \"navigating\", \"not\", \"by\", \"sight\", \"or\", \"reflection,\", \"but\", \"entirely\", \"by\", \"sound,\", \"homing\", \"in\", \"on\", \"the\", \"acoustic\", \"signature\", \"of\", \"the\", \"heat.\", \"The\", \"Aurora\", \"softly\", \"touched\", \"down\", \"near\", \"the\", \"massive,\", \"towering\", \"chimneys\", \"of\", \"the\", \"vent,\", \"discovering\", \"a\", \"thriving\", \"alien\", \"ecosystem\", \"simply\", \"by\", \"learning\", \"how\", \"to\", \"listen\", \"in\", \"the\", \"dark.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.766, 1.347, 1.881, 2.879, 3.564, 3.808, 4.017, 4.342, 4.493, 5.492, 5.689, 6.385, 6.594, 7.419, 7.802, 8.069, 8.208, 8.324, 8.8, 9.276, 9.381, 9.497, 11.006, 11.169, 11.517, 11.947, 12.249, 12.504, 12.69, 12.817, 13.317, 13.839, 14.234, 14.338, 14.443, 15.093, 15.685, 15.778, 16.347, 16.777, 17.52, 17.891, 18.065, 18.379, 18.518, 18.623, 18.936, 19.041, 19.145], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.72, 1.254, 1.834, 2.635, 3.471, 3.75, 3.936, 4.296, 4.435, 5.248, 5.642, 6.304, 6.502, 7.175, 7.732, 7.976, 8.173, 8.278, 8.742, 9.242, 9.334, 9.451, 9.892, 11.122, 11.459, 11.889, 12.225, 12.446, 12.643, 12.759, 13.282, 13.769, 14.199, 14.292, 14.408, 14.919, 15.639, 15.709, 16.266, 16.719, 17.427, 17.845, 17.996, 18.332, 18.472, 18.565, 18.89, 18.994, 19.11, 19.737]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(559, 48, 'Page 1', 'In a gentle kelp forest near the coast lived a young seahorse named Mira. Seahorses survived by wrapping their tails tightly around swaying plants to anchor themselves against currents.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_48_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"a\", \"gentle\", \"kelp\", \"forest\", \"near\", \"the\", \"coast\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"young\", \"seahorse\", \"named\", \"Mira.\", \"Seahorses\", \"survived\", \"by\", \"wrapping\", \"their\", \"tails\", \"tightly\", \"around\", \"swaying\", \"plants\", \"to\", \"anchor\", \"themselves\", \"against\", \"currents.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.395, 0.766, 1.068, 1.521, 1.707, 1.823, 2.229, 2.473, 2.577, 2.833, 3.355, 3.622, 4.54, 5.213, 5.747, 5.909, 6.281, 6.467, 6.838, 7.233, 7.523, 7.918, 8.301, 8.452, 8.742, 9.183, 9.52], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.325, 0.72, 0.987, 1.463, 1.672, 1.776, 2.148, 2.45, 2.496, 2.763, 3.309, 3.564, 4.156, 5.166, 5.7, 5.851, 6.235, 6.42, 6.769, 7.187, 7.454, 7.86, 8.255, 8.371, 8.707, 9.149, 9.451, 10.263]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(560, 48, 'Page 2', 'Mira, however, had a slightly injured tail. It was weak. When the tides shifted strongly, she often lost her grip, tumbling awkwardly through the kelp while her friends held fast.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_48_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira,\", \"however,\", \"had\", \"a\", \"slightly\", \"injured\", \"tail.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"weak.\", \"When\", \"the\", \"tides\", \"shifted\", \"strongly,\", \"she\", \"often\", \"lost\", \"her\", \"grip,\", \"tumbling\", \"awkwardly\", \"through\", \"the\", \"kelp\", \"while\", \"her\", \"friends\", \"held\", \"fast.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.592, 1.37, 1.544, 1.625, 2.055, 2.403, 3.181, 3.332, 3.483, 4.586, 4.795, 4.899, 5.213, 5.573, 6.188, 6.409, 6.722, 7.012, 7.152, 7.721, 8.231, 8.754, 8.998, 9.102, 9.451, 9.683, 9.81, 10.136, 10.379], \"end_times\": [0.569, 1.196, 1.509, 1.567, 1.997, 2.368, 2.856, 3.297, 3.425, 3.889, 4.76, 4.865, 5.19, 5.538, 6.142, 6.327, 6.664, 6.966, 7.105, 7.546, 8.15, 8.707, 8.975, 9.067, 9.381, 9.648, 9.764, 10.089, 10.31, 11.099]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(561, 48, 'Page 3', 'She felt useless, often forced to hide in the calmest, shallowest pools where food was scarce, rather than braving the nutrient-rich currents of the outer forest.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_48_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"felt\", \"useless,\", \"often\", \"forced\", \"to\", \"hide\", \"in\", \"the\", \"calmest,\", \"shallowest\", \"pools\", \"where\", \"food\", \"was\", \"scarce,\", \"rather\", \"than\", \"braving\", \"the\", \"nutrient-rich\", \"currents\", \"of\", \"the\", \"outer\", \"forest.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.592, 1.428, 1.776, 2.078, 2.183, 2.473, 2.554, 2.659, 3.471, 4.087, 4.516, 4.737, 4.969, 5.132, 5.968, 6.246, 6.409, 6.78, 6.896, 7.546, 7.93, 8.034, 8.162, 8.44], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.522, 1.254, 1.718, 2.055, 2.125, 2.438, 2.519, 2.624, 3.297, 4.029, 4.47, 4.69, 4.923, 5.074, 5.759, 6.2, 6.362, 6.745, 6.85, 7.5, 7.895, 7.988, 8.104, 8.371, 9.195]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(562, 48, 'Page 4', 'One afternoon, a fast-moving school of mackerel swept through, followed closely by a hunting sea lion. The sudden chaos whipped the kelp violently. Many seahorses, rigidly gripping the stalks, were knocked loose by the thrashing stems, unable to uncurl fast enough to escape the immediate danger area.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_48_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"afternoon,\", \"a\", \"fast-moving\", \"school\", \"of\", \"mackerel\", \"swept\", \"through,\", \"followed\", \"closely\", \"by\", \"a\", \"hunting\", \"sea\", \"lion.\", \"The\", \"sudden\", \"chaos\", \"whipped\", \"the\", \"kelp\", \"violently.\", \"Many\", \"seahorses,\", \"rigidly\", \"gripping\", \"the\", \"stalks,\", \"were\", \"knocked\", \"loose\", \"by\", \"the\", \"thrashing\", \"stems,\", \"unable\", \"to\", \"uncurl\", \"fast\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"escape\", \"the\", \"immediate\", \"danger\", \"area.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.395, 0.998, 1.138, 1.73, 2.009, 2.125, 2.577, 2.914, 3.715, 4.11, 4.586, 4.76, 4.841, 5.213, 5.445, 6.444, 6.629, 6.943, 7.43, 7.767, 7.883, 8.208, 9.416, 9.706, 10.588, 11.053, 11.401, 11.517, 12.063, 12.249, 12.55, 12.806, 12.945, 13.05, 13.479, 14.478, 14.837, 14.965, 15.43, 15.731, 15.964, 16.08, 16.393, 16.509, 16.916, 17.264], \"end_times\": [0.36, 0.964, 1.057, 1.683, 1.962, 2.055, 2.508, 2.868, 3.39, 4.063, 4.528, 4.702, 4.783, 5.143, 5.387, 5.933, 6.571, 6.896, 7.349, 7.709, 7.837, 8.115, 8.905, 9.648, 10.472, 11.006, 11.355, 11.471, 12.028, 12.214, 12.492, 12.771, 12.899, 13.015, 13.421, 14.094, 14.814, 14.895, 15.371, 15.685, 15.929, 16.01, 16.37, 16.463, 16.892, 17.206, 17.833]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(563, 48, 'Page 5', 'Mira couldn\'t hold on anyway. Instead of gripping tight, she let go at the first sign of turbulent water. But instead of tumbling, she used her small, rapid dorsal fins to angle her body perfectly with the chaotic flow of displaced water. She rode the wave created by the sea lion\'s wake, spinning gracefully upward and out of the danger zone long before the heavy predator crashed through the lower stalks.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_48_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"couldn\'t\", \"hold\", \"on\", \"anyway.\", \"Instead\", \"of\", \"gripping\", \"tight,\", \"she\", \"let\", \"go\", \"at\", \"the\", \"first\", \"sign\", \"of\", \"turbulent\", \"water.\", \"But\", \"instead\", \"of\", \"tumbling,\", \"she\", \"used\", \"her\", \"small,\", \"rapid\", \"dorsal\", \"fins\", \"to\", \"angle\", \"her\", \"body\", \"perfectly\", \"with\", \"the\", \"chaotic\", \"flow\", \"of\", \"displaced\", \"water.\", \"She\", \"rode\", \"the\", \"wave\", \"created\", \"by\", \"the\", \"sea\", \"lion\'s\", \"wake,\", \"spinning\", \"gracefully\", \"upward\", \"and\", \"out\", \"of\", \"the\", \"danger\", \"zone\", \"long\", \"before\", \"the\", \"heavy\", \"predator\", \"crashed\", \"through\", \"the\", \"lower\", \"stalks.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.476, 0.755, 1.022, 1.219, 2.461, 2.891, 3.007, 3.367, 3.936, 4.145, 4.342, 4.574, 4.69, 4.807, 5.062, 5.352, 5.457, 5.968, 7.129, 7.338, 7.674, 7.779, 8.789, 9.009, 9.311, 9.485, 10.054, 10.426, 10.82, 11.18, 11.331, 11.68, 11.819, 12.144, 12.783, 13.003, 13.108, 13.595, 13.92, 14.036, 14.57, 15.882, 16.091, 16.358, 16.486, 16.788, 17.182, 17.322, 17.426, 17.612, 17.949, 18.564, 18.982, 19.551, 19.899, 20.038, 20.213, 20.305, 20.41, 20.747, 21.06, 21.362, 21.699, 21.815, 22.059, 22.593, 23.127, 23.359, 23.463, 23.742], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.72, 0.952, 1.161, 1.765, 2.856, 2.949, 3.309, 3.82, 4.075, 4.296, 4.505, 4.656, 4.76, 5.027, 5.317, 5.399, 5.921, 6.432, 7.291, 7.639, 7.732, 8.464, 8.928, 9.265, 9.416, 9.985, 10.391, 10.751, 11.122, 11.25, 11.633, 11.761, 12.063, 12.69, 12.968, 13.073, 13.537, 13.851, 13.978, 14.524, 15.069, 16.021, 16.335, 16.428, 16.741, 17.136, 17.264, 17.391, 17.565, 17.902, 18.355, 18.924, 19.493, 19.864, 19.969, 20.178, 20.259, 20.375, 20.689, 21.002, 21.292, 21.664, 21.768, 22, 22.476, 23.08, 23.324, 23.429, 23.684, 24.52]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(564, 48, 'Page 6', 'Her weakness in holding fast forced her to master letting go and navigating the chaos, a skill that saved her that day.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_48_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Her\", \"weakness\", \"in\", \"holding\", \"fast\", \"forced\", \"her\", \"to\", \"master\", \"letting\", \"go\", \"and\", \"navigating\", \"the\", \"chaos,\", \"a\", \"skill\", \"that\", \"saved\", \"her\", \"that\", \"day.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.801, 0.964, 1.312, 1.707, 2.032, 2.171, 2.322, 2.763, 3.042, 3.39, 3.646, 4.249, 4.354, 5.248, 5.399, 5.724, 5.921, 6.281, 6.444, 6.664], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.755, 0.882, 1.242, 1.637, 1.997, 2.113, 2.241, 2.705, 3.007, 3.274, 3.564, 4.203, 4.319, 5.004, 5.317, 5.677, 5.851, 6.235, 6.374, 6.606, 7.152]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(565, 49, 'Page 1', 'In the coldest part of the ocean, where floating icebergs cast long blue shadows, a young seal named Iko loved exploring beneath the ice sheets. It was a dangerous playground; the shifting ice could easily trap a marine mammal who needed to breathe air.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"the\", \"coldest\", \"part\", \"of\", \"the\", \"ocean,\", \"where\", \"floating\", \"icebergs\", \"cast\", \"long\", \"blue\", \"shadows,\", \"a\", \"young\", \"seal\", \"named\", \"Iko\", \"loved\", \"exploring\", \"beneath\", \"the\", \"ice\", \"sheets.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"a\", \"dangerous\", \"playground;\", \"the\", \"shifting\", \"ice\", \"could\", \"easily\", \"trap\", \"a\", \"marine\", \"mammal\", \"who\", \"needed\", \"to\", \"breathe\", \"air.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.395, 0.882, 1.115, 1.207, 1.358, 1.962, 2.206, 2.647, 3.286, 3.68, 4.017, 4.284, 5.166, 5.352, 5.666, 6.095, 6.444, 6.92, 7.314, 7.872, 8.173, 8.313, 8.533, 9.601, 9.752, 9.903, 9.985, 10.461, 11.459, 11.633, 12.086, 12.365, 12.585, 13.084, 13.468, 13.549, 13.944, 14.362, 14.536, 14.826, 14.919, 15.244], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.348, 0.824, 1.08, 1.161, 1.277, 1.881, 2.159, 2.566, 3.216, 3.599, 3.947, 4.249, 4.957, 5.236, 5.573, 6.002, 6.351, 6.827, 7.268, 7.814, 8.139, 8.243, 8.51, 9.091, 9.718, 9.857, 9.927, 10.414, 11.134, 11.564, 12.016, 12.33, 12.516, 13.026, 13.398, 13.491, 13.897, 14.303, 14.466, 14.791, 14.872, 15.186, 15.743]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(566, 49, 'Page 2', 'An older, scarred seal named Torak always warned him, “Stay close to the breathing holes. The ice changes every hour.”', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"An\", \"older,\", \"scarred\", \"seal\", \"named\", \"Torak\", \"always\", \"warned\", \"him,\", \"u201cStay\", \"close\", \"to\", \"the\", \"breathing\", \"holes.\", \"The\", \"ice\", \"changes\", \"every\", \"hour.u201d\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.731, 1.161, 1.486, 1.73, 2.252, 2.624, 2.914, 3.402, 3.808, 4.11, 4.214, 4.319, 4.679, 5.236, 5.445, 5.724, 6.235, 6.513], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.697, 1.103, 1.416, 1.683, 2.183, 2.566, 2.879, 3.193, 3.75, 4.075, 4.168, 4.284, 4.621, 5.062, 5.364, 5.677, 6.165, 6.467, 7.198]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(567, 49, 'Page 3', 'Iko thought he was fast enough to outswim any shifting block.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Iko\", \"thought\", \"he\", \"was\", \"fast\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"outswim\", \"any\", \"shifting\", \"block.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.685, 0.766, 0.929, 1.231, 1.474, 1.591, 2.043, 2.218, 2.601], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.65, 0.731, 0.871, 1.184, 1.44, 1.521, 1.985, 2.183, 2.566, 3.111]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(568, 49, 'Page 4', 'Deep under an enormous shelf, Iko discovered a beautiful phenomena—a \"brinicle,\" an underwater icicle growing downwards, trapping salt and freezing the water around it into a delicate, deadly tube. He lingered too long watching it.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Deep\", \"under\", \"an\", \"enormous\", \"shelf,\", \"Iko\", \"discovered\", \"a\", \"beautiful\", \"phenomenau2014a\", \"\"brinicle,\"\", \"an\", \"underwater\", \"icicle\", \"growing\", \"downwards,\", \"trapping\", \"salt\", \"and\", \"freezing\", \"the\", \"water\", \"around\", \"it\", \"into\", \"a\", \"delicate,\", \"deadly\", \"tube.\", \"He\", \"lingered\", \"too\", \"long\", \"watching\", \"it.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.673, 0.789, 1.219, 1.695, 2.02, 2.485, 2.566, 3.007, 4.098, 5.12, 5.329, 5.886, 6.339, 6.687, 7.477, 7.953, 8.29, 8.464, 8.87, 8.975, 9.276, 9.613, 9.729, 9.973, 10.066, 10.553, 10.948, 12.144, 12.33, 12.666, 12.864, 13.108, 13.502], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.627, 0.731, 1.184, 1.637, 1.95, 2.45, 2.508, 2.949, 4.04, 4.841, 5.248, 5.817, 6.293, 6.629, 7.361, 7.883, 8.243, 8.382, 8.824, 8.94, 9.218, 9.555, 9.683, 9.903, 9.996, 10.519, 10.89, 11.447, 12.26, 12.643, 12.794, 13.05, 13.444, 13.886]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(569, 49, 'Page 5', 'When he turned back, a massive section of the ice shelf above had shifted, completely blocking the path to the breathing hole he used to enter. Panic flared. His lungs burned. The solid white roof stretched endlessly in every direction.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"When\", \"he\", \"turned\", \"back,\", \"a\", \"massive\", \"section\", \"of\", \"the\", \"ice\", \"shelf\", \"above\", \"had\", \"shifted,\", \"completely\", \"blocking\", \"the\", \"path\", \"to\", \"the\", \"breathing\", \"hole\", \"he\", \"used\", \"to\", \"enter.\", \"Panic\", \"flared.\", \"His\", \"lungs\", \"burned.\", \"The\", \"solid\", \"white\", \"roof\", \"stretched\", \"endlessly\", \"in\", \"every\", \"direction.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.406, 0.697, 1.37, 1.556, 1.974, 2.345, 2.438, 2.589, 2.81, 3.088, 3.402, 3.541, 4.342, 4.83, 5.224, 5.329, 5.654, 5.759, 5.863, 6.246, 6.455, 6.606, 6.815, 6.931, 8.139, 8.568, 9.381, 9.601, 9.927, 10.797, 10.995, 11.366, 11.61, 11.889, 12.318, 12.817, 12.934, 13.154], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.36, 0.65, 1.161, 1.44, 1.939, 2.31, 2.403, 2.508, 2.786, 3.019, 3.367, 3.495, 4.133, 4.783, 5.178, 5.294, 5.608, 5.7, 5.828, 6.188, 6.42, 6.525, 6.792, 6.861, 7.442, 8.498, 9.102, 9.532, 9.868, 10.472, 10.925, 11.331, 11.575, 11.807, 12.26, 12.771, 12.875, 13.108, 14.582]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(570, 49, 'Page 6', 'He swam frantically along the ice face, looking for cracks, but the surface was seamless.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"swam\", \"frantically\", \"along\", \"the\", \"ice\", \"face,\", \"looking\", \"for\", \"cracks,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"surface\", \"was\", \"seamless.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.615, 1.161, 1.393, 1.533, 1.753, 2.067, 2.38, 2.519, 3.135, 3.32, 3.425, 3.796, 3.947], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.534, 1.103, 1.358, 1.463, 1.707, 2.032, 2.322, 2.473, 3.019, 3.286, 3.39, 3.762, 3.901, 4.69]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(571, 49, 'Page 7', 'He stopped, forcing down the panic. He remembered something Torak had muttered once: “Fresh water flows differently.”', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"stopped,\", \"forcing\", \"down\", \"the\", \"panic.\", \"He\", \"remembered\", \"something\", \"Torak\", \"had\", \"muttered\", \"once:\", \"u201cFresh\", \"water\", \"flows\", \"differently.u201d\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.778, 1.207, 1.416, 1.521, 2.287, 2.461, 2.868, 3.216, 3.634, 3.773, 4.122, 4.795, 5.352, 5.724, 6.095], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.731, 1.149, 1.37, 1.486, 2.043, 2.392, 2.833, 3.146, 3.576, 3.727, 4.052, 4.586, 5.283, 5.654, 6.037, 7.012]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-06 08:04:10'),
(572, 49, 'Page 8', 'He looked closely at the ice above. He noticed a faint, rippling distortion against the crystal ceiling. It was a stream of slightly warmer, less salty meltwater flowing along the underside of the glacier. Meltwater always flowed toward the open ocean edge.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"looked\", \"closely\", \"at\", \"the\", \"ice\", \"above.\", \"He\", \"noticed\", \"a\", \"faint,\", \"rippling\", \"distortion\", \"against\", \"the\", \"crystal\", \"ceiling.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"a\", \"stream\", \"of\", \"slightly\", \"warmer,\", \"less\", \"salty\", \"meltwater\", \"flowing\", \"along\", \"the\", \"underside\", \"of\", \"the\", \"glacier.\", \"Meltwater\", \"always\", \"flowed\", \"toward\", \"the\", \"open\", \"ocean\", \"edge.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.522, 0.987, 1.103, 1.242, 1.486, 2.473, 2.659, 3.019, 3.111, 3.82, 4.307, 4.923, 5.271, 5.375, 5.782, 7.047, 7.187, 7.326, 7.396, 7.709, 7.814, 8.255, 8.707, 8.986, 9.427, 9.996, 10.414, 10.681, 10.809, 11.285, 11.378, 11.482, 12.701, 13.282, 13.642, 13.99, 14.269, 14.408, 14.745, 15.151], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.476, 0.929, 1.068, 1.173, 1.451, 2.032, 2.577, 2.984, 3.042, 3.576, 4.226, 4.876, 5.236, 5.341, 5.724, 6.351, 7.152, 7.279, 7.349, 7.663, 7.755, 8.185, 8.673, 8.928, 9.358, 9.927, 10.356, 10.646, 10.751, 11.262, 11.331, 11.447, 12.098, 13.224, 13.595, 13.955, 14.234, 14.338, 14.675, 15.058, 15.743]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-05 17:47:59'),
(573, 49, 'Page 9', 'Iko stopped fighting the solid barriers and simply followed the subtle, invisible river against the roof. The current gently guided him straight to the open sea just as his air ran out.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Iko\", \"stopped\", \"fighting\", \"the\", \"solid\", \"barriers\", \"and\", \"simply\", \"followed\", \"the\", \"subtle,\", \"invisible\", \"river\", \"against\", \"the\", \"roof.\", \"The\", \"current\", \"gently\", \"guided\", \"him\", \"straight\", \"to\", \"the\", \"open\", \"sea\", \"just\", \"as\", \"his\", \"air\", \"ran\", \"out.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.94, 1.254, 1.358, 1.707, 2.241, 2.415, 2.775, 3.17, 3.286, 3.646, 4.214, 4.528, 4.853, 4.969, 5.735, 5.909, 6.269, 6.606, 6.931, 7.094, 7.419, 7.535, 7.674, 7.976, 8.29, 8.557, 8.696, 8.858, 9.125, 9.381], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.882, 1.219, 1.324, 1.672, 2.194, 2.357, 2.705, 3.135, 3.239, 3.622, 4.156, 4.47, 4.818, 4.923, 5.41, 5.851, 6.223, 6.548, 6.896, 7.024, 7.384, 7.477, 7.605, 7.895, 8.22, 8.51, 8.638, 8.8, 9.067, 9.311, 9.892]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-05 17:47:59'),
(574, 49, 'Page 10', 'He broke the surface with a loud gasp, learning a hard lesson: speed means nothing without direction.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_49_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"broke\", \"the\", \"surface\", \"with\", \"a\", \"loud\", \"gasp,\", \"learning\", \"a\", \"hard\", \"lesson:\", \"speed\", \"means\", \"nothing\", \"without\", \"direction.\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.534, 0.65, 1.033, 1.184, 1.265, 1.533, 2.252, 2.589, 2.659, 2.891, 3.738, 4.203, 4.505, 4.841, 5.132], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.499, 0.604, 1.01, 1.149, 1.207, 1.474, 2.101, 2.543, 2.612, 2.833, 3.355, 4.133, 4.435, 4.795, 5.097, 5.898]}', '2026-02-26 12:17:31', '2026-03-05 17:47:59'),
(575, 1, 'Page 1', 'Leo was a child who loved watching the sky. At night, when everyone else was asleep, he would sit by the window and watch the stars shine. To him, every star was a story waiting to be told.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Leo\", \"was\", \"a\", \"child\", \"who\", \"loved\", \"watching\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"At\", \"night,\", \"when\", \"everyone\", \"else\", \"was\", \"asleep,\", \"he\", \"would\", \"sit\", \"by\", \"the\", \"window\", \"and\", \"watch\", \"the\", \"stars\", \"shine.\", \"[cite:\", \"4]\", \"To\", \"him,\", \"every\", \"star\", \"was\", \"a\", \"story\", \"waiting\", \"to\", \"be\", \"told.\", \"[cite:\", \"5]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.604, 0.685, 1.057, 1.254, 1.625, 1.997, 2.101, 3.39, 3.611, 4.11, 4.319, 4.656, 4.853, 5.027, 5.84, 5.956, 6.142, 6.327, 6.467, 6.583, 7.012, 7.221, 7.512, 7.628, 8.092, 8.835, 10.31, 11.111, 11.308, 11.923, 12.272, 12.666, 12.852, 12.934, 13.328, 13.653, 13.758, 13.886, 14.745, 15.929], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.569, 0.639, 1.01, 1.161, 1.567, 1.95, 2.067, 2.694, 3.553, 4.029, 4.272, 4.632, 4.818, 4.969, 5.561, 5.909, 6.107, 6.293, 6.42, 6.536, 6.931, 7.163, 7.454, 7.581, 8.022, 8.661, 9.706, 10.832, 11.227, 11.714, 12.214, 12.597, 12.794, 12.875, 13.259, 13.607, 13.7, 13.839, 14.362, 15.488, 16.486]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(576, 1, 'Page 2', 'One night, the sky was brighter than ever. The stars seemed to wink at Leo. At that moment, he felt a warm feeling inside him, as if someone was calling his name.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"night,\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"was\", \"brighter\", \"than\", \"ever.\", \"The\", \"stars\", \"seemed\", \"to\", \"wink\", \"at\", \"Leo.\", \"[cite:\", \"6]\", \"At\", \"that\", \"moment,\", \"he\", \"felt\", \"a\", \"warm\", \"feeling\", \"inside\", \"him,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"someone\", \"was\", \"calling\", \"his\", \"name.\", \"[cite:\", \"7]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.557, 0.673, 1.022, 1.196, 1.533, 1.695, 2.635, 2.81, 3.123, 3.355, 3.46, 3.704, 3.82, 4.47, 5.108, 6.293, 6.455, 6.664, 7.012, 7.14, 7.372, 7.454, 7.755, 8.092, 8.51, 8.998, 9.195, 9.334, 9.718, 9.88, 10.24, 10.414, 10.879, 11.482], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.534, 0.627, 0.952, 1.126, 1.486, 1.649, 2.125, 2.752, 3.088, 3.332, 3.402, 3.657, 3.762, 4.261, 5.074, 5.596, 6.42, 6.606, 6.978, 7.07, 7.326, 7.396, 7.686, 8.046, 8.475, 8.847, 9.149, 9.276, 9.683, 9.822, 10.182, 10.344, 10.82, 11.436, 12.074]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(577, 1, 'Page 3', 'Suddenly, a soft light appeared in the middle of his room. The light grew, took shape, and turned into a small, glowing space capsule. Leo was not afraid. Deep in his heart, he knew this was the beginning of an adventure.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Suddenly,\", \"a\", \"soft\", \"light\", \"appeared\", \"in\", \"the\", \"middle\", \"of\", \"his\", \"room.\", \"[cite:\", \"8]\", \"The\", \"light\", \"grew,\", \"took\", \"shape,\", \"and\", \"turned\", \"into\", \"a\", \"small,\", \"glowing\", \"space\", \"capsule.\", \"Leo\", \"was\", \"not\", \"afraid.\", \"[cite:\", \"9]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.58, 0.662, 1.022, 1.242, 1.602, 1.683, 1.788, 2.02, 2.113, 2.264, 2.856, 3.831, 4.54, 4.714, 4.946, 5.492, 5.77, 6.118, 6.246, 6.56, 6.815, 6.896, 7.291, 7.721, 8.069, 9.079, 9.392, 9.543, 9.706, 10.252, 11.308], \"end_times\": [0.557, 0.604, 0.952, 1.219, 1.567, 1.66, 1.753, 1.997, 2.067, 2.206, 2.647, 3.68, 4.331, 4.656, 4.899, 5.399, 5.712, 6.095, 6.211, 6.525, 6.734, 6.838, 7.256, 7.651, 8.034, 8.638, 9.334, 9.485, 9.671, 10.228, 10.983, 11.935]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(578, 1, 'Page 4', 'The capsule quietly rose into the sky. The clouds stayed below. The city began to look like a tiny toy. The Earth turned into a blue ball.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Deep\", \"in\", \"his\", \"heart,\", \"he\", \"knew\", \"this\", \"was\", \"the\", \"beginning\", \"of\", \"an\", \"adventure.\", \"[cite:\", \"10]\", \"The\", \"capsule\", \"quietly\", \"rose\", \"into\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"The\", \"clouds\", \"stayed\", \"below.\", \"The\", \"city\", \"began\", \"to\", \"look\", \"like\", \"a\", \"tiny\", \"toy.\", \"[cite:\", \"11]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.58, 0.766, 1.37, 1.556, 1.846, 2.043, 2.206, 2.322, 2.717, 2.821, 2.914, 3.669, 4.609, 5.596, 5.759, 6.2, 6.699, 7.105, 7.372, 7.477, 8.22, 8.382, 8.8, 9.137, 9.996, 10.182, 10.461, 10.786, 10.902, 11.122, 11.296, 11.378, 11.773, 12.771, 13.723], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.511, 0.697, 1.196, 1.474, 1.776, 1.985, 2.148, 2.276, 2.682, 2.763, 2.879, 3.634, 4.435, 5.213, 5.712, 6.165, 6.618, 7.059, 7.303, 7.442, 8.046, 8.336, 8.766, 9.091, 9.671, 10.124, 10.403, 10.728, 10.844, 11.076, 11.262, 11.32, 11.703, 12.33, 13.572, 14.629]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(579, 1, 'Page 5', 'After a while, they landed on the surface of the Moon. The Moon was quieter than Leo had imagined. Everything was gray, but the starlight shone on the ground like silver.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"Earth\", \"turned\", \"into\", \"a\", \"blue\", \"ball.\", \"[cite:\", \"12]\", \"After\", \"a\", \"while,\", \"they\", \"landed\", \"on\", \"the\", \"surface\", \"of\", \"the\", \"Moon.\", \"The\", \"Moon\", \"was\", \"quieter\", \"than\", \"Leo\", \"had\", \"imagined.\", \"[cite:\", \"13]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.615, 0.975, 1.219, 1.289, 1.533, 2.055, 2.926, 3.982, 4.342, 4.412, 4.783, 4.946, 5.236, 5.329, 5.433, 5.782, 5.886, 5.991, 6.722, 6.896, 7.152, 7.326, 7.79, 7.964, 8.255, 8.394, 9.172, 10.066], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.546, 0.929, 1.138, 1.242, 1.498, 2.009, 2.775, 3.599, 4.284, 4.365, 4.76, 4.899, 5.201, 5.294, 5.399, 5.759, 5.84, 5.956, 6.444, 6.838, 7.094, 7.256, 7.744, 7.906, 8.197, 8.348, 9.021, 9.915, 11.331]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(580, 1, 'Page 6', 'When Leo stepped onto the surface, he felt lighter. Every step lifted him a little higher. Jumping felt easier than walking.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Everything\", \"was\", \"gray,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"starlight\", \"shone\", \"on\", \"the\", \"ground\", \"like\", \"silver.\", \"[cite:\", \"14]\", \"When\", \"Leo\", \"stepped\", \"onto\", \"the\", \"surface,\", \"he\", \"felt\", \"lighter.\", \"Every\", \"step\", \"lifted\", \"him\", \"a\", \"little\", \"higher.\", \"[cite:\", \"15]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.65, 0.836, 1.602, 1.8, 1.927, 2.508, 2.844, 2.949, 3.053, 3.379, 3.587, 4.76, 5.956, 7.605, 7.848, 8.162, 8.499, 8.731, 8.847, 9.718, 9.857, 10.089, 10.983, 11.331, 11.691, 12.051, 12.202, 12.272, 12.527, 13.955, 14.919], \"end_times\": [0.592, 0.766, 1.393, 1.765, 1.869, 2.438, 2.81, 2.914, 3.019, 3.32, 3.541, 4.156, 5.515, 6.653, 7.79, 8.092, 8.464, 8.673, 8.8, 9.474, 9.799, 10.043, 10.542, 11.273, 11.61, 12.005, 12.156, 12.225, 12.492, 13.003, 14.64, 15.929]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(581, 1, 'Page 7', 'On the Moon, he noticed a small, glowing cloud of dust. This was not ordinary dust. It shimmered like a tiny star. As Leo moved closer, the dust glowed even brighter.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Jumping\", \"felt\", \"easier\", \"than\", \"walking.\", \"[cite:\", \"16]\", \"On\", \"the\", \"Moon,\", \"he\", \"noticed\", \"a\", \"small,\", \"glowing\", \"cloud\", \"of\", \"dust.\", \"This\", \"was\", \"not\", \"ordinary\", \"dust.\", \"[cite:\", \"17]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.673, 1.022, 1.463, 1.672, 2.508, 3.309, 4.563, 4.795, 4.923, 5.584, 5.759, 6.153, 6.258, 6.815, 7.279, 7.628, 7.767, 8.87, 9.125, 9.323, 9.683, 10.252, 11.54, 12.388], \"end_times\": [0.592, 0.94, 1.405, 1.602, 2.334, 3.251, 4.122, 4.76, 4.865, 5.41, 5.677, 6.107, 6.177, 6.757, 7.21, 7.581, 7.686, 8.359, 9.067, 9.242, 9.613, 10.182, 10.844, 12.33, 13.653]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(582, 1, 'Page 8', 'It sparkled with a quiet sense of loneliness. Standing there, in the great silence, Leo realized something: no matter how big space is, one heart can still feel another.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"It\", \"shimmered\", \"like\", \"a\", \"tiny\", \"star.\", \"As\", \"Leo\", \"moved\", \"closer,\", \"the\", \"dust\", \"glowed\", \"even\", \"brighter.\", \"[cite:\", \"18]\", \"It\", \"sparkled\", \"with\", \"a\", \"quiet\", \"sense\", \"of\", \"loneliness.\", \"[cite:\", \"19]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.743, 0.917, 1.01, 1.428, 2.508, 2.752, 3.088, 3.379, 4.156, 4.331, 4.737, 5.19, 5.468, 6.676, 7.57, 8.777, 8.998, 9.532, 9.694, 9.776, 10.217, 10.519, 10.635, 12.063, 13.073], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.708, 0.894, 0.952, 1.347, 2.067, 2.67, 3.007, 3.32, 4.04, 4.261, 4.656, 5.132, 5.41, 6.072, 7.535, 8.394, 8.928, 9.497, 9.659, 9.718, 10.159, 10.484, 10.565, 11.459, 12.957, 14.164]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(583, 1, 'Page 9', 'He walked on the Moon for a while and looked back at Earth. He saw his home. He thought about how small people looked, yet how big their dreams could be.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Standing\", \"there,\", \"in\", \"the\", \"great\", \"silence,\", \"Leo\", \"realized\", \"something:\", \"no\", \"matter\", \"how\", \"big\", \"space\", \"is,\", \"one\", \"heart\", \"can\", \"still\", \"feel\", \"another.\", \"[cite:\", \"20]\", \"He\", \"walked\", \"on\", \"the\", \"Moon\", \"for\", \"a\", \"while\", \"and\", \"looked\", \"back\", \"at\", \"Earth.\", \"He\", \"saw\", \"his\", \"home.\", \"[cite:\", \"21]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.627, 0.917, 1.033, 1.149, 1.428, 2.357, 2.67, 3.077, 4.284, 4.423, 4.667, 4.83, 5.027, 5.399, 6.014, 6.304, 6.583, 6.78, 7.024, 7.256, 8.29, 9.091, 9.88, 10.043, 10.333, 10.437, 10.542, 10.774, 10.913, 10.971, 11.308, 11.436, 11.691, 11.923, 12.04, 12.701, 12.875, 13.096, 13.247, 13.955, 14.733], \"end_times\": [0.58, 0.882, 0.998, 1.103, 1.358, 2.148, 2.601, 3.042, 3.68, 4.377, 4.621, 4.772, 4.969, 5.352, 5.863, 6.246, 6.525, 6.722, 6.978, 7.198, 7.779, 8.94, 9.636, 9.985, 10.298, 10.403, 10.507, 10.716, 10.879, 10.937, 11.262, 11.401, 11.645, 11.877, 11.981, 12.492, 12.817, 13.038, 13.201, 13.677, 14.605, 15.557]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(584, 1, 'Page 10', 'When it was time to return, Leo left a small mark behind. He drew a star-shaped symbol on the Moon\'s surface. It was a promise that one day, he would come back.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"thought\", \"about\", \"how\", \"small\", \"people\", \"looked,\", \"yet\", \"how\", \"big\", \"their\", \"dreams\", \"could\", \"be.\", \"[cite:\", \"22]\", \"When\", \"it\", \"was\", \"time\", \"to\", \"return,\", \"Leo\", \"left\", \"a\", \"small\", \"mark\", \"behind.\", \"[cite:\", \"23]\", \"He\", \"drew\", \"a\", \"star-shaped\", \"symbol\", \"on\", \"the\", \"Moon\'s\", \"surface.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"a\", \"promise\", \"that\", \"one\", \"day,\", \"he\", \"would\", \"come\", \"back.\", \"[cite:\", \"24]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.511, 0.731, 0.906, 1.289, 1.602, 2.229, 2.438, 2.635, 2.902, 3.1, 3.46, 3.657, 4.888, 5.805, 7.663, 7.872, 7.953, 8.104, 8.371, 8.51, 9.381, 9.729, 9.973, 10.054, 10.379, 10.658, 11.529, 12.597, 13.769, 13.932, 14.176, 14.257, 14.907, 15.302, 15.43, 15.534, 15.848, 17.067, 17.218, 17.357, 17.438, 17.891, 18.077, 18.309, 18.669, 18.785, 18.971, 19.168, 20.097, 21.084], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.476, 0.685, 0.836, 1.219, 1.567, 2.02, 2.392, 2.554, 2.844, 3.053, 3.402, 3.611, 4.075, 5.631, 6.548, 7.837, 7.918, 8.046, 8.336, 8.429, 9.137, 9.66, 9.927, 9.996, 10.321, 10.588, 11.285, 12.272, 13.328, 13.886, 14.118, 14.199, 14.861, 15.232, 15.395, 15.499, 15.813, 16.556, 17.183, 17.31, 17.392, 17.856, 18.019, 18.274, 18.634, 18.739, 18.936, 19.133, 19.656, 20.84, 22.338]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(585, 1, 'Page 11', 'As the capsule traveled back to Earth, Leo was no longer just a child who watched the sky. He was a dreamer who had touched the stars.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"capsule\", \"traveled\", \"back\", \"to\", \"Earth,\", \"Leo\", \"was\", \"no\", \"longer\", \"just\", \"a\", \"child\", \"who\", \"watched\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"[cite:\", \"25]\", \"He\", \"was\", \"a\", \"dreamer\", \"who\", \"had\", \"touched\", \"the\", \"stars.\", \"[cite:\", \"26]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.418, 0.824, 1.184, 1.405, 1.544, 2.159, 2.496, 2.647, 2.798, 3.088, 3.309, 3.379, 3.75, 3.901, 4.226, 4.331, 5.016, 5.817, 6.769, 6.908, 7.059, 7.129, 7.5, 7.639, 7.767, 8.092, 8.208, 8.893, 9.613], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.372, 0.801, 1.161, 1.358, 1.463, 1.95, 2.438, 2.589, 2.717, 3.042, 3.262, 3.332, 3.715, 3.843, 4.191, 4.296, 4.807, 5.7, 6.618, 6.861, 7.012, 7.082, 7.465, 7.593, 7.732, 8.057, 8.162, 8.835, 9.497, 10.542]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(586, 1, 'Page 12', 'From that night on, Leo knew that no star was ever truly alone. Because even in space, a seed of friendship could grow. And some journeys do not bring you closer to home, but closer to yourself.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_1_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"From\", \"that\", \"night\", \"on,\", \"Leo\", \"knew\", \"that\", \"no\", \"star\", \"was\", \"ever\", \"truly\", \"alone.\", \"[cite:\", \"27]\", \"Because\", \"even\", \"in\", \"space,\", \"a\", \"seed\", \"of\", \"friendship\", \"could\", \"grow.\", \"[cite:\", \"28]\", \"And\", \"some\", \"journeys\", \"do\", \"not\", \"bring\", \"you\", \"closer\", \"to\", \"home,\", \"but\", \"closer\", \"to\", \"yourself.\", \"[cite:\", \"29]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.569, 0.824, 1.219, 1.579, 1.811, 2.009, 2.276, 2.659, 2.844, 3.123, 3.506, 4.598, 5.201, 6.188, 6.56, 6.885, 7.024, 7.686, 7.872, 8.185, 8.29, 8.8, 8.998, 9.892, 10.565, 11.389, 11.633, 11.912, 12.376, 12.55, 12.748, 12.968, 13.108, 13.468, 13.595, 14.141, 14.35, 14.779, 14.93, 16.765, 17.415], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.511, 0.766, 1.126, 1.521, 1.753, 1.95, 2.183, 2.601, 2.775, 3.065, 3.448, 4.087, 5.155, 6.072, 6.513, 6.827, 6.954, 7.605, 7.755, 8.139, 8.231, 8.742, 8.951, 9.451, 10.484, 11.273, 11.552, 11.865, 12.318, 12.469, 12.701, 12.922, 13.05, 13.421, 13.526, 14.048, 14.303, 14.721, 14.849, 15.65, 17.334, 18.344]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(587, 2, 'Page 1', 'Far away from Earth, there was a red planet called Mars. Mars was silent. Its wind was thin, its soil red. There were no trees, no flowers.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Far\", \"away\", \"from\", \"Earth,\", \"there\", \"was\", \"a\", \"red\", \"planet\", \"called\", \"Mars.\", \"[cite:\", \"31]\", \"Mars\", \"was\", \"silent.\", \"Its\", \"wind\", \"was\", \"thin,\", \"its\", \"soil\", \"red.\", \"There\", \"were\", \"no\", \"trees,\", \"no\", \"flowers.\", \"[cite:\", \"32]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.685, 0.906, 1.254, 1.486, 1.637, 1.741, 2.009, 2.67, 3.03, 4.075, 4.772, 5.654, 6.014, 6.177, 7.047, 7.279, 7.558, 7.767, 8.348, 8.603, 9.044, 9.88, 10.112, 10.263, 10.426, 11.238, 11.447, 12.318, 13.177], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.639, 0.824, 1.207, 1.451, 1.591, 1.672, 1.927, 2.496, 2.961, 3.692, 4.725, 5.503, 5.956, 6.13, 6.803, 7.221, 7.5, 7.686, 8.255, 8.545, 8.951, 9.497, 10.077, 10.228, 10.356, 11.064, 11.378, 12.144, 13.003, 14.164]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(588, 2, 'Page 2', 'On Earth lived a child named Ada, who loved plants very much. She had small pots in her garden. Every morning, she watered her flowers, touched their leaves, and watched them grow.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"On\", \"Earth\", \"lived\", \"a\", \"child\", \"named\", \"Ada,\", \"who\", \"loved\", \"plants\", \"very\", \"much.\", \"She\", \"had\", \"small\", \"pots\", \"in\", \"her\", \"garden.\", \"[cite:\", \"33]\", \"Every\", \"morning,\", \"she\", \"watered\", \"her\", \"flowers,\", \"touched\", \"their\", \"leaves,\", \"and\", \"watched\", \"them\", \"grow.\", \"[cite:\", \"34]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.685, 0.929, 1.01, 1.416, 1.683, 2.078, 2.276, 2.543, 2.972, 3.239, 3.971, 4.156, 4.331, 4.609, 4.934, 5.05, 5.19, 5.782, 6.653, 7.779, 8.092, 8.487, 8.649, 8.975, 9.102, 9.868, 10.228, 10.414, 10.739, 10.89, 11.215, 11.389, 11.9, 12.736], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.604, 0.894, 0.952, 1.358, 1.614, 2.055, 2.218, 2.485, 2.891, 3.181, 3.646, 4.098, 4.272, 4.551, 4.888, 4.992, 5.132, 5.666, 6.478, 7.535, 8.034, 8.464, 8.591, 8.94, 9.056, 9.752, 10.194, 10.368, 10.716, 10.832, 11.18, 11.331, 11.784, 12.585, 13.653]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(589, 2, 'Page 3', 'One day at school, Ada learned about Mars. Her teacher said, “There is no life on Mars yet.” When Ada heard this, her heart felt a little heavy. “Maybe there is just no life yet,” she thought.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"day\", \"at\", \"school,\", \"Ada\", \"learned\", \"about\", \"Mars.\", \"Her\", \"teacher\", \"said,\", \"\'There\", \"is\", \"no\", \"life\", \"on\", \"Mars\", \"yet.\'\", \"[cite:\", \"35]\", \"When\", \"Ada\", \"heard\", \"this,\", \"her\", \"heart\", \"felt\", \"a\", \"little\", \"heavy.\", \"[cite:\", \"36]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.453, 0.569, 1.08, 1.37, 1.602, 1.858, 2.717, 2.926, 3.32, 4.052, 4.389, 4.563, 4.748, 5.027, 5.19, 5.526, 6.188, 7.291, 8.568, 8.789, 9.067, 9.288, 9.764, 9.95, 10.182, 10.426, 10.484, 10.739, 11.54, 12.481], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.418, 0.522, 1.022, 1.324, 1.579, 1.8, 2.438, 2.868, 3.251, 3.773, 4.342, 4.481, 4.667, 4.981, 5.132, 5.457, 6.037, 6.908, 8.057, 8.742, 9.009, 9.242, 9.671, 9.892, 10.136, 10.379, 10.449, 10.693, 11.215, 12.307, 13.421]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(590, 2, 'Page 4', 'That night, Ada had a strange dream. She was walking on red soil, holding a small seed in her hand. The sky was orange, and far away, Earth shone like a blue pearl.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"\'Maybe\", \"there\", \"is\", \"just\", \"no\", \"life\", \"yet,\'\", \"she\", \"thought.\", \"[cite:\", \"37]\", \"That\", \"night,\", \"Ada\", \"had\", \"a\", \"strange\", \"dream.\", \"She\", \"was\", \"walking\", \"on\", \"red\", \"soil,\", \"holding\", \"a\", \"small\", \"seed\", \"in\", \"her\", \"hand.\", \"[cite:\", \"38]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.639, 0.766, 1.022, 1.231, 1.521, 1.788, 1.985, 2.403, 2.891, 4.934, 5.213, 5.561, 5.84, 5.979, 6.049, 6.478, 7.14, 7.314, 7.465, 7.825, 7.964, 8.185, 8.824, 9.149, 9.218, 9.52, 9.787, 9.915, 10.054, 10.704, 11.401], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.604, 0.708, 0.952, 1.149, 1.474, 1.765, 1.916, 2.38, 2.844, 3.634, 5.155, 5.515, 5.782, 5.944, 6.002, 6.432, 6.931, 7.268, 7.407, 7.767, 7.895, 8.127, 8.707, 9.114, 9.172, 9.462, 9.741, 9.845, 9.996, 10.495, 11.355, 12.725]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(591, 2, 'Page 5', 'Ada knelt down and placed the seed into the ground. She covered it with soil and waited. Days passed. The wind blew. Sand moved across the land. But Ada did not give up.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"sky\", \"was\", \"orange,\", \"and\", \"far\", \"away,\", \"Earth\", \"shone\", \"like\", \"a\", \"blue\", \"pearl.\", \"[cite:\", \"39]\", \"Ada\", \"knelt\", \"down\", \"and\", \"placed\", \"the\", \"seed\", \"into\", \"the\", \"ground.\", \"She\", \"covered\", \"it\", \"with\", \"soil\", \"and\", \"waited.\", \"[cite:\", \"40]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.685, 0.894, 1.602, 1.846, 2.125, 2.821, 3.17, 3.587, 3.773, 3.843, 4.122, 5.445, 6.304, 7.396, 7.721, 7.964, 8.29, 8.44, 8.777, 8.905, 9.195, 9.404, 9.509, 10.658, 10.867, 11.215, 11.32, 11.494, 11.9, 12.074, 13.444, 14.234], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.615, 0.813, 1.486, 1.765, 2.078, 2.647, 3.088, 3.541, 3.75, 3.796, 4.075, 4.632, 6.177, 7.012, 7.674, 7.918, 8.231, 8.382, 8.742, 8.847, 9.149, 9.346, 9.474, 10.054, 10.797, 11.18, 11.285, 11.436, 11.831, 12.016, 12.632, 14.118, 15.464]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(592, 2, 'Page 6', 'Every day, she returned and imagined watering the soil. One morning, a tiny crack appeared in the ground. The crack grew wider, and a small green sprout came out.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Days\", \"passed.\", \"The\", \"wind\", \"blew.\", \"Sand\", \"moved\", \"across\", \"the\", \"land.\", \"But\", \"Ada\", \"did\", \"not\", \"give\", \"up.\", \"[cite:\", \"41]\", \"Every\", \"day,\", \"she\", \"returned\", \"and\", \"imagined\", \"watering\", \"the\", \"soil.\", \"[cite:\", \"42]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.964, 1.126, 1.335, 2.055, 2.368, 2.589, 2.914, 3.03, 3.773, 3.982, 4.261, 4.423, 4.598, 4.807, 5.805, 6.258, 7.129, 7.419, 7.674, 7.86, 8.371, 8.545, 9.021, 9.474, 9.59, 10.414, 10.971], \"end_times\": [0.36, 0.871, 1.08, 1.289, 1.776, 2.322, 2.566, 2.868, 2.984, 3.448, 3.936, 4.203, 4.377, 4.551, 4.76, 5.108, 6.235, 6.92, 7.372, 7.651, 7.79, 8.301, 8.487, 8.963, 9.427, 9.543, 10.089, 10.937, 11.749]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(593, 2, 'Page 7', 'For the first time, a new color was born on the red surface of Mars. The sprout grew into a small flower. Its petals shone in the sunlight.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"morning,\", \"a\", \"tiny\", \"crack\", \"appeared\", \"in\", \"the\", \"ground.\", \"The\", \"crack\", \"grew\", \"wider,\", \"and\", \"a\", \"small\", \"green\", \"sprout\", \"came\", \"out.\", \"[cite:\", \"43]\", \"For\", \"the\", \"first\", \"time,\", \"a\", \"new\", \"color\", \"was\", \"born\", \"on\", \"the\", \"red\", \"surface\", \"of\", \"Mars.\", \"[cite:\", \"44]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.917, 1.045, 1.416, 1.823, 2.229, 2.322, 2.426, 3.251, 3.413, 3.75, 3.982, 4.423, 4.586, 4.656, 4.992, 5.271, 5.7, 5.944, 6.42, 7.396, 8.905, 9.067, 9.183, 9.451, 9.903, 10.043, 10.252, 10.553, 10.728, 11.076, 11.204, 11.331, 11.575, 12.005, 12.132, 12.759, 13.584], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.882, 0.975, 1.347, 1.753, 2.194, 2.276, 2.392, 2.926, 3.367, 3.692, 3.936, 4.4, 4.54, 4.609, 4.934, 5.213, 5.631, 5.898, 6.304, 7.245, 8.208, 9.033, 9.137, 9.416, 9.845, 9.961, 10.182, 10.507, 10.67, 11.006, 11.169, 11.273, 11.505, 11.97, 12.051, 12.736, 13.468, 14.443]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(594, 2, 'Page 8', 'It was as if Mars had awakened from a long sleep. When Ada woke up, she was still in her bed. It had been a dream. But the feeling it left behind was real.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"sprout\", \"grew\", \"into\", \"a\", \"small\", \"flower.\", \"Its\", \"petals\", \"shone\", \"in\", \"the\", \"sunlight.\", \"[cite:\", \"45]\", \"It\", \"was\", \"as\", \"if\", \"Mars\", \"had\", \"awakened\", \"from\", \"a\", \"long\", \"sleep.\", \"[cite:\", \"46]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.697, 0.952, 1.184, 1.254, 1.556, 2.276, 2.508, 2.914, 3.309, 3.413, 3.518, 4.714, 5.817, 7.129, 7.303, 7.465, 7.605, 7.79, 8.266, 8.429, 8.986, 9.183, 9.288, 9.659, 10.298, 11.18], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.639, 0.906, 1.103, 1.207, 1.509, 2.101, 2.461, 2.856, 3.262, 3.379, 3.483, 4.11, 5.375, 6.618, 7.256, 7.407, 7.546, 7.697, 8.208, 8.382, 8.928, 9.125, 9.207, 9.567, 10.182, 10.971, 12.167]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(595, 2, 'Page 9', 'That day, she planted a new seed in her garden. And every time she watered it, she thought: Just because something doesn’t happen right away doesn’t mean it will never happen.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"When\", \"Ada\", \"woke\", \"up,\", \"she\", \"was\", \"still\", \"in\", \"her\", \"bed.\", \"It\", \"had\", \"been\", \"a\", \"dream.\", \"[cite:\", \"47]\", \"But\", \"the\", \"feeling\", \"it\", \"left\", \"behind\", \"was\", \"real.\", \"[cite:\", \"48]\", \"That\", \"day,\", \"she\", \"planted\", \"a\", \"new\", \"seed\", \"in\", \"her\", \"garden.\", \"[cite:\", \"49]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.592, 0.859, 1.149, 1.324, 1.463, 1.718, 1.823, 1.95, 2.705, 2.879, 3.007, 3.216, 3.286, 4.505, 5.747, 7.384, 7.581, 7.709, 8.173, 8.336, 8.661, 9.416, 9.694, 10.96, 11.796, 13.549, 13.862, 14.327, 14.536, 14.954, 15.07, 15.279, 15.557, 15.697, 15.824, 16.904, 17.81], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.546, 0.813, 1.08, 1.277, 1.428, 1.66, 1.776, 1.904, 2.38, 2.833, 2.972, 3.17, 3.239, 3.808, 5.306, 6.687, 7.546, 7.651, 8.092, 8.266, 8.58, 9.137, 9.601, 10.147, 11.68, 12.597, 13.804, 14.257, 14.466, 14.896, 14.988, 15.209, 15.511, 15.627, 15.778, 16.393, 17.636, 18.762]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(596, 2, 'Page 10', 'Mars might still be red and silent. But one day, somewhere, someone might plant a seed.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"And\", \"every\", \"time\", \"she\", \"watered\", \"it,\", \"she\", \"thought:\", \"Just\", \"because\", \"something\", \"doesn\'t\", \"happen\", \"right\", \"away\", \"doesn\'t\", \"mean\", \"it\", \"will\", \"never\", \"happen.\", \"[cite:\", \"51]\", \"Mars\", \"might\", \"still\", \"be\", \"red\", \"and\", \"silent.\", \"[cite:\", \"52]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.604, 0.813, 0.987, 1.393, 1.521, 1.683, 2.45, 2.682, 2.984, 3.32, 3.576, 3.878, 4.063, 4.389, 4.714, 5.016, 5.132, 5.306, 5.561, 6.351, 7.245, 8.266, 8.626, 8.847, 9.137, 9.276, 9.497, 9.625, 10.379, 11.273], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.557, 0.778, 0.917, 1.347, 1.498, 1.625, 2.125, 2.647, 2.949, 3.274, 3.541, 3.831, 4.04, 4.319, 4.667, 4.934, 5.097, 5.259, 5.503, 6.072, 7.036, 8.022, 8.568, 8.8, 9.079, 9.218, 9.451, 9.567, 10.17, 11.029, 12.399]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(597, 2, 'Page 11', 'And sometimes, changing a planet begins with a child’s dream.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_2_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"But\", \"one\", \"day,\", \"somewhere,\", \"someone\", \"might\", \"plant\", \"a\", \"seed.\", \"[cite:\", \"53]\", \"And\", \"sometimes,\", \"changing\", \"a\", \"planet\", \"begins\", \"with\", \"a\", \"child\'s\", \"dream.\", \"[cite:\", \"54]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.546, 0.929, 1.8, 2.229, 2.438, 2.74, 2.844, 3.82, 4.969, 6.444, 6.664, 7.57, 7.988, 8.069, 8.51, 8.87, 9.033, 9.102, 9.567, 10.194, 11.32], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.511, 0.882, 1.591, 2.194, 2.392, 2.694, 2.775, 3.379, 4.528, 5.747, 6.594, 7.454, 7.941, 8.011, 8.452, 8.835, 8.998, 9.056, 9.52, 10.077, 11.041, 12.725]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(598, 3, 'Page 1', 'The sky was paler than usual that night. The stars were there, but their light was weak. It felt as if someone had erased their brightness.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"sky\", \"was\", \"paler\", \"than\", \"usual\", \"that\", \"night.\", \"[cite:\", \"56]\", \"The\", \"stars\", \"were\", \"there,\", \"but\", \"their\", \"light\", \"was\", \"weak.\", \"It\", \"felt\", \"as\", \"if\", \"someone\", \"had\", \"erased\", \"their\", \"brightness.\", \"[cite:\", \"57]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.627, 0.824, 1.219, 1.405, 1.776, 1.985, 2.821, 3.379, 4.563, 4.725, 5.085, 5.248, 5.515, 5.642, 5.863, 6.153, 6.351, 7.082, 7.279, 7.57, 7.697, 7.825, 8.139, 8.278, 8.673, 8.847, 9.729, 10.217], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.557, 0.743, 1.173, 1.335, 1.718, 1.927, 2.438, 3.344, 4.319, 4.667, 5.039, 5.213, 5.492, 5.619, 5.793, 6.095, 6.281, 6.838, 7.221, 7.512, 7.639, 7.767, 8.104, 8.231, 8.638, 8.812, 9.578, 10.182, 11.564]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(599, 3, 'Page 2', 'Most people in the city didn’t notice. The streetlights were already bright. But two siblings who loved watching the sky, Eren and Mira, noticed the change right away.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Most\", \"people\", \"in\", \"the\", \"city\", \"didn\'t\", \"notice.\", \"The\", \"streetlights\", \"were\", \"already\", \"bright.\", \"[cite:\", \"58]\", \"But\", \"two\", \"siblings\", \"who\", \"loved\", \"watching\", \"the\", \"sky,\", \"Eren\", \"and\", \"Mira,\", \"noticed\", \"the\", \"change\", \"right\", \"away.\", \"[cite:\", \"59]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.418, 0.685, 0.778, 0.882, 1.138, 1.405, 2.345, 2.519, 3.111, 3.309, 3.704, 4.621, 5.677, 6.687, 6.92, 7.198, 7.686, 7.848, 8.104, 8.452, 8.557, 9.079, 9.427, 9.543, 10.159, 10.542, 10.658, 11.029, 11.227, 11.889, 12.643], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.662, 0.743, 0.848, 1.091, 1.358, 1.962, 2.461, 3.065, 3.262, 3.646, 4.18, 5.503, 6.513, 6.885, 7.117, 7.651, 7.779, 8.057, 8.406, 8.522, 9.009, 9.381, 9.497, 9.985, 10.507, 10.612, 10.995, 11.192, 11.645, 12.562, 13.746]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(600, 3, 'Page 3', 'Eren placed his telescope by the window. Mira sat beside him, wrapped in a blanket. “Something is missing,” Mira said.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Eren\", \"placed\", \"his\", \"telescope\", \"by\", \"the\", \"window.\", \"Mira\", \"sat\", \"beside\", \"him,\", \"wrapped\", \"in\", \"a\", \"blanket.\", \"\'Something\", \"is\", \"missing,\'\", \"Mira\", \"said.\", \"[cite:\", \"60]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.418, 0.708, 0.824, 1.324, 1.451, 1.567, 2.264, 2.577, 2.81, 3.181, 3.518, 3.889, 3.994, 4.063, 5.433, 6.014, 6.165, 6.873, 7.221, 7.616, 8.15], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.673, 0.789, 1.3, 1.405, 1.521, 2.09, 2.531, 2.752, 3.146, 3.46, 3.855, 3.947, 4.017, 4.621, 5.956, 6.107, 6.722, 7.163, 7.581, 8.127, 9.474]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(601, 3, 'Page 4', 'She was right. The soft, magical glow around the stars was gone. The sky looked more ordinary, a little quieter.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"She\", \"was\", \"right.\", \"The\", \"soft,\", \"magical\", \"glow\", \"around\", \"the\", \"stars\", \"was\", \"gone.\", \"The\", \"sky\", \"looked\", \"more\", \"ordinary,\", \"a\", \"little\", \"quieter.\", \"[cite:\", \"61]\", \"That\", \"night,\", \"Mira\", \"had\", \"a\", \"dream.\", \"[cite:\", \"62]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.511, 1.567, 1.765, 2.206, 2.728, 3.135, 3.471, 3.587, 4.098, 4.342, 5.538, 5.712, 6.002, 6.258, 6.467, 7.477, 7.616, 7.86, 9.799, 10.681, 12.237, 12.539, 13.386, 13.839, 14.036, 14.118, 15.348, 16.08], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.441, 0.964, 1.707, 2.159, 2.67, 3.042, 3.425, 3.541, 4.017, 4.272, 4.841, 5.666, 5.944, 6.211, 6.42, 7.233, 7.546, 7.837, 8.499, 10.507, 11.633, 12.469, 13.108, 13.769, 13.99, 14.06, 14.652, 15.987, 17.043]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(602, 3, 'Page 5', 'That night, Mira had a dream. In her dream, fine golden dust was falling from the sky. This dust made the stars shine brighter.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"In\", \"her\", \"dream,\", \"fine\", \"golden\", \"dust\", \"was\", \"falling\", \"from\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"This\", \"dust\", \"made\", \"the\", \"stars\", \"shine\", \"brighter.\", \"[cite:\", \"63]\", \"But\", \"suddenly,\", \"the\", \"wind\", \"changed\", \"direction\", \"and\", \"blew\", \"all\", \"the\", \"stardust\", \"away.\", \"[cite:\", \"64]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.441, 1.126, 1.486, 1.823, 2.101, 2.276, 2.612, 2.786, 2.891, 4.238, 4.505, 4.853, 5.039, 5.143, 5.515, 5.793, 7.024, 7.79, 9.033, 9.218, 9.659, 9.776, 10.008, 10.379, 10.867, 10.983, 11.238, 11.436, 11.54, 12.04, 12.957, 13.7], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.383, 0.952, 1.44, 1.765, 2.055, 2.218, 2.566, 2.74, 2.856, 3.425, 4.435, 4.783, 5.016, 5.108, 5.468, 5.759, 6.327, 7.639, 8.649, 9.183, 9.636, 9.729, 9.95, 10.344, 10.82, 10.937, 11.18, 11.378, 11.505, 11.993, 12.516, 13.584, 14.582]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(603, 3, 'Page 6', 'But suddenly, the wind changed direction and blew all the stardust away. The stars lost their light and were left in darkness.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"stars\", \"lost\", \"their\", \"light\", \"and\", \"were\", \"left\", \"in\", \"darkness.\", \"[cite:\", \"65]\", \"As\", \"soon\", \"as\", \"Mira\", \"woke\", \"up,\", \"she\", \"told\", \"Eren\", \"about\", \"her\", \"dream.\", \"[cite:\", \"66]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.708, 1.033, 1.242, 1.567, 1.718, 1.881, 2.159, 2.287, 3.135, 3.68, 5.689, 5.898, 6.13, 6.269, 6.56, 6.827, 7.036, 7.21, 7.512, 7.767, 8.022, 8.173, 9.253, 9.845], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.639, 0.987, 1.184, 1.509, 1.66, 1.834, 2.101, 2.229, 3.007, 3.646, 4.574, 5.851, 6.084, 6.2, 6.502, 6.78, 7.012, 7.152, 7.454, 7.732, 7.976, 8.115, 8.649, 9.81, 11.146]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(604, 3, 'Page 7', 'As soon as Mira woke up, she told Eren about her dream. Eren thought for a moment. “Maybe stardust really exists,” he said. “And maybe it’s waiting for us somewhere.”', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Eren\", \"thought\", \"for\", \"a\", \"moment.\", \"[cite:\", \"67]\", \"\'Maybe\", \"stardust\", \"really\", \"exists,\'\", \"he\", \"said.\", \"[cite:\", \"68]\", \"\'And\", \"maybe\", \"it\'s\", \"waiting\", \"for\", \"us\", \"somewhere.\'\", \"[cite:\", \"69]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.406, 0.65, 0.801, 0.882, 1.428, 2.113, 3.146, 3.576, 4.052, 4.307, 4.76, 4.899, 5.294, 5.793, 6.56, 6.815, 7.036, 7.187, 7.465, 7.628, 7.767, 8.394, 8.951], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.615, 0.755, 0.824, 1.254, 1.997, 2.972, 3.529, 4.005, 4.261, 4.737, 4.841, 5.213, 5.77, 6.409, 6.769, 7.001, 7.152, 7.419, 7.57, 7.721, 8.324, 8.916, 10.077]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(605, 3, 'Page 8', 'The two siblings worked for days. Using cardboard boxes, old metal parts, batteries, and small lights, they built a space capsule. It wasn’t a real rocket, of course. But imagination can be stronger than fuel.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"two\", \"siblings\", \"worked\", \"for\", \"days.\", \"Using\", \"cardboard\", \"boxes,\", \"old\", \"metal\", \"parts,\", \"batteries,\", \"and\", \"small\", \"lights,\", \"they\", \"built\", \"a\", \"space\", \"capsule.\", \"[cite:\", \"70]\", \"It\", \"wasn\'t\", \"a\", \"real\", \"rocket,\", \"of\", \"course.\", \"But\", \"imagination\", \"can\", \"be\", \"stronger\", \"than\", \"fuel.\", \"[cite:\", \"71]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.546, 1.01, 1.312, 1.498, 2.438, 2.775, 3.32, 4.017, 4.319, 4.609, 5.248, 5.793, 5.944, 6.293, 7.059, 7.245, 7.512, 7.581, 7.941, 8.824, 9.253, 10.321, 10.495, 10.832, 10.937, 11.204, 11.622, 11.761, 12.62, 12.829, 13.595, 13.758, 13.897, 14.338, 14.512, 15.836, 16.312], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.476, 0.964, 1.265, 1.428, 2.113, 2.717, 3.274, 3.924, 4.249, 4.551, 5.155, 5.77, 5.886, 6.235, 6.885, 7.198, 7.465, 7.546, 7.895, 8.615, 9.218, 9.996, 10.449, 10.786, 10.867, 11.134, 11.598, 11.691, 12.295, 12.783, 13.537, 13.711, 13.851, 14.292, 14.454, 15.023, 16.277, 17.369]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(606, 3, 'Page 9', 'That night, they sat inside the capsule and closed their eyes. And the world grew quiet. Suddenly, they found themselves floating in a dark space. Pale stars surrounded them, no longer bright as before.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"That\", \"night,\", \"they\", \"sat\", \"inside\", \"the\", \"capsule\", \"and\", \"closed\", \"their\", \"eyes.\", \"[cite:\", \"72]\", \"And\", \"the\", \"world\", \"grew\", \"quiet.\", \"[cite:\", \"73]\", \"Suddenly,\", \"they\", \"found\", \"themselves\", \"floating\", \"in\", \"a\", \"dark\", \"space.\", \"[cite:\", \"74]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.383, 0.615, 0.778, 1.033, 1.335, 1.44, 1.892, 2.032, 2.345, 2.554, 3.111, 3.762, 4.365, 4.516, 4.632, 4.923, 5.143, 5.817, 6.397, 7.546, 8.022, 8.197, 8.406, 8.87, 9.288, 9.369, 9.439, 9.718, 10.391, 10.913], \"end_times\": [0.325, 0.592, 0.731, 0.975, 1.312, 1.405, 1.858, 1.974, 2.322, 2.496, 3.088, 3.704, 4.342, 4.481, 4.586, 4.876, 5.085, 5.724, 6.351, 7.268, 7.999, 8.139, 8.371, 8.812, 9.23, 9.334, 9.392, 9.659, 10.298, 10.867, 11.889]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(607, 3, 'Page 10', 'After a while, they saw a golden cloud in the distance. It shimmered gently. As they got closer, they realized it was stardust drifting in the wind.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Pale\", \"stars\", \"surrounded\", \"them,\", \"no\", \"longer\", \"bright\", \"as\", \"before.\", \"[cite:\", \"74]\", \"After\", \"a\", \"while,\", \"they\", \"saw\", \"a\", \"golden\", \"cloud\", \"in\", \"the\", \"distance.\", \"It\", \"shimmered\", \"gently.\", \"[cite:\", \"75]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.592, 1.126, 1.637, 1.846, 2.009, 2.299, 2.577, 2.705, 3.367, 3.982, 5.19, 5.538, 5.608, 5.968, 6.13, 6.351, 6.432, 6.803, 7.175, 7.268, 7.372, 8.057, 8.243, 8.684, 9.323, 9.88], \"end_times\": [0.534, 1.068, 1.591, 1.811, 1.939, 2.252, 2.531, 2.647, 3.251, 3.924, 4.807, 5.48, 5.561, 5.944, 6.084, 6.293, 6.374, 6.745, 7.129, 7.233, 7.338, 7.976, 8.185, 8.626, 9.242, 9.834, 11.238]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(608, 3, 'Page 11', 'But the dust was scattered. It couldn’t shine while separated. Mira reached out her hand. A few pieces fell into her palm. When the tiny particles came together, they glowed brighter.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"they\", \"got\", \"closer,\", \"they\", \"realized\", \"it\", \"was\", \"stardust\", \"drifting\", \"in\", \"the\", \"wind.\", \"[cite:\", \"76]\", \"But\", \"the\", \"dust\", \"was\", \"scattered.\", \"It\", \"couldn\'t\", \"shine\", \"while\", \"separated.\", \"[cite:\", \"77]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.43, 0.627, 1.184, 1.382, 1.765, 1.846, 1.985, 2.496, 2.856, 2.949, 3.053, 3.669, 4.365, 5.387, 5.561, 5.666, 5.921, 6.049, 6.989, 7.152, 7.454, 7.744, 7.941, 8.754, 9.497], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.395, 0.58, 1.126, 1.324, 1.73, 1.811, 1.927, 2.461, 2.821, 2.914, 3.019, 3.495, 4.214, 5.178, 5.526, 5.631, 5.875, 6.014, 6.606, 7.105, 7.419, 7.721, 7.906, 8.626, 9.288, 10.542]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(609, 3, 'Page 12', 'Eren helped her. Together, they gently gathered the stardust. As the pieces joined, the light grew stronger, and the sky slowly came back to life. With every piece they collected, a star began to shine again. One star. Then another. Darkness slowly turned into sparkle.', 12, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_12.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mira\", \"reached\", \"out\", \"her\", \"hand.\", \"A\", \"few\", \"pieces\", \"fell\", \"into\", \"her\", \"palm.\", \"[cite:\", \"78]\", \"When\", \"the\", \"tiny\", \"particles\", \"came\", \"together,\", \"they\", \"glowed\", \"brighter.\", \"[cite:\", \"79]\", \"Eren\", \"helped\", \"her.\", \"Together,\", \"they\", \"gently\", \"gathered\", \"the\", \"stardust.\", \"[cite:\", \"80]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.488, 0.755, 0.917, 1.057, 1.428, 1.556, 1.753, 2.159, 2.38, 2.612, 2.74, 3.448, 4.063, 4.876, 5.085, 5.19, 5.526, 6.014, 6.235, 6.699, 6.896, 7.221, 7.988, 8.661, 9.381, 9.752, 10.031, 10.507, 10.995, 11.169, 11.505, 11.877, 11.981, 12.91, 13.618], \"end_times\": [0.418, 0.72, 0.871, 0.998, 1.393, 1.486, 1.695, 2.101, 2.334, 2.531, 2.694, 3.204, 4.017, 4.783, 5.05, 5.155, 5.468, 5.968, 6.2, 6.664, 6.838, 7.175, 7.663, 8.545, 9.311, 9.694, 9.996, 10.298, 10.971, 11.111, 11.459, 11.842, 11.947, 12.666, 13.468, 14.396]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(610, 3, 'Page 13', 'When they placed the last stardust back where it belonged, the sky returned to its old brightness. The stars were strong, warm, and alive again. At that moment, Eren and Mira realized something: stars were weak alone, but together, they could defeat the darkness.', 13, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_13.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"pieces\", \"joined,\", \"the\", \"light\", \"grew\", \"stronger,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"slowly\", \"came\", \"back\", \"to\", \"life.\", \"[cite:\", \"80]\", \"With\", \"every\", \"piece\", \"they\", \"collected,\", \"a\", \"star\", \"began\", \"to\", \"shine\", \"again.\", \"[cite:\", \"81]\", \"One\", \"star.\", \"Then\", \"another.\", \"[cite:\", \"82-83]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.395, 0.801, 1.196, 1.312, 1.521, 1.718, 2.252, 2.438, 2.543, 2.926, 3.309, 3.506, 3.715, 3.855, 4.76, 5.608, 6.351, 6.583, 6.838, 7.094, 7.256, 7.837, 7.988, 8.336, 8.649, 8.766, 9.056, 9.845, 10.67, 11.482, 11.784, 12.249, 12.469, 13.502, 14.431], \"end_times\": [0.244, 0.36, 0.731, 1.161, 1.265, 1.486, 1.672, 2.218, 2.392, 2.508, 2.844, 3.262, 3.483, 3.669, 3.785, 4.319, 5.492, 6.177, 6.525, 6.792, 7.059, 7.21, 7.79, 7.906, 8.266, 8.603, 8.707, 9.021, 9.52, 10.553, 11.331, 11.738, 12.202, 12.423, 12.992, 14.187, 16.115]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(611, 3, 'Page 14', 'When they opened their eyes, they were back in their room. The telescope was still by the window. They looked up at the sky. The stars were brighter than ever. Maybe they hadn’t really gone to space. Or maybe they had.', 14, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_14.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Darkness\", \"slowly\", \"turned\", \"into\", \"sparkle.\", \"[cite:\", \"84]\", \"When\", \"they\", \"placed\", \"the\", \"last\", \"stardust\", \"back\", \"where\", \"it\", \"belonged,\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"its\", \"old\", \"brightness.\", \"[cite:\", \"85]\", \"The\", \"stars\", \"were\", \"strong,\", \"warm,\", \"and\", \"alive\", \"again.\", \"[cite:\", \"86]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.685, 1.161, 1.498, 1.707, 2.763, 3.727, 4.737, 4.934, 5.085, 5.41, 5.538, 5.933, 6.525, 6.803, 7.001, 7.094, 7.918, 8.081, 8.452, 8.905, 9.033, 9.195, 9.427, 10.786, 11.854, 12.806, 12.968, 13.317, 13.502, 14.211, 14.71, 14.919, 15.232, 15.952, 16.881], \"end_times\": [0.627, 1.103, 1.451, 1.649, 2.322, 3.518, 4.528, 4.899, 5.039, 5.375, 5.48, 5.84, 6.444, 6.757, 6.966, 7.047, 7.709, 8.022, 8.359, 8.87, 8.951, 9.149, 9.369, 10.182, 11.575, 12.632, 12.922, 13.27, 13.456, 14.095, 14.687, 14.861, 15.209, 15.708, 16.707, 17.833]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(612, 3, 'Page 15', 'But they knew this: When light disappears, someone has to act to bring it back. And sometimes, even the smallest pieces of light, when united, can change the entire sky.', 15, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_3_page_15.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"At\", \"that\", \"moment,\", \"Eren\", \"and\", \"Mira\", \"realized\", \"something:\", \"stars\", \"were\", \"weak\", \"alone,\", \"but\", \"together,\", \"they\", \"could\", \"defeat\", \"the\", \"darkness.\", \"[cite:\", \"87]\", \"They\", \"looked\", \"up\", \"at\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"The\", \"stars\", \"were\", \"brighter\", \"than\", \"ever.\", \"[cite:\", \"89-90]\", \"When\", \"light\", \"disappears,\", \"someone\", \"has\", \"to\", \"act\", \"to\", \"bring\", \"it\", \"back.\", \"[cite:\", \"93]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.29, 0.511, 1.324, 1.753, 1.892, 2.334, 2.786, 3.785, 4.261, 4.447, 4.702, 5.375, 5.573, 6.42, 6.606, 6.792, 7.198, 7.314, 9.23, 9.752, 10.646, 10.855, 11.146, 11.296, 11.401, 11.517, 12.469, 12.643, 13.061, 13.259, 13.642, 13.827, 14.907, 15.441, 16.649, 16.916, 17.183, 17.914, 18.251, 18.448, 18.576, 18.82, 18.924, 19.145, 19.249, 19.946, 20.596], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.441, 1.173, 1.683, 1.834, 2.252, 2.763, 3.402, 4.214, 4.4, 4.644, 5.259, 5.538, 6.269, 6.571, 6.757, 7.14, 7.268, 8.115, 9.729, 10.577, 10.809, 11.099, 11.25, 11.366, 11.471, 12.144, 12.585, 13.015, 13.212, 13.584, 13.769, 14.303, 15.418, 16.556, 16.846, 17.136, 17.879, 18.228, 18.39, 18.506, 18.785, 18.866, 19.087, 19.203, 19.737, 20.561, 21.502]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(613, 4, 'Page 1', 'Deep in space, there was a planet shining with golden rings: Saturn. What made Saturn special were the magnificent rings surrounding it. Made of tiny pieces of ice and stone, they circled the planet like a crown.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Deep\", \"in\", \"space,\", \"there\", \"was\", \"a\", \"planet\", \"shining\", \"with\", \"golden\", \"rings:\", \"Saturn.\", \"[cite:\", \"96]\", \"What\", \"made\", \"Saturn\", \"special\", \"were\", \"the\", \"magnificent\", \"rings\", \"surrounding\", \"it.\", \"[cite:\", \"97]\", \"Made\", \"of\", \"tiny\", \"pieces\", \"of\", \"ice\", \"and\", \"stone,\", \"they\", \"circled\", \"the\", \"planet\", \"like\", \"a\", \"crown.\", \"[cite:\", \"98]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.418, 0.557, 1.556, 1.765, 1.892, 1.985, 2.426, 2.902, 3.1, 3.553, 4.574, 5.352, 6.165, 7.674, 7.906, 8.139, 8.545, 8.986, 9.149, 9.265, 10.008, 10.333, 10.867, 11.517, 12.26, 13.201, 13.41, 13.514, 13.886, 14.269, 14.396, 14.663, 14.826, 15.534, 15.743, 16.08, 16.184, 16.544, 16.718, 16.811, 18.158, 18.971], \"end_times\": [0.36, 0.488, 1.231, 1.73, 1.858, 1.927, 2.345, 2.844, 3.03, 3.483, 4.133, 5.236, 6.037, 6.978, 7.86, 8.092, 8.487, 8.928, 9.114, 9.218, 9.938, 10.298, 10.809, 11.134, 12.132, 13.026, 13.386, 13.468, 13.827, 14.222, 14.327, 14.629, 14.768, 15.36, 15.685, 16.057, 16.149, 16.498, 16.684, 16.742, 17.345, 18.797, 19.83]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(614, 4, 'Page 2', 'One night, an observatory on Earth noticed something strange. A small gap had appeared in Saturn’s ring, as if a piece were missing.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"night,\", \"an\", \"observatory\", \"on\", \"Earth\", \"noticed\", \"something\", \"strange.\", \"A\", \"small\", \"gap\", \"had\", \"appeared\", \"in\", \"Saturn\'s\", \"ring,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"a\", \"piece\", \"were\", \"missing.\", \"[cite:\", \"99]\", \"The\", \"first\", \"person\", \"to\", \"notice\", \"this\", \"was\", \"Deniz,\", \"a\", \"child\", \"with\", \"a\", \"great\", \"curiosity\", \"for\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"[cite:\", \"100]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.789, 0.964, 1.637, 1.8, 2.159, 2.519, 2.868, 3.947, 4.098, 4.435, 4.737, 4.876, 5.259, 5.387, 5.863, 6.177, 6.351, 6.49, 6.571, 6.873, 7.036, 8.278, 8.777, 9.787, 9.961, 10.228, 10.553, 10.681, 11.018, 11.273, 11.482, 12.26, 12.399, 12.713, 12.852, 12.922, 13.166, 13.851, 13.99, 14.106, 15.197, 15.732], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.755, 0.917, 1.567, 1.73, 2.043, 2.496, 2.81, 3.506, 4.017, 4.377, 4.69, 4.841, 5.224, 5.329, 5.793, 6.153, 6.293, 6.432, 6.513, 6.838, 7.001, 7.581, 8.742, 9.636, 9.903, 10.182, 10.507, 10.612, 10.983, 11.204, 11.413, 12.19, 12.33, 12.678, 12.817, 12.875, 13.108, 13.793, 13.944, 14.06, 14.756, 15.697, 16.579]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(615, 4, 'Page 3', 'The first person to notice this was Deniz, a child with a great curiosity for the sky despite his young age. His father was an astronomer, and they often observed planets together through a telescope.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"His\", \"father\", \"was\", \"an\", \"astronomer,\", \"and\", \"they\", \"often\", \"observed\", \"planets\", \"together\", \"through\", \"a\", \"telescope.\", \"[cite:\", \"101]\", \"When\", \"Deniz\", \"looked\", \"through\", \"the\", \"telescope,\", \"he\", \"saw\", \"the\", \"gap.\", \"The\", \"order\", \"of\", \"the\", \"ring\", \"was\", \"broken.\", \"[cite:\", \"102]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.685, 0.859, 0.964, 1.741, 1.927, 2.101, 2.438, 2.821, 3.239, 3.611, 3.843, 3.913, 5.039, 6.037, 7.14, 7.396, 7.755, 7.976, 8.231, 8.336, 9.218, 9.358, 9.59, 9.706, 10.53, 10.739, 11.053, 11.146, 11.273, 11.517, 11.691, 12.759, 13.63], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.639, 0.813, 0.917, 1.66, 1.881, 2.043, 2.392, 2.786, 3.193, 3.564, 3.82, 3.866, 4.656, 5.863, 6.896, 7.338, 7.709, 7.953, 8.197, 8.301, 9.067, 9.3, 9.532, 9.659, 10.205, 10.658, 10.995, 11.099, 11.215, 11.459, 11.633, 12.318, 13.537, 14.954]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(616, 4, 'Page 4', 'When Deniz looked through the telescope, he saw the gap. The order of the ring was broken. A sense of unease filled him.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"sense\", \"of\", \"unease\", \"filled\", \"him.\", \"[cite:\", \"103]\", \"That\", \"night,\", \"he\", \"dreamed\", \"he\", \"was\", \"floating\", \"through\", \"space.\", \"Passing\", \"between\", \"the\", \"stars,\", \"he\", \"moved\", \"closer\", \"to\", \"Saturn.\", \"[cite:\", \"104]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.255, 0.522, 0.65, 1.149, 1.486, 1.939, 2.577, 4.063, 4.331, 4.946, 5.097, 5.468, 5.561, 5.747, 6.142, 6.397, 7.291, 7.744, 8.057, 8.162, 8.649, 8.777, 9.067, 9.485, 9.625, 10.809, 11.517], \"end_times\": [0.186, 0.488, 0.569, 1.091, 1.44, 1.823, 2.508, 3.367, 4.284, 4.772, 5.027, 5.422, 5.515, 5.677, 6.107, 6.362, 6.966, 7.686, 8.022, 8.127, 8.615, 8.707, 9.009, 9.427, 9.555, 10.205, 11.401, 12.446]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(617, 4, 'Page 5', 'That night, he dreamed he was floating through space. Passing between the stars, he moved closer to Saturn. The planet was much bigger than he had imagined. Its rings flowed around it like a giant river. And truly, one section was missing.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"planet\", \"was\", \"much\", \"bigger\", \"than\", \"he\", \"had\", \"imagined.\", \"Its\", \"rings\", \"flowed\", \"around\", \"it\", \"like\", \"a\", \"giant\", \"river.\", \"[cite:\", \"105]\", \"And\", \"truly,\", \"one\", \"section\", \"was\", \"missing.\", \"[cite:\", \"106]\", \"Deniz\", \"moved\", \"closer.\", \"[cite:\", \"107]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.697, 0.894, 1.138, 1.428, 1.602, 1.707, 1.834, 2.868, 3.135, 3.46, 3.75, 4.063, 4.18, 4.354, 4.447, 4.841, 6.142, 6.803, 7.558, 7.744, 8.301, 8.557, 8.963, 9.137, 9.903, 10.565, 11.494, 11.912, 12.19, 13.096, 13.723], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.65, 0.813, 1.08, 1.382, 1.544, 1.66, 1.788, 2.485, 3.065, 3.402, 3.727, 4.005, 4.133, 4.319, 4.377, 4.783, 5.329, 6.734, 7.523, 7.697, 8.243, 8.51, 8.905, 9.079, 9.659, 10.507, 11.413, 11.842, 12.132, 12.817, 13.677, 14.721]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(618, 4, 'Page 6', 'Deniz moved closer. Near the gap, small pieces of ice were drifting, as if blown away by a wind. The pieces had scattered and lost their harmony. In that moment, Deniz understood something: the rings were not one single piece. They were made of thousands of small parts moving together. Order was born from staying united.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Near\", \"the\", \"gap,\", \"small\", \"pieces\", \"of\", \"ice\", \"were\", \"drifting,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"blown\", \"away\", \"by\", \"a\", \"wind.\", \"[cite:\", \"107]\", \"The\", \"pieces\", \"had\", \"scattered\", \"and\", \"lost\", \"their\", \"harmony.\", \"[cite:\", \"108]\", \"In\", \"that\", \"moment,\", \"Deniz\", \"understood\", \"something:\", \"the\", \"rings\", \"were\", \"not\", \"one\", \"single\", \"piece.\", \"[cite:\", \"109]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.372, 0.488, 0.952, 1.312, 1.672, 1.788, 1.985, 2.148, 2.577, 2.705, 2.856, 3.204, 3.46, 3.657, 3.738, 4.598, 5.201, 6.351, 6.513, 6.885, 7.07, 7.558, 7.697, 7.953, 8.162, 9.091, 9.927, 10.937, 11.146, 11.389, 11.773, 12.156, 12.632, 13.56, 13.735, 14.036, 14.199, 14.42, 14.768, 15.163, 16.196, 16.811], \"end_times\": [0.337, 0.441, 0.836, 1.254, 1.625, 1.73, 1.962, 2.113, 2.554, 2.659, 2.786, 3.158, 3.402, 3.587, 3.68, 4.272, 5.155, 6.026, 6.467, 6.838, 7.001, 7.523, 7.639, 7.918, 8.104, 8.766, 9.799, 10.693, 11.088, 11.32, 11.738, 12.086, 12.585, 13.235, 13.665, 13.99, 14.164, 14.35, 14.687, 15.116, 15.755, 16.765, 17.833]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(619, 4, 'Page 7', 'Deniz reached out his hands and gently brought the ice pieces together. As they moved closer, they slowly began to rotate and align again.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"They\", \"were\", \"made\", \"of\", \"thousands\", \"of\", \"small\", \"parts\", \"moving\", \"together.\", \"Order\", \"was\", \"born\", \"from\", \"staying\", \"united.\", \"[cite:\", \"110]\", \"Deniz\", \"reached\", \"out\", \"his\", \"hands\", \"and\", \"gently\", \"brought\", \"the\", \"ice\", \"pieces\", \"together.\", \"[cite:\", \"111]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.476, 0.697, 0.824, 1.358, 1.474, 1.776, 2.136, 2.426, 3.39, 3.773, 3.959, 4.284, 4.481, 4.841, 5.77, 6.502, 7.825, 8.29, 8.626, 8.789, 8.951, 9.346, 9.532, 9.915, 10.182, 10.321, 10.577, 10.971, 11.97, 12.783], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.441, 0.673, 0.755, 1.324, 1.416, 1.718, 2.078, 2.38, 2.949, 3.715, 3.901, 4.226, 4.423, 4.772, 5.445, 6.467, 7.314, 8.208, 8.58, 8.742, 8.893, 9.3, 9.462, 9.868, 10.147, 10.252, 10.542, 10.925, 11.529, 12.725, 14.071]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(620, 4, 'Page 8', 'Space was silent. Only the soft movement of the rings could be felt. When each piece returned to its place, the ring was complete again. The gap closed. Saturn regained its former beauty. At that moment, Deniz saw a soft light spread across the planet, as if Saturn was saying thank you.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"they\", \"moved\", \"closer,\", \"they\", \"slowly\", \"began\", \"to\", \"rotate\", \"and\", \"align\", \"again.\", \"[cite:\", \"112]\", \"Space\", \"was\", \"silent.\", \"Only\", \"the\", \"soft\", \"movement\", \"of\", \"the\", \"rings\", \"could\", \"be\", \"felt.\", \"[cite:\", \"113]\", \"When\", \"each\", \"piece\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"its\", \"place,\", \"the\", \"ring\", \"was\", \"complete\", \"again.\", \"[cite:\", \"114]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.453, 0.731, 1.591, 1.788, 2.159, 2.485, 2.635, 3.146, 3.297, 3.622, 4.632, 5.851, 7.361, 7.79, 7.976, 8.928, 9.218, 9.334, 9.683, 10.066, 10.159, 10.286, 10.612, 10.786, 10.902, 11.726, 12.562, 14.153, 14.396, 14.663, 14.988, 15.395, 15.511, 15.685, 16.289, 16.451, 16.684, 16.858, 17.252, 18.402, 19.18], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.406, 0.685, 1.347, 1.741, 2.113, 2.426, 2.543, 3.1, 3.251, 3.587, 4.122, 5.341, 7.036, 7.755, 7.918, 8.603, 9.172, 9.288, 9.613, 10.019, 10.124, 10.228, 10.553, 10.751, 10.855, 11.343, 12.446, 13.827, 14.338, 14.594, 14.942, 15.36, 15.441, 15.627, 16.173, 16.382, 16.625, 16.8, 17.229, 17.705, 19.11, 20.573]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(621, 4, 'Page 9', 'When morning came, Deniz was back on Earth. He looked through the telescope again. The ring looked perfect. Maybe it was a dream. Maybe it wasn’t.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"gap\", \"closed.\", \"Saturn\", \"regained\", \"its\", \"former\", \"beauty.\", \"[cite:\", \"114]\", \"At\", \"that\", \"moment,\", \"Deniz\", \"saw\", \"a\", \"soft\", \"light\", \"spread\", \"across\", \"the\", \"planet,\", \"as\", \"if\", \"Saturn\", \"was\", \"saying\", \"thank\", \"you.\", \"[cite:\", \"115]\", \"When\", \"morning\", \"came,\", \"Deniz\", \"was\", \"back\", \"on\", \"Earth.\", \"[cite:\", \"116]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.627, 1.544, 2.02, 2.543, 2.728, 3.111, 4.261, 5.259, 7.082, 7.268, 7.488, 8.022, 8.452, 8.707, 8.835, 9.207, 9.485, 9.787, 10.17, 10.275, 10.948, 11.157, 11.308, 11.726, 11.889, 12.272, 12.585, 13.584, 14.373, 15.604, 15.859, 16.219, 16.765, 17.206, 17.392, 17.67, 17.833, 18.762, 19.714], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.546, 1.3, 1.95, 2.485, 2.67, 3.053, 3.657, 5.016, 6.269, 7.221, 7.43, 7.941, 8.394, 8.638, 8.742, 9.149, 9.427, 9.752, 10.112, 10.24, 10.832, 11.099, 11.238, 11.68, 11.842, 12.179, 12.516, 12.98, 14.257, 15.395, 15.801, 16.161, 16.637, 17.148, 17.322, 17.601, 17.763, 18.321, 19.54, 21.037]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(622, 4, 'Page 10', 'But Deniz now knew this: great things exist through the harmony of small parts. And sometimes, when order is broken, patience is needed to bring the pieces back together. Space was infinite. But everything within it was connected by an unseen balance.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_4_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"ring\", \"looked\", \"perfect.\", \"[cite:\", \"117]\", \"But\", \"Deniz\", \"now\", \"knew\", \"this:\", \"great\", \"things\", \"exist\", \"through\", \"the\", \"harmony\", \"of\", \"small\", \"parts.\", \"[cite:\", \"120]\", \"Space\", \"was\", \"infinite.\", \"But\", \"everything\", \"within\", \"it\", \"was\", \"connected\", \"by\", \"an\", \"unseen\", \"balance.\", \"[cite:\", \"122]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.557, 0.836, 1.556, 2.299, 3.599, 3.796, 4.203, 4.423, 4.632, 5.422, 5.724, 6.072, 6.536, 6.792, 6.931, 7.361, 7.488, 7.848, 8.475, 9.474, 10.635, 11.157, 11.401, 12.26, 12.469, 12.934, 13.247, 13.363, 13.549, 14.106, 14.303, 14.443, 14.919, 15.662, 16.533], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.499, 0.778, 1.463, 2.241, 3.425, 3.762, 4.122, 4.365, 4.574, 5.143, 5.666, 6.002, 6.49, 6.769, 6.861, 7.303, 7.419, 7.779, 8.44, 9.3, 10.391, 11.111, 11.308, 12.051, 12.423, 12.887, 13.201, 13.317, 13.479, 14.06, 14.245, 14.362, 14.849, 15.546, 16.358, 17.601]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(623, 5, 'Page 1', 'One summer night, the sky was calmer than usual. The stars were bright but silent. Little Arda sat in the garden, watching the sky through his telescope. To him, space was an endless mystery.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"One\", \"summer\", \"night,\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"was\", \"calmer\", \"than\", \"usual.\", \"The\", \"stars\", \"were\", \"bright\", \"but\", \"silent.\", \"[cite:\", \"124]\", \"Little\", \"Arda\", \"sat\", \"in\", \"the\", \"garden,\", \"watching\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"through\", \"his\", \"telescope.\", \"To\", \"him,\", \"space\", \"was\", \"an\", \"endless\", \"mystery.\", \"[cite:\", \"125]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.348, 0.615, 0.836, 0.94, 1.173, 1.324, 1.66, 1.834, 2.531, 2.694, 3.007, 3.158, 3.553, 3.773, 5.712, 6.142, 7.14, 7.442, 7.755, 8.022, 8.115, 8.231, 8.684, 9.102, 9.195, 9.485, 9.718, 9.857, 10.797, 10.995, 11.227, 11.633, 11.807, 11.935, 12.341, 12.945, 13.468], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.569, 0.813, 0.906, 1.126, 1.277, 1.625, 1.776, 2.357, 2.647, 2.972, 3.123, 3.46, 3.727, 4.412, 6.095, 6.931, 7.396, 7.686, 7.964, 8.081, 8.185, 8.638, 9.056, 9.172, 9.439, 9.694, 9.81, 10.519, 10.913, 11.192, 11.587, 11.761, 11.865, 12.283, 12.91, 13.433, 14.303]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(624, 5, 'Page 2', 'Suddenly, a thin blue light appeared in the sky. It quickly descended and landed in the empty area behind the garden. Arda couldn’t believe his eyes. His heart was racing, but his curiosity was stronger than his fear.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Suddenly,\", \"a\", \"thin\", \"blue\", \"light\", \"appeared\", \"in\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"It\", \"quickly\", \"descended\", \"and\", \"landed\", \"in\", \"the\", \"empty\", \"area\", \"behind\", \"the\", \"garden.\", \"[cite:\", \"126]\", \"Arda\", \"couldn\'t\", \"believe\", \"his\", \"eyes.\", \"His\", \"curiosity\", \"was\", \"stronger\", \"than\", \"his\", \"fear.\", \"[cite:\", \"127]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.65, 0.824, 1.149, 1.451, 1.73, 2.125, 2.206, 2.322, 3.228, 3.413, 3.796, 4.319, 4.481, 4.865, 4.957, 5.085, 5.41, 5.817, 6.165, 6.281, 7.268, 8.173, 10.286, 10.623, 10.948, 11.273, 11.447, 12.214, 12.446, 13.166, 13.328, 13.827, 14.013, 14.211, 15.325, 16.173], \"end_times\": [0.615, 0.708, 1.057, 1.393, 1.683, 2.09, 2.171, 2.276, 2.902, 3.355, 3.738, 4.261, 4.412, 4.818, 4.923, 5.027, 5.341, 5.747, 6.118, 6.235, 6.827, 7.964, 9.334, 10.577, 10.902, 11.238, 11.389, 12.005, 12.376, 13.096, 13.282, 13.769, 13.955, 14.129, 14.721, 15.999, 17.276]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(625, 5, 'Page 3', 'From the light emerged a small being with round eyes and soft gray skin. It was shorter than Arda and wore a glowing suit. It was an alien.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"From\", \"the\", \"light\", \"emerged\", \"a\", \"small\", \"being\", \"with\", \"round\", \"eyes\", \"and\", \"soft\", \"gray\", \"skin.\", \"[cite:\", \"128]\", \"It\", \"was\", \"shorter\", \"than\", \"Arda\", \"and\", \"wore\", \"a\", \"glowing\", \"suit.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"an\", \"alien.\", \"[cite:\", \"129-130]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.464, 0.789, 1.219, 1.3, 1.637, 2.043, 2.252, 2.612, 3.03, 3.239, 3.622, 3.924, 4.656, 5.584, 6.78, 6.954, 7.129, 7.523, 7.709, 8.092, 8.266, 8.499, 8.58, 9.033, 9.81, 9.973, 10.112, 10.24, 11.297, 12.051], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.395, 0.731, 1.173, 1.254, 1.567, 1.974, 2.183, 2.543, 2.961, 3.17, 3.564, 3.855, 4.481, 5.375, 6.455, 6.908, 7.07, 7.477, 7.639, 8.046, 8.208, 8.464, 8.533, 8.94, 9.601, 9.938, 10.077, 10.17, 10.913, 11.935, 13.653]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(626, 5, 'Page 4', 'The alien carefully observed its surroundings. Earth was unfamiliar to it. It examined the leaves of the trees, the smell of the soil, and the sound of the wind. But there was a slight worry on its face.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"alien\", \"carefully\", \"observed\", \"its\", \"surroundings.\", \"Earth\", \"was\", \"unfamiliar\", \"to\", \"it.\", \"[cite:\", \"131]\", \"It\", \"examined\", \"the\", \"leaves\", \"of\", \"the\", \"trees,\", \"the\", \"smell\", \"of\", \"the\", \"soil,\", \"and\", \"the\", \"sound\", \"of\", \"the\", \"wind.\", \"But\", \"there\", \"was\", \"a\", \"slight\", \"worry\", \"on\", \"its\", \"face.\", \"[cite:\", \"132-133]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.766, 1.289, 1.718, 1.834, 3.03, 3.344, 3.529, 4.145, 4.331, 4.714, 5.224, 6.269, 6.432, 6.943, 7.07, 7.384, 7.5, 7.616, 8.29, 8.44, 8.731, 8.835, 8.963, 9.543, 9.729, 9.845, 10.159, 10.275, 10.403, 11.494, 11.668, 11.842, 11.993, 12.063, 12.446, 12.806, 12.922, 13.096, 13.769, 14.362], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.708, 1.231, 1.683, 1.811, 2.705, 3.286, 3.46, 4.087, 4.214, 4.644, 5.201, 6.118, 6.385, 6.908, 7.012, 7.349, 7.454, 7.57, 8.173, 8.394, 8.684, 8.789, 8.905, 9.485, 9.683, 9.799, 10.101, 10.217, 10.344, 10.89, 11.645, 11.819, 11.947, 12.016, 12.388, 12.736, 12.875, 13.038, 13.618, 14.327, 16.625]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(627, 5, 'Page 5', 'Arda slowly stepped closer. Without speaking, he raised his hand in greeting. The alien did the same. In that moment, Arda realized something. Words were not necessary. They both understood that they were not alone.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Arda\", \"slowly\", \"stepped\", \"closer.\", \"Without\", \"speaking,\", \"he\", \"raised\", \"his\", \"hand\", \"in\", \"greeting.\", \"[cite:\", \"134]\", \"The\", \"alien\", \"did\", \"the\", \"same.\", \"[cite:\", \"135]\", \"In\", \"that\", \"moment,\", \"Arda\", \"realized\", \"something.\", \"Words\", \"were\", \"not\", \"necessary.\", \"[cite:\", \"136]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.813, 1.115, 1.997, 2.38, 3.32, 3.483, 3.796, 3.947, 4.214, 4.342, 4.957, 5.898, 7.221, 7.43, 7.802, 7.953, 8.081, 8.591, 9.474, 10.67, 10.844, 11.041, 11.598, 11.923, 12.341, 13.224, 13.572, 13.758, 13.944, 14.861, 15.685], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.766, 1.068, 1.718, 2.322, 2.995, 3.402, 3.762, 3.889, 4.156, 4.284, 4.876, 5.724, 7.012, 7.349, 7.755, 7.918, 8.022, 8.533, 9.323, 10.344, 10.797, 10.983, 11.482, 11.854, 12.318, 12.899, 13.537, 13.711, 13.897, 14.687, 15.569, 16.811]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(628, 5, 'Page 6', 'The alien’s name was Mimo. Arda understood this from the gentle vibrations coming from a small device on Mimo’s wrist. The device showed emotions with colors. Blue meant calm. Yellow meant curiosity. Green meant happiness.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"They\", \"both\", \"understood\", \"that\", \"they\", \"were\", \"not\", \"alone.\", \"[cite:\", \"136]\", \"The\", \"alien\'s\", \"name\", \"was\", \"Mimo.\", \"Arda\", \"understood\", \"this\", \"from\", \"the\", \"gentle\", \"vibrations\", \"coming\", \"from\", \"a\", \"small\", \"device\", \"on\", \"Mimo\'s\", \"wrist.\", \"[cite:\", \"137]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.627, 1.115, 1.265, 1.416, 1.591, 1.8, 2.705, 3.541, 5.271, 5.492, 6.026, 6.432, 6.711, 8.092, 8.533, 9.067, 9.3, 9.52, 9.659, 10.031, 10.716, 11.018, 11.204, 11.285, 11.622, 12.051, 12.225, 12.608, 13.607, 14.373], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.569, 1.08, 1.231, 1.382, 1.544, 1.741, 2.322, 3.39, 4.83, 5.399, 5.956, 6.362, 6.629, 7.396, 8.464, 9.021, 9.242, 9.462, 9.59, 9.996, 10.646, 10.96, 11.157, 11.227, 11.564, 12.005, 12.167, 12.574, 13.096, 14.257, 15.79]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(629, 5, 'Page 7', 'Mimo’s device first glowed yellow. Then it slowly turned green. Arda showed Mimo the garden. He touched the grass, pointed to the sky, and tried to explain what Earth was like.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"device\", \"showed\", \"emotions\", \"with\", \"colors.\", \"Blue\", \"meant\", \"calm.\", \"Yellow\", \"meant\", \"curiosity.\", \"Green\", \"meant\", \"happiness.\", \"[cite:\", \"138]\", \"Mimo\'s\", \"device\", \"first\", \"glowed\", \"yellow.\", \"Then\", \"it\", \"slowly\", \"turned\", \"green.\", \"[cite:\", \"139]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.662, 0.894, 1.335, 1.509, 2.276, 2.554, 2.798, 3.367, 3.692, 3.913, 5.108, 5.48, 5.712, 6.594, 7.396, 8.847, 9.288, 9.764, 10.124, 10.461, 11.134, 11.355, 11.482, 11.981, 12.341, 12.852, 13.688], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.639, 0.859, 1.3, 1.463, 2.125, 2.531, 2.74, 3.251, 3.646, 3.855, 4.83, 5.41, 5.654, 6.478, 7.349, 8.406, 9.242, 9.706, 10.066, 10.426, 10.983, 11.308, 11.424, 11.912, 12.283, 12.829, 13.642, 15.186]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(630, 5, 'Page 8', 'Mimo opened a small hologram of his own planet. It had two suns and a purple sky. Two different worlds. Two different beings. But the same curiosity.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Arda\", \"showed\", \"Mimo\", \"the\", \"garden.\", \"He\", \"touched\", \"the\", \"grass,\", \"pointed\", \"to\", \"the\", \"sky,\", \"and\", \"tried\", \"to\", \"explain\", \"what\", \"Earth\", \"was\", \"like.\", \"[cite:\", \"140]\", \"Mimo\", \"opened\", \"a\", \"small\", \"hologram\", \"of\", \"his\", \"own\", \"planet.\", \"It\", \"had\", \"two\", \"suns\", \"and\", \"a\", \"purple\", \"sky.\", \"[cite:\", \"141]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.708, 0.998, 1.103, 2.02, 2.183, 2.461, 2.566, 3.216, 3.564, 3.669, 3.773, 4.214, 4.377, 4.609, 4.725, 5.132, 5.317, 5.538, 5.7, 6.339, 7.14, 8.336, 8.696, 8.975, 9.044, 9.369, 9.903, 9.996, 10.124, 10.286, 11.064, 11.227, 11.378, 11.622, 12.074, 12.26, 12.33, 12.655, 13.317, 14.199], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.673, 0.94, 1.068, 1.579, 2.125, 2.438, 2.531, 3.088, 3.529, 3.611, 3.738, 4.18, 4.342, 4.586, 4.656, 5.074, 5.271, 5.503, 5.642, 6.06, 7.012, 7.895, 8.626, 8.951, 8.998, 9.311, 9.857, 9.95, 10.077, 10.24, 10.786, 11.18, 11.343, 11.54, 12.016, 12.214, 12.283, 12.62, 13.166, 13.99, 15.093]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(631, 5, 'Page 9', 'After a while, a soft signal came from Mimo’s ship. It was time to return. Mimo paused. He looked at the sky, then at Arda. This time, the device glowed blue and green together—calm and happiness.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Two\", \"different\", \"worlds.\", \"Two\", \"different\", \"beings.\", \"But\", \"the\", \"same\", \"curiosity.\", \"[cite:\", \"142-144]\", \"After\", \"a\", \"while,\", \"a\", \"soft\", \"signal\", \"came\", \"from\", \"Mimo\'s\", \"ship.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"time\", \"to\", \"return.\", \"[cite:\", \"145]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.464, 0.824, 1.358, 1.625, 1.962, 2.694, 2.902, 3.053, 3.448, 5.039, 5.991, 9.102, 9.451, 9.52, 9.927, 10.077, 10.461, 10.867, 11.169, 11.366, 11.773, 12.434, 12.597, 12.748, 13.026, 13.154, 14.675, 15.267], \"end_times\": [0.383, 0.789, 1.277, 1.556, 1.927, 2.485, 2.868, 2.972, 3.39, 4.342, 5.747, 8.15, 9.404, 9.474, 9.903, 9.961, 10.391, 10.797, 11.122, 11.308, 11.749, 12.225, 12.562, 12.69, 12.992, 13.084, 13.723, 15.209, 16.858]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(632, 5, 'Page 10', 'Arda placed his hand over his heart. Mimo did the same. As the ship rose, it left a blue trail behind. It became a small point of light in the sky and disappeared.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Mimo\", \"paused.\", \"He\", \"looked\", \"at\", \"the\", \"sky,\", \"then\", \"at\", \"Arda.\", \"[cite:\", \"146]\", \"This\", \"time,\", \"the\", \"device\", \"glowed\", \"blue\", \"and\", \"green\", \"togetheru2014calm\", \"and\", \"happiness.\", \"[cite:\", \"147]\", \"Arda\", \"placed\", \"his\", \"hand\", \"over\", \"his\", \"heart.\", \"Mimo\", \"did\", \"the\", \"same.\", \"[cite:\", \"148]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.511, 1.358, 1.521, 1.753, 1.846, 1.95, 2.519, 2.728, 2.844, 3.843, 4.481, 5.863, 6.142, 6.455, 6.571, 6.978, 7.349, 7.709, 7.883, 8.185, 9.625, 9.845, 10.82, 11.378, 12.864, 13.212, 13.537, 13.7, 14.071, 14.373, 14.547, 15.116, 15.464, 15.615, 15.732, 16.684, 17.299], \"end_times\": [0.43, 1.149, 1.463, 1.73, 1.811, 1.916, 2.461, 2.682, 2.786, 3.402, 4.423, 5.48, 6.084, 6.432, 6.525, 6.931, 7.291, 7.651, 7.814, 8.127, 9.543, 9.764, 10.612, 11.32, 12.585, 13.154, 13.502, 13.642, 13.99, 14.292, 14.478, 14.942, 15.395, 15.581, 15.685, 16.173, 17.241, 18.53]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(633, 5, 'Page 11', 'That night, as Arda looked at the stars, he knew that space was not cold. It was vast and unknown, but it also held friendship. Sometimes, even someone from the farthest planet is not a stranger, if they can speak to your heart. And maybe somewhere under a purple sky, Mimo was looking back at Earth too.', 11, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_5_page_11.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"ship\", \"rose,\", \"it\", \"became\", \"a\", \"small\", \"point\", \"of\", \"light\", \"in\", \"the\", \"sky\", \"and\", \"disappeared.\", \"[cite:\", \"149-150]\", \"That\", \"night,\", \"Arda\", \"knew\", \"that\", \"space\", \"was\", \"not\", \"cold.\", \"[cite:\", \"151]\", \"It\", \"was\", \"vast,\", \"but\", \"it\", \"also\", \"held\", \"friendship.\", \"[cite:\", \"152]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.36, 0.476, 0.755, 1.242, 1.393, 1.683, 1.753, 2.101, 2.322, 2.438, 2.647, 2.74, 2.844, 3.367, 3.587, 4.83, 5.793, 7.767, 8.057, 8.591, 8.94, 9.149, 9.323, 9.683, 9.857, 10.077, 10.902, 11.831, 12.899, 13.061, 13.235, 13.932, 14.129, 14.234, 14.536, 14.756, 15.546, 16.475], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.43, 0.673, 1.207, 1.358, 1.66, 1.707, 2.043, 2.287, 2.368, 2.624, 2.705, 2.81, 3.216, 3.541, 4.319, 5.619, 7.442, 7.988, 8.475, 8.882, 9.102, 9.276, 9.648, 9.799, 10.008, 10.577, 11.656, 12.725, 13.026, 13.166, 13.839, 14.083, 14.187, 14.466, 14.71, 15.372, 16.324, 17.508]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(634, 6, 'Page 1', 'Deep in space, a small exploration ship drifted among the stars. Inside was Arin, one of humanity’s most curious children. Arin wanted to see planets and understand what the universe was truly like with his own eyes.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Deep\", \"in\", \"space,\", \"a\", \"small\", \"exploration\", \"ship\", \"drifted\", \"among\", \"the\", \"stars.\", \"Inside\", \"was\", \"Arin,\", \"one\", \"of\", \"humanity\'s\", \"most\", \"curious\", \"children.\", \"[cite:\", \"156]\", \"Arin\", \"wanted\", \"to\", \"see\", \"planets\", \"and\", \"understand\", \"what\", \"the\", \"universe\", \"was\", \"truly\", \"like.\", \"[cite:\", \"157]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.43, 0.569, 0.998, 1.091, 1.474, 2.171, 2.426, 2.798, 3.042, 3.146, 4.226, 4.737, 4.923, 5.457, 5.642, 5.747, 6.293, 6.525, 7.001, 7.814, 8.673, 9.834, 10.182, 10.472, 10.565, 10.786, 11.308, 11.459, 12.028, 12.179, 12.318, 12.759, 12.957, 13.433, 14.257, 14.93], \"end_times\": [0.372, 0.499, 0.975, 1.033, 1.405, 2.113, 2.38, 2.763, 2.995, 3.111, 3.843, 4.702, 4.841, 5.375, 5.608, 5.689, 6.246, 6.467, 6.954, 7.605, 8.499, 9.659, 10.124, 10.437, 10.519, 10.728, 11.262, 11.401, 11.97, 12.144, 12.249, 12.736, 12.887, 13.351, 13.874, 14.872, 16.3]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(635, 6, 'Page 2', 'As the ship left Earth, the blue planet slowly grew smaller, turning into a bright sphere in the dark void. Space was not as frightening as Arin had imagined. It was silent, but the silence felt peaceful.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"ship\", \"left\", \"Earth,\", \"the\", \"blue\", \"planet\", \"slowly\", \"grew\", \"smaller,\", \"turning\", \"into\", \"a\", \"bright\", \"sphere\", \"in\", \"the\", \"dark\", \"void.\", \"[cite:\", \"158]\", \"Space\", \"was\", \"not\", \"as\", \"frightening\", \"as\", \"Arin\", \"had\", \"imagined.\", \"It\", \"was\", \"silent,\", \"but\", \"peaceful.\", \"[cite:\", \"159]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.453, 0.72, 0.998, 1.579, 1.73, 1.95, 2.334, 2.717, 2.937, 3.878, 4.249, 4.481, 4.563, 4.899, 5.306, 5.422, 5.538, 5.851, 7.314, 7.976, 9.601, 9.961, 10.147, 10.321, 10.449, 10.89, 11.041, 11.331, 11.482, 12.411, 12.562, 12.725, 13.189, 13.351, 14.594, 15.36], \"end_times\": [0.279, 0.406, 0.65, 0.929, 1.428, 1.683, 1.927, 2.276, 2.67, 2.891, 3.553, 4.203, 4.4, 4.505, 4.83, 5.259, 5.375, 5.492, 5.782, 6.362, 7.86, 9.276, 9.927, 10.077, 10.286, 10.391, 10.844, 10.96, 11.285, 11.436, 12.132, 12.527, 12.666, 13.166, 13.305, 13.99, 15.209, 16.672]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(636, 6, 'Page 3', 'On the third day of the journey, an unusual image appeared on the ship’s screens. A softly glowing stream of energy flowed between the stars. It was a rare river of light, formed by space dust and tiny particles drawn together by an unseen force.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"On\", \"the\", \"third\", \"day\", \"of\", \"the\", \"journey,\", \"an\", \"unusual\", \"image\", \"appeared\", \"on\", \"the\", \"ship\'s\", \"screens.\", \"[cite:\", \"160]\", \"A\", \"softly\", \"glowing\", \"stream\", \"of\", \"energy\", \"flowed\", \"between\", \"the\", \"stars.\", \"[cite:\", \"161]\", \"It\", \"was\", \"a\", \"rare\", \"river\", \"of\", \"light,\", \"formed\", \"by\", \"space\", \"dust\", \"and\", \"tiny\", \"particles.\", \"[cite:\", \"162]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.43, 0.72, 0.906, 1.01, 1.138, 1.753, 1.962, 2.519, 2.821, 3.239, 3.355, 3.471, 3.796, 4.911, 5.909, 7.291, 7.488, 8.046, 8.452, 8.8, 8.951, 9.59, 10.066, 10.449, 10.553, 11.691, 12.806, 14.234, 14.396, 14.571, 14.687, 15.023, 15.36, 15.523, 16.208, 16.579, 16.776, 17.206, 17.554, 17.694, 18.088, 19.307, 20.271], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.372, 0.673, 0.859, 0.964, 1.08, 1.66, 1.892, 2.438, 2.798, 3.193, 3.309, 3.425, 3.762, 4.528, 5.666, 6.85, 7.372, 7.988, 8.382, 8.754, 8.87, 9.416, 10.008, 10.403, 10.519, 11.25, 12.423, 13.955, 14.362, 14.512, 14.605, 14.965, 15.29, 15.43, 15.999, 16.521, 16.695, 17.16, 17.496, 17.647, 18.019, 18.866, 20.062, 21.595]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(637, 6, 'Page 4', 'As Arin approached the light river, the ship filled with golden color. When the particles collided, they created small sparks that lit up the darkness. The sight reminded Arin of something: the universe was not made of lonely shining stars, but of millions of tiny pieces moving together.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"Arin\", \"approached\", \"the\", \"light\", \"river,\", \"the\", \"ship\", \"filled\", \"with\", \"golden\", \"color.\", \"[cite:\", \"163]\", \"When\", \"the\", \"particles\", \"collided,\", \"they\", \"created\", \"small\", \"sparks\", \"that\", \"lit\", \"up\", \"the\", \"darkness.\", \"[cite:\", \"164]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.557, 0.987, 1.115, 1.347, 1.985, 2.148, 2.45, 2.844, 3.03, 3.402, 4.563, 5.584, 7.546, 7.744, 7.848, 8.348, 9.253, 9.451, 9.857, 10.205, 10.658, 10.844, 11.018, 11.146, 11.262, 12.481, 13.41], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.522, 0.952, 1.057, 1.3, 1.811, 2.09, 2.368, 2.81, 2.972, 3.344, 3.866, 5.306, 6.594, 7.721, 7.814, 8.29, 9.044, 9.404, 9.799, 10.136, 10.612, 10.786, 10.971, 11.099, 11.215, 11.97, 13.166, 14.629]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(638, 6, 'Page 5', 'The ship slowly passed through the stream. The particles swirled around it, then continued on their way. None of them were strong alone, but together, they could light up the sky.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"sight\", \"reminded\", \"Arin\", \"of\", \"something:\", \"the\", \"universe\", \"was\", \"not\", \"made\", \"of\", \"lonely\", \"shining\", \"stars,\", \"but\", \"of\", \"millions\", \"of\", \"tiny\", \"pieces\", \"moving\", \"together.\", \"[cite:\", \"165]\", \"The\", \"ship\", \"slowly\", \"passed\", \"through\", \"the\", \"stream.\", \"[cite:\", \"166]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.569, 1.045, 1.312, 1.428, 2.183, 2.392, 2.868, 3.065, 3.297, 3.518, 3.646, 3.994, 4.4, 5.213, 5.41, 5.561, 6.118, 6.258, 6.629, 7.14, 7.5, 8.638, 9.485, 10.809, 10.983, 11.25, 11.68, 11.993, 12.26, 12.376, 12.968, 13.862], \"end_times\": [0.232, 0.522, 0.987, 1.265, 1.37, 2.009, 2.299, 2.833, 2.995, 3.251, 3.483, 3.564, 3.936, 4.331, 5.004, 5.375, 5.468, 6.06, 6.188, 6.571, 7.059, 7.43, 8.127, 9.311, 10.484, 10.925, 11.192, 11.622, 11.958, 12.225, 12.33, 12.934, 13.688, 15.186]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(639, 6, 'Page 6', 'As the journey continued, Arin thought about the vastness of the universe. Planets, moons, asteroids, and stars all moved within an invisible order. When this order was disturbed, darkness grew. When balance returned, light became stronger.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"The\", \"particles\", \"swirled\", \"around\", \"it,\", \"then\", \"continued\", \"on\", \"their\", \"way.\", \"[cite:\", \"166]\", \"None\", \"of\", \"them\", \"were\", \"strong\", \"alone,\", \"but\", \"together,\", \"they\", \"could\", \"light\", \"up\", \"the\", \"sky.\", \"[cite:\", \"167]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.313, 0.824, 1.254, 1.625, 1.892, 2.09, 2.612, 2.717, 2.926, 3.913, 4.458, 6.246, 6.478, 6.571, 6.722, 6.896, 7.245, 7.837, 8.034, 8.603, 8.777, 8.963, 9.172, 9.311, 9.427, 10.101, 10.693], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.766, 1.219, 1.556, 1.823, 2.043, 2.566, 2.682, 2.868, 3.309, 4.435, 5.921, 6.444, 6.525, 6.687, 6.85, 7.187, 7.755, 7.999, 8.557, 8.742, 8.916, 9.137, 9.265, 9.381, 9.95, 10.635, 12.074]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(640, 6, 'Page 7', 'Eventually, the ship moved away from the light river. The glowing stream continued its path through the darkness. Space grew quiet again, but the silence now felt different to Arin.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"journey\", \"continued,\", \"Arin\", \"thought\", \"about\", \"the\", \"vastness\", \"of\", \"the\", \"universe.\", \"[cite:\", \"168]\", \"Planets,\", \"moons,\", \"asteroids,\", \"and\", \"stars\", \"all\", \"moved\", \"within\", \"an\", \"invisible\", \"order.\", \"[cite:\", \"169]\", \"When\", \"balance\", \"returned,\", \"light\", \"became\", \"stronger.\", \"[cite:\", \"170]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.464, 0.778, 1.672, 2.009, 2.264, 2.519, 2.647, 3.239, 3.344, 3.495, 4.656, 5.399, 6.641, 7.396, 7.976, 8.684, 8.882, 9.392, 9.706, 10.066, 10.414, 10.542, 11.064, 11.784, 12.527, 13.688, 13.909, 14.28, 15.012, 15.279, 15.627, 16.637, 17.392], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.406, 0.72, 1.498, 1.962, 2.229, 2.473, 2.589, 3.204, 3.297, 3.413, 4.145, 5.248, 6.467, 7.303, 7.918, 8.649, 8.812, 9.323, 9.625, 10.019, 10.356, 10.484, 11.018, 11.54, 12.353, 13.537, 13.862, 14.245, 14.861, 15.232, 15.592, 16.312, 17.218, 18.39]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(641, 6, 'Page 8', 'He understood that the universe was not an empty void. It was a living system shaped by the harmony of countless small parts. Even the smallest light, when shining in the right place, could change the darkness.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Space\", \"grew\", \"quiet\", \"again,\", \"but\", \"the\", \"silence\", \"now\", \"felt\", \"different\", \"to\", \"Arin.\", \"[cite:\", \"172]\", \"He\", \"understood\", \"that\", \"the\", \"universe\", \"was\", \"not\", \"an\", \"empty\", \"void.\", \"[cite:\", \"173]\", \"It\", \"was\", \"a\", \"living\", \"system\", \"shaped\", \"by\", \"the\", \"harmony\", \"of\", \"countless\", \"small\", \"parts.\", \"[cite:\", \"174]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.488, 0.697, 1.08, 1.718, 1.904, 2.02, 2.496, 2.694, 2.926, 3.309, 3.46, 4.145, 4.957, 6.803, 6.978, 7.535, 7.709, 7.86, 8.359, 8.568, 8.928, 9.067, 9.381, 10.205, 11.006, 12.318, 12.469, 12.62, 12.701, 13.015, 13.56, 13.967, 14.118, 14.257, 14.733, 14.896, 15.337, 15.627, 16.602, 17.45], \"end_times\": [0.464, 0.65, 1.045, 1.509, 1.869, 1.974, 2.45, 2.624, 2.879, 3.274, 3.379, 3.971, 4.841, 6.107, 6.908, 7.477, 7.674, 7.779, 8.313, 8.487, 8.858, 9.009, 9.323, 9.88, 10.832, 12.144, 12.434, 12.574, 12.643, 12.945, 13.433, 13.92, 14.071, 14.187, 14.652, 14.814, 15.302, 15.569, 16.219, 17.276, 18.622]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(642, 6, 'Page 9', 'When the ship began its return to Earth, Arin was no longer just a passenger. He was an explorer who had witnessed the universe’s balance. When he looked at the stars, he no longer saw just points of light, but a shining whole.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Even\", \"the\", \"smallest\", \"light,\", \"when\", \"shining\", \"in\", \"the\", \"right\", \"place,\", \"could\", \"change\", \"the\", \"darkness.\", \"[cite:\", \"175]\", \"When\", \"the\", \"ship\", \"began\", \"its\", \"return\", \"to\", \"Earth,\", \"Arin\", \"was\", \"no\", \"longer\", \"just\", \"a\", \"passenger.\", \"[cite:\", \"176]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.569, 1.068, 1.358, 1.567, 1.939, 2.02, 2.136, 2.368, 3.251, 3.483, 3.831, 3.947, 4.714, 5.526, 7.117, 7.314, 7.419, 7.674, 7.999, 8.162, 8.522, 8.661, 9.276, 9.613, 9.799, 9.985, 10.344, 10.577, 10.646, 11.726, 12.597], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.511, 0.998, 1.335, 1.509, 1.904, 1.985, 2.09, 2.322, 2.926, 3.448, 3.785, 3.901, 4.598, 5.352, 6.606, 7.279, 7.384, 7.616, 7.941, 8.104, 8.464, 8.58, 9.067, 9.555, 9.718, 9.903, 10.275, 10.542, 10.6, 11.343, 12.353, 14.164]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(643, 6, 'Page 10', 'And every light drifting through space reminded him of this truth: greatness is often born from small pieces coming together.', 10, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_6_page_10.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"He\", \"was\", \"an\", \"explorer\", \"who\", \"had\", \"witnessed\", \"the\", \"universe\'s\", \"balance.\", \"[cite:\", \"177]\", \"When\", \"he\", \"looked\", \"at\", \"the\", \"stars,\", \"he\", \"no\", \"longer\", \"saw\", \"just\", \"points\", \"of\", \"light,\", \"but\", \"a\", \"shining\", \"whole.\", \"[cite:\", \"178]\", \"Greatness\", \"is\", \"often\", \"born\", \"from\", \"small\", \"pieces\", \"coming\", \"together.\", \"[cite:\", \"179]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.302, 0.453, 0.557, 1.207, 1.347, 1.486, 1.892, 2.032, 2.531, 3.646, 4.632, 6.223, 6.409, 6.49, 6.722, 6.815, 6.92, 7.523, 7.686, 7.872, 8.208, 8.464, 8.731, 9.033, 9.16, 9.845, 10.043, 10.124, 10.553, 11.575, 12.457, 13.932, 14.408, 14.547, 14.826, 15.128, 15.348, 15.65, 16.068, 16.347, 17.136, 18.123], \"end_times\": [0.255, 0.406, 0.511, 1.149, 1.312, 1.44, 1.869, 1.962, 2.473, 3.204, 4.423, 5.944, 6.374, 6.455, 6.699, 6.78, 6.885, 7.465, 7.605, 7.79, 8.139, 8.394, 8.661, 8.986, 9.079, 9.636, 10.008, 10.066, 10.507, 11.064, 12.307, 13.723, 14.362, 14.478, 14.779, 15.07, 15.279, 15.592, 16.01, 16.3, 16.927, 17.949, 19.551]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(644, 7, 'Page 1', 'Deep within the Solar System, between Mars and Jupiter, stretched a vast asteroid belt. It was made of thousands of rock pieces of different sizes. Some were as small as a house, others as large as mountains. All of them moved along their orbits in the silence of space.', 1, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_1.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Deep\", \"within\", \"the\", \"Solar\", \"System,\", \"between\", \"Mars\", \"and\", \"Jupiter,\", \"stretched\", \"a\", \"vast\", \"asteroid\", \"belt.\", \"[cite:\", \"181]\", \"It\", \"was\", \"made\", \"of\", \"thousands\", \"of\", \"rock\", \"pieces\", \"of\", \"different\", \"sizes.\", \"[cite:\", \"182]\", \"Some\", \"were\", \"as\", \"small\", \"as\", \"a\", \"house,\", \"others\", \"as\", \"large\", \"as\", \"mountains.\", \"[cite:\", \"183]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.453, 0.72, 0.836, 1.173, 1.788, 2.218, 2.589, 2.728, 3.553, 3.947, 4.04, 4.481, 5.074, 6.211, 7.105, 8.336, 8.475, 8.649, 8.882, 9.009, 9.532, 9.683, 9.95, 10.356, 10.472, 10.844, 11.912, 12.968, 14.234, 14.489, 14.663, 14.779, 15.139, 15.267, 15.36, 16.184, 16.579, 16.742, 17.078, 17.252, 18.425, 19.331], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.673, 0.789, 1.115, 1.695, 2.159, 2.531, 2.67, 3.344, 3.913, 3.971, 4.389, 5.027, 5.515, 6.931, 8.092, 8.44, 8.58, 8.847, 8.94, 9.497, 9.59, 9.892, 10.31, 10.414, 10.797, 11.529, 12.643, 13.909, 14.466, 14.629, 14.733, 15.081, 15.209, 15.29, 15.906, 16.521, 16.66, 17.055, 17.16, 17.914, 19.156, 20.712]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33');
INSERT INTO `story_sections` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `content`, `page_number`, `elevenlabs_audio_url`, `elevenlabs_voice_id`, `audio_duration`, `word_timestamps`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(645, 7, 'Page 2', 'Kaan had loved spacecraft since childhood. One day, he had the chance to join an exploration mission. His task was to pass through the asteroid belt and create a new route map.', 2, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_2.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"All\", \"of\", \"them\", \"moved\", \"along\", \"their\", \"orbits\", \"in\", \"the\", \"silence\", \"of\", \"space.\", \"[cite:\", \"184]\", \"Kaan\", \"had\", \"loved\", \"spacecraft\", \"since\", \"childhood.\", \"[cite:\", \"185]\", \"One\", \"day,\", \"he\", \"had\", \"the\", \"chance\", \"to\", \"join\", \"an\", \"exploration\", \"mission\", \"to\", \"map\", \"the\", \"asteroid\", \"belt.\", \"[cite:\", \"186]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.43, 0.604, 0.882, 1.126, 1.3, 1.637, 1.73, 1.834, 2.264, 2.368, 2.995, 3.785, 4.934, 5.364, 5.55, 5.863, 6.502, 6.757, 7.535, 8.359, 9.509, 9.752, 10.344, 10.461, 10.6, 10.716, 11.064, 11.227, 11.529, 11.668, 12.365, 12.701, 12.829, 13.073, 13.201, 13.688, 14.211, 15.012], \"end_times\": [0.29, 0.383, 0.546, 0.848, 1.091, 1.254, 1.602, 1.695, 1.8, 2.241, 2.322, 2.902, 3.669, 4.609, 5.294, 5.48, 5.805, 6.467, 6.722, 7.407, 8.231, 9.125, 9.718, 10.136, 10.414, 10.565, 10.67, 11.029, 11.146, 11.471, 11.598, 12.318, 12.643, 12.771, 13.015, 13.142, 13.642, 14.094, 14.919, 16.068]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(646, 7, 'Page 3', 'As the spacecraft approached the belt, the view changed. What once seemed like empty space became a busy region. Large rocks drifted slowly, while smaller ones moved between them. Each traveled at a different speed, yet within an unseen order.', 3, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_3.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"As\", \"the\", \"spacecraft\", \"approached\", \"the\", \"belt,\", \"the\", \"view\", \"changed.\", \"What\", \"once\", \"seemed\", \"like\", \"empty\", \"space\", \"became\", \"a\", \"busy\", \"region.\", \"[cite:\", \"187]\", \"Large\", \"rocks\", \"drifted\", \"slowly,\", \"while\", \"smaller\", \"ones\", \"moved\", \"between\", \"them.\", \"[cite:\", \"188]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.325, 0.441, 1.033, 1.44, 1.556, 1.95, 2.101, 2.334, 3.216, 3.495, 3.796, 4.122, 4.342, 4.679, 5.108, 5.457, 5.526, 5.84, 6.618, 7.14, 8.882, 9.242, 9.648, 10.043, 10.565, 10.832, 11.262, 11.54, 11.854, 12.249, 12.91, 13.468], \"end_times\": [0.267, 0.395, 0.998, 1.405, 1.509, 1.916, 2.043, 2.276, 2.972, 3.425, 3.762, 4.087, 4.296, 4.621, 5.062, 5.422, 5.48, 5.759, 6.374, 7.105, 8.557, 9.183, 9.59, 9.996, 10.542, 10.797, 11.192, 11.471, 11.796, 12.202, 12.585, 13.433, 14.582]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(647, 7, 'Page 4', 'At first, Kaan thought the area was dangerous. The rocks looked chaotic. But the ship’s sensors showed that they were moving in balance. Each asteroid followed its own path, as if respecting the others.', 4, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_4.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Each\", \"traveled\", \"at\", \"a\", \"different\", \"speed,\", \"yet\", \"within\", \"an\", \"unseen\", \"order.\", \"[cite:\", \"189]\", \"At\", \"first,\", \"Kaan\", \"thought\", \"the\", \"area\", \"was\", \"dangerous.\", \"The\", \"rocks\", \"looked\", \"chaotic.\", \"[cite:\", \"190]\", \"But\", \"they\", \"were\", \"moving\", \"in\", \"balance.\", \"[cite:\", \"191]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.859, 0.975, 1.045, 1.382, 2.241, 2.461, 2.833, 2.972, 3.483, 4.493, 5.375, 6.978, 7.163, 7.512, 7.802, 8.057, 8.185, 8.487, 8.638, 9.671, 9.834, 10.159, 10.414, 11.436, 12.341, 13.677, 13.851, 13.99, 14.164, 14.524, 14.663, 15.836, 16.544], \"end_times\": [0.395, 0.824, 0.929, 0.998, 1.335, 1.997, 2.426, 2.763, 2.902, 3.413, 3.982, 5.132, 6.165, 7.105, 7.477, 7.755, 8.034, 8.127, 8.44, 8.591, 9.346, 9.776, 10.112, 10.368, 11.111, 12.098, 13.351, 13.827, 13.955, 14.118, 14.478, 14.594, 15.325, 16.428, 17.508]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(648, 7, 'Page 5', 'During the journey, a small asteroid began to drift slightly off course. If its direction changed further, it could collide with others. Kaan carefully adjusted the ship and used small guidance engines instead of powerful thrusters. A gentle touch was enough. The asteroid returned to its path.', 5, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_5.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"During\", \"the\", \"journey,\", \"a\", \"small\", \"asteroid\", \"began\", \"to\", \"drift\", \"slightly\", \"off\", \"course.\", \"[cite:\", \"193]\", \"If\", \"its\", \"direction\", \"changed\", \"further,\", \"it\", \"could\", \"collide\", \"with\", \"others.\", \"[cite:\", \"194]\", \"Kaan\", \"carefully\", \"adjusted\", \"the\", \"ship.\", \"[cite:\", \"195]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.441, 0.557, 1.115, 1.242, 1.556, 2.067, 2.345, 2.438, 2.728, 3.135, 3.332, 4.272, 5.352, 6.885, 7.059, 7.221, 7.686, 8.046, 8.661, 8.812, 8.986, 9.358, 9.52, 10.693, 11.552, 13.026, 13.351, 13.769, 14.187, 14.292, 15.418, 16.509], \"end_times\": [0.406, 0.511, 1.057, 1.173, 1.498, 2.02, 2.299, 2.392, 2.682, 3.077, 3.274, 3.889, 4.969, 6.502, 7.012, 7.187, 7.628, 7.988, 8.545, 8.777, 8.951, 9.334, 9.474, 10.089, 11.308, 12.643, 13.293, 13.735, 14.153, 14.257, 14.721, 16.068, 17.786]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(649, 7, 'Page 6', 'That moment taught Kaan something important. In space, big problems are not always solved with big actions. Sometimes, a small and precise move is enough to protect balance.', 6, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_6.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"A\", \"gentle\", \"touch\", \"was\", \"enough.\", \"The\", \"asteroid\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"its\", \"path.\", \"[cite:\", \"196]\", \"That\", \"moment\", \"taught\", \"Kaan\", \"something\", \"important:\", \"in\", \"space,\", \"big\", \"problems\", \"are\", \"not\", \"always\", \"solved\", \"with\", \"big\", \"actions.\", \"[cite:\", \"197]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.279, 0.639, 0.929, 1.103, 2.043, 2.229, 2.763, 3.297, 3.483, 3.646, 4.505, 5.979, 7.93, 8.22, 8.591, 8.87, 9.265, 9.613, 10.971, 11.169, 11.749, 12.04, 12.597, 12.771, 13.015, 13.386, 13.862, 14.071, 14.292, 15.581, 16.904], \"end_times\": [0.197, 0.592, 0.882, 1.045, 1.602, 2.159, 2.694, 3.228, 3.402, 3.599, 4.18, 5.283, 7.326, 8.15, 8.545, 8.824, 9.195, 9.567, 10.275, 11.099, 11.68, 11.97, 12.55, 12.725, 12.957, 13.34, 13.816, 14.013, 14.234, 15.07, 16.3, 18.158]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(650, 7, 'Page 7', 'After passing through the asteroid belt, the vast sea of rocks lay behind them. Space grew calm again. But for Kaan, asteroids were no longer just rocks. They were part of a system that seemed chaotic but held order within.', 7, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_7.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Sometimes,\", \"a\", \"small\", \"and\", \"precise\", \"move\", \"is\", \"enough\", \"to\", \"protect\", \"balance.\", \"[cite:\", \"198]\", \"After\", \"passing\", \"through\", \"the\", \"asteroid\", \"belt,\", \"space\", \"grew\", \"calm\", \"again.\", \"[cite:\", \"199]\", \"Kaan\", \"saw\", \"that\", \"asteroids\", \"were\", \"part\", \"of\", \"a\", \"system\", \"with\", \"order\", \"within.\", \"[cite:\", \"200]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.801, 0.94, 1.37, 1.521, 2.043, 2.345, 2.496, 2.786, 2.914, 3.309, 4.087, 4.992, 6.385, 6.687, 7.036, 7.256, 7.384, 7.883, 8.429, 8.789, 9.009, 9.288, 9.973, 10.937, 12.156, 12.643, 12.992, 13.177, 13.7, 13.862, 14.129, 14.234, 14.315, 14.733, 14.93, 15.232, 16.033, 16.962], \"end_times\": [0.766, 0.848, 1.3, 1.451, 1.985, 2.31, 2.438, 2.752, 2.844, 3.251, 3.913, 4.714, 5.875, 6.629, 7.001, 7.233, 7.326, 7.825, 8.255, 8.754, 8.963, 9.242, 9.729, 10.612, 11.947, 12.562, 12.922, 13.119, 13.665, 13.827, 14.083, 14.187, 14.257, 14.687, 14.872, 15.174, 15.79, 16.684, 17.926]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(651, 7, 'Page 8', 'When he returned to Earth and looked at the sky, he realized that space was more balanced than he had imagined. Many things that appear chaotic from afar move in harmony when seen closely. Space was infinite. Yet even within this infinity, everything had a path, a speed, and a balance.', 8, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_8.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"When\", \"he\", \"returned\", \"to\", \"Earth,\", \"he\", \"realized\", \"space\", \"was\", \"more\", \"balanced\", \"than\", \"he\", \"had\", \"imagined.\", \"[cite:\", \"201]\", \"Many\", \"things\", \"that\", \"appear\", \"chaotic\", \"from\", \"afar\", \"move\", \"in\", \"harmony\", \"when\", \"seen\", \"closely.\", \"[cite:\", \"202]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.337, 0.476, 0.836, 0.952, 1.428, 1.591, 2.02, 2.392, 2.577, 2.798, 3.286, 3.495, 3.622, 3.796, 5.422, 6.269, 7.86, 8.15, 8.44, 8.591, 8.928, 9.451, 9.648, 10.089, 10.333, 10.472, 10.879, 11.111, 11.413, 12.608, 13.317], \"end_times\": [0.302, 0.395, 0.813, 0.882, 1.312, 1.521, 1.985, 2.357, 2.508, 2.74, 3.251, 3.437, 3.553, 3.75, 4.47, 6.06, 7.047, 8.092, 8.406, 8.557, 8.87, 9.404, 9.59, 9.996, 10.298, 10.391, 10.82, 11.041, 11.343, 12.098, 13.189, 14.443]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33'),
(652, 7, 'Page 9', 'And sometimes, the greatest discovery is noticing the hidden order within chaos.', 9, 'https://lingola-stories-kids.b-cdn.net/audio/story_7_page_9.mp3', NULL, NULL, '{\"words\": [\"Space\", \"was\", \"infinite.\", \"Yet\", \"even\", \"within\", \"this\", \"infinity,\", \"everything\", \"had\", \"a\", \"path,\", \"a\", \"speed,\", \"and\", \"a\", \"balance.\", \"[cite:\", \"203]\", \"Sometimes,\", \"the\", \"greatest\", \"discovery\", \"is\", \"noticing\", \"the\", \"hidden\", \"order\", \"within\", \"chaos.\", \"[cite:\", \"204]\"], \"start_times\": [0, 0.546, 0.743, 1.765, 2.009, 2.322, 2.682, 2.868, 3.831, 4.284, 4.447, 4.528, 5.352, 5.503, 6.142, 6.374, 6.444, 8.185, 10.136, 11.819, 12.446, 12.562, 12.922, 13.526, 13.711, 14.164, 14.292, 14.629, 14.907, 15.197, 16.509, 17.403], \"end_times\": [0.511, 0.673, 1.324, 1.95, 2.264, 2.624, 2.81, 3.506, 4.226, 4.412, 4.481, 5.108, 5.422, 6.049, 6.316, 6.397, 7.07, 9.021, 11.436, 12.411, 12.516, 12.875, 13.444, 13.63, 14.118, 14.234, 14.571, 14.861, 15.139, 15.906, 17.194, 18.344]}', '2026-03-06 12:40:00', '2026-03-06 13:33:33');
